20190318066:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
int a,b,c;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else{
		double x1,x2;
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	
}
 return 0;
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%4 == 0)
    {
        if( year%100 == 0)
        {
            if ( year%400 == 0)
                printf("L");
            else
                printf("N");
        }
        else
            printf("L");
    }
    else
        printf("N");
    return 0;
}

{

	n=a%4;
	m=a%100;
	x=a%400;

		printf("L");
	}

main()
{

 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  d=a,a=b,b=d;  
 } 
 if(a>c)
 {
  d=a,a=c,c=d; 
 }
 if(b>c)
 {
 d=c,c=b,b=d; 
 }
 printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);

20190301048:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char aa,bb,cc,dd;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&aa,&bb,&cc);
	if(aa>bb) {dd=aa;aa=bb;bb=dd;
	}
	if(aa>cc) {dd=aa;aa=cc;cc=dd;
	}
	if(bb>cc) {dd=cc;cc=bb;bb=dd;
	}
	    printf("%c%c%c",aa,bb,cc);
    return 0; 
}

20190301030:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int leap(int yy)// 输入年份，判断是否闰年，是则输出 整数 1 否 则输出 整数 0 
{
	if (yy%4==0)
	{
		if (yy%100==0)
		{
			if (yy%400==0)
				return 1;
			return 0;
		}
		return 1;
	}
	return 0;
}
main()
{
	int t,i,j,n,len;
	scanf("%d",&n);
	if (leap(n))
		printf("L\n");
	else
		printf("N\n");
}

/*输入一个字符，判断是否阿拉伯数字。 
若是则输出：YES 
否则输出:NO */
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a;
	int b;
	scanf("%c",&a);
	b=(int)a;
	if (b>=48&&b<=57){
		printf("YES\n");
	}
	else
	printf("NO\n");
 }

main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
	if(a>c){
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
	}
	if(b>c){
		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190318012:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,max,min,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>c)
	{
	max=a;
	min=c;}
	else
	{
		max=c;
		min=a;
	}
if(b>max)
	max=b;
	if(b<min)
	min=b;
	t=a+b+c-max-min;
	printf("%c%c%c",min,t,max);
	
	
	
}

20190301030:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int t,i,j,n,len;
	char str[4],c;
	gets(str);
	if (str[0] > str[1])
	{
		c = str[0];
		str[0] = str[1];
		str[1] = c;
	}
	if (str[1] > str[2])
	{
		c = str[1];
		str[1] = str[2];
		str[2] = c;
	}
	if (str[0] > str[1])
	{
		c = str[0];
		str[0] = str[1];
		str[1] = c;
	}
	printf("%s\n",str);
}

20190318066:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int n,m,x,y;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
n=(x-1)*30+(y-1);
m=(n+2)%7;
switch(m){
    case(1):
        printf("Monday");break;
    case(2):
    printf("Tuesday");break;
    case(3):
    printf("Wednesday");break;
    case(4):
    printf("Thursday");break;
    case(5):
    printf("Friday");break;
    case(6):
    printf("Saturday ");break;
    case(7):
    printf("Sunday");break;
    }
    return 0; 
}

20190318148:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	int d,e,f,t;
	d=(int)a;
	e=(int)b;
	f=(int)c;
	if(d<f)
	{t=d,d=e,e=t;
	}
	if(d<f){
		t=d,d=f,f=t;
	}
	if(e<f)
	{t=e,e=f,f=t;
	}
	a=(char)d;
	b=(char)e;
	c=(char)f;
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
}

#include <stdio.h>
 
int main()
{
    int year;
 
    
    scanf("%d",&year);
 
    if(year%4 == 0)
    {
        if( year%100 == 0)
        {
            
            if ( year%400 == 0)
                printf("L");
            else
                printf("N");
        }
        else
            printf("L");
    }
    else
        printf("N");
    
    return 0;
}

main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	int d,e,f,t;
	d=(int)a;
	e=(int)b;
	f=(int)c;
	if(d<e)
	{t=d,d=e,e=t;
	}
	if(d<f){
		t=d,d=f,f=t;
	}
	if(e<f)
	{t=e,e=f,f=t;
	}
	a=(char)d;
	b=(char)e;
	c=(char)f;
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
}

	b=a+b+c-m-n;

	c=m;

20190302035:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,m,n;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	m=a,n=b;
	else
	n=a,m=b;
	if(c>m) m=c;
	if(c<n) n=c;
	b=a+b+c-m-n;
	a=n;
	c=m;
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190301022:Problem1034:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a;
	int n=0;
	scanf("%c",&a);
    if(a=='0'||a=='1'||a=='2'||a=='3'||a=='4'||a=='5')
    {
    	n+=1;
	}
	if(a=='6'||a=='7'||a=='8'||a=='9')
	{
		n+=1;
	}
	if(n==0)printf("NO\n");
	else printf("YES\n");
	}
------------------------------------------------------
20190302009:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
 float a, b, c;
 double s, x1, x2;
 while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
 {
 s = b * b - 4 * a*c;
 if(s >= 0)
 {
  x1 = (-b + sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  x2 = (-b - sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
 }
 else if(s < 0)
 {
 printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
 }
 }
}

20190318066:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) { 
y--;
m+=12;
}
c= y/100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w+1){
    case(1):
        printf("Monday");break;
    case(2):
    printf("Tuesday");break;
    case(3):
    printf("Wednesday");break;
    case(4):
    printf("Thursday");break;
    case(5):
    printf("Friday");break;
    case(6):
    printf("Saturday ");break;
    case(7):
    printf("Sunday");break;
    }
    return 0; 
}

------------------------------------------------------
20190318136:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a, b, c, *i, *j, *k;
    i=&a, j=&b, k=&c;
   
    scanf("%c%c%c", i, j, k);
    if (*i<*j){
        if (*j<*k) printf("%c%c%c\n", *i, *j, *k);
        else{
            if (*i<*k) printf("%c%c%c\n", *i, *k, *j);
            else printf("%c%c%c\n", *k, *i, *j);
        }
    }
    else{
        if (*j>*k) printf("%c%c%c\n", *k, *j, *i);
        else{
            if (*i<*k) printf("%c%c%c\n", *j, *i, *k);
            else printf("%c%c%c\n", *j, *k, *i);
        }
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302025:Problem1059:正确
/*给年份year，判别该年份是否闰年。
一个年份如果是4的倍数但不是100的倍数，或这个年份是400的倍数，则这个年份为闰年。
根据是否闰年输出，是输出"L",否输出"N"*/
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if (year%100==0)
		if (year%400==0)
			printf("L\n");
		else 
			printf("N\n");
	else if (year%4==0)	
		 printf("L\n");
	     else
		 printf("N\n");
 }

20190318136:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
 
int main()
{
        float a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
      
        scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c);
        if(a!=0)
        {
                d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(x1<x2) 
                    printf("%0.2f %0.2f\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("%0.2f %0.2f\n",x1,x2);
        }
        return 0;
}

20190301026:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	//1.整倍数年
	//2.非跨世纪年 
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);

	if(!(year%400)){ 
	printf("L");
}else if(!(year%4) && year%100){
		printf("L");
}else printf("N");
	//得：优先级：！ >> % >> &&    
}

# include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char ch1,ch2,ch3,x;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&ch1,&ch2,&ch3);
	if(ch1>ch2)
	{
		x=ch2;
		ch2=ch1;
		ch1=x;
	}
	if(ch1>ch3)
	{
		x=ch3;
		ch3=ch1;
		ch1=x;
	}
	if(ch2>ch3)
	{
		x=ch3;
		ch3=ch2;
		ch2=x;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",ch1,ch2,ch3);
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
 
int main()
{
        float a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
      
        scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c);
        d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        if(a!=0&&d>=0)
        {
              
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(x1<x2) 
                    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
        if(a=0||d<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
        
        return 0;
}

20190318066:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
int a,b,c;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	if(b*b-4.0*a*c<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else{
		double x1,x2;
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/2.0*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/2.0*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	
}
 return 0;
}

{

	scanf("%d%d%d",&d,&e,&f);
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	m=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		n=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		if(e*e-4*a*c>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",m,n);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	double x,y,m,n;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d%d%d",&d,&e,&f);
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	m=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		n=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		if(e*e-4*a*c>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION");

#include"math.h"

	b=year%100;
	c=year%400;

		printf("L");

20190301030:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
double a,b,c;
int root()
{
	double detal = b * b - 4 * a * c,x1,x2;
	if (detal < 0)
	{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");return 0;}
	x1 = (- b + sqrt(detal)) / (2 * a);
	x2 = (- b - sqrt(detal)) / (2 * a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	return 0;
}
main()
{
	int t,i,j;
	char str[15];
	while (gets(str))
	{
		if (strcmp(str,"") == 0)
			break;
		sscanf(str,"%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
		root();
	}
}

20190318066:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
    d=pow(b,2)-4*a*c;
    if (d>=0)
    {
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a),
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        if (x1>=x2)
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        else
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
    }
    else
      	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}

20190302025:Problem1069:正确
/*输入三个字母，按字母表顺序输出这三个字母。*/
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	a=(int)a;
	b=(int)b;
	c=(int)c;
	if (a>b&&b>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)c,(char)b,(char)a);
	}
	if (a>c&&c>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)b,(char)c,(char)a);
	}
	if (b>a&&a>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)c,(char)a,(char)b);
	}
	if (c>a&&a>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)b,(char)a,(char)c);
	}
	if (c>b&&b>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)a,(char)b,(char)c);
	}
	if (b>c&&c>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)a,(char)c,(char)b);
	}	
 }

20190318012:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	double x,y,m,n;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	m=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		n=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/2*d;
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		if(e*e-4*d*f>=0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",m,n);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	
	
	
	
}

main(){
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		d=a;
		a=b;
		b=d;
	}
	if(a>c){
		d=a;
		a=c;
		c=d;
	}
	if(b>c){
		d=c;
		c=b;
		b=d;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

20190301026:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main(){
	//用指针变量 来解决 顺序问题
	//输入字母 例如：cba   按ascii顺序输出 abc
	char a,b,c,*Fir=&a,*Sec=&b,*Thi=&c;
	char *Rep;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(*Fir>*Sec) Rep=Fir,Fir=Sec,Sec=Rep;
	if(*Sec>*Thi) Rep=Sec,Sec=Thi,Thi=Rep;
	if(*Fir>*Sec) Rep=Fir,Fir=Sec,Sec=Rep;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",*Fir,*Sec,*Thi); 
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
int a,b,c;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	if(b*b-4.0*a*c<0&&a==0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else{
		double x1,x2;
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/2.0*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/2.0*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	
}
 return 0;
}

20190318114:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int c,f,g,h;
	scanf("%d,%d",&c,&f);
	switch(c)
	{
		case 12:  g +=30;
		case 11:  g +=31;
		case 10:  g +=30;
		case 9:   g +=31;
		case 8:   g +=31;
		case 7:   g +=30;
		case 6:   g +=31;
		case 5:   g +=30;
		case 4:   g +=31;
		case 3:   g +=28;
		case 2:   g +=31;
		case 1:   g +=0;

	}
	h=(g+f-1)%7;
		switch(h)
	{
		case 5:    printf("Sunday");break;
		case 4:    printf("Saturday");break;
		case 3:    printf("Friday");break;
		case 2:    printf("Thursday");break;
		case 1:    printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 0:    printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 6:    printf("Monday");break;

	}
		
	
 }

20190318084:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, x, y, x1, x2, s;
	scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
	y=a*(x)*(x)+b*x+c;
	s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	if (s<0)
	   printf("NO SOLUTION ");
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f", x1, x2);
	
}

int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char x,y,z,m,n,p;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	if(x>y)
	{
		m=x;
		x=y;
		y=m;
	}//此时x为最大的数 
	if(x>z)
	{
		n=x;
		x=z;
		z=n;//同上 
	}
	if(y>z);
	{
		p=y;
		y=z;
		z=p;
	}	
	printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);	 
		
		
 }

20190302002:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
  char a,b,c,t;
  scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
  if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
    if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
      if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	float a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(a!=0)
        {
                d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(d>=0) 
                    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("NO SOLUTION");
        }
        return 0;
	}
}

20190301045:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int x,y,i,m,sum;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
int a[100]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
for(i=0;i<x-1;i++)
{
sum+=a[i];
}
sum+=y;
m=sum%7;
switch(m)
{
case 0:printf("Monday");break;
case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
case 4:printf("Friday");break;
case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
case 6:printf("Sunday");break;	 
}	
}

20190318187:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,max,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		max=a;
		min=b;
	}
	else{
		max=b;
		min=a;
	}
	if(c>max) max=c;
	if(min>c) min=c;
	b=a+b+c-max-min;
	c=max;
	a=min;
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);       
}

20190302035:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,s,q;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
do
{
s=b*b-4*a*c;
q=sqrt(s);
x1=(-b+q)/2*a;
x2=(-b-q)/2*a;
if(s>0||s==0) printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
if(s<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
}

20190318136:Problem1147:时间超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
 
int main()
{
       double a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
      
      while( scanf("%.f%.f%.f", &a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
       d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        if(a!=0&&d>=0)
        {
              
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(x1<x2) 
                    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
        else
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
        
        return 0;
}

	{
		if(a!=0)
        {
            e=b*b-4*a*c;
			d=sqrt(e);
            x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
            if(d>=0) 
                printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
            else
                printf("NO SOLUTION");
        }
        return 0;
	}
}

20190318066:Problem1114:正确

#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
y=2019;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
if (m ==1 || m == 2) {
y--;
m += 12;
}
c=y/100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while(w<0)w+=7;
w %= 7;
switch(w){
    case(1):
        printf("Monday");break;
    case(2):
    printf("Tuesday");break;
    case(3):
    printf("Wednesday");break;
    case(4):
    printf("Thursday");break;
    case(5):
    printf("Friday");break;
    case(6):
    printf("Saturday ");break;
    case(7):
    printf("Sunday");break;
    }

return 0;

}

20190318084:Problem1147:时间超限
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, x, y, x1, x2, s;
	scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
	y=a*(x)*(x)+b*x+c;
	s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	while (s>0 || s==0);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f", x1, x2);
}

20190302038:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h> 
main(){
    char m,n,j,max,min,mod;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&m,&n,&j);
    max=m,min=n;
    if(max<n)
      max=n;
    if(max<j)
      max=j;
    if(min>m)
      min=m;
    if(min>j)
      min=j;
    mod=m+n+j-max-min;
    printf("%c%c%c",min,mod,max);
	
}

20190301026:Problem1147:输出超限
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	int delta;
	double x1,x2;
	do{
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0){
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}else printf("NO SOLUTION");
	if(NULL) break;	
}   while(1);	
}

20190302048:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
void main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double delta,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c )!=EOF)
	{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0){
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else if(delta<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	double disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	double e=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
	if (disc>=0)
	  printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e-(b/(2*a)),-e-(b/(2*a)));
	else
	  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0||year%40==0)
	printf("L");
	else
	printf("N");
 } 
 /*题目描述
   给年份year，判别该年份是否闰年。一个年份如果是4的倍数但不是100的倍数，或这个年份是400的倍数，则这个年份为闰年。
   输入
   一个年份 
   输出
   根据是否闰年输出，是输出"L",否输出"N" */

20190318081:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,m,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1||x==10)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 0:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==2||x==3||x==11)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 4:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==4||x==7)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 1:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==12||x==9)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 2:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==5)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 6:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==6)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 3:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 5:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}
	else if(x==8)
	{
		d=y%7;
		switch(d)
		{
			case 5:printf("Monay\n");break;
			case 6:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
			case 0:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
			case 1:printf("Thursday\n");break;
			case 2:printf("Friday\n");break;
			case 3:printf("Saturday\n");break;
			case 4:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		}
	}

20190318135:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include <math.h> 
int main(void)
{
float a, b, c, x1, x2;
while(scanf("%f %f %f", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
return 0;
}

	int bottle;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	if (x>y)
	{
		bottle=x;
		x=y;
		y=bottle;
	}
	if (x>z)
	{
		bottle=x;
		x=z;
		z=bottle;
	}
	if (y>z)
	{
		bottle=y;
		y=z;
		z=bottle;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

void main(){
	int a,b,c,delt;
	double x1,x2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delt=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delt<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	if(delt>=0){
		 x1 = (-b+sqrt(delt))/(2*a);
		 x2 = (-b-sqrt(delt))/(2*a);
		 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	if (delta>=0)
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
    return 0;

#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta,flag=1;
	double solution1,solution2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (delta<0)
		flag=0;
		if (flag==1)
		{
			solution1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			solution2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",solution1,solution2);
		}
		else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta,flag;
	double solution1,solution2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (delta<0)
		flag=0;
		else flag=1;
		if (flag==1)
		{
			solution1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			solution2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",solution1,solution2);
		}
		else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2;
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	if(disc>=0)
	{
		x1=-b/(2*a)+sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		x2=-b/(2*a)-sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include <math.h> 
int main()
{
float a, b, c, x1, x2;
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
}
return 0;
}

20190301017:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<string.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,max,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	max=a;
	min=c;
	if(max<b)
	max=b;
	if(max<c)
	max=c;
	if(min>a)
	min=a;
	if(min>b)
	min=b;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",min,a+b+c-max-min,max);
}

		t=a,a=b,b=t;
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
		t=a,a=c,c=t;

	if(b>c)

int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    switch(x)
    {
    	case 1 : a=1+y;break;
    	case 2 : a=31+y;break;
    	case 3 : a=31+28+y;break;
    	case 4 : a=31*2+y+28;break;
    	case 5 : a=31*2+y+28+30;break;
    	case 6 : a=31*3+y+28+30;break;
    	case 7 : a=31*3+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 8 : a=31*4+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 9 : a=31*5+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 10 : a=31*5+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 11 : a=31*6+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 12 : a=31*6+y+28+30*4;break;
	}
	int b=(a+2)%7;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0 : printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 1 : printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2 : printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3 : printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4 : printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5 : printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6 : printf("Saturday\n");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int m1,d1,m2,d2,day,w;
	scanf("%d,%d,&m2,&d2");
	m1=1;
	d1=1;
	day=(m2-m1)*31+d2-d1;
	if(m2>=3 && m2<5)
		day=day-3;
	if(m2>=5&&m2<7)
		day=day-3-1;
	if(m2>=7&&m2<10)
		day=day-3-1-1;
	if(m2>=10&&m2<12)
		day=day-3-1-1-1;
	if(m2=12)
		day=day-3-1-1-1-1;
	w=day%7;
	switch(w)
	{
		case 0 :
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Saturday");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Sunday");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Monday");
			break;
	}
	
	
 }

20190318081:Problem1147:运行错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2,q,p;
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=-b/(2*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	if(disc>=0)
	{
		x1=p+q;
		x2=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

20190301017:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,r;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		r=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(r<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",((-1)*b+sqrt(r))/(2*a),((-1)*b-sqrt(r))/(2*a));
	}
	
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int c,f,g,h;
	 while

		(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&c,&f,&g)!= EOF)
	{
			switch(c)
	{
		case 5:    printf("伍佰");break;
		case 4:    printf("肆佰");break;
		case 3:    printf("叁佰");break;
		case 2:    printf("贰佰");break;
		case 1:    printf("壹佰");break;
		case 7:    printf("柒佰");break;
		case 6:    printf("陆佰");break;
        case 8:    printf("捌佰");break;
        case 9:    printf("玖佰");break;

	}
		
	     switch(f)
	{
		case 5:    printf("伍拾");break;
		case 4:    printf("肆拾");break;
		case 3:    printf("叁拾");break;
		case 2:    printf("贰拾");break;
		case 1:    printf("壹拾");break;
		case 7:    printf("柒拾");break;
		case 6:    printf("陆拾");break;
        case 8:    printf("捌拾");break;
        case 9:    printf("玖拾");break;
        case 0:    
		if(g==0)
		printf("");
        else
        printf("零");
                break;
	}		
	switch(g)
	{
		case 5:    printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 4:    printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 3:    printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 2:    printf("贰元整\n");break;
		case 1:    printf("壹元整\n");break;
		case 7:    printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 6:    printf("陆元整\n");break;
        case 8:    printf("捌元整\n");break;
        case 9:    printf("玖元整\n");break;
        case 0:    printf("元整\n");break;

	}
		
}
 }

20190301048:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	float x1,x2,d;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(a!=0)
        {
            d=b*b-4*a*c;
            if(d>=0){
            	d=sqrt(d);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
			}
            else
                printf("NO SOLUTION");
        }
	}
}

20190302055:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double d,e,f;
	while
	(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d = b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d>=0)
		{
			e=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			f=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e,f);
		}
		else if(d<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n") ;
		}
	}
}

20190318135:Problem1147:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
{
float a, b, c,e,f,g, x1, x2,x3,x4;
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&e,&f,&g)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
if (f*f - 4*e*g < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-f + sqrt(f*f - 4*e*g))/2*e;
x2 = (-f - sqrt(b*b - 4*e*g))/2*e;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x3,x4);
}
}
return 0;
}

20190318012:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,i=0,k[2],j=0;
	double x,y,d[2],e[2];
	while(i<2)
{
		scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
	d[i]=x;
	e[i]=y;
	k[i]=1;
}else
k[i]=0;

	i++;}
while(j<2)
		{
		if(k[j]==1)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",d[j],e[j]);
		if(k[j]==0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		j++;}
	}

20190302044:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
//是否是闰年
main()
{
	int y;
	scanf("%d",&y);
	if((y%400==0)||(y%4==0 && y%100!=0)){
		printf("L");
	}
	else{
		printf("N");
	}
 }

20190301003:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int year,x;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        x=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            x=1;
        else
            x=0;
    }
    if(x==1)
        printf("L\n");
    else
        printf("N\n");
    return 0;
}

20190318081:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2,q,p;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=-b/(2*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
	if(disc>=0)
	{
		x1=p+q;
		x2=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
float a, b, c,e,f,g, x1, x2,x3,x4;
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&e,&f,&g)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
if (f*f - 4*e*g < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-f + sqrt(f*f - 4*e*g))/2*e;
x2 = (-f - sqrt(b*b - 4*e*g))/2*e;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x3,x4);
}
}
return 0;
}

20190301012:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h> 
int main() 
{ 
char a,b,c,t; 
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;} 
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;} 
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;} 
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c); 
return 0;
}

20190302009:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    int i,year=2019,month,day,sum;
    int a[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
    int b[12]={31,29,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
    scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
    sum=0;
    if(year%4==0)
    {
     for(i=0;i<month-1;i++)
     {
      sum+=b[i];
     }
     sum+=day;
    }
    else
    {
     for(i=0;i<month-1;i++)
     {
      sum+=a[i];
     }
     sum+=day;
	 }
	 for(sum>7;sum=sum-7;)
	sum=sum+1;
	switch(sum)
	{
		case 1:{printf("Monday\n");break;}
		case 2:{printf("Tuesday\n");break;}
		case 3:{printf("Wednesday\n");break;}
		case 4:{printf("Thursday\n");break;}
		case 5:{printf("Friday\n");break;}
		case 6:{printf("Saturday\n");break;}
		case 7:{printf("Sunday\n");break;}
		default:break;
	}
    return 0;
}

20190318038:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    switch(x)
    {
    	case 1 : a=1+y;break;
    	case 2 : a=31+y;break;
    	case 3 : a=31+28+y;break;
    	case 4 : a=31*2+y+28;break;
    	case 5 : a=31*2+y+28+30;break;
    	case 6 : a=31*3+y+28+30;break;
    	case 7 : a=31*3+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 8 : a=31*4+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 9 : a=31*5+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 10 : a=31*5+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 11 : a=31*6+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 12 : a=31*6+y+28+30*4;break;
	}
	int b=(a+1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0 : printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 1 : printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2 : printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3 : printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4 : printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5 : printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6 : printf("Saturday\n");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

int main()
{
	int x,y,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	x=x-1;
	y=y-1;
	i=(x*31+y+2)%7;
	switch(i)
	{
        case 1:
            printf("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf("Saturday\n");
            break;
        case 7:
            printf("Sunday\n");
            break;
        default:
            printf("error\n");
            break;
	} 
	return 0;
}

20190301044:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a1,a2,a3;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a1,&a2,&a3);
	if(a1>=a2&&a1>=a3&&a2>=a3)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a3,a2,a1);
	else if(a1>=a2&&a1>=a3&&a3>=a2)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a2,a3,a1);
	else if(a2>=a1&&a2>=a3&&a1>=a3)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a3,a1,a2);
	else if(a2>=a1&&a2>=a3&&a3>=a1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a1,a3,a2);
	else if(a3>=a1&&a3>=a2&&a1>=a2)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a2,a1,a3);
	else if(a3>=a1&&a3>=a2&&a2>=a1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a1,a2,a3);
}

	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d<0)
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		else
		{
			e=sqrt(d);
			x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}

#include <stdio.h>
#include<string.h>
#define N 100
main()
{
char all[N];
int i;
gets(all);
for(i=0;all[i];i++)
{
if(all[i]>'a'&&all[i]<'z'||all[i]>'A'&&all[i]<'Z')
printf("NO\n");
else if(all[i]>'0'&&all[i]<'9')
printf("YES\n");
else
printf("NO\n");
}
}

20190301046:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char t,a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
		if(a>c)
	{
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
	}
		if(b>c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=b;
		b=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 }

#include<stdio.h> 
#include <math.h>
main(){
    int a,b,c,s,d,j;
    double m,n,x1,x2,x3,x4;
    scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
    scanf("%d %d %d",&s,&d,&j);
    m=b*b-4*a*c;
    n=d*d-4*s*j;
    if(m>=0)
    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1=(-b+sqrt(m))/2*a,x2=(-b-sqrt(m))/2*a);
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    if(n>=0)
    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x3=(-d+sqrt(n))/2*s,x4=(-d-sqrt(n))/2*s);
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION");
   
    
   
}

	printf("NO SOLUTION");

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	{	
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	}
}

20190301030:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,d,t = 0,i,mond[12] = {0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
	char day[7][15] = {"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	for (i = 0 ; i < m ; i++)
		t = t + mond[i];
	t = t + d;
	printf("%s\n",day[t%7]);
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
char r;
scanf("%c",&r);
if(r>=48&&r<=57)
printf("Yes\n");
else
printf("No\n");
return 0;
}

20190301023:Problem1034:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    char ch;
    scanf("%c",&ch);
    if(ch>='a'&&ch<='z'||ch>='A'&&ch<='Z')
       printf("NO\n",ch);
    else if(ch>='0'&&ch<='9')
       printf("YES\n",ch);
    else
       printf("NO\n",ch);
}

20190318059:Problem1059:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	b=a%4;
	c=a%100;
	d=a%400;
	if((b==0&&c!=0)||d==0)
	printf("L");
	else
	printf("N");
}

20190301008:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int month_day[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	char *week[7]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	int x,y,i,day;
	while (scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y)!=EOF)
	{
		day=y;
		for (i=0;i<x-1;i++)
		{
			day=day+month_day[i];
		}
		printf("%s\n",week[day%7]);
	}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,x,D,m,t;
	t=1;
	while(t<=2)
	{
		scanf("%lf %lf %lf\n",&a,&b,&c);
		a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	    D=b*b-4*a*c;
  	    t++;
		if(D>=0) {
		          m=sqrt(D);
	              printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",(-b+m)/2*a,(-b-m)/2*a);
				 }
		else printf("NO SOLUTION");
   } ;
}

20190302048:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
void xs(int a)
{
	if(a==0) printf("零");
	else if(a==1) printf("壹");
	else if(a==2) printf("贰")
	else if(a==3) printf("叁");
	else if(a==4) printf("肆");
	else if(a==5) printf("伍");
	else if(a==6) printf("陆");
	else if(a==7) printf("柒");
	else if(a==8) printf("捌");
	else if(a==9) printf("玖");
	
}
void main()
{
	int y=1;
	while(y)
	{
		double i;
		int j,j1,j2;
		int k,k1,k2;
		int m,m1,m2;
		int g,g1,g2;
		int h,h1,h2;
		scanf("&d%d%d\n",&j,&j1,&j2);
		scanf("&d%d%d\n",&k,&k1,&k2);
		scanf("&d%d%d\n",&m,&m1,&m2);
		scanf("&d%d%d\n",&g,&g1,&g2);
		scanf("&d%d%d\n",&jh,&h1,&h2);
		xs(j)
	}
 }

20190301026:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
//今天是星期2,2019年1月1日 
// x月，y日是星期几？ 
char *day(int n);
main()
{
	int i,sum;
	int x,y; 
	char a[12]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1,sum=0;i<x;i++){
	sum=a[i]*1+sum;	
 } sum=sum+y;
 	i=sum%7;
 	printf("%d\n",i);
	printf("%s\n",day(i));
	
}
char *day(int n)
{
	char *name[]={"Monday",
				"Tuesday",
				"Wednesday",
				"Thursday",
				"Friday",
				"Saturday",
				"Sunday"};
	if(!n) n=0;	
	return name[n];
}

20190318012:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,i=0,k[i],j=0;
	double x,y,d[i],e[i];
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
		
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
	d[i]=x;
	e[i]=y;
	k[i]=1;
}else
k[i]=0;

	i++;
	}
while(j<i+1)
		{
		if(k[j]==1)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",d[j],e[j]);
		if(k[j]==0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		j++;}
	}

20190301023:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%4 == 0)
    {
        if( year%100 == 0)
        {
            if ( year%400 == 0)
                printf("L\n", year);
            else
                printf("N\n", year);
        }
        else
            printf("L\n", year );
    }
    else
        printf("N\n", year);
}

20190318106:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    switch(a)
	    {
	    	case 1: printf("壹佰");break;
    		case 2: printf("贰佰");break;
	    	case 3: printf("叁佰");break;
    		case 4: printf("肆佰");break;
	    	case 5: printf("伍佰");break;
	    	case 6: printf("陆佰");break;
	    	case 7: printf("柒佰");break;
	    	case 8: printf("捌佰");break;
	    	case 9: printf("玖佰");break;
    	}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1: printf("壹拾");break;
    		case 2: printf("贰拾");break;
	    	case 3: printf("叁拾");break;
    		case 4: printf("肆拾");break;
	    	case 5: printf("伍拾");break;
	    	case 6: printf("陆拾");break;
	    	case 7: printf("柒拾");break;
	    	case 8: printf("捌拾");break;
	    	case 9: printf("玖拾");break;
	        case 0: 
			if(c==0) 
			printf("");
			else
			printf("零");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
		    case 1: printf("壹元整\n");break;
    		case 2: printf("贰元整\n");break;
	    	case 3: printf("叁元整\n");break;
    		case 4: printf("肆元整\n");break;
	    	case 5: printf("伍元整\n");break;
	    	case 6: printf("陆元整\n");break;
	    	case 7: printf("柒元整\n");break;
	    	case 8: printf("捌元整\n");break;
	    	case 9: printf("玖元整\n");break;	
	    	case 0: printf("元整\n");break;
		}	
	}
	
}

20190318135:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
  int x, y, c, w;
  scanf ("%d %d", &x,&y);
  if (x ==1 || x == 2) { 
    x += 12;
  }
  c = 2019/100;
  y =2019-c*100;
  w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (2019 + 2019 / 4) + (13 * (x + 1) / 5) + y - 1;
  while (w < 0) w += 7;
  w %= 7;
  if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
  if (w == 1) printf ("Monday");
  if (w == 2) printf ("Tuesday");
  if (w == 3) printf ("Wednesday");
  if (w == 4) printf ("Thursday");
  if (w == 5) printf ("Friday");
  if (w == 6) printf ("Saturday");
  return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int x,y;
	int i,r,sum,m;
	int s[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	r=0;
	for(i=0;i<(x-1);i++){
		r=r+s[i];
	}
	sum=r+y;
	m=(sum+2+7)%7-1;
	if(m==0)
	printf("Sunday\n");
	if(m==1)
	printf("Monday\n");
	if(m==2)
	printf("Tuesday\n");
	if(m==3)
	printf("Wednesday\n");
	if(m==4)
	printf("Thursday\n");
	if(m==5)
	printf("Friday\n");
	if(m==6)
	printf("Saturday\n");

#include<stdio.h>
//今天是星期2,2019年1月1日 
// x月，y日是星期几？ 
char *day(int n);
main()
{
	int i,sum;
	int x,y; 
	char a[12]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1,sum=0;i<x;i++){
	sum=a[i]*1+sum;	
 } sum=sum+y;
 	i=sum%7;
	printf("%s\n",day(i));
	
}
char *day(int n)
{
	char *name[]={"Monday",
				"Tuesday",
				"Wednesday",
				"Thursday",
				"Friday",
				"Saturday",
				"Sunday"};
	if(!n) n=0;	
	return name[n];
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int x,y;
	int i,r,sum,m;
	int s[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	r=0;
	for(i=0;i<(x-1);i++){
		r=r+s[i];
	}
	sum=r+y;
	m=(sum+1+7)%7;
	if(m==0)
	printf("Sunday\n");
	if(m==1)
	printf("Monday\n");
	if(m==2)
	printf("Tuesday\n");
	if(m==3)
	printf("Wednesday\n");
	if(m==4)
	printf("Thursday\n");
	if(m==5)
	printf("Friday\n");
	if(m==6)
	printf("Saturday\n");

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int d,n,x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	n=19+19/4+20/4-2*20+26*(x+1)/10+y-1;
    d=n%7;
	switch(d)
{   case 1:printf("Monday");break;
    case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	case 7:printf("Sunday"); }
}

main()
{

        scanf("%lf %lf %lf\n%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c,&t,&y,&u);
		a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	    D=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(D>=0) {
		          m=sqrt(D);
	              printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-b+m)/2*a,(-b-m)/2*a);
				 }
		else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		a=t;
		b=y;
		c=u;
		D=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(D>=0) {
		          m=sqrt(D);
	              printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-b+m)/2*a,(-b-m)/2*a);

20190318081:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2,q,p;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	if(disc>=0)
	{
		x1=p+q;
		x2=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
    {   
        if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
        else
        {
        	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
        
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318038:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,disc,p,q;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if (disc>=0)
     {
	 q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
     p=-b/(2*a);
     printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",p+q,p-q);
     }
     else 
     printf("NO SOLUTION\n");break;
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,i;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	
	{
		i=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	    if(i<0)
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	        x1=(-b+i)/2*a;
	        x2=(-b-i)/2*a;
	        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	    }
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318107:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
	t=b;
	b=a;
	a=t;
}
	if(b>c)
{
	t=c;
	c=b;
	b=t;
}
	if(a>b)
	{
	
	t=a;
	a=b;
	b=t;
}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	
	

}

/*判断是否为闰年*/
#include"stdio.h"

int main()
{
	int z;
	scanf("%d",&z);
	int a,b,c;
	a=z%4;
	b=z%100;
	c=z%400;
	if((a==0&&b!=0)||c==0){printf("L\n");
	}
	else{printf("N\n");
	}
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
        double a,b,c,x1,x2;
        int d,t;
        scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
        if(a!=0)
        {
                d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                t=(b*b-4*a*c);
                if(t<0)
                    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
                if(t>=0)
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                    if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    else
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
}

#include "math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {   
        if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
        else
        {
        	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        	x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        	x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
        
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		double delta;
		delta=b^2-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else
		{
			double x1,x2;
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b^2-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(b^2-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3Lf~~~%.3Lf",x1,x2);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

    if(a!=0)
    {
        d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        t=(b*b-4*a*c);
        x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	char d,e,f;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&d,&e,&f);
    //scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
    a=d;
    b=e;
    c=f;
	if(a<b)
	{
		t=b;
		b=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(a<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(b<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=b;
		b=t;
	} 
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
}

#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,disc,p,q;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if (disc>=0)
     {
	 q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
     p=-b/(2*a);
     printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",p+q,p-q);
     }
     else 
     printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
    return 0;
}

    	printf("NO SOLUTION");

	if(delta>=0){
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);

	}

		c=x;
	}

		c=x;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,d,e,f;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){ 
	if(b*b-4*a*c>0||b*b-4*a*c==0)
	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	e=(-b+d)/2*a;
	f=(-b-d)/2*a;
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",e,f);
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
} 
}

20190318081:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2,q,p;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	    p=-b/(2.0*a);
	    q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	    if(disc>=0)
	    {
	   	    x1=p+q;
		    x2=p-q;
		    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    else
	    {
		    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
    }
	return 0;
}

#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, x, x1, x2, s;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF);	
	s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	if (s<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1, x2);
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char money[10][3] = {"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	int mon;
	char str[4];
	while (gets(str))
	{
		if (strcmp(str,"") == 0)
			break;
		if (str[1] == '0')
		{
			if (str[2] == '0')
				printf("%s佰元整\n",money[str[0] - 48]);
			else
				printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",money[str[0] - 48],money[str[2] - 48]);
		}
		else if (str[2] == '0')
			printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[str[0] - 48],money[str[1] - 48]);
		else
			printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",money[str[0] - 48],money[str[1] - 48],money[str[2] - 48]);
	}
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,s,q;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
do
{
s=b*b-4*a*c;
q=sqrt(s);
x1=(-b+q)/2*a;
x2=(-b-q)/2*a;
if(s>0||s==0) printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2); 
if(s<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
}

20190301008:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
	char *number[10]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","拾"};
	while (scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
	{
		a=n/100;
		n-=100*a;
		b=n/10;
		n-=10*b;
		c=n; 
		if (b==0 && c!=0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",number[a-1],number[c-1]);
		else if (c==0 & b!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",number[a-1],number[b-1]);
		else if (b==0 && c==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",number[a-1]);
		else printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",number[a-1],number[b-1],number[c-1]);
	}
}

#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);	}
    }
 } 
 /*题目描述
   求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。 
   输入
   有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
   输出
   如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
   如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
   样例输入 
   1 -2 1
   1 1 2
   样例输出	
   1.000~~~1.000
   NO SOLUTION */

20190318092:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	switch (a){
	         case 0:b=y-2;break;
	         case 1:b=y-2+31;break;
	         case 2:b=y-2+59;break;
	         case 3:b=y-2+90;break;
	         case 4:b=y-2+120;break;
	         case 5:b=y-2+151;break;
	         case 6:b=y-2+181;break;
			 case 7:b=y-2+211;break;
			 case 8:b=y-2+242;break;
			 case 9:b=y-2+273;break;
			 case 10:b=y-2+303;break;
			 case 11:b=y-2+334;break;
			 };
	c=b%7;
	if(b<=6) d=b+2;
	else d=c+2;
	if(d<=7) d=d;
	else d=d-7;
	switch (d){
	         case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	         case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	         case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	         case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	         case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	         case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	         case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
			 };
}

20190318043:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
 int year=2019, x, y;
  scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
  if (x == 1 || x == 2)//判断month是否为1或2　
   year--, x += 12;
  int a = year / 100;
  int b = year - a * 100;
  int c = b + b / 4 + a / 4 - 2 * a + 26 * (x + 1) / 10 + y - 1;
  while (c < 0)
   c += 7;
  c%= 7;
  switch (c)
  {
  case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
  case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
  case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
  case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
  case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
  }
}

20190302045:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,max,cur,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c){max=a,cur=b,min=c;}
	if(a>c&&c>b){max=a,cur=c,min=b;}
    if(b>a&&a>c){max=b,cur=a,min=c;}
    if(b>c&&c>a){max=b,cur=c,min=b;}
    if(c>a&&a>b){max=c,cur=a,min=b;}
    if(c>b&&b>a){max=c,cur=b,min=a;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",min,cur,max);
}

20190302040:Problem1069:正确
/*输出三字母*/
#include"stdio.h"

int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	char max,mid,min;
	if(x>y){max=x,min=y;
	}
	else{max=y,min=x;
	}
	if(z>max){mid=max,max=z;
	}
	if(z<min){mid=min,min=z;
	}
	if(z<max&&z>min){mid=z;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",min,mid,max);
 }

20190301030:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char money[10][4] = {"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	int mon,a,b,c;
	char str[4];
	while (gets(str))
	{
		if (strcmp(str,"") == 0)
			break;
		a = str[0] - '0';b = str[1] - '0';c = str[2] - '0';
		if (str[1] == '0')
		{
			if (str[2] == '0')
				printf("%s佰元整\n",money[a]);
			else
				printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",money[a],money[c]);
		}
		else if (str[2] == '0')
			printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[a],money[b]);
		else
			printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",money[a],money[b],money[c]);
	}
}

	if(b*b-4*a*c>0||b*b-4*a*c==0)
	{
	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	e=(-1*b+d)/(2*a);
	f=(-1*b-d)/(2*a);

}

main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2;
    int d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
            if(t>=0)
                printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1);
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

main ()
{
    int m,d,c,w,y;
    scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
    if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
        y--;
        m += 12;
    }
    c = y / 100;
    y = y - c * 100;
    w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1 ;
    while (w < 0) w += 7;
        w %= 7;
    switch(w)
    {
		case 0:printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday\n");break;

20190301044:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	double a,b,c,delta,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

20190302009:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
  int a=2019,b,c,d,s;
  scanf("%d,%d",&b,&c);
  if(b <= 0 || b > 12)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c <= 0)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c >= 31)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 3: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 5: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 7: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 8: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 10:printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 12:printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if(c >= 30)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 4: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 6: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 9: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 11: printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if((a%4 == 0 && a%100 != 0) || (a%400 == 0))
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 29)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
  else
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 28)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
  /*闰年*/
  if((a%4 == 0 && a%100 != 0) || (a%400 == 0))
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335;
    break;
   }
  }
  /*同年*/
  else
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31 - 1;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60 - 1;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91 - 1;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121- 1;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152- 1;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182- 1;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213- 1;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244- 1;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274- 1;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305- 1;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335- 1;
    break;
   }
  }
  s = (a-1 + (a-1)/4 - (a-1)/100 + (a-1)/400 + d)%7;
  switch(s)
  {
   case 0: printf("Sunday\n");
         break;
   case 1: printf("Monduy\n");
   break;
   case 2: printf("Tuesday\n");
   break;
   case 3: printf("Wednesday\n");
   break;
   case 4: printf("Thursday\n");
   break;
   case 5: printf("Friday\n");
   break;
   case 6: printf("Saturday\n");
   break;
  }
 }

#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2;
    int d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);	}
    }
 } 
 /*题目描述
   求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。 
   输入
   有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
   输出
   如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
   如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
   样例输入 
   1 -2 1
   1 1 2
   样例输出	
   1.000~~~1.000
   NO SOLUTION */

	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
		    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		    x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    char a,b,c,t;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a>b)
    { t=a;a=b;b=t; }
    if(a>c)
    {t=a;a=c;c=t;  }
    if(b>c)
    {
        t=c;c=b;b=t;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int day,month,sum=0;
    
    scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);  
    switch(month-1) 
    {
        case  11:sum+=30;
        case  10:sum+=31;
        case 9:sum+=30;
        case 8:sum+=31;
        case 7:sum+=31;
        case 6:sum+=30;
        case 5:sum+=31;
        case 4:sum+=30;
        case 3:sum+=31;
        case 2:sum+=28;
        case 1:sum+=31;
    }
    sum=sum+day; 


    if((1+sum)%7==0)
    printf("Sunday");
    if((1+sum)%7==1)
    printf("Monday");
    if((1+sum)%7==2)
    printf("Tuesday");
    if((1+sum)%7==3)
    printf("Wednesday");
    if((1+sum)%7==4)
    printf("Thursday");
    if((1+sum)%7==5)
    printf("Friday");
    if((1+sum)%7==6)
    printf("Saturday");
    


}

20190318092:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;//a为月差 
	switch (a){
	         case 0:b=y-1;break;
	         case 1:b=y-1+31;break;
	         case 2:b=y-1+59;break;
	         case 3:b=y-1+90;break;
	         case 4:b=y-1+120;break;
	         case 5:b=y-1+151;break;
	         case 6:b=y-1+181;break;
			 case 7:b=y-1+212;break;
			 case 8:b=y-1+243;break;
			 case 9:b=y-1+273;break;
			 case 10:b=y-1+304;break;
			 case 11:b=y-1+334;break;
			 };
	c=b%7;//c为余数 b为日期差 d为星期号 
    if(b>=7) d=2+c;
    else d=2+b;
    if(d>7) d=d-7;
    else d=d;
    switch (d){
	         case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	         case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	         case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	         case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	         case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	         case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	         case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
			 };
}

#include <stdio.h>  
#include <string.h>  
  
void trans(int a)  
{  
    if(a == 1)printf("壹");  
  
    else if(a == 2)printf("贰");  
  
    else if(a == 3)printf("叁");  
  
    else if(a == 4)printf("肆");  
  
    else if(a == 5)printf("伍");  
  
    else if(a == 6)printf("陆");  
  
    else if(a == 7)printf("柒");  
  
    else if(a == 8)printf("捌");  
  
    else if(a == 9)printf("玖");  
  
    else if(a == 0)printf("零");  
  
}  
void weight(int i)  
{  
    if(i==1||i==5||i==9)  
        printf("拾");  
    if(i==2||i==6||i==10)  
        printf("佰");  
    if(i==3||i==7||i==11)  
        printf("仟");  
    if(i==4)  
        printf("万");  
    if(i==8)  
        printf("亿");  
    if(i==0)  
        printf("元整\n");  
}  
int main()  
{  
    while(1)  
    {  
        char a[10];  
    while(scanf("%s",&a)!=EOF) {
        strrev(a);  
        for(int i=strlen(a) - 1; a[i]; i--)  
        {  
            trans(a[i]-'0');  
            weight(i);  
        }  }
    }  
}

20190318016:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

	{
	    if((b*b-4*a*c)>0)
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	        x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	        x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	    }

	return 0;

		a=c;
		c=t;

		b=c;
		c=t;

    {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d<0)
    {
        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
    else
    {
       x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);

	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 1:{printf("壹佰");break;}
		case 2:{printf("贰佰");break;}
		case 3:{printf("叁佰");break;}
		case 4:{printf("肆佰");break;}
		case 5:{printf("伍佰");break;}
		case 6:{printf("陆佰");break;}

		case 8:{printf("捌佰");break;}
		case 9:{printf("玖佰");break;}
	}

	{
		case 1:{printf("壹拾");break;}
		case 2:{printf("贰拾");break;}
		case 3:{printf("叁拾");break;}
		case 4:{printf("肆拾");break;}

		case 7:{printf("柒拾");break;}
		case 8:{printf("捌拾");break;}

	}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x,y,m;
	int A,B,C,D,X,Y,M;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d%d%d",&A,&B,&C);
	m=b*b-4*a*c;
	d=sqrt(m);
	x=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	y=(-b-d)/(2*a);
	if(m<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",1.0*x,1.0*y);
	
	D=sqrt(B*B-4*A*C);
	X=(-B+D)/(2*A);
	Y=(-B-D)/(2*A);
	M=B*B-4*A*C;
	D=sqrt(M);
	if(M<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",1.0*X,1.0*Y);
}

/*2019年1月1日是星期二，2019年x月y日是星期几。
（0<x<13,0<y<32,请根据具体月份给出真实的日期y值）*/
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int y,d,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&y,&d);
	w=19+19/4+20/4-2*20+26*(y+1)/10+d-1;
    while (w<0)
     w+=7;
    w%=7;
	switch (w)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Monday\n");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Tuesday\n");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Wednesday\n");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Thursday\n");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Friday\n");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Saturday \n");
			break;
		case 7:
			printf("Sunday\n");
			break;
	}
 }

 main()
{
     char a,b,c,t;

     if (a>b) 
	 {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
     if (a>c)
	  {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
     if (b>c)
	  {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
     printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);

20190302040:Problem1147:答案错误
/*解方程*/
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"

int main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2;
	double x11,x12,x21,x22;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a2,&b2,&c2);
	int d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	int d2=b2*b2-4*a2*c2;
	if(d1<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{x11=(-b1)/2*a1+sqrt(d1),x12=(-b1)/2*a1-sqrt(d1),printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x11,x12);
	}
	if(d2<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{x21=(-b2)/2*a2+sqrt(d2),x22=(-b2)/2*a2-sqrt(d2),printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x21,x22);
	}
	
 }

main()
{
	int x, y, s;
	scanf("%d,%d", &x, &y);
	if (x=1){
	s=(y+2)%7;
	switch (s){
		       case 2:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	       case 3:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	       case 4:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	       case 5:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	       case 6:printf("Friday\n");break;
	   	       case 7:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	   	       case 1:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;

20190301051:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	long y;
	scanf("%ld",&y);
	if(y%4==0&&y%100!=0||y%400==0)
	printf("L\n");
	else
	printf("N\n");
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{

	b=x/100;
	s=(x%100)/10;
	g=x%10;
	switch(b){
		      case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			  case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			  case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			  case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			  case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			  case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			  case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			  case 8:printf("捌佰");break;

        	};

	{
	switch(s){
		                case 0:printf("零");break;
		                case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		                case 2:printf("贰拾");break;

					    case 0:printf("");break;

		                case 5:printf("伍拾");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int day,month,sum,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	switch(month)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
	}
	sum=sum+day;
	y=(sum-1)%7;
	if(y==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(y==1)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Friday");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Satueday");
	if(y==5)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(y==6)
	printf("Monday");
}

	{
		case 0:{printf("零");break;}
		case 1:{printf("壹佰");break;}
		case 2:{printf("贰佰");break;}
		case 3:{printf("叁佰");break;}

		case 1:{printf("壹拾");break;}

20190318110:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
	while
	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;

	if (delta>=0)
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
 }
 
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z,h;
	float x1,x2;    
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
    z=b*b-4*a*c;
	h=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
 	x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
 	if(z>=0)
    {printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
	else	
	{printf("NO SOLUTION");} 
	}   
    return 0;
}

20190302016:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%4==0)
	{
		if(year%100==0)
		{
			if(year%400==0)
			    printf("L");
			else
			    printf("N");
		}
		else
		    printf("L");
	}
	else
	    printf("N");
}

			j=30;
			break;
		case 10:
			j=31;
			break;
		case 11:
			j=30;
			break;
		case 12:
		    j=31;
			break;
		default:
		    break;			
	}
	i=(x*j+y+2)%7;
	switch(i)
	{
        case 1:
            printf("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf("Saturday\n");
            break;
        case 7:
            printf("Sunday\n");
            break;
        default:
            printf("error\n");
            break;
	} 
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z,h;
	float x1,x2;    
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
    z=b*b-4*a*c;
	h=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
 	x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
 	if(z>=0)
    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else	
	printf("NO SOLUTION"); 
	}   
    return 0;
}

20190318107:Problem1114:正确

	#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int days(int x,int y);
  int a,b,c,d,e;
  scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
  
  d=days(a,b);
  c=1+d;
  e=c%7;
  switch(e)
  {
  	case 1:printf("Monday");break;
  	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
  	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
  	case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
  	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
  	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
  	case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
  	
  }
  //printf("%d",d);
  return 0;
  }
  
  
   int days(int x,int y)
  {
  	int a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};

  int sum,i;
	 	{
		 for(i=0,sum=0;i<x;i++)
	 	{
		 sum=sum+a[i];
	 	}
	 	sum=sum+y;
	 }
	 	return(sum);
  }

20190318066:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>  
#include <string.h>  
void trans(int a)  
{  
    if(a==1)printf("壹");  
    else if(a==2)printf("贰");  
    else if(a==3)printf("叁");  
    else if(a==4)printf("肆");  
    else if(a==5)printf("伍");  
    else if(a==6)printf("陆");  
    else if(a==7)printf("柒");  
    else if(a==8)printf("捌");  
    else if(a==9)printf("玖");  
    else if(a==0)printf("零");  
}  
void weight(int i)  
{  if(i==1||i==5||i==9)  
        printf("拾");  
    if(i==2||i==6||i==10)  
        printf("佰");  
    if(i==3||i==7||i==11)  
        printf("仟");  
    if(i==4)  
        printf("万");  
    if(i==0)  
        printf("元整\n");  
}  
int main()  
{while(1)  
    {  
    char a[10];  
    while(scanf("%s",&a)!=EOF) {
        strrev(a); 
		int i; 
        for(i=strlen(a)-1;a[i]; i--)  
        {  
            trans(a[i]-'0');  
            weight(i);  
        }                       
	 }
    }  
    return 0;
}

20190318026:Problem1059:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int  a;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	if(a%400<=0) printf("L");
	else if (a%100<=0) printf("N");
	else if (a%4<=0) printf("L");
	else printf("N");
}

20190318031:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int day,month,sum=0;
    
    scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);  
    switch(month-1) 
    {
        case  11:sum+=30;
        case  10:sum+=31;
        case 9:sum+=30;
        case 8:sum+=31;
        case 7:sum+=31;
        case 6:sum+=30;
        case 5:sum+=31;
        case 4:sum+=30;
        case 3:sum+=31;
        case 2:sum+=28;
        case 1:sum+=31;
    }
    sum=sum+day; 


    if((1+sum)%7==0)
    printf("Sunday");
    if((1+sum)%7==1)
    printf("Monday");
    if((1+sum)%7==2)
    printf("Tuesday");
    if((1+sum)%7==3)
    printf("Wednesday");
    if((1+sum)%7==4)
    printf("Thursday");
    if((1+sum)%7==5)
    printf("Friday");
    if((1+sum)%7==6)
    printf("Saturday");
    


}

20190302035:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=y-1;
	if(x==1||x==2) b=(x-1)*31+a;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
    if(b==1) printf("Monday");
    if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(b==5) printf("Friday");
    if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
}

20190302016:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char word1,word2,word3,a,b,c;
	word1=getchar();
	word2=getchar();
	word3=getchar();
	if(word1>word2&&word1>word3)
	    a=word1;
	else if(word2>word1&&word2>word3)
	    a=word2;
	else
	    a=word3;
	if(word1<word2&&word1<word3)
	    b=word1;
	else if(word2<word1&&word2<word3)
	    b=word2;
	else
	    b=word3;
	c=word1+word2+word3-a-b;
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
}

20190318043:Problem1158:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int t,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&t)!=EOF)
	{
		a=t/100;
		b=(t-100*a)/10;
		c=t-100*a-10*b;
	if(t%100==0)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	else
	{
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,leap;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%100==0)	
				{ if(year%400==0)	leap=1;
				  else	leap=0;
				}
	else	{if(year%4==0)	leap=1;
			 else	leap=0;
			}
	
	if(leap==1)	printf("L");
	else	printf("N");
}

20190301045:Problem1158:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
void dx(int a)
{
if(a==0) printf("零");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆");
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
main()
{
int x,k,m,n;
while(scanf("%d",&x)){
    k=x/100;
    m=x/10%10;
    n=x%10;
    if(m!=0&&n!=0){
        dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        printf("拾");
        dx(n);
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(n==0&&m!=0){
        dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        printf("拾");
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(m==0&&n==0){
	    dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(m==0&&n!=0){
    	dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        dx(n);
        printf("元整\n");
	}
}
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0){
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
	}

main()

	{

	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	 while

		(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;

        case 9:printf("玖佰");break;

	}

	{
		case 0:if(c==0)
		            printf("");
               else printf("零");break;

		case 2:printf("肆拾");break;

main()
{

	double x1,x2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d>0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d)/2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d)/2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		
	}
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(d==0)
	{
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(d)/2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d)/2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);	
	}
	return 0;

main(){

    if(x==1){
    	switch((y-1)%7){
    		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
    		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
    		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
    		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
    		case 3:printf("Friday");break;

    		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d%d%d\n",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d%d%d",&d,&e,&f);
	x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	x3=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/(2*d);
	x4=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f))/(2*d);
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0){
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(e*e-4*d*f<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	if(e*e-4*d*f>=0){
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	}
}

20190318059:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x,y,m;
	int A,B,C,D,X,Y,M;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d%d%d",&A,&B,&C);
	m=b*b-4*a*c;
	d=sqrt(m);
	x=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	y=(-b-d)/(2*a);
	if(m<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",1.0*x,1.0*y);
	
	D=sqrt(B*B-4*A*C);
	X=(-B+D)/(2*A);
	Y=(-B-D)/(2*A);
	M=B*B-4*A*C;
	D=sqrt(M);
	if(M<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",1.0*X,1.0*Y);
}

	scanf("%d%d%d",&A,&B,&C);

	d=sqrt(m);
	x=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	y=(-b-d)/(2*a);

	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",1.0*x,1.0*y);

	X=(-B+D)/(2*A);
	Y=(-B-D)/(2*A);

	D=sqrt(M);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,s,q;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
do
{
s=b*b-4*a*c;
if(s>0||s==0) 
{
q=sqrt(s);
x1=(-b+q)/2*a;
x2=(-b-q)/2*a;
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2); 
}
if(s<0)  printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	 while

		(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
        case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
        case 9:printf("玖佰");break;

	}
		
	    switch(b)
	{
		case 0:if(c==0)
		            printf("");
               else printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
        case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
        case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
        
	}		
	    switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
        case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
        case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
        case 0:printf("元整\n");break;

	}
		
}

20190318075:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) 
w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w)
{
case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
}
}

	if(b*b-4*a*c>0)
	{
		d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
		x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);

    }
