20190318066:Problem1158:时间超限
#include<stdio.h>
void xs(int a)
{
if(a==0) printf("零");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆");
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
int main()
{
int y=1;
while(y)
{
double i;
int j,j1;
int k,k1;
int m,m1;
int n,n1;
int g,g1;
int h,h1;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
j=(int)i%10000000%1000000%100000%10000/1000;
k=(int)i%1000/100;
m=(int)i%1000%100/10;
n=(int)i%1000%100%10;
if(i<10000&&i>=0)
{
xs(k);
printf("佰");
xs(m);
printf("拾");
xs(n);
printf("元整");
printf("\n");
}
else
scanf("%d",&y);
printf("\n");
printf("\n");
}}
return 0;
}

20190301044:Problem1114:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int month,day;
	int i,y,sum=0;
	int a[100]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	for(i=0;i<month-1;i++)
	{
		sum=sum+a[i];
	}
	y=sum+day+2-1;
	y=y%7;
	switch(y)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
	}
	
}

void xs(int a) 
{   
    if(a==0) printf("零"); 
 else if(a==1) printf("壹"); 
 else if(a==2) printf("贰"); 
 else if(a==3) printf("叁"); 
 else if(a==4) printf("肆"); 
 else if(a==5) printf("伍"); 
 else if(a==6) printf("陆"); 
 else if(a==7) printf("柒"); 
 else if(a==8) printf("捌"); 
 else if(a==9) printf("玖"); 
 
} 
 
main() 
{ 
 int y=1; 
 while(y) 
 { 
 double i; 
 int j,j1; 
 int k,k1; 
 int m,m1; 
 int n,n1; 
 int g,g1; 
 int h,h1; 
scanf("%lf",&i); 
  j=(int)i%10000000%1000000%100000%10000/1000; 
  k=(int)i%1000/100; 
  m=(int)i%1000%100/10; 
  n=(int)i%1000%100%10; 
 
{

printf("佰"); 
xs(m); 
printf("拾"); 
xs(n); 
printf("元整"); 

printf("\n");

#include<stdio.h>
void xs(int a)
{
if(a==0) printf("零");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆");
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
int main()
{
while(1)
{
double i;
int j,k,m,n;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
j=(int)i%10000000%1000000%100000%10000/1000;
k=(int)i%1000/100;
m=(int)i%1000%100/10;
n=(int)i%1000%100%10;
if(i<1000&&i>=0)
{
xs(k);
printf("佰");
xs(m);
printf("拾");
xs(n);
printf("元整");
printf("\n");
}
}
}
return 0;
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{

{

if(s>0||s==0) 
{

int main()
{
double i;
int k,m,n;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
k=(int)i%1000/100;
m=(int)i%1000%100/10;
n=(int)i%1000%100%10;
if(i<1000&&i>=0)
{
xs(k);
printf("佰");
xs(m);
printf("拾");
xs(n);
printf("元整");
printf("\n");
}

}
return 0;
}

20190318026:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,d,x,z;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	d=a;
	if(d<b)d=b;
	if(d<c)d=c;
	x=a;
	if(x>b)x=b;
	if(x>c)x=c;
	z=a;
	if(z<=x)z=b;
	if(z>=d)z=b;
	if(z<=x)z=c;
	if(z>=d)z=c;
	printf("%c%c%c",x,z,d);
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,f,g,d,h;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&e,&f,&g);
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	h=f*f-4*e*g;
	if(d>0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		
	}
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(d==0)
	{
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);	
	}
	if(h<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(h>=0)
	{
		x3=(-f+sqrt(h))/(2*e);
		x4=(-f-sqrt(h))/(2*e);
	}
	
}

20190318046:Problem1158:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int t,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&t)!=EOF)
	{
		a=t/100;
		b=(t-100*a)/10;
		c=t-100*a-10*b;
	if(t%100==0)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	else
	{
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	}
}

main()
{
 int y=2019,m,d,a;
scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
if(m==1||m==2)
 {
 m+=12;
 y--;
 }
 a=(d+2*m+3*(m+1)/5+y+y/4-y/100+y/400)%7+1;
  if (a == 0) printf ("Sunday");
  if (a == 1) printf ("Monday");
  if (a == 2) printf ("Tuesday");
  if (a == 3) printf ("Wednesday");
  if (a == 4) printf ("Thursday");
  if (a == 5) printf ("Friday");

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{

char ch;
ch=getchar();
	if(ch>='a'&&ch<='z'||ch>='A'&&ch<='Z')
		printf("NO\n");
	else if(ch>='0'&&ch<='9')
		printf("YES\n");
	else
		printf("NO\n");
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
main()
{
  int a=2019,b,c,d,e;
  scanf("%d,%d",&b,&c);
  if(b <= 0 || b > 12)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c <= 0)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c >= 31)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 3: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 5: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 7: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 8: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 10:printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 12:printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if(c >= 30)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 4: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 6: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 9: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 11: printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if((a%4 == 0 && a%100 != 0) || (a%400 == 0))
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 29)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
  else
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 28)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335;
    break;
  }
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31 - 1;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60 - 1;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91 - 1;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121- 1;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152- 1;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182- 1;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213- 1;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244- 1;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274- 1;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305- 1;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335- 1;
    break;
   }
  }
  e = (a-1 + (a-1)/4 - (a-1)/100 + (a-1)/400 + d)%7;
  switch(e)
  {
   case 0: printf("Sunday\n");
         break;
   case 1: printf("Monduy\n");
   break;
   case 2: printf("Tuesday\n");
   break;
   case 3: printf("Wednesday\n");
   break;
   case 4: printf("Thursday\n");
   break;
   case 5: printf("Friday\n");
   break;
   case 6: printf("Saturday\n");
   break;
  }
 }

20190318050:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h> 
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) 
	{
	t=a;a=b;b=t;
	}
	if (a>c) 
	{
	t=a;a=c;c=t;
	}
	if (b>c) 
	{
	t=c;c=b;b=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f,disc1,disc2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		disc2=d*d-4*e*f;
	    	if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    	if(disc2<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	    x3=(-e+sqrt(disc2))/(2*d);
	    x4=(-e-sqrt(disc2))/(2*d);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
		}
	} 
 }

void xs(int a)
{

else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");

else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");

{

int k,m,n;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
k=(int)i%1000/100;
m=(int)i%1000%100/10;
n=(int)i%1000%100%10;
if(i<1000&&i>=100)
{

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {   
        char *m[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","零"};
        b=a/100;
        c=a/10%10;
        d=a%10;
        if(c==0&&d==0)
        printf("%s元整",m[b-1]);
        else if(c!=0&&d==0)
        printf("%s佰%s拾元整",m[b-1],m[c-1]);
        else if(c==0&&d!=0)
        printf("%s佰零%s元整",m[b-1],m[d-1]);
        else
        printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整",m[b-1],m[c-1],m[d-1]);
    }
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2;
    int d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

20190318174:Problem1114:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int month[]{31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int x,y,a,b,day;
	day=0; 
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(a=0;a<x-1;a++){
		day+=month[a];
	}
	day+=y;
	b=day%7;
	switch(b){
		case 0:printf("Monday"); break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday"); break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday"); break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday"); break;
		case 4:printf("Friday"); break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday"); break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday"); break;					
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301023:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, x, x1, x2, s;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF);	 
	s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	if (s<0) 
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	
	else{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1, x2);
}

20190318188:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

int main(void)
{
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		double delta;
		delta=b^2-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else
		{
			double x1,x2;
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b^2-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(b^2-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3Lf~~~%.3Lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

{

    {

        d=a%10;

        else if(c!=0&&d==0)
        printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",m[b-1],m[c-1]);
        else if(c==0&&d!=0)
        printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",m[b-1],m[d-1]);
        else
        printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",m[b-1],m[c-1],m[d-1]);
    }
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, s;
	double x1, x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF);	 
    s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	if (s<0) 
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	
	else{
	x1=(-b + sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b - sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n", x1, x2);
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
float a, b, c, x1, x2;
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/2*a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x,y;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
	if((b*b-4*a*c)>=0)
	{
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);
}
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f,disc1,disc2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		disc2=e*e-4*d*f;
	    	if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    	if(disc2<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	    x3=(-e+sqrt(disc2))/(2*d);
	    x4=(-e-sqrt(disc2))/(2*d);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
		}
	}

20190301012:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int day,month,sum,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	switch(month)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
	}
	sum=sum+day;
	y=(sum-1)%7;
	if(y==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(y==1)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Friday");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(y==5)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(y==6)
	printf("Monday");
}

main(int argc,char *argv[])

	char w[7][10]={"Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday","Monday"};
	if (x==1)
        y=y;
    if (x==2)
        y=31+y;
    if (x==3)
        y=31+28+y;
    if (x==4) 
        y=31+28+31+y;
    if (x==5)
        y=31+28+31+30+y;
    if (x==6)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==7)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+y;
    if (x==8)
        y=31+28+30+31+30+31+31+y;
    if (x==9) 
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y;
    if (x==10)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y;
    if (x==11)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==12)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y;

20190301023:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
 char a,b,c,t;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  t=a;
  a=b;
  b=t;
 }
 if(a>c)
 {
  t=a;
  a=c;
  c=t;
     }
    if(b>c)
     {
  t=c;
  c=b;
  b=t;
     }
     printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
     return 0;
}

	    D=b*b-4*a*c;

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0)
	{
		printf("L");
	}
	else
	{
		printf("N");
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301023:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>  
#include <string.h>  
  
void trans(int a)  
{  
    if(a == 1)printf("壹");  
  
    else if(a == 2)printf("贰");  
  
    else if(a == 3)printf("叁");  
  
    else if(a == 4)printf("肆");  
  
    else if(a == 5)printf("伍");  
  
    else if(a == 6)printf("陆");  
  
    else if(a == 7)printf("柒");  
  
    else if(a == 8)printf("捌");  
  
    else if(a == 9)printf("玖");  
  
    else if(a == 0)printf("零");  
  
}  
void weight(int i)  
{  
    if(i==1||i==5||i==9)  
        printf("拾");  
    if(i==2||i==6||i==10)  
        printf("佰");  
    if(i==3||i==7||i==11)  
        printf("仟");  
    if(i==4)  
        printf("万");  
    if(i==8)  
        printf("亿");  
    if(i==0)  
        printf("元整\n");  
}  
int main()  
{  
    while(1)  
    {  
        char a[10];  
        scanf("%s",a);  
        strrev(a);  
        for(int i=strlen(a) - 1; a[i]; i--)  
        {  
            trans(a[i]-'0');  
            weight(i);  
        }  
    }  
}

	#include<stdio.h>
	main() 
{ 
int a,b,c,d,e;
while(scanf("%d",&a) != EOF)
b=a/100;
c=(a/10)%10;
d=a%100%10;
switch(b)
{
	case 1:printf("Ò¼°Û");break;
	case 2:printf("·¡°Û");break;
	case 3:printf("Èþ°Û");break;
	case 4:printf("ËÁ°Û");break;
	case 5:printf("Îé°Û");break;
	case 6:printf("Â½°Û");break;
	case 7:printf("Æâ°Û");break;
	case 8:printf("°Æ°Û");break;
	case 9:printf("¾Á°Û");break; 
}
if (c==0&&d==0)
printf("ÔªÕû");
else
	{
	
	switch(c)
	{	
	case 1:printf("Ò¼Ê°");break;
	case 2:printf("·¡Ê°");break;
	case 3:printf("ÈþÊ°");break;
	case 4:printf("ËÁÊ°");break;
	case 5:printf("ÎéÊ°");break;
	case 6:printf("Â½Ê°");break;
	case 7:printf("ÆâÊ°");break;
	case 8:printf("°ÆÊ°");break;
	case 9:printf("¾ÁÊ°");break; 
	case 0:printf("Áã");break;
	}


	switch(d)
	{
	case 1:printf("Ò¼ÔªÕû");break;
	case 2:printf("·¡ÔªÕû");break;
	case 3:printf("ÈþÔªÕû");break;
	case 4:printf("ËÁÔªÕû");break;
	case 5:printf("ÎéÔªÕû");break;
	case 6:printf("Â½ÔªÕû");break;
	case 7:printf("ÆâÔªÕû");break;
	case 8:printf("°ÆÔªÕû");break;
	case 9:printf("¾ÁÔªÕû");break; 
	case 0:printf("ÔªÕû");break;
	}
}

20190301023:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>  
#include <string.h>  
void trans(int a)  
{  
    if(a == 1)printf("壹");  
    else if(a == 2)printf("贰"); 
    else if(a == 3)printf("叁"); 
    else if(a == 4)printf("肆"); 
    else if(a == 5)printf("伍"); 
    else if(a == 6)printf("陆"); 
    else if(a == 7)printf("柒"); 
    else if(a == 8)printf("捌"); 
    else if(a == 9)printf("玖"); 
    else if(a == 0)printf("零");
}  
void weight(int i)  
{  
    if(i==1||i==5||i==9) 
        printf("拾");
    if(i==2||i==6||i==10)  
        printf("佰");
    if(i==3||i==7||i==11)
        printf("仟"); 
    if(i==4) 
        printf("万");
    if(i==8)
        printf("亿");
    if(i==0)
        printf("元整\n"); 
} 
main()
{ 
    while(1)  
    {
        char a[10];  
        scanf("%s",a); 
        strrev(a);
        for(int i=strlen(a) - 1; a[i]; i--)
        {
            trans(a[i]-'0');
            weight(i); 
        }
    }
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,a,b,c;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    if(x==1)
        a=y-1;
    else if(x==2)
        a=30+y;
    else if(x==3)
        a=30+28+y;
    else if(x==4)
        a=30+28+31+y;
    else if(x==5)
        a=30+28+31+30+y;
    else if(x==6)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+y;
    else if(x==7)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+y;
    else if(x==8)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+y;
    else if(x==9)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y;
    else if(x==10)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+30+30+y;
    else if(x==11)
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+30+30+31+y;
    else
        a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+30+30+31+30+y;
        b=a%7;
        c=(2+b)%7;
        if(c==1)
            printf("Monday");
        else if(c==2)
            printf("Tuesday");
        else if(c==3)
            printf("Wednesday");
        else if(c==4)
            printf("Thursday");
        else if(c==5)
            printf("Friday");
        else if(c==6)
            printf("Saturday");
        else
            printf("Sunday");
    return 0;
}

20190318109:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	x=getchar();
	y=getchar();
	z=getchar();
	if (x>y)
	{
		if(y>z)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
		}
		else if (x>z)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",y,z,x);
		}
		else if (z>x)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",y,x,z);
		}
	}
	if (x<y)
	{
		if (x>z)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
		}
		else if (y>z)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",x,z,y);
		}
		else if (y<z)
		{
			printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190302002:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,t;
    scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
    t=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
    if(t>=0)
    {
        x1=(-b+t)/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+t)/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }
    else
    {
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318037:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f,disc1;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    
	}

 }

#include<stdio.h>
//2019年1月1日是星期二，2019年x月y日是星期几

main()
{
	int x,y;
	int a,b;
	int c;
	int m;
	int z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	b=y-1;
	if(x==2){c=30;
	}
	if(x==3){c=58;
	}
	if(x==4){c=89;
	}
	if(x==5){c=119;
	}
	if(x==6){c=150;
	}
	if(x==7){c=180;
	}
	if(x==8){c=211;
	}
	if(x==9){c=242;
	}
	if(x==10){c=272;
	}
	if(x==11){c=303;
	}
	if(x==12){c=333;
	}
	m=c+b;
	z=m%7;
	switch(z)
	
	{
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	}
	
}

	#include<stdio.h>
	main() 
{ 
int a,b,c,d,e;
while(scanf("%d",&a) != EOF)
b=a/100;
c=(a/10)%10;
d=a%100%10;
switch(b)
{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break; 
}
if (c==0&&d==0)
printf("元整");
else
	{
	
	switch(c)
	{	
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
	case 0:printf("零");break;
	}


	switch(d)
	{
	case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
	case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
	case 3:printf("叁元整");break;
	case 4:printf("肆元整");break;
	case 5:printf("伍元整");break;
	case 6:printf("陆元整");break;
	case 7:printf("柒元整");break;
	case 8:printf("捌元整");break;
	case 9:printf("玖元整");break; 
	case 0:printf("元整");break;
	}
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
	x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
    if ((b*b-4*a*c)<0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    else
    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
    }
}

20190302020:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	if(a%100==0){
		b=a;
		if(b%400==0){
			printf("L");
		}
		else{
			printf("N");
		}
	}
	else{
		if(a%4==0){
			printf("L");
		}
		else{
			printf("N");
		}
	}
}

	main() 
{ 
int a,b,c,d,e;
while(scanf("%d",&a) != EOF)
b=a/100;
c=(a/10)%10;
d=a%100%10;
switch(b)
{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break; 
}
if (c==0&&d==0)
printf("元整\n");
else
	{
	
	switch(c)
	{	
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
	case 0:printf("零");break;
	}


	switch(d)
	{
	case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
	case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
	case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
	case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
	case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
	case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
	case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
	case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break; 
	case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
	}
}
}

20190301045:Problem1158:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>

main()
{
int x,k,m,n;
while(scanf("%d",&x)){
    k=x/100;
    m=x/10%10;
    n=x%10;
    int dx(int a)
   {
   if(a==0) printf("零");
   if(a==1) printf("壹");
   if(a==2) printf("贰");
   if(a==3) printf("叁");
   if(a==4) printf("肆");
   if(a==5) printf("伍");
   if(a==6) printf("陆");
   if(a==7) printf("柒");
   if(a==8) printf("捌");
   if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
    if(m!=0&&n!=0){
        dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        printf("拾");
        dx(n);
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(n==0&&m!=0){
        dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        printf("拾");
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(m==0&&n==0){
	    dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        printf("元整\n");
    }
    if(m==0&&n!=0){
    	dx(k);
        printf("佰");
        dx(m);
        dx(n);
        printf("元整\n");
	}
}
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,i=0;
	double x,y;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
		
	
		
	x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
}

20190318064:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	int t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
    if(x>y)
    {
	t=x;
    x=y;
    y=t;
    }
    if(z<y&&z>x)
	{
		t=y;
		y=z;
		z=t;
	}
	if(z<x)printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
	else printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
}

20190318084:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, s;
	double x1, x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF);
	{	 
        s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	      if (s<0) 
	         printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	      else
	      {
	       x1=(-b + sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	       x2=(-b - sqrt(s))/(2*a);
        	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n", x1, x2);
          }
    }
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z,h;
    double x1,x2;   
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)	
	{z=b*b-4*a*c; 
	if(z<0)
 	{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}  
	else	
	{
	  h=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
 	  x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	  x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
      printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
#include<string.h>
main()
{
	int n;
	int a,b,c;
	char *s2[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};;
	char *s1[100]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};;
	while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF){
		a=n/100;
		b=(n-a*100)/10;
		c=n%10;
		if(c==0 && b==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",s1[a-1]);
		else if(c==0&&b!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",s1[a-1],s2[b]);
		if(c!=0&&b==0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",s1[a-1],s1[c-1]);
		if(c!=0&&b!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",s1[a-1],s2[b],s1[c-1]);
	}
}

#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z;
    double x1,x2,h;   
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)	
	{
	z=b*b-4*a*c; 
	if(z<0)
 	printf("NO SOLUTION\n"); 
	else	
	{
	  h=sqrt(z);
 	  x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	  x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
      printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}

20190318106:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,A,B,C;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	A=a;
	if(a>b)
	B=b;
	else
	{
		A=b;
		B=a;
	}
	if(c<B)
	C=c;
	else
	{
		if(c>A)
		{
		    C=B;
	    	B=A;
	    	A=c;	
		}
		else
		{
			C=B;
	    	B=c;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",C,B,A);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
#include<string.h>
main()
{
	int n;
	int a,b,c;
	char *s2[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};;
	char *s1[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};;
	while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF){
		a=n/100;
		b=(n-a*100)/10;
		c=n%10;
		if(c==0 && b==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",s1[a-1]);
		else if(c==0&&b!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",s1[a-1],s2[b-1]);
		else if(c!=0&&b==0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",s1[a-1],s1[c-1]);
		else if(c!=0&&b!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",s1[a-1],s2[b-1],s1[c-1]);
	}
}

20190318028:Problem1114:正确
#include<time.h>
#include<string.h> 
main()
{
int a,b;
scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
char*arr[]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
struct tm info;
memset(&info,0,sizeof(info));
info.tm_year=119;
info.tm_mon=a-1;
info.tm_mday=b;
mktime(&info);
printf("%s",arr[info.tm_wday]);
}

20190302020:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	int one,two,three;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	if(x>y&&x>z){
		three=x;
		if(z>y){
			two=z;
			one=y;
		}
		else{
			two=y;
			one=z;
		}
	}
	if(z>y&&z>x){
		three=z;
		if(x>y){
			two=x;
			one=y;
		}
		else{
			two=y;
			one=x;
		}
	}
	if(y>x&&y>z){
		three=y;
		if(z>x){
			two=z;
			one=x;
		}
		else{
			two=x;
			one=z;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",one,two,three);
}

20190301051:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
	if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double disc,x1,x2;
	double d,e;
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
   {
	 if(disc>=0)
	{
	  d=(-b)/(2.0*a);
    	e=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
    	x1=d-e;
    	x2=d+e;
    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	
    }
}

{
	int a,b,c;

	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(disc)/(2*a));

	int a,b,c,z,t,t1,a1,b1,c1;
	scanf("%d%d%d\n",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	t=b*b-4*a*c;
	t1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	x1=(-b-sqrt(t))/2*a;
	x2=(-b+sqrt(t))/2*a;
	x3=(-b1-sqrt(t1))/2*a1;
	x4=(-b1+sqrt(t1))/2*a1;
	if(t<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
	if(t1<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x4,x3);
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190318050:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

int main(void)
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,disc;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

main()
{
	int A,B,C,x;
	char *a[]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while (scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	A=x/100;
	C=x%10;
	B=x%100/10;
	if(B==0){if(C==0)printf("%s佰元整",a[A]);else printf("%s佰零%s元整",a[A],a[C]);}
	else if(C==0)printf("%s佰%s拾元整",a[A],a[B]);
	else printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整",a[A],a[B],a[C]);
}}

main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:c=0;break;
		case 2:c=31;break;
		case 3:c=59;break;
		case 4:c=90;break;
		case 5:c=120;break;
		case 6:c=151;break;
		case 7:c=181;break;
		case 8:c=212;break;
		case 9:c=243;break;
		case 10:c=273;break;
		case 11:c=304;break;
		case 12:c=334;break;	
	}
	int d;
	d=(b+c-1)%7;
	switch(d)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
	}

main()
{
	int d,m,s,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:s=0;break;
		case 2:s=31;break;
		case 3:s=59;break;
		case 4:s=90;break;
		case 5:s=120;break;
		case 6:s=151;break;
		case 7:s=181;break;
		case 8:s=212;break;
		case 9:s=243;break;
		case 10:s=273;break;
		case 11:s=304;break;
		case 12:s=334;break;
	}
	s=s+d;
	y=(s-1)%7;
	if(y==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(y==1)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Friday");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(y==5)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(y==6)
	printf("Monday");

#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,A,B,C;
	float x1,x2,y1,y2,d1,d2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&A,&B,&C)!=EOF)
	{
		d1=b*b-4*a*c;
		d2=B*B-4*A*C;
		{   
		    if(d1>=0){
		    	x1=(-b+sqrt(d1))/(2*a);
			    x2=(-b-sqrt(d1))/(2*a);
			    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			}
			else
			    printf("NO SOLUTION");
		    if(d2>=0){
				y1=(-B+sqrt(d2))/(2*A);
				y2=(-B-sqrt(d2))/(2*A);
				printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",y1,y2);
			}
			else
			    printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
	}
	return 0; 
}

		else{

20190301045:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,n,m,t;
	char *a[]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	char *b[]={"元","整","佰","拾"};
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
		n=x/100;
		m=x/10%10;
		t=x%10;
		if(m!=0&&t!=0){
			printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",a[n],a[m],a[t]); 
		}
		if(m==0&&t!=0){
			printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",a[n],a[t]);
		}
	if(m!=0&&t==0){
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",a[n],a[m]);
	}
	if(m==0&&t==0){
		printf("%s佰元整\n",a[n]);
	}
}
}

20190301048:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,A,B,C;
	float x1,x2,y1,y2,d1,d2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&A,&B,&C)!=EOF)
	{
		{
			if(a!=0)
		{
		    d1=b*b-4*a*c;
		    if(d1>=0){
		    	x1=(-b+sqrt(d1))/(2*a);
			    x2=(-b-sqrt(d1))/(2*a);
			    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			}
			else
			    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
	    else
	        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
			if(A!=0)
		{
		    d2=B*B-4*A*C;
			if(d2>=0){
				y1=(-B+sqrt(d2))/(2*A);
				y2=(-B-sqrt(d2))/(2*A);
				printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",y1,y2);
			}
			else
			    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
	    else
	        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0; 
}

20190302045:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
    int x,y,day,day1;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    switch(x)
    {case 1:day=y;break;
    case 2:day=31+y;break;
    case 3:day=59+y;break;
    case 4:day=90+y;break;
    case 5:day=120+y;break;
    case 6:day=151+y;break;
    case 7:day=181+y;break;
    case 8:day=212+y;break;
    case 9:day=243+y;break;
    case 10:day=273+y;break;
    case 11:day=304+y;break;
    case 12:day=334+y;break;
	}
	day1=day%7;
	if(day1==1){printf("Tuesday");}
	else if(day1==2){printf("Wednesday");}
	else if(day1==3){printf("Thursday");}
	else if(day1==4){printf("Friday");}
	else if(day1==5){printf("Saturday");}
	else if(day1==6){printf("Sunday");}
	else if(day1==0){printf("Monday");}	
}

20190318050:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
void trans(int a)
{
    if(a == 1)printf("壹");
    else if(a == 2)printf("贰");
    else if(a == 3)printf("叁");
    else if(a == 4)printf("肆");
    else if(a == 5)printf("伍");
	else if(a == 6)printf("陆");
    else if(a == 7)printf("柒");
    else if(a == 8)printf("捌");
    else if(a == 9)printf("玖");
	else if(a == 0)printf("零");
}
void weight(int i)
{
    if(i==1||i==5||i==9)
      printf("拾");
    if(i==2||i==6||i==10)
        printf("佰");
    if(i==3||i==7||i==11)
        printf("仟");
    if(i==4)
        printf("万");
    if(i==8)
        printf("亿");
    if(i==0)        
		printf("元整\n");
}
int main()
{
	while(1)
	{
		char a[10];
		while(scanf("%s",a)!=EOF);
		strrev(a);
		for(int i=strlen(a) - 1; a[i]; i--)
		{
			trans(a[i]-'0');
			weight(i);
		}
	}
}

20190318050:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
main()
{
	int t,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&t)!=EOF)
	{
		a=t/100;
		b=(t-100*a)/10;
		c=t-100*a-10*b;
	if(t%100==0)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	else
	{
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	}
}

printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);

printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);

20190318106:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2,k;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-a*c*4;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			k=sqrt(delta);
			x1=(-b+k)/a*2;
			x2=(-b-k)/a*2;
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
	while
	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;

	if (delta>=0)
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
 }
 
 }

20190318101:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	if(a>c){t=a;a=c;c=t;} 
	if(b>c){t=c;c=b;b=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);	}
    }
 } 
 /*题目描述
   求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。 
   输入
   有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
   输出
   如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
   如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
   样例输入 
   1 -2 1
   1 1 2
   样例输出	
   1.000~~~1.000
   NO SOLUTION */
------------------------------------------------------

int main()
{
	int a;
	
	scanf("%d",&a);
	
	if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0){
		printf("L\n");
	}else{
		if(a%400==0){
			printf("L\n");
		}else{
			if(a%4==0&&a%100==0){
				printf("L\n");
			}else{
				printf("N\n");
			}
		}
	}
}

{

	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
		else printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}

20190318149:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{char a,b,c;
char max,min,middle;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
max=(a>b?a:b)>c?(a>b?a:b):c;
min=(a<b?a:b)<c?(a<b?a:b):c;
middle=a+b+c-max-min;
printf("%c%c%c\n",min,middle,max); 
}

    while( scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
   
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
    }
	else
	{
     x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a)	;
	 x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a)	;
     printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2); 
    }
    
}
}

#include "stdio.h"
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
	if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,m,n,y,t1,t2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c,&m,&n,&y)!=EOF)//读多组数据
	{
		t1=b*b-4*a*c;
		t2=n*n-4*m*y; 
		if(t1<0)
		{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
		else
		{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(t1))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(t1))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
		if(t2<0)
		{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
		else
		{
		x3=(-b+sqrt(t2))/(2*a);
		x4=(-b-sqrt(t2))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

	{
		t=a;a=b;b=t;
	}
	if (a>c) 
	{
		t=a;a=c;c=t;
	}

20190318155:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>

main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    char max,mid,min;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a>b)
      {max=a;min=b;}
    else
      {max=b;min=a;}
    if(max<c)
      max=c;
    else 
      if(min>c)
    min=c;   
    if(a!=max&&a!=min)
      mid=a;
    if(b!=max&&b!=min)
      mid=b;
    if(c!=max&&c!=min)
      mid=c;
    printf("%c%c%c",min,mid,max);    
}

20190318063:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a<b&&b<c){printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);}
    if(a<c&&b>c){printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);}
    if(a>b&&a<c){printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);}
    if(a>c&&b<c){printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);}
    if(a>b&&b>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);}
    if(a<b&&a>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int c[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int m,d,sum=0,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	for(i=0;i<m;i++)
	{
	  sum+=c[i];
	}
	sum=(sum+d+2-1)%7;
	if(sum==0)printf("Sunday");
	if(sum==1)printf("Monday");
	if(sum==2)printf("Tuesday");
	if(sum==3)printf("Wednesday");
	if(sum==4)printf("Thursday");
	if(sum==5)printf("Friday");
	if(sum==6)printf("Saturday"); 
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    int x,y,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x){
		case 1:z=y%7;break;
		case 2:z=(y+31)%7;break;
		case 3:z=(y+59)%7;break;
		case 4:z=(y+90)%7;break;
		case 5:z=(y+120)%7;break;
		case 6:z=(y+151)%7;break;
		case 7:z=(y+181)%7;break;
		case 8:z=(y+212)%7;break;
		case 9:z=(y+243)%7;break;
		case 10:z=(y+273)%7;break;
		case 11:z=(y+304)%7;break;
		case 12:z=(y+334)%7;break;
	}
	switch(z){
		case 0:printf("Monday");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday");break;

#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int x,y;
	int count,date;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
	case 1:
		count=y-1;	
		break;
	case 2:
		count=31+y-1;
		break;
	case 3:
		count=59+y-1;
		break;
	case 4:
		count=90+y-1;
		break;
	case 5:
		count=120+y-1;
		break;
	case 6:
		count=151+y-1;
		break;	
	case 7:
		count=181+y-1;
		break;	
	case 8:
		count=212+y-1;
		break;
	case 9:
		count=243+y-1;
		break;
	case 10:
		count=273+y-1;
		break;
	case 11:
		count=304+y-1;
		break;
	case 12:
		count=334+y-1;
		break;
    }
	date=(count%7)+2;
	switch(date)
	{
	case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
	case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
	case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
	case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
	case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
	case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;
	case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		
	}
 } 
 /*题目描述
   2019年1月1日是星期二，2019年x月y日是星期几。（0<x<13,0<y<32,请根据具体月份给出真实的日期y值）
   输入
   整数月 x, 日 y
   输出
   输出星期几，用英文输出。 
  Monday，Tuesday，Tuesday，Thursday，Friday，Saturday ，Sunday  */

	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/2*a;
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}

20190318080:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,max,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b){max=a,min=b;};
	if (a<b){max=b,min=a;};
	if(c>max){max=c;};
    if(c<min){min=c;};
    b=a+b+c-max-min;
    printf("%c%c%c",min,b,max);	
}

	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;

		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;

	{

	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);

20190301003:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
	int y=2019, m, d, c, w;
	scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
	c=y/100;
	y=y-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
	while (w<0)w+=7;
	w%=7;
	if (w==0) printf ("Sunday\n");
	if (w==1) printf ("Monday\n");
	if (w==3) printf ("Wednesday\n");
	if (w==2) printf ("Tuesday\n");
	if (w==4) printf ("Thursday\n");
	if (w==5) printf ("Friday\n");
	if (w==6) printf ("Saturday\n");
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
int year;
scanf("%d",&year);
if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
printf("L\n");
else if(year%400==0)
printf("L\n");
else
printf("N\n");
return 0;
}

20190301052:Problem1034:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char c;
	while(scanf("%c",&c)!=EOF)
	{
		getchar();
		if(c>='0'&&c<='9')
		printf("YES\n");
		else if(c>='a'&&c<='z'||c>='A'&&c<='Z')
		printf("NO\n");
		else printf("NO\n");
	}
	
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190302023:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%f,%f,%f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302022:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
    if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
    if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190301026:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
//输入多组数字人民币，范围100~~999 
//输出大写数字汉字 
//123，400,560，708,999
char *money(int n);
int main()
{
	int data;
	int  B,S,G;
	char b,s,g;
	 
	while(scanf("%d",&data) != EOF)
	{
		B=data/100;
		G=data%10;
		S=(data-B*100-G)/10;
		
		//B！=0
		//G=0，不会输出这个位的数
		//S=0，会输出零 
		if((!S) && (!G) ){//100
			printf("%s佰元整\n",money(B));
			
		}
		else if(!S) {//708
		
			printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",money(B),money(S),money(G));
		}
		else if(!G){//560
		
			printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money(B),money(S)); 
		}
		 
		else{//123
		printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",money(B),money(S),money(G));
		}
	}
	
	
	return 0;
}
char *money(int n)
{
	char *name[]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","拾","佰"};
	return name[n];
}

20190301052:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%100!=0&&year%4==0||year%400==0)
	{
	printf("L");
	}
	else
	{
	printf("N");
	}
}

20190318063:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
void kx(int a)
{
if(a==0) printf("");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆");
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
main()
{
double i;
int k,m,n;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
k=(int)i/100;
m=(int)i%100/10;
n=(int)i%100%10;	
kx(k);
printf("佰");
kx(m);
if(m!=0){
printf("拾");}
if(n!=0&&m==0){
printf("零");} 
kx(n);
printf("元整\n");
}
}

20190318158:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
char d;
char r,w,x;
scanf("%c %c %c",&r,&w,&x);
if(r>w)
{
d=r;
r=w;
w=d;
}
if(r>x)
{
d=r;
r=x;
x=d;
}
if(w>x)
{
d=w;
w=x;
x=d;
}
printf("%c%c%c",r,w,x);
return 0;
}

20190301052:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
	t=a;
	a=b;
	b=t;
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
	t=a;
	a=c;
	c=t;
	}
	if(b>c)
    {
    t=b;
	b=c;
	c=t;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 }

20190318109:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	double n,m;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
    	if (b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		{
			n=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
            m=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",n,m);   
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
    }  
          

	return 0;
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	double n,m;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
    	if (b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		{
			n=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
            m=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",n,m);   
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
    }          
	return 0;	
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,a1,b1,c1,d1;
	double x1,x2,y1,y2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	x1=(-1*b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-1*b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    y1=(-1*b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	y2=(-1*b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	if (d>=0&&d1<0){
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
     }
    else if(d>=0&&d1>=0){
    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
   		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",y1,y2);
	}
	else if(d<0&&d1>=0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",y1,y2);}
	else {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int r,w,x,l,m,n;
scanf("%d %d %d",&r, &w, &x);
m=-w/2*r;
double x1,x2;
l=w*w-4*r*x;
n=sqrt(l)/(2*r);
x1=m+n;
x2=m-n;
if(l<0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else if(l>=0)
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    return 0;
}

else if(a==6) printf("Â½");

{

int q,w,e;
while( scanf("%lf" ,&d)!=EOF){
k=(int)d/100;
m=(int)d%100/10;
n=(int)d%100%10;
kx(q);
printf("°Û");
kx(w);
if(w!=0){
printf("Ê°");}
if(e!=0&&w==0){
printf("Áã");}
kx(e);
printf("ÔªÕû\n");
}

20190318145:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(b<a)
	{
		t=b;
		b=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(c<a)
	{
		t=c;
		c=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(c<b)
	{
		t=c;
		c=b;
		b=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,x;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){x=a;a=b;b=x;
	}if(a>c){x=a;a=c;c=x;
	}if(b>c){x=c;c=b;b=x;
	}printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);

20190318199:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char X,Y,Z,MAX;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&X,&Y,&Z);
	if(X<Y)
		{
			MAX=X;
			X=Y;
			Y=MAX;
		}
	if(X<Z)
		{
			MAX=X;
			X=Z;
			Z=MAX;
		}
	if(Y<Z)
		{
			MAX=Y;
			Y=Z;
			Z=MAX;
		}
	printf("%c%c%c",Z,Y,X);
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int year,leap;
scanf("%d",&year);
if((year%4==0&&year%100!=0)||year%400==0)
leap=1;
else
leap=0;
if(leap)      
printf("L",year);
else
printf("N ",year);

return 0;
}

20190318136:Problem1158:运行错误
#include<stdio.h>

main()
{
	int a,b,c,d; 
	
	while 
	(scanf("%ld%ld%ld",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
    	switch(a)
		{   case 1:  printf("壹佰");break;
		    case 2:  printf("贰佰");break;
		    case 3:  printf("叁佰");break;   
		    case 4:  printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:  printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:  printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:  printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:  printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:  printf("玖佰");break;
		} 
		switch(b)
		{  case 0:{
		         if(b==0)
		           {printf("");break;} 
		         else 
		            printf("零");break;
				   }
		   case 1:  printf("壹拾");break;
		   case 2:  printf("贰拾");break;
		   case 3:  printf("叁拾");break;
		   case 4:  printf("肆拾");break;
		   case 5:  printf("伍拾");break;
		   case 6:  printf("陆拾");break;
		   case 7:  printf("柒拾");break;
		   case 8:  printf("捌拾");break;
		   case 9:  printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
          case 0:  printf("元整")  ;break;
		  case 1:  printf("壹元整");break;
          case 2:  printf("贰元整");break;
		  case 3:  printf("叁元整");break;
		  case 4:  printf("肆元整");break;
		  case 5:  printf("伍元整");break;
		  case 6:  printf("陆元整");break;
		  case 7:  printf("柒元整");break;
		  case 8:  printf("捌元整");break;
		  case 9:  printf("玖元整");break; 		
		}
	}
}

 printf("L\n");
 else if(b==0,c==0,d!=0)
 printf("F\n");
 else if(d==0)
 printf("L\n");
}

20190302023:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%f,%f,%f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318157:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
    char zm1,zm2,zm3;
    int a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&zm1,&zm2,&zm3);
    a=zm1;
    b=zm2;
    c=zm3;
    if(a>b&&b>c)printf("%c%c%c",zm3,zm2,zm1);
    if(b>a&&a>c)printf("%c%c%c",zm3,zm1,zm2);
    if(a>c&&c>b)printf("%c%c%c",zm2,zm3,zm1);
    if(c>a&&a>b)printf("%c%c%c",zm2,zm1,zm3);
    if(b>c&&c>a)printf("%c%c%c",zm1,zm3,zm2);
    if(c>b&&b>a)printf("%c%c%c",zm1,zm2,zm3);
    
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>

main()
{
	int a,b,c,d; 
	
	while 
	(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
    	switch(a)
		{   case 1:  printf("壹佰");break;
		    case 2:  printf("贰佰");break;
		    case 3:  printf("叁佰");break;   
		    case 4:  printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:  printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:  printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:  printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:  printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:  printf("玖佰");break;
		} 
		switch(b)
		{  case 0:
		         if(b==0)
		            printf(""); 
		         else 
		            printf("零");break;
				   
		   case 1:  printf("壹拾");break;
		   case 2:  printf("贰拾");break;
		   case 3:  printf("叁拾");break;
		   case 4:  printf("肆拾");break;
		   case 5:  printf("伍拾");break;
		   case 6:  printf("陆拾");break;
		   case 7:  printf("柒拾");break;
		   case 8:  printf("捌拾");break;
		   case 9:  printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
          case 0:  printf("元整")  ;break;
		  case 1:  printf("壹元整");break;
          case 2:  printf("贰元整");break;
		  case 3:  printf("叁元整");break;
		  case 4:  printf("肆元整");break;
		  case 5:  printf("伍元整");break;
		  case 6:  printf("陆元整");break;
		  case 7:  printf("柒元整");break;
		  case 8:  printf("捌元整");break;
		  case 9:  printf("玖元整");break; 		
		}
	}
}

20190318199:Problem1147:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c))
		{
			d=b*b-4*a*c;
			if(d<0)	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
			else if(d>=0)	{x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2.000*a);
							x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2.000*a);
							printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
						    }
		}
	
}

20190318175:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318175:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>

main()
{

	while 
	(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
    {
    	switch(a)
		{   case 1:  printf("壹佰");break;
		    case 2:  printf("贰佰");break;
		    case 3:  printf("叁佰");break;   
		    case 4:  printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:  printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:  printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:  printf("柒佰");break;

			case 9:  printf("玖佰");break;

		switch(b)
		{  case 0:
		         if(b==0)
		            printf(""); 
		         else 
		            printf("零");break;
				   
		   case 1:  printf("壹拾");break;
		   case 2:  printf("贰拾");break;
		   case 3:  printf("叁拾");break;
		   case 4:  printf("肆拾");break;
		   case 5:  printf("伍拾");break;
		   case 6:  printf("陆拾");break;
		   case 7:  printf("柒拾");break;
		   case 8:  printf("捌拾");break;
		   case 9:  printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
          case 0:  printf("元整\n")  ;break;
		  case 1:  printf("壹元整\n");break;
          case 2:  printf("贰元整\n");break;

20190318145:Problem1147:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	int delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=0)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			x1=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
  int a=2019,b,c,d,s;
  scanf("%d,%d",&b,&c);
  if(b <= 0 || b > 12)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c <= 0)
  {
   printf("wrong");
  }
  if(c >= 31)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 3: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 5: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 7: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 8: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 10:printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 12:printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if(c >= 30)
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 4: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 6: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 9: printf("wrong");
    break;
    case 11: printf("wrong");
    break;
   }
  }
  if((a%4 == 0 && a%100 != 0) || (a%400 == 0))
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 29)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
  else
  {
   if(b == 2)
   {
    if(c >= 28)
    {
    printf("wrong");
    }
   }
  }
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335;
    break;
  }
  {
   switch(b)
   {
    case 1: d = c;
    break;
    case 2: d = c + 31 - 1;
    break;
    case 3: d = c + 60 - 1;
    break;
    case 4: d = c + 91 - 1;
    break;
    case 5: d = c + 121- 1;
    break;
    case 6: d = c + 152- 1;
    break;
    case 7: d = c + 182- 1;
    break;
    case 8: d = c + 213- 1;
    break;
    case 9: d = c + 244- 1;
    break;
    case 10:d = c + 274- 1;
    break;
    case 11:d = c + 305- 1;
    break;
    case 12:d = c + 335- 1;
    break;
   }
  }
  s = (a-1 + (a-1)/4 - (a-1)/100 + (a-1)/400 + d)%7;
  switch(s)
  {
   case 0: printf("Sunday\n");
         break;
   case 1: printf("Monduy\n");
   break;
   case 2: printf("Tuesday\n");
   break;
   case 3: printf("Wednesday\n");
   break;
   case 4: printf("Thursday\n");
   break;
   case 5: printf("Friday\n");
   break;

main()
{
	int x,y,week,day;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
		{case 1:day=y-1;break;
		 case 2:day=31+y-1;break;
		 case 3:day=59+y-1;break;
		 case 4:day=90+y-1;break;
		 case 5:day=120+y-1;break;
		 case 6:day=151+y-1;break;
		 case 7:day=181+y-1;break;
		 case 8:day=212+y-1;break;
		 case 9:day=243+y-1;break;
		 case 10:day=273+y-1;break;
		 case 11:day=304+y-1;break;
		 case 12:day=334+y-1;break;
		}
	
	switch(day%7)
		{case 0:printf("Tuthday");break;
		 case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		 case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		 case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		 case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		 case 5:printf("Sunday");break;

		}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
int main()
{    
    int a,b,c;
	int delta;
	double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
    {   
    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0)
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
    return 0;
}

20190302025:Problem1147:答案错误
/*求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。 
有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。
2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。*/
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	int j;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
	    j=(int)sqrt((double)b*b-4*a*c);
	if (j>=0){
		x1=(-b+j)/(a*2);
		x2=(-b-j)/(a*2);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);} 
	else 
		{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");} 
		
 }return 0; 
 }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	d = b*b-4*a*c;
	if (d<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		return 0;
	}
	double x1=-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	double x2=-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	printf("%4.3f~~~%4.3f\n",x1/2*a,x2/2*a);
	return 0;
}

20190302002:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main(){
    int month[]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
    char *week[8]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
    int x,y,sum=0,temp,i;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(i=1;i<x;i++){
        sum+=month[i-1];
    }
    temp=(sum+y)%7;
    printf("%s",week[temp]);
    return 0;
}

20190302002:Problem1147:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main(){
    double a,b,c,dis,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)){
        dis=b*b-4*a*c;
        if (a==0) {
            if(b==0){
                if(c==0){
                    printf("0.000~~~0.000\n");
                }else{
                    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
                }
            }else{
                printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-c/b,-c/b);
            }
        }else if(dis==0){
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-b/(a*2.0),-b/(a*2.0));
        }else if(dis>0){
            x1=((-b)+sqrt(dis))/(2.0*a);
            x2=((-b)-sqrt(dis))/(2.0*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }else {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
    }
    return 0;
}

#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,e,f,g,disc,x1,x2,d,t;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
     scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&e,&f,&g);
    t=a;a=t;a=e;
    t=b;b=t;b=f;
    t=c;c=t;c=g;
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
      printf("NO SOLUTION");
     else
      d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
       x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
       x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
       printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x1,x2);

/*	壹（1）、贰（2）、叁（3）、肆（4）、伍（5）、陆（6）、柒（7）、捌（8）、玖（9）、拾（10）、
    题目描述
    输入一个三位数的整数（100至999）输出这个数的人民币大写。
    输入
    输入100至999的整数。
    输出
    人民币大写。可能有多组数据。
    样例输入 
    123
    400
    560
    708
    999
    样例输出	
    壹佰贰拾叁元整
    肆佰元整
    伍佰陆拾元整 
    柒佰零捌元整
    玖佰玖拾玖元整*/

20190318148:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF)
	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
		{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else {
		
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
             }
		 
	}return 0;
}

20190302025:Problem1147:正确
/*求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。 
有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。
2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。*/
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double j,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
	    j=b*b-4*a*c;
	if (j>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(j))/(a*2);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(j))/(a*2);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);} 
		//1.000~~~1.000
	else 
		{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");} 
		
 }return 0; 
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,e,f,g,disc,x1,x2,d,t;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
     scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&e,&f,&g);
    t=a;a=t;a=e;
    t=b;b=t;b=f;
    t=c;c=t;c=g;
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
      printf("NO SOLUTION");
     else
      d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
       x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
       x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
       printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf",x1,x2);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double h,x,y;
	double d,e;
	h=b*b-4*a*c;
	while
	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF)
    {
	if(h>=0)
    {
     x=((-b)+sqrt(h))/2*a;
     y=((-b)-sqrt(h))/2*a; 
    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);
	}
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
}

/*输入一个三位数的整数（100至999）输出这个数的人民币大写。
 壹 贰 叁 肆 伍 陆 柒 捌 玖 拾 佰 仟 万 亿 零 */
#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
	int rmb,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&rmb)!=EOF){
		a=rmb/100;b=(rmb%100)/10;c=(rmb%100)%10;
		switch (a)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹佰");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰佰");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁佰");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆佰");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍佰");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆佰");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒佰");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌佰");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖佰");
				break;
		}
		switch (b)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹拾");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰拾");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁拾");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆拾");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍拾");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆拾");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒拾");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌拾");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖拾");
				break;
		}if (b==0&&c!=0)
		{printf("零");}
		if (b==0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		if (b!=0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		else{
		switch (c)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹元整\n");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰元整\n");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁元整\n");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆元整\n");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍元整\n");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆元整\n");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒元整\n");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌元整\n");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖元整\n");
				break;	 
	}
    }
	}return 0;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double h,x,y;
	while
	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF)
    {
	if(h=b*b-4*a*c,h>=0)
    {
    
     x=((-b)+sqrt(h))/2*a;
     y=((-b)-sqrt(h))/2*a; 
    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);
	}
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
}

main()
{

	scanf("%d",&year);
	a=year%4;
	b=year%100;

	if((a==0&&b!=0)||c==0) 
	printf("L");
	else
	printf("N");
}

20190318145:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,day=0,xq;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:day=0;break;
		case 2:day=31;break;
		case 3:day=59;break;
		case 4:day=90;break;
		case 5:day=120;break;
		case 6:day=151;break;
		case 7:day=181;break;
		case 8:day=212;break;
		case 9:day=243;break;
		case 10:day=273;break;
		case 11:day=304;break;
		case 12:day=334;break;
	}
	day+=y;
	xq=day%7+1;
	switch(xq)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 7:printf("Sunday ");break;
	}	
}

20190318048:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a > b)
{
t = a;
a = b;
b = t;
}
if(a > c)
{
t = a;
a = c;
c = t;
}
if(b > c)
{
t = b;
b = c;
c = t;
}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,g,s,b;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
	b=x/100;
	s=(x%100)/10;
	g=x%10;
	switch(b){
		      case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			  case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			  case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			  case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			  case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			  case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			  case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			  case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			  case 9:printf("玖佰");break; 
        	};
	if(g!=0) 
	{
	switch(s){
		                case 0:printf("零");break;
		                case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		                case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		                case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		                case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		                case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		                case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		                case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	            	    case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		                case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		    };
    }
	else
            switch(s){
					    case 0:;break;
		                case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		                case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		                case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		                case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		                case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		                case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		                case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	            	    case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		                case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
                       } ;
    switch(g){
    	                case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		                case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
		                case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
		                case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		                case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		                case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		                case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		                case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
	            	    case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
		                case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	};
   };

	int a,b,c,d,e,f,t,y;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
    {
    	t=b*b-4*a*c;
    	y=e*e-4*d*f;
            if (t<0) printf("NO SOULUTION\n");
        else
        {
        x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
            if (y<0) printf("NO SOULUTION\n");
        else
        {
        x1=(-e+sqrt(y))/(2*d);
        x2=(-e-sqrt(y))/(2*d);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
        }

20190302016:Problem1114:答案错误
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char * week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
	scanf("%d%d",&x,&y);
	b=x-1;
    if(b==0)
    {
        a=(y+1)%7;
        printf("%s",week[a]);
	}
	else if(b==1)
	{
		a=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b==2)
	{
		a=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b>=3&&b<=7) 
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*30+(b-c-1)*31+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*31+(b-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7; 
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
}

20190318139:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
   int x,y,n,t,a;
   scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    if(x=1)
    a=x+12;
     if(x=2)
     a=x+12; 
   n=20/4-2*20+19+26*(a+1)/10+y-1;//蔡勒公式，w=c/4-2c+y+y/4+26(m+1)/10+d-1,例如2019，c=20,y=19,m为月，d为天。
    t=n%7;//余数为星期几，1月换为13，2换为14。
   switch (t)
{
    case 4:
    printf("Thursday\n");
    break;
    case 5:
    printf("Friday\n");
    break;
    case 6:
    printf("Saturday\n");
    break;
    case 0:
    printf("Sunday\n");
    break;
    case 1:
    printf("Monday\n");
    break;
    case 2:
    printf("Tuesday\n");
    break;
    case 3:
    printf("Wednesday\n");
    break;
}
}

20190318145:Problem1158:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int A,B,first,mid,last;
    while(scanf("%d",&A)!=0)
    {
    	first=A/100;
    	mid=(A/10)%10;
    	last=A%10;
		switch(first)
	    {
	    	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	    	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	    	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	    	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	    	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	    	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	    	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖");break;
		}
    	printf("佰");
		 
    	switch(mid)
	    {
	    	case 0:
	    		if(last!=0)
	    		printf("零");break;
	    	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	    	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	    	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	    	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	    	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	    	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	    	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int RMB,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&RMB)!=EOF){
		a=RMB/100;b=(RMB-a*100)/10;c=RMB-a*100-b*10;
		switch (a)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹佰");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰佰");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁佰");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆佰");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍佰");
				break;

				printf("陆佰");
				break;

				printf("柒佰");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌佰");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖佰");
				break;
		}
		switch (b)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹拾");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰拾");
				break;
			case 3:

				break;

				break;

				break;

				printf("陆拾");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒拾");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌拾");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖拾");
				break;
		}if (b==0&&c!=0)
		{printf("零");}
		if (b==0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		if (b!=0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		else{
		switch (c)
		{

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char * week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	b=x-1; 
    if(b==0)
    {
        a=(y+1)%7;
        printf("%s",week[a]);
	}
	else if(b==1)
	{
		a=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b==2)
	{
		a=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b>=3&&b<=7) 
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*30+(b-c-1)*31+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*31+(b-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7; 
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
}

		if ((b*b-4*a*c)>=0)
		{
			x1=((-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a));
			x2=((-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a));
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}

int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
return 0;

20190318175:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>  
#include <math.h>  
#define EXP 0.00000001  
int main()  
{  
double a = 0.0;  
double b = 0.0;  
double c = 0.0;  
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);  
if ((a>=-EXP)&&(a<=EXP))  
{  
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");  
}  
else  
{  
double disc = b*b-4*a*c;  
if(( disc >= -EXP)&&( disc <= EXP))  
 {  
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-b/(2*a),-b/(2*a));  
}  
else if ( disc > 0.0)  
 {  
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",  
(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a),  
(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a));  
 }  
}  
return 0;  
}

	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		if(delta>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	} 
}

#include <math.h>  
#define EXP 0.00000001  
int main()  
{  
double a = 0.0;  
double b = 0.0;  
double c = 0.0;  
while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);  
if ((a>=-EXP)&&(a<=EXP))  
{  
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");  
}  
else  
{  
double disc=b*b-4*a*c;  
if((disc>=-EXP)&&(disc<=EXP))  
 {  
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-b/(2*a),-b/(2*a));  
}  
else if(disc>0.0)  
 {  
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a),(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a));  
 }  
}  
return 0;

20190301022:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,s,g;
	char r[100][9]={{"零"},{"壹"},{"贰"},{"叁"},{"肆"},{"伍"},{"陆"},{"柒"},{"捌"},{"玖"}};
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{b=a/100;
	s=a/10-b*10;
	g=a%10;
	if(s==0&&g==0)printf("%s佰元整\n",r[b]);
	if(s!=0&&g==0)printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",r[b],r[s]);
	if(g!=0&&s==0)printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",r[b],r[g]);
	if(s!=0&&g!=0)printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",r[b],r[s],r[g]);}
}

20190318037:Problem1114:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,*30,31,30,31};
	int x,y,add=0,i,m;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1) add=y-1;
	else
	{
	for(i=0;i<=x-2;i++) add+=a[i];
	add+=y-1;
    }
	m=add%7+2;
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
 }

20190318077:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int is_leap_year(int year)
{
    return (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) || year % 400 == 0;
}
int get_days (int year, int month)
{
    switch (month)
    {
        case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31;
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default: // 2 月
            if (is_leap_year(year))
                return 29;
            else
                return 28;
    }
}
void print_week(int weekday)
{
    switch (weekday)
    {
        case 0:
            printf ("星期天\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("星期一\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("星期二\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("星期三\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("星期四\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf ("星期五\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("星期六\n");
            break;
    }
}
 
int main(int argc, char** argv)
{
    int year, month, day, i;
    scanf  ("%d,%d",&month, &day);
 
    int sum = 0;
    for (i = 2019; i < year; ++i)
    {
        if (is_leap_year(i)) // 是闰年
        {
            sum += 366;
        } 
        else
        {
            sum += 365;
        }
    }
 
    for (i = 1; i < month; ++i)
    {
        sum += get_days(year, i);
    }
 
    sum += day + 1;
 
    printf ("",  day);
    print_week (sum % 7);
 
    return 0;
}

		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;

int main()
{

	int x,y,add=0,i,m;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1) add=y-1;
	else
	{
	for(i=0;i<=x-2;i++) add+=a[i];
	add+=y-1;
    }
	m=add%7+2;
	m%=7;
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;

20190318077:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int is_leap_year(int year)
{
    return (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) || year % 400 == 0;
}

int get_days (int year, int month)
{
    switch (month)
    {
        case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31; 
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default: // 2 月
            if (is_leap_year(year))
                return 29;
            else
                return 28;
    }
}
void print_week(int weekday)
{
    switch (weekday)
    {
        case 0:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
}
 
int main(int argc, char** argv)
{
    int year, month, day, i;
    scanf  ("%d,%d",&month, &day);
 
    int sum = 0;
    for (i = 2019; i < year; ++i)
    {
        if (is_leap_year(i)) // 是闰年
        {
            sum += 366;
        } 
        else
        {
            sum += 365;
        }
    }
 
    for (i = 1; i < month; ++i)
    {
        sum += get_days(year, i);
    }
 
    sum += day + 1;
 
    printf ("",  day);
    print_week (sum % 7);
 
    return 0;
}
