20190318037:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int x,y,add=0,i,m;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1) add=y-1;
	else
	{
	for(i=0;i<=x-2;i++) add+=a[i];
	add+=y-1;
    }
	m=add%7+2;
	m%=7;
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
 }

20190318175:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a==0) 
        printf("%.3f\n",-c/b);
    else
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3f～～～%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            }
    return 0;
}

	else if (a==2)
	t=(30+b)%7;
	else if (a==3)
	t=(59+b)%7;
	else if (a==4)
	t=(90+b)%7;
	else if (a==5)
	t=(120+b)%7;
	else if (a==6)
	t=(151+b)%7;
	else if (a==7)
	t=(181+b)%7;
	else if (a==8)
	t=(212+b)%7;
	else if (a==9)
	t=(243+b)%7;
	else if (a==10)
	t=(273+b)%7;
	else if (a==11)
	t=(304+b)%7;
	else 
	t=(334+b)%7;
	f=(t+1)%7;
	if (f==1)
	printf("Monsday");
	else if (f==2)
	printf("Tuesday");
	else if (f==3)
	printf("Wdnesday");

20190318188:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
    int x, y;
    scanf("%d,%d", &x, &y);

    int MONTH[] = { 0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31 };

    int i=0;
    int days=0;
    for (i = 0; i < x; i++)
    {
        days += MONTH[i];
    }

    days = days + y-1;

    int a;
    a= days % 7;
    switch (a)
    {
    case 0:printf("Tuesday"); break;
    case 1:printf("Wednesday"); break;
    case 2:printf("Thursday"); break;
    case 3:printf("Friday"); break;
    case 4:printf("Saturday"); break;
    case 5:printf("Sunday"); break;
    case 6:printf("Monday"); break;
    }

    return 0;
}

{

    while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
    if(a==0) 
        printf("%.3f\n",-c/b);
    else
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3f～～～%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            }}
    return 0;

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int b,c,sum=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&b,&c);
	if(b==1)
		sum=c;
	else if(b==2)
		sum=31+c;
	else if(b==3)
		sum=60+c-1;
	else if(b==4)
		sum=91+c-1;
	else if(b==5)
		sum=121+c-1;
	else if(b==6)
		sum=152+c-1;
	else if(b==7)
		sum=182+c-1;
	else if(b==8)
		sum=213+c-1;
	else if(b==9)
		sum=244+c-1;
	else if(b==10)
		sum=274+c-1;
	else if(b==11)
		sum=305+c-1;
	else if(b==12)
		sum=335+c-1;
	switch(sum%7+1)
	{
	case 1:printf("Monday"); break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday"); break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday"); break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday"); break;
	case 5:printf("Friday"); break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday"); break;
	case 7:printf("Sunday"); break;
	}   
}

20190318173:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h> 
main() 
{  
  int year,a;  
  scanf("%d",&year); 
  if(year%400==0) a=1; 
  else 
  {  
    if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0) a=1; 
    else a=0; } 
    if(a==1) 
  {
   printf("L\n",year);
  } 
   else 
  {
  printf("N\n",year); 
  }  
}

20190318173:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
    char c[4],n[4];
    int c1,c2,c3,i,*cp;
    scanf("%s",c);
    for(i=0;i<3;i++)
    {
        if(i==0)
        {
            cp=&c1;
        }
        if(i==1)
        {
            cp=&c2;
        }
        if(i==2)
        {
            cp=&c3;
        }
        if((c[i]>=65 && c[i]<=90))
        {
            *cp=c[i];
        }
        else if(c[i]>=97 && c[i]<=122)
        {
            *cp=c[i]-32;
        }
    }
    if(c2>=c1 && c3>=c1)
    {
        n[0]=c[0];
        if(c3>c2)
        {
            n[1]=c[1];
            n[2]=c[2];
        }
        else
        {
            n[1]=c[2];
            n[2]=c[1];
        }
    }
    if(c1>=c2 && c3>=c2)
    {
        n[0]=c[1];
        if(c3>c1)
        {
            n[1]=c[0];
            n[2]=c[2];
        }
        else
        {
            n[1]=c[2];
            n[2]=c[0];
        }
    }
    if((c1>=c3 && c2>=c3))
    {
        n[0]=c[2];
        if(c2>c1)
        {
            n[1]=c[0];
            n[2]=c[1];
        }
        else
        {
            n[1]=c[1];
            n[2]=c[0];
        }
    }
    printf("%c%c%c  \n\n\n\n",n[0],n[1],n[2]);
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF);
	{
	b=a/100;
	c=(a-100*b)/10;
	d=a-100*b-10*c;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 1 : printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2 : printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3 : printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4 : printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5 : printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6 : printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7 : printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8 : printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9 : printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1 : printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2 : printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3 : printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4 : printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5 : printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6 : printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7 : printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8 : printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9 : printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch(d)
	{
		case 1 : printf("壹元整\n");break;
		case 2 : printf("贰元整\n");break;
		case 3 : printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4 : printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5 : printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6 : printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7 : printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8 : printf("捌元整\n");break;
		case 9 : printf("玖元整\n");break;

	{

	{

20190301025:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,n;
	double x1,x2,t;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/2*a;
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else if(t<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}

20190301025:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	double x1,x2,t,a,b,c;
	while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else 
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318012:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:if(z!=0)printf("零");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}
}

int main()

		c=x%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;

			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;

			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;

20190318037:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=(x/10)%10;
		c=x%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(b==0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
		if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零"); 
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		}
		if(b!=0&&c==0) printf("元整\n"); 
	}
 }

main()
{
	int x, y, s;
	scanf("%d,%d", &x, &y);
	if (x=1){
	   s=(y+1)%7; 
	switch(s){
	   	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	   	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	   	case 7:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;
	   	default:printf("Tuesday\n");
		}
    }
    else{
    	s=(30*x+y+1)%7;
    switch(s){
	   	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	   	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	   	case 7:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;
	   	default:printf("Tuesday\n");

#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	float a,b,c,e,f,g,x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else {
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
	}while(scanf("%f %f %f",&e,&f,&g)!=EOF){
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x3=(-f+sqrt(f*f-4*e*g))/2*a;
			x4=(-f+sqrt(f*f-4*e*g))/2*a;
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
		}
	}
	
}

20190318010:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
void main()
{
int four , hundred , fourhundred , year;
scanf("%d",&year);
four = year % 4;
hundred = year % 100;
fourhundred = year % 400;
if (four == 0 && hundred == 0 && fourhundred == 0)
 printf("L\n");
else if (four == 0 && hundred != 0 && fourhundred != 0)
 printf("L\n");
else printf("N\n");
}

20190318018:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a1,b1,c1;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	if(a1<b1&&b1<c1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a1,b1,c1);
	if(a1<c1&&c1<b1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a1,c1,b1);
	if(b1<a1&&a1<c1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",b1,a1,c1);
	if(b1<c1&&c1<a1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",b1,c1,a1);
	if(c1<a1&&a1<b1)
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c1,a1,b1);
	else
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c1,b1,a1);
 }

20190318010:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

20190318174:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(delta>=0){
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}else printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	return 0;
}

		printf("Yes\n",n);

20190601016:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,delt1,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		delt1=b*b-4*a*c;
		delt2=e*e-4*d*f;
		if(delt1<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		if(delt2<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x3=(-e+sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			x4=(-e-sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
		}
		break;
	}
	
	return 0;
		
		
		
	
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,delt1,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		delt1=b*b-4*a*c;
		delt2=e*e-4*d*f;
		if(delt1<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		if(delt2<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x3=(-e+sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			x4=(-e-sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
		}
		;
	}
	
	return 0;

20190601016:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,delt1,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		delt1=b*b-4*a*c;
		delt2=e*e-4*d*f;
		if(delt1<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		if(delt2<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x3=(-e+sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			x4=(-e-sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
		}
		
	}
	
	return 0;
		
		
		
	
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}
	return 0;
}

20190318099:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L\n");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N\n");
    }
    return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,disc,x1,x2,d;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{   disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
      printf("NO SOLUTION");
     else
      d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
       x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
       x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
       printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf",x1,x2);
}
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x,x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sprt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		x2=(-b-sprt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	}
}
return 0;
}

20190318099:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);//注意输入没有空格的，直接就这3个字母
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

{

		mld=x;
		x=y  ;
		y=mld;
	}	//printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);
	if(x>z){ 
		mld=x;
		x=z  ;
		z=mld;
	}	//printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);
	if(y>z){
		mld=z;
		z=y  ;
		y=mld;
	}	//printf("%c%c%c\n\n",x,y,z);
	printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);

20190318018:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	c=a-1;d=b-1;
	if(a==1){e=d;
	}
	if(a==2){e=31+d;
	}
	if(a==3){e=31+28+d;
	}
	if(a==4){e=31+28+31+d;
	}
	if(a==5){e=31+28+61+d;
	}
	if(a==6){e=59+61+31+d;
	}
	if(a==7){e=59+61+61+d;
	}
	if(a==8){e=59+61+61+31+d; 
	}
	if(a==9){e=59+61+61+62+d;
	}
	if(a==10){e=120+123+30+d;
	}
	if(a==11){e=120+123+61+d;
	}
	if(a==12){e=120+123+91+d;
	}
	f=e%7;
	if(f==6)
	{printf("Monday\n");}
	if(f==5)
	{printf("Sunday\n");}
	if(f==4)
	{printf("Saturday\n");}
	if(f==3)
	{printf("Friday\n");}
	if(f==2)
	{printf("Thursday\n");}
	if(f==1)
	{printf("Wednesday\n");}
	if(f==0)
	{printf("Tuesday\n");}
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,temp;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		temp=a,a=b,b=temp;
	}
	if(a>c){
		temp=a,a=c,c=temp;
	}
	if(b>c){
		temp=c,c=b,b=temp;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	a=x,b=y,c=z;
	if (a<=b&&b<=b)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);
	else if (a<=c&&c<=b)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",x,z,y);
	else if (b<=a&&a<=c)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",y,x,z);
	else if (b<=c&&c<=a)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",y,z,x);
	else if (c<=a&&a<=b)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",z,x,y);
	else
		printf("%c%c%c\n",z,y,x);

}

	{

	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;

		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;

		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;

		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		case 0:if(c==0)
		printf("");
		else 
		printf("零");break; 
	}
	
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
		case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
		case 3:printf("叁元整");break;

20190302051:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2,e;
	while
	(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d<0)
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			e=sqrt(d);
			x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		
	}
	
	
 }

int main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%4==0&&year%400!=0||year%4==0&&year%400==0)
	printf("L\n",year);
	else
	printf("N\n",year);

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c; 
	while(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	
		switch(b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		case 0:if(c==0)
		printf("");
		else 
		printf("零");break; 
	}
	
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;

main()
{
	int a;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	if((a%4)!=0)
	printf("N");
	else if((a%100)!=0)
	printf("L");
	else if((a%400)==0)
	printf("L");
	else printf("N");

20190601016:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main(){
	int m,d,x,A;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m){
	case 1:x=d-1;break;
	case 2:x=d+28-1;break;
	case 3:x=d+28+31-1;break;
	case 4:x=d+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 5:x=d+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 6:x=d+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 7:x=d+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 8:x=d+31+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 9:x=d+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 10:x=d+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 11:x=d+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	case 12:x=d+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31-1;break;
	}
	A=(x+2)%7;
	switch(A){
	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	default :printf("Sunday\n");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	{
		x1=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
		x2=(-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
}
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int m1,d1,m2,d2,day,w;
	scanf("%d,%d,&m2,&d2");
	m1=1;
	d1=1;
	day=(m2-m1)*31+d2-d1;
	if(m2>=3 && m2<5)
		day=day-3;
	if(m2>=5&&m2<7)
		day=day-3-1;
	if(m2>=7&&m2<10)
		day=day-3-1-1;
	if(m2>=10&&m2<12)
		day=day-3-1-1-1;
	if(m2=12)
		day=day-3-1-1-1-1;
	w=day%7;
	switch(w)
	{
		case 0 :
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Saturday");

		case 5:

if(x==1)

if(x==2)
z=y-1+31;
if(x==3)
z=y-1+59;

z=y-1+90;

z=y-1+121;

z=y-1+151;
if(x==7)
z=y-1+181;
if(x==8)
z=y-1+212;

z=y-1+242;
if(x==10)
z=y-1+273;

z=y-1+303;
if(x==12)
z=y-1+334;

20190302002:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,y,t;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		y=e*e-4*d*f;
		if (t<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTTION\n");
		  else
		  {x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		  }
		  if (y<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTTION\n");
		  else
		  {
		  	x3=(-e+sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	x4=(-e-sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
		  }
	}
	return 0;
}

20190302002:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,y,t;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		y=e*e-4*d*f;
		if (t<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTTON\n");
		  else
		  {x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		  }
		  if (y<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTTON\n");
		  else
		  {
		  	x3=(-e+sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	x4=(-e-sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
		  }
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318155:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>

main()
{      
    char b[7][10]={"Tuesday","Wesderday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday","Monday"};
    int m,d,a;
    scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
    switch(m){
    case 1: printf("%s",b[d%7-1]);break;
    case 2: printf("%s",b[d%7+2]);break;
    case 3: printf("%s",b[d%7+2]);break;
    case 4: printf("%s",b[d%7+5]);break;
    case 5: printf("%s",b[d%7]);break;

{

    c=a-1;d=b-1;
    if(a==1){e=d;
    }
    if(a==2){e=31+d;
    }
    if(a==3){e=31+28+d;
    }
    if(a==4){e=31+28+31+d;
    }
    if(a==5){e=31+28+61+d;
    }
    if(a==6){e=59+61+31+d;
    }
    if(a==7){e=59+61+61+d;
    }
    if(a==8){e=59+61+61+31+d; 
    }
    if(a==9){e=59+61+61+62+d;
    }
    if(a==10){e=120+123+30+d;
    }
    if(a==11){e=120+123+61+d;
    }
    if(a==12){e=120+123+91+d;
    }
    day=e%7;
    switch(day)
{

main(){

	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		y=e*e-4*d*f;
		if (t<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		  else
		  {
		  x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
		  printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		  }
		  if (y<0)
		  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		  else
		  {
		  	x3=(-e+sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	x4=(-e-sqrt(y))/(2*d);
		  	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);

scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f);
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
	{x3=(sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)-e)/2*d;
	x4=(-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)-e)/2*d;
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);}
	if(e*e-4*d*f<0)
	{x1=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
	x2=(-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0&&e*e-4*d*f<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0&&e*e-4*d*f>=0)
	{
		x1=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
		x2=(-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		x3=(sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)-e)/2*d;

		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a, b, c;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
{
x1 = ((-b)+ sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
x2 = ((-b) - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1,x2);
}
}

   if(x<3) 
{ 
    t=(x-1)*31+y-1;
}
   else if(3<=x&&x<=4)
{
   t=x/2*31+28+y-1;
}
   else if(5<=x&&x<=6)
{
   t=x/2*31+28+30+y-1;
}
    else if(7<=x&&x<=8)
{
    t=x/2*31+28+2*30+y-1;
}
    else if(x==9)
{
    t=5*31+28+30*2+y-1;
}
    else if(10<=x&&x<=11)
{
     t=(x+1)/2+28+3*30+y-1;
}
     else
{
     t=6*31+28+4*30+y-1;
}
     w=t%7;

20190318008:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,disc,p,q;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF){
    	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
    	p=-b/(2*a);
    	q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
    	x1=p+q;
		x2=p-q;
		if(disc<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
}

20190318198:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>


int main()
{
	char a, b, c;
	char n;

	scanf("%c %c %c", &a, &b, &c);

	if (a > b)
	{
		n = a;
		a = b;
		b = n;
	}

	if (a > c)
	{
		n = a;
		a = c;
		c = n;
	}

	if (b > c)
	{
		n = c;
		c = b;
		b = n;
	}

	printf("%c %c %c",a,b,c);


	return 0;

}

20190302012:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,N;
	double x1,x2,q;
	while (scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF){
		N=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (N>=0){
			x1=(-b+sqrt(N))/2/a;
			x2=(-b-sqrt(N))/2/a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else 
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	} 
}

20190318198:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>


int main()
{
	char a, b, c;
	char n;

	scanf("%c %c %c", &a, &b, &c);

	if (a > b)
	{
		n = a;
		a = b;
		b = n;
	}

	if (a > c)
	{
		n = a;
		a = c;
		c = n;
	}

	if (b > c)
	{
		n = c;
		c = b;
		b = n;
	}

	printf("%c %c %c",a,b,c);


	return 0;

}

20190318008:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int m,n,x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&n);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:x=0;break;
		case 2:x=31;break;
		case 3:x=59;break;
		case 4:x=90;break;
		case 5:x=120;break;
		case 6:x=151;break;
		case 7:x=181;break;
		case 8:x=212;break;
		case 9:x=243;break;
		case 10:x=273;break;
		case 11:x=304;break;
		case 12:x=334;break;
	}
	x=x+n;
	y=(x-1)%7;
	if(y==1)
	printf("Wednesday\n");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Thursday\n");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Friday\n");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Saturday\n");
	if(y==5)
	printf("Sunday\n");
	if(y==6)
	printf("Monday\n");
	if(y==0)
	printf("Tuesday\n");
 }

20190318008:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
void trans(int a) 
{   
    if(a==0) printf("零"); 
 else if(a==1) printf("壹"); 
 else if(a==2) printf("贰"); 
 else if(a==3) printf("叁"); 
 else if(a==4) printf("肆"); 
 else if(a==5) printf("伍"); 
 else if(a==6) printf("陆"); 
 else if(a==7) printf("柒"); 
 else if(a==8) printf("捌"); 
 else if(a==9) printf("玖"); 
 } 
main() 
{ int y; 
  while(scanf("%d",&y)!=EOF) 
 {   
   int k; 
   int m; 
   int n; 
   k=(int)y%1000/100; 
   m=(int)y%1000%100/10; 
   n=(int)y%1000%100%10; 
   if(y%100==0)
   {
    int a;
    a=y/100;     
    trans(a);
    printf("佰元整\n");
    }
    else{
   trans(k); 
   printf("佰"); 
   trans(m); 
   printf("拾"); 
   trans(n); 
   printf("元整"); 
   printf("\n"); 
}}}

20190318198:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>


int main()
{
	char a, b, c;
	char n;

	scanf("%c%c%c", &a, &b, &c);

	if (a > b)
	{
		n = a;
		a = b;
		b = n;
	}

	if (a > c)
	{
		n = a;
		a = c;
		c = n;
	}

	if (b > c)
	{
		n = c;
		c = b;
		b = n;
	}

	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);


	return 0;

}

20190318008:Problem1158:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int t,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&t)!=EOF)
	{
		a=t/100;
		b=(t-100*a)/10;
		c=t-100*a-10*b;
	if(t%100==0)
	{
		switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	else
	{
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
		switch(c)
	{
		case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}
	}
	}
}

     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
      printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
     else
      d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
       x1=(-b+d)/(2.0*a);
       x2=(-b-d)/(2.0*a);
       printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);

#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,dt1;               int a2,b2,c2,dt2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1); 	scanf("%d %d %d",&a2,&b2,&c2); 
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	dt1=(b1*b1-4*a1*c1);
	if(dt1<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else    {
		x1=(-b1+sqrt(dt1))/2*a1;
		x2=(-b1-sqrt(dt1))/2*a1;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	
//	scanf("%d %d %d",&a2,&b2,&c2); 
	dt2=(b2*b2-4*a2*c2);
	if(dt2<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else    {
		x3=(-b2+sqrt(dt2))/2*a2;
		x4=(-b2-sqrt(dt2))/2*a2;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
	}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,disc;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF){
    	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
		if(disc<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
}

20190318175:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190318109:Problem1114:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int  month, day;
    scanf("%d%d",&month,&day);
    int year=19;
    if (month == 1 || month == 2)
        {
        	year--, month += 12;
		}
    int c = year / 100;
    int y = year - c * 100;
    int week = y + y / 4 + c / 4 - 2 * c + 26 * (month + 1) / 10 + day - 1;
    while (week < 0)
    week += 7;
    week %= 7;
    switch (week)
    {
        case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
        case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
        case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
        case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
        case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
        case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
        case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
    }
 return 0;

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

	return 0;

20190502028:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{double d=(b*b-4*a*c);
	if(a==0)
	{
		if (b==0)
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
			printf("x=%.3f\n",-c/b);
	}
	else
	{
		if (d >= 0)
		{
			x1 = (-b - sqrt(d)) / (2 * a);
			x2 = (-b + sqrt(d)) / (2 * a);
		    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x2, x1);
		}
		else
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}}
}

20190318199:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
		{
			delta=b*b-4*a*c;
			if(delta<0)	
						printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
			else if(delta>=0)
						{x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2.000*a);
						 x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2.000*a);
						 printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
						}
		}
	return 0;
}

20190301004:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
#include<math.h>
main() 
{ 
	double a,b,c,disc,x1,x2,p,q;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	x1=p+q;
	x2=p-q;
	if(disc>=0)
	   printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a1,a2,a3,b1,b2,b3;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a1,&a2,&a3,&b1,&b2,&b3);
	if(a2*a2-4*a1*a3<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(a2*a2-4*a1*a3==0)printf("%d.000~~~%d.000\n",-a2/(2*a1),-a2/(2*a1));
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-a2+sqrt(pow(a2,2)-4*a1*a3)/(2*a1)),(-a2-sqrt(pow(a2,2)-4*a1*a3))/(2*a1));
	if(b2*b2-4*b1*b3<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(b2*b2-4*b1*b3==0)printf("%d.000~~~%d.000\n",-b2/(2*b1),-b2/(2*b1));
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-b2+sqrt(pow(b2,2)-4*b1*b3)/(2*b1)),(-b2-sqrt(pow(b2,2)-4*b1*b3))/(2*b1));
}

   {
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0)
	    {
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
	    else
	    {   
		e=sqrt(d);
	    x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	    }
	}
	return 0;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int s,m,n,q;
	char*p[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while(scanf("%d",&s)!=EOF){
		m=s/100;
		n=(s-m*100)/10;
		q=s%10;
		if(n==0&&q==0)
		printf("%s百元整",p[m-1]);
		if(n!=0&&q==0)
		printf("%s百%s十元整",p[m-1],p[n-1]);
		if(n==0&q!=0)
		printf("%s百零%s元整",p[m-1],p[q-1]);
		if(n!=0&&q!=0)
		printf("%s百%s十%s元整",p[m-1],p[n-1],p[q-1]);
	}

}

20190318022:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

20190318084:Problem1114:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>

int main ()

{

int m, d, c, w;


scanf ("%d %d %d", &y, &m, &d);

if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 

y--;

m += 12;

}

c = 2019 / 100;


w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (2019 + 2019 / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;

while (w < 0) w += 7;

w %= 7;

switch (w) {
	        case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	    case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	    case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	    case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	    case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	     	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	    	case 7:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;
	    	default:printf("Tuesday\n");
	
        }
    }

#include "stdio.h"

main ()

{

y=2019;

if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 

y--;

m += 12;

}

w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;

w %= 7;

switch (w) {
	        case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	    case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	    case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	    case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	    case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	     	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	    	case 0:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;
	
        }
    }

	scanf("%f",&b);

	printf("YES\n");
	else
	printf("NO\n");

main ()

{

int x, y, c, w, s;


scanf ("%d %d ", &x, &y);

s=2019;

if (x ==1 || x == 2) { 

s--;

x += 12;

}

c = s / 100;

s = s - c * 100;

w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (s + s / 4) + (13 * (x + 1) / 5) + y - 1;

while (w < 0) 

w += 7;

w %= 7;

switch (w) {
	        case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	    case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;

20190318042:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,dt;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);{
	double x1,x2;
	dt=(b*b-4*a*c);
	if(dt<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	else    {
		x1=(-b+sqrt(dt))/2*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(dt))/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	}
  }
}

		x+=12;

	c=s/100;
	s=s-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1;

	w%=7;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,a,b,c;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	a=year%4;
	b=year%100;
	c=year%400;
	if(c==0 || (a==0 && b!=0)){
		printf("L");
	}
	else{
		printf("N");
	}
}

20190301012:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
#include<string.h>
main()
{
	int s,m,n,q;
	char*p[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while(scanf("%d",&s)!=EOF){
		m=s/100;
		n=(s-m*100)/10;
		q=s%10;
		if(n==0&&q==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",p[m-1]);
		else if(n!=0&&q==0)
		printf("%s佰%s十元整\n",p[m-1],p[n-1]);
		else if(n==0&&q!=0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",p[m-1],p[q-1]);
		else if(n!=0&&q!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s十%s元整\n",p[m-1],p[n-1],p[q-1]);
	}

}

	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d)/(2*a);

	{ 
		b=a/100;

	    d=c/10;
	    e=c%10;
	    if(c==0)
	        printf("%s佰元整",money[b]);
	    else

20190318181:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	b=a%100;
	if((a%4==0)&&(b!=0))
	    printf("L");
	     else if(a%400==0)
	     printf("L");
	     else
	     printf("N");
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	char * money[10]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{ 
		b=a/100;
	    c=a%100;
	    d=c/10;
	    e=c%10;
	    if(c==0)
	        printf("%s佰元整\n",money[b]);\
	    else if(d==0)
	        printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);
	    else if(e==0)
		    printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[b],money[d]);
	    else
	        printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);
	}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int w,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&w)!=EOF)
{
     if(w>=100&&w<=999)
{
	a=w/100;
	b=(w%100)/10;
	c=w%10;
}
	switch(a)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
}
	switch(b)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
}
    if(b==0&&c!=0)
{
     printf("零");
}
	switch(c)
{
     case(0):printf("元整");break;
	case(1):printf("壹元整");break;
	case(2):printf("贰元整");break;
	case(3):printf("叁元整");break;

20190302031:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	c=b-1;
	if(a==1||a==2) d=(a-1)*31+c;
	if(a==3) d=31+28+c;
	if(a==4) d=31*2+28+c;
	if(a==5) d=31*2+30+28+c;
	if(a==6) d=31*3+30+28+c;
	if(a==7) d=31*3+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==8) d=31*4+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==9) d=31*5+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==10) d=31*5+30*3+28+c;
	if(a==11) d=31*6+30*3+28+c;
	if(a==12) d=31*7+30*3+28+c;
    
	for(d=d+2;d>7;d=d-7) 
	d=d;
    
	if(d==1) printf("Monday");
    if(d==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(d==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(d==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(d==5) printf("Friday");
    if(d==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(d==7) printf("Sunday");

}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{

	float a, b, c;
 	double s, x, x1;
 	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
	 {
    s = b * b - 4 * a*c;
	 if(s >= 0)
	 {
	   x = (-b + sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
 	   x1 = (-b - sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
 	   printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,x1);
 	}
 	else if(s < 0)
 	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
 	}
 	}
}

20190318153:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L\n",year);
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N\n",year);
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302031:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int RMB,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&RMB)!=EOF){
		a=RMB/100;b=(RMB-a*100)/10;c=RMB-a*100-b*10;
		switch (a)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹佰");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰佰");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁佰");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆佰");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍佰");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆佰");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒佰");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌佰");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖佰");
				break;
		}
		switch (b)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹拾");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰拾");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁拾");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆拾");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍拾");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆拾");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒拾");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌拾");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖拾");
				break;
		}if (b==0&&c!=0)
		{printf("零");}
		if (b==0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		if (b!=0&&c==0)
		{printf("元整\n");}
		else{
		switch (c)
		{
			case 1:
				printf("壹元整\n");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰元整\n");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁元整\n");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆元整\n");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍元整\n");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆元整\n");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒元整\n");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌元整\n");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖元整\n");
				break;	 
	}
    }
	}return 0;
 }

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,z;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		z=a;a=b;b=z;
	}		
	if(b>c){
		z=b;b=c;c=z;
	}
	if (a>b) {
		z=a;a=b;b=z;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c", a, b, c);
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
   int x,y,n,t;
   scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
   if(x==1)
   n=(y-1)%7;
   if(x==2)
   n=(31+y-1)%7;
    if(x==3)
     n=(59+y-1)%7;
    if(x==4)
     n=(90+y-1)%7;
    if(x==5)
     n=(120+y-1)%7;
     if(x==6)
     n=(151+y-1)%7;
      if(x==7)
      n=(181+y-1)%7;
       if(x==8)
       n=(212+y-1)%7;
       if(x==9)
       n=(243+y-1)%7;
       if(x==10)
       n=(273+y-1)%7;
        if(x==11)
        n=(304+y-1)%7;
        if(x==12)
         n=(334+y-1)%7;
    t=n+2;
   switch (t)
{
    case 4:
    printf("Thursday\n");
    break;
    case 5:
    printf("Friday\n");
    break;
    case 6:
    printf("Saturday\n");
    break;
    case 7:
    printf("Sunday\n");
    break;
    case 8:
    printf("Monday\n");
    break;
    case 2:
    printf("Tuesday\n");
    break;
    case 3:
    printf("Wednesday\n");
    break;
}
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    if(x==1) a=(y+1)%7;
    if(x==2) a=(32+y)%7;
    if(x==3) a=(32+28+y)%7;
    if(x==4) a=(32+28+31+y)%7;
    if(x==5) a=(32+28+31+y+30)%7;
    if(x==6) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31)%7;
    if(x==7) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30)%7;
    if(x==8) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30+31)%7;
    if(x==9) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30+31+31)%7;
    if(x==10) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30+31+31+30)%7;
    if(x==11) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30+31+31+30+31)%7;
    if(x==12) a=(32+28+31+y+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30)%7;
    
    
    
    if(a==0) printf("Sunday");
    if(a==1) printf("Monday");
    if(a==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(a==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(a==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(a==5) printf("Friday");
    if(a==6) printf("Saturday");
    
    
    return 0;

    switch(x)
    {
       case(1):a=y-1;break;
       case(2):a=30+y;break;
       case(3):a=30+28+y;break;
       case(4):a=30+28+31+y;break;
       case(5):a=30+28+31+30+y;break;
       case(6):a=30+28+31+30+31+y;break;
       case(7):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+y;break;
       case(8):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+y;break;
       case(9):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y;break;
       case(10):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y;break;
	   case(11):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+31+31+y;break;
	   case(12):a=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+31+30+30+y;break;
       default:printf("\n");
    }
    b=a%7;
    switch(b)
    {  
       case(0):printf("Tuesday");break;
       case(1):printf("Wednesday");break;
       case(2):printf("Thursday");break;
       case(3):printf("Friday");break;
       case(4):printf("Saturday");break;
       case(5):printf("Sunday");break;
       case(6):printf("Monday");break;
       default:printf("\n");
    }
    
    return 0;
}

	if(a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}

20190318070:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        if(d>=0){
            x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%f,%f,%f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else if(d>=0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    }

20190318146:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char z,w,h;
	z=getchar();
	w=getchar();
	h=getchar();
	if (z>w)
	{
		if (w>h)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",h,w,z);
		else if (h>w)
		{
			if (h>z)
			printf("%c%c%c\n",w,z,h);
			else if (h<z)
			printf("%c%c%c\n",w,h,z);
		}
		
	}
	else if (w>z)
	{
		if (z>h)
		printf("%c%c%c\n",h,z,w);
		else if (h>z)
		{
			if (w>h)
			printf("%c%c%c\n",z,h,w);
			else if (h<w)
			printf("%c%c%c\n",z,w,h);
		}
		
	}

}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&a) !=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;
		c=(a-a/100)/10;
		d=a-b*100-c*10;
		switch (b)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	            case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	            case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	            case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
              	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
             	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
             	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
              	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
            }
	    switch(c)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	            case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	            case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
             	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
             	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
              	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
              	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
            	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
           }
	    switch(d)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹");break;
              	case(2):printf("贰");break;
            	case(3):printf("叁");break;
            	case(4):printf("肆");break;
            	case(5):printf("伍");break;
              	case(6):printf("陆");break;
             	case(7):printf("柒");break;
             	case(8):printf("捌");break;
               	case(9):printf("玖");break;
            }
	printf("元整\n");		 				
    }
    return 0;

20190318198:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>
#include<math.h>

int main()
{
	int i;
	double a, b, c;
	double x1, x2;

	for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
	{
		scanf("%lf %lf %lf", &a, &b, &c);

		x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;
		x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;

		if (b*b - 4 * a*c < 0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		else
		{
			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n", x1, x2);

		}
	}

	return 0;

}

	int a, b, c;
	double x1, x2;

	for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
	{
		scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);

		x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;
		x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;

		if (b*b - 4 * a*c < 0&&a!=0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		else
		{
			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n", x1, x2);

		}
		
	}

	return 0;

20190318181:Problem1147:时间超限
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	double m,n,p,q,disc;
	int a,b,c;
	    disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		p=b/(2*a);
		q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		m=p+q;
		n=p-q;
		while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c));
	{
		if(q>0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
}

20190318198:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>
#include<math.h>

int main()
{
	int i;
	double a, b, c;
	double x1, x2;

	for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
	{
		scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);

		x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;
		x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;

		if (b*b - 4 * a*c < 0&&a!=0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		else
		{
			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f", x1, x2);

		}
		
		if(a!=0)
		{
		    x2=x1=-b/c;
		    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f", x1, x2);
		}
	}

	return 0;

}

20190301054:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,temp;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
		temp=a,a=b,b=temp;
		
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
		temp=a,a=c,c=temp;
		
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		temp=c,c=b,b=temp;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>
#include<math.h>

int main()
{
	int i;
	double a, b, c;
	double x1, x2;

	for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
	{
		scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);

		if (b*b - 4 * a*c < 0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		else
		{
			x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;
			x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;


			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n", x1, x2);

		}
	}

	return 0;

}

	{
		scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);

		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		else

			x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;

20190318198:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>
#include<math.h>

int main()
{
	int i;
	double a, b, c;
	double x1, x2;

	for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
	{
		scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);

		if (b*b - 4 * a*c < 0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION ");
		}

		if(b*b - 4 * a*c > 0&&a!=0)
		{
			x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;
			x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4 * a*c)) / 2 * a;


			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n", x1, x2);

		}
		if(a=0)
		{
		    x1=x2=-b/c;
		    printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n", x1, x2);
		}
	}

	return 0;

}

main()
{
	double m,n,p,q,disc;
	int a,b,c;
	    disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		p=b/(2*a);
		q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		m=p+q;
		n=p-q;
		while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(q>0)
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		if(q==0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	double m,n,p,q,disc;
	int a,b,c;
		while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(q>0)
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		p=b/(2*a);
		q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		m=p+q;
		n=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		if(q==0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}

20190318103:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int y,a,b,c;
	scanf("%d",&y);
	a=y%4;b=y%100;c=y%400;
	if(a==0&&b!=0||c==0)
	printf("L");
	else
	printf("N");
	return 0;
}

20190302023:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,d,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	a=d-1;
	if(m==1||m==2) b=(m-1)*31+a;
	if(m==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(m==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(m==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(m==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(m==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(m==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(m==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(m==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(m==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(m==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
	switch(b)
    { 
	case 1:{printf("Monday");break;}
	case 2:{printf("Tuesday");break;}
	case 3:{printf("Wednesda");break;}
	case 4:{printf("Thursday");break;}
	case 5:{printf("Friday");break;}
	case 6:{printf("Saturday");break;}
	case 7:{printf("Sunday");break;}
	default:break;
    }
    return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	double m,n,p,q,disc;
	int a,b,c;
		while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		if(q>=0)
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		p=-b/(2*a);
		m=p+q;
		n=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		if(q==0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
}

20190318072:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		d=a;
		a=b;
		b=d;
	}
	if(a>c){
		d=a;
		a=c;
		c=d;
	}
	if(b>c){
		d=b;
		b=c;
		c=d;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

main()
{
	double m,n,p,q,disc;
	int a,b,c;
		while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q>=0)
	    q=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
		p=-b/(2*a);
		m=p+q;
		n=p-q;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",m,n);
		if(q<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}

20190318077:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        if(d>=0){
            x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	int b,c,d;
	b=a%4;
	c=a%100;
	d=a%400;
	if(b==0&&c!=0||d==0){
		printf("L",a);
	}
	else{
		printf("N",a);
	}
		return 0;
	
}

20190318198:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>

int main()
{
	int x, y;
	int today, month;
	int i;
	int num = 0;


	scanf("%d %d", &x, &y);

	if (x <= 8)
	{
		if (x % 2 == 0)
			num = 61 * x / 2 + y ;
		else
		{
			num = (x - 1) * 15 + 31 * (x + 1) / 2 + y;
		}
	}

	if (x > 8&&x%2==0)
	{
		num = 4 * 61 + (x - 8) * 61 / 2 + y ;
	}
	else
	{
		num = 4 * 61 + 15 * (x - 7) + 31 * (x - 9) / 2 + y ;
	}

	
	today = num % 7;

	if (today == 1)
		printf("Monday");
	if (today == 2)
		printf("Tuesday");
	if (today == 3)
		printf("Wednesday");
	if (today == 4)
		printf("Thursday");
	if (today == 5)
		printf("Friday");
	if (today == 6)
		printf("Saturday");
	if (today == 7)
		printf("Sunday");

	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,disc,x1,x2,m,n;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	else {
		m=-b/(2.0*a);
		n=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
		x1=m+n;x2=m-n;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		if(a<=999&&a>=100)
		{
		x=a/100;
		y=(a%100)/10;
		z=a/10;
		switch(x)
		{
			case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
			case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
			case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
			case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
			case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
			case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
			case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
			case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
			case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
			default:printf(""); 
		}
		switch(y)
		{
			case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
			case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
			case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
			case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
			case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
			case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
			case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
			case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
			case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
			default:
				{
					if(z==0) printf("");
					else printf("零");
				} 
		}
		switch(z)
		{
			case(1):printf("壹");break;
			case(2):printf("贰");break;
			case(3):printf("叁");break;
			case(4):printf("肆");break;
			case(5):printf("伍");break;
			case(6):printf("陆");break;
			case(7):printf("柒");break;
			case(8):printf("捌");break;
			case(9):printf("玖");break;
			default:printf("");
		}
		printf("元整\n");
	    }
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:{
					if(z==0) printf("");
					else printf("零");
				} 
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}
}

20190318162:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main(){
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);

	if(a>b){
		d=b;
		b=a;
		a=d;
	}
	if(a>c){
		d=c;
		c=a;
		a=d;
	}
	if(b>c){
		d=c;
		c=b;
		b=d;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,x,d,z;
     while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
    
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    x=(-2*a)/b;
    z=sqrt(d);
    x1=(-b+z)/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-z)/(2*a);
    if(d==0) printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x,x);
    if(d>0) printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
   if(d<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");

        default :c=c;}

    if(a==2)
	printf("Wednesday");

	if(a==6)

	if(a==0)
	printf("Monday");

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int m,d,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:a=0;break;
		case 2:a=31;break;
		case 3:a=59;break;
		case 4:a=90;break;
		case 5:a=120;break;
		case 6:a=151;break;
		case 7:a=181;break;
		case 8:a=212;break;
		case 9:a=243;break;
		case 10:a=273;break;
		case 11:a=304;break;
		case 12:a=335;break;
	}
	b=(a+d-1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{   case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

     while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);

    x=(-2*a)/b;
    z=sqrt(d);
    x1=(-b+z)/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-z)/(2*a);
    if(d==0) printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x,x);

   if(d<0) printf("NO SOLUTION");

20190318113:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,month,day,W;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	if(month==1||month==2)
	year=2018;
	else
	year=2019;
	W=(day+2*month+3*(month+1)/5+year+year/4-year/100+year/400)%7;
	switch(W)
	{
		case 0:printf("Monday");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }

#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
	int num;
	while (scanf("%d", &num) != EOF)
	{
		int n, u, m;
		n = num / 100;
		m = num % 10;
		u = ((num - n * 100) - m) / 10;

		char HTO[] = { "壹贰叁肆伍陆柒捌玖" };
			while (n)
			{
				printf("%c%c", HTO[2*n-2],HTO[2*n-1]);
				printf("佰");
				break;
			}
			while (u)
			{
				printf("%c%c", HTO[2*u - 2],HTO[2*u-1]);
				printf("拾");
				break;
			}
			while (m)
			{
				printf("%c%c", HTO[2*m - 2],HTO[2*m-1]);
				printf("元整\n");
				break;
			}
	}

	return 0;
}

{

		printf("L",y);
	else if (y%400==0)
	printf("L",y);

		printf("N",y);

20190318090:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c) printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	if(a>b&&a>c&&c>b) printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	if(b>a&&a>c) printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	if(b>a&&b>c&&a<c) printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	if(c>a&&a>b) printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	if(c>a&&c>b&&a<b) printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190318188:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
	int num;
	while (scanf("%d", &num) != EOF)
	{
		int n, u, m;
		n = num / 100;
		m = num % 10;
		u = ((num - n * 100) - m) / 10;

		char HTO[] = { "壹贰叁肆伍陆柒捌玖" };
		while (n)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * n - 2], HTO[2 * n - 1]);
			printf("佰");
			break;
		}
		while (u)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * u - 2], HTO[2 * u - 1]);
			printf("拾");
			break;
		}
		if (u == 0) {
			printf("零");
		}

		while (m)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * m - 2], HTO[2 * m - 1]);
			printf("元整\n");
			break;
		}
	}

	return 0;
}

20190318135:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
void trans(int a)
{
  if(a == 1)printf("壹");     
  else if(a == 2)printf("贰");    
  else if(a == 3)printf("叁");     
  else if(a == 4)printf("肆");     
  else if(a == 5)printf("伍");     
  else if(a == 6)printf("陆");     
  else if(a == 7)printf("柒");     
  else if(a == 8)printf("捌");     
  else if(a == 9)printf("玖"); 
  else if(a == 0)printf("零");    
}
  void weight(int i)
{  
  if(i==1||i==5||i==9)        
  printf("拾");    
  if(i==2||i==6||i==10)        
  printf("佰"); 
   if(i==0)
  printf("元整\n");
}
int main()
{	
while(1)	
{		
char a[10];		
scanf("%s",a);		
strrev(a);		
for(int i=strlen(a) - 1; a[i]; i--)		
{			
trans(a[i]-'0');			
weight(i);		
}	
}
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
	int num;
	while (scanf_s("%d", &num) != EOF)
	{
		int n, u, m;
		n = num / 100;
		m = num % 10;
		u = ((num - n * 100) - m) / 10;
		char HTO[] = { "壹贰叁肆伍陆柒捌玖" };
		while (n)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * n - 2], HTO[2 * n - 1]);
			printf("佰");
			break;
		}
		while (u)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * u - 2], HTO[2 * u - 1]);
			printf("拾");
			break;
		}
		if (u == 0 && m != 0) {
			printf("零");
		}


		while (m)
		{
			printf("%c%c", HTO[2 * m - 2], HTO[2 * m - 1]);
			printf("元整\n");
			break;
		}
		if (m == 0) {
			printf("元整");
		}
	}

	return 0;
}

	            case(4):printf("肆拾");break;

             	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
              	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
              	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
            	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
            }
	    switch(d)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹");break;
              	case(2):printf("贰");break;
            	case(3):printf("叁");break;
            	case(4):printf("肆");break;
            	case(5):printf("伍");break;
              	case(6):printf("陆");break;
             	case(7):printf("柒");break;

20190318022:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
}
if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
else x1=g,x2=f;
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
printf("x1=%.3lf~~~x2=%.3lf",x1,x2);
else
{
printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()

p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
}
if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
else x1=g,x2=f;

printf("x1=%.3lf~~~x2=%.3lf",x1,x2);

	            case(2):printf("贰佰");break;

20190318188:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
	int num=0;
	
	while (scanf("%d", &num) != EOF)
	{
		int n, u, m;
		n = num / 100;
		m = num % 10;
		u = ((num - n * 100) - m) / 10;

		char *HTO[] = { "壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖" };
		while (n)
		{
			printf("%s", HTO[n-1]);
			printf("佰");
			break;
		}
		while (u)
		{
			printf("%s", HTO[u-1]);
			printf("拾");
			break;
		}
		if (u == 0 && m != 0) {
			printf("零");
		}


		while (m)
		{
			printf("%s", HTO[m-1]);
			printf("元整\n");
			break;
		}
		if (m == 0) {
			printf("元整\n");
		}
	}

	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%1d%1d%1d",&b,&c,&d) !=EOF)
	{

		switch (b)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	            case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	            case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	            case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
              	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
             	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
             	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
              	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
              }
        switch(c)
            {
            	case 0:
            		if(c==0)
            		printf("");
            		else
            		printf("零");
					break;
	            case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	            case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	            case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
             	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
             	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
              	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
              	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
            	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
            }
	    switch(d)
            {
            	case(0):printf("元整");break;
	            case(1):printf("壹元整");break;
              	case(2):printf("贰元整");break;
            	case(3):printf("叁元整");break;
            	case(4):printf("肆元整");break;

20190318059:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x,y,m;	
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
			
	m=b*b-4*a*c;
	d=sqrt(m);
	x=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	y=(-b-d)/(2*a);
	if(m<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",1.0*x,1.0*y);
    }
}

20190302016:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	    {
		    x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	        x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
        else
	    {
		    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
    }
}

{

   {printf("YES\n",a);}
   else{
   printf("NO\n",a);}

            	case 0:
            		if(c==0)
            		printf("");
            		else
            		printf("零");
					break;
	            case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	            case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	            case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
             	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;

              	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
            	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
            }
	    switch(d)
            {
            	case(0):printf("元整\n");break;

              	case(2):printf("贰元整\n");break;

20190318113:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2.0*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    }
}

	double x1,x2;
	    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF){
	if(delta>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n\n",x1,x2);

	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}

20190301006:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main(void)
{
    int y, b = 0;
    scanf("%d", &y);
    if (y%4 == 0&&y%100 != 0)
    {
        b = 1;
    }
    if (y%400 == 0)
    {
        b = 1;
    }
    if (b)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
}
	switch(y)
{
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
}
	switch(z)
{
	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	case 9:printf("玖");break;
}
	printf("元整\n");}
}

20190302041:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char o,m,n,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&o,&m,&n);
	if(o>m){t=o;o=m;m=t;}
	if(o>n){t=o;o=n;n=t;}
	if(m>n){t=n;n=m;m=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c",o,m,n);
	
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a1,a2,a3,b1,b2,b3;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a1,&a2,&a3,&b1,&b2,&b3);
	if(a2*a2-4*a1*a3<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(a2*a2-4*a1*a3==0)printf("%d.000~~~%d.000\n",-a2/(2*a1),-a2/(2*a1));
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-a2+sqrt(a2*a2-4*a1*a3))/(2*a1),(-a2-sqrt(a2*a2-4*a1*a3))/(2*a1));
	if(b2*b2-4*b1*b3<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(b2*b2-4*b1*b3==0)printf("%d.000~~~%d.000\n",-b2/(2*b1),-b2/(2*b1));
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-b2+sqrt(b2*b2-4*b1*b3))/(2*b1),(-b2-sqrt(b2*b2-4*b1*b3))/(2*b1));
}

20190318026:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a1,a2,a3,b1,b2,b3,d1,d2;
	double a4,a5,b4,b5;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a1,&a2,&a3,&b1,&b2,&b3);
	d1=a2*a2-4*a1*a3;
	d2=b2*b2-4*b1*b3;
	a4=(-a2+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	a5=(-a2-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	b4=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*b1);
	b5=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*b1);
	if(d1<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(d1==0)printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",a4,a5);
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",a4,a5);
	if(d2<0)printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(d2==0)printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",b4,b5);
	else printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",b4,b5);
}

{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c))
	{
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		if(d>=0)
		{
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
}

	if(d>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);

20190318172:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
 
int main()
{
   char a[3], t;
   int i, j;
   
   for(i = 0; i < 3; i++)
   {
   		scanf("%c", &a[i]);
   }
	for(i = 0; i < 3; i++)
	{
		for(j = i + 1; j < 3; j++ )
		{
			if(a[i] > a[j])
			{
				t = a[i];
				a[i] = a[j];
				a[j] = t;
			}
		}
	}
   for(i = 0; i < 3; i++)
   {
   		printf("%c", a[i]);
   }
    return 0; 
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
x1=f,x2=g;
printf("x1=%.3lf~~~x2=%.3lf",x1,x2);}
else
{
printf("NO SOLUTION");}
return 0;
}

20190318134:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,disc;
    double x1,x2,d;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
      printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
     else
{
      d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
       x1=(-b+d)/(2.0*a);
       x2=(-b-d)/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
   double a, b, c, a1, b1, c1;
   scanf("%lf%lf%lf%lf%lf%lf", &a, &b, &c, &a1, &b1, &c1);
   if(b*b - 4*a*c >= 0)
   {
   		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",((0 - b) + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a),((0 - b) - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a));
   }
   else
   {
   		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
   }
   if(b1*b1 - 4*a1*c1 >= 0)
   {
   		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",((0 - b1) + sqrt(b1*b1 - 4*a1*c1))/(2*a1),((0 - b1) - sqrt(b1*b1 - 4*a1*c1))/(2*a1));
   }
   else
   {
   		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
   }
    return 0; 
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:w=(y+1)%7;break;
		case 2:w=(y+32)%7;break;
		case 3:w=(y+60)%7;break;
		case 4:w=(y+91)%7;break;
		case 5:w=(y+121)%7;break;
		case 6:w=(y+152)%7;break;
		case 7:w=(y+182)%7;break;
		case 8:w=(y+213)%7;break;
		case 9:w=(y+244)%7;break;
		case 10:w=(y+274)%7;break;
		case 11:w=(y+305)%7;break;
		case 12:w=(y+335)%7;break;
	}
	switch(w)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wedneesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

#include  <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,a;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%400==0)
	    a=1;
	else
	{
		if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
		     a=1;
		else
		     a=0;
	}
	if(a==1)
	{
		printf("L");
	}
	else
	{
		printf("N");
	}
	
}

20190302040:Problem1147:正确
/*解方程*/
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"

main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,d1;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1)!=EOF){
	d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	if(d1<0){
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
	x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	//return 0;
}
	
 }

20190318172:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int mouth[12] = {31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int m,d,i,t = 0;
	scanf("%d,%d", &m, &d);
	for(i = 0; i < m - 1; i++)
	{
		t += mouth[i];
	}
	t += d - 1;
	t = (t + 2) % 7;
	switch(t)
	{
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	} 
    return 0; 
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
    if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
    if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
 }

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,n,p,k;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&m)!=EOF){
	n=m/100;
	p=(m%100)/10;
	k=m%10;
	switch(n)
{
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	default:break;
}
	switch(p)
{
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	default:break;
}
	switch(k)
{
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;

	default:break;
}

	printf("元整\n");}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,x;
	scanf("%d",&x);
	a=x/100;
	b=(x-a*100)/10;
	c=(x-a*100-b*10);
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
    }
	switch(b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		default:if(c!=0)printf("零");break; 
	}
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
		case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
		case 3:printf("叁元整");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整");break;

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,x;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
    {
	a=x/100;
	b=(x-a*100)/10;
	c=(x-a*100-b*10);
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
    }
	switch(b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		default:if(c!=0)printf("零");break; 
	}
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
		case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
		case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
		case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		default:printf("元整\n");break;
	}
    }
