20190318078:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,MONTH;
	int z=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	//x=x-1; 
	if(x==2) 
	{
		b=31+28+y;
		b=b%7+1;
		printf("%d",b);
		switch(b){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
		case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
		case 5:
		break;
		printf("Friday");
		break;
		case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;	
		case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		break;
	} 
		return 0;
	} 
	else if(x%2==0&&x!=2&&x<8||x==9||x==10)//偶数
	{MONTH=30;} 
	else if(x%2==1&&x<8||x==10||x==12)//奇数月
	{MONTH=31;}
	switch(x){
	case 3:z=-3;
	break;
	case 10:z=-4;
	break;
	case 11:z=+3;
	break;
	case 12:z=0;
	break; 
	case 5:z=-4;
	break;
	case 6:z=+1;
	break;
	case 7:z=-5;
	break;
	case 8:z=+2;
	break;
	case 9:z=-4;
	break;}
		
	x=x-1;
	a=x*MONTH+y+z;//month=月份天数 
	a=a%7+1;
//	printf("%d",a);
	switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
		case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
		case 5:
		break;
		printf("Friday");
		break;
		case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;	
		case 7:

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,f;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	f=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(f<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	if(f>=0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(f))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(f))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
}

20190318090:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
 
int main()
{
        double a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
        while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
        {
		if(a!=0)
        {
                d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                if(d>=0)
                {
				x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(x1<x2) 
                    printf("%0.2f~~~%0.3lf\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("%0.2f~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
                    else
                    printf("NO SOLUTION");
        }
        
        return 0;}
}

20190318180:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,x;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){x=a;a=b;b=x;}
	if(a>c){x=a;a=c;c=x;}
	if(b>c){x=c;c=b;b=x;}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

20180318109:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char A,B,C,t;
	A=getchar();B=getchar();C=getchar();
	if(A>B)
	{
		t=A;A=B;B=t;
	}
	if(A>C)
	{
		t=A;A=C;C=t;
	}
	if(B>C)
	{
		t=B;B=C;C=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",A,B,C);
}

	f=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(f<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	if(f>=0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(f))/(2*a);

    a[7]=31;a[8]=31;a[9]=30;a[10]=31;a[11]=30;a[12]=31;
    for(i=1;i<x;i++)
       d=d+a[i];
	d1=d%7;
	    if (d1==6){printf("Sunday");}

		c=t;

		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;

20190318089:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if((a>b)&&(b>c))
	{
	d=a;a=c;c=d;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	else if((a<b)&&(b>c)&&(a<c))
	{d=b;b=c;c=d;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	else if((a<b)&&(b<c))
	{printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	else if((a<b)&&(b>c)&&(a>c))
	{
	d=b;b=a;a=c;c=d;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	else if((a>b)&&(b<c)&&(a>c))
	{
	d=a;a=b;b=c;c=d;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	else
	{
	d=a;a=b;b=d;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,d,d1;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    if(x=1) d=y;
    else if(x=2) d=y+31;
    else if(x=3) d=y+59;
    else if(x=4) d=y+90;
    else if(x=5) d=y+120;
    else if(x=6) d=y+151;
    else if(x=7) d=y+181;
    else if(x=8) d=y+212;
    else if(x=9) d=y+243;
    else if(x=10) d=y+273;
    else if(x=11)d=y+304;
    else if(x=12) d=y+334;
    d1=d%7;
    switch(d1)
    {case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
    case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
    case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
    case 4:printf("Friday");break;
    case 5:printf("Satueday");break;
    case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
    case 0:printf("Monday");break;
	}
}

20190318090:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
 
int main()
{
        int a,b,c,x1,x2,d;
        while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
        if(a!=0)
       {
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
                d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                if(x1<x2) 
                    printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x2,x1); 
                else
                    printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
        if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
        return 0;}
}

#include<stdio.h> 
#include <math.h>
main(){
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,m;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	m=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(m>=0){
	
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1=(-b+sqrt(m))/(2*a),x2=(-b-sqrt(m))/(2*a));}
    else {
	
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,d,d1;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
    {case 1:d=y+1;break;
	case 2:d=32+y;break;
	case 3:d=60+y;break;
    case 4:d=91+y;break;
    case 5:d=121+y;break;
	case 6:d=152+y;break;
	case 7:d=182+y;break;
	case 8:d=y+213;break;
	case 9:d=y+244;break;
	case 10:d=y+274;break;
    case 11:d=y+305;break;
	case 12:d=y+335;break;}
	d1=d%7;
	    if (d1==0)printf("Sunday");
	    else if(d1==1)printf("Monday");
		else if(d1==2)printf("Tuesday");
		else if(d1==3)printf("Wednesday");
		else if(d1==4)printf("Thursday");
		else if(d1==5)printf("Friday");
		else if(d1==6)printf("Saturday");
}

20190301028:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h" 
main()
{
	double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
    	if(a!=0)
    	{
    		d=(b*b-4*a*c);
    		if(d>=0)
    		{
    			x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    			if(x1<x2)
    			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
    			if(x1>=x2)
    			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
			}
			if(d<0)
			{
				printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		   }
	   }
   }
}

20190318097:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc,p,q;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc>=0)
{
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	x1=p+q;x2=p-q;
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
}

20190302045:Problem1158:答案错误
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int number,bai,shi,ge;
	while(scanf("%d",&number)!=EOF){
		bai=number/100;
		shi=number%100/10;
		ge=number%100%10;
		switch(bai)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(shi)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(shi==0&&ge!=0){
			printf("零");   //例：101 
		}else if(shi!=0&&ge==0){
			printf("元整");   //例：110 
		} 
		else if(shi==0&&ge==0){
			printf("元整");  //例：100 
		}
		switch(ge)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整");break;

main()
{

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
		int a[100]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	for (i=0;i<x-1;i++)
	{
		sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;
	m=sum%7;
	switch(m) 
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,b,d,sum;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	int a[100]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	for (b=0;b<x-1;b++)
	{
		sum+=a[b];
	}
	sum+=y;
	d=sum%7;
	switch(d) 
	{
		case 0:printf("Monday");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

20190318097:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc,p,q;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
{
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
{
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	x1=p+q;x2=p-q;
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int number,bai,shi,ge;
	while(scanf("%d",&number)!=EOF){
		bai=number/100;
		shi=number%100/10;
		ge=number%100%10;
		switch(bai)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(shi)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(shi==0&&ge!=0){
			printf("零");   //例：101 
		}else if(shi!=0&&ge==0){
			printf("元整\n");   //例：110 
		} 
		else if(shi==0&&ge==0){
			printf("元整\n");  //例：100 
		}
		switch(ge)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;

main()
{

	int m,d,s,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	s=int(xz[m]);
	s=s+(d-1);
	z=s%7;
	if(z==0)
	{
		printf("Tuesday"); 
	}
	if(z==1)
	{
		printf("Wednesday");
	}
	if(z==2)
	{
		printf("Thursday");
	}

	{
		printf("Friday");
	}
	if(z==4)
	{
		printf("Saturday");
	}

	{
		printf("Sunday");
	}

		printf("Monday");

	printf("NO SOLUTION");

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int xz[13] = {0,0,31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334};
	int m,d,s,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	s=int(xz[m]);
	s=s+(d-1);
	z=s%7;
	if(z==0)
	{
		printf("Tuesday\n"); 
	}
	if(z==1)
	{
		printf("Wednesday\n");
	}
	if(z==2)
	{
		printf("Thursday\n");
	}
	if(z==3)
	{
		printf("Friday\n");
	}
	if(z==4)
	{
		printf("Saturday\n");
	}
	if(z==5)
	{
		printf("Sunday\n");
	}
	if(z==6)
	{
		printf("Monday\n");
	}
	
}

20190318084:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    int a, b, c, disc;
    double x1, x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
	{
        disc=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
            if (disc<0)
               printf("NO SOLUTION");
            else
			{
                x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n", x1, x2);
            }
    }
}

20190301048:Problem1158:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,x;
	char *m[]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	char *n[]={"元","整","佰","拾"}; 
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=x/10%10;
		c=x%10;
		if (b!=0 && c!=0){
			printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",m[a],m[b],m[c]);
		}
	if(b!=0 && c==0){
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",m[a],m[b]);
	}
	if(m==0 && c==0){
		printf("%s佰元整\n",m[a]);
	}
	}
 }

20190318084:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    int a, b, c, disc;
    double x1, x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
	{
        disc=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
            if (disc<0)
               printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
            else
			{
                x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n", x1, x2);
            }
    }
}

20190318097:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

		c=x%10;

			printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",m[a],m[b],m[c]);
		}
		if (b==0 && c!=0){
		    printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",m[a],m[c]);

main()
{

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);

	t=n%7;
	switch(t)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int y=2019,m,d,c,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
    if(m==1||m==2)
    { y=y-1; m=m+12;}
    c=m+1;
    w=(d+2*m+3*c/5+y+y/4-y/100+y/400+1)%7;
    while(w<0)
    { w=w+7; w=w%7;}
	if(w==0) printf("Sunday");
	if(w==1) printf("Monday\n");
	if(w==2) printf("Tuesday\n");
	if(w==3) printf("Wendnesday\n");	
	if(w==4) printf("Thursday\n");
	if(w==5) printf("Friday\n");
	if(w==6) printf("Saturday\n");

20190318173:Problem1034:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
  char ch;
  scanf("%c",&ch);
  if(ch>='a'&&ch<='z'||ch>='A'&&ch<='Z')
  printf("NO\n");
  else if(ch>='0'&&ch<='9')
  printf("YES\n");
  else
  printf("NO\n");
}

20190318173:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c); 
	scanf("%d %d %d",&e,&f,&g);
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);		
		printf("%4.3f~~~%4.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	h=f*f-4*e*g;
	if(h<0)
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else{
		x3=(-f+sqrt(h))/(2*e);
		x4=(-f-sqrt(h))/(2*e);		
		printf("%4.3f~~~%4.3f",x3,x4);
	}
 }

20190318145:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,delta;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318145:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int A,B,first,mid,last;
    while(scanf("%d",&A)!=EOF)
    {
    	first=A/100;
    	mid=(A/10)%10;
    	last=A%10;
		switch(first)
	    {
	    	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	    	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	    	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	    	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	    	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	    	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	    	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖");break;
		}
    	printf("佰");
		 
    	switch(mid)
	    {
	    	case 0:
	    		if(last!=0)
	    		printf("零");break;
	    	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	    	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	    	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	    	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	    	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	    	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	    	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		 
    	switch(last)
	    {
	    	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	    	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	    	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	    	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	    	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	    	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	    	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖");break;
		}
	printf("元整\n");	
	}
    
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x,y,m;	
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
			
	m=b*b-4*a*c;
	d=sqrt(m);
	x=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	y=(-b-d)/(2*a);
	if(m<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",1.0*x,1.0*y);
    }
}

20190302051:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int x,y,z,i,a;
    while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {   
        char *i[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","零"};
        x=a/100;//百位 
        y=a/10-10*x;//十位 
        z=a%10;//个位 
        if(y==0&&z==0)
        printf("%s佰元整\n",i[x-1]);
        if(y!=0&&z==0)
        printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",i[x-1],i[y-1]);
        if(y==0&&z!=0)
        printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",i[x-1],i[z-1]);
        if(y!=0&&z!=0)
        printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",i[x-1],i[y-1],i[z-1]);
    }
}

20190302035:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
float a,b,c;
double x1,x2,s;
scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF;
do 
{
    s=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(s>=0) 
    {
        x1=(-b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
    }
    else if(s<0)  
    {
    	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
}
while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{

	int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	char *week[8]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&m2,&d2);
	m1=1;
	d1=1;
	day=0;
	for(i=1;i<m2;i++)
	{
		day+=days[i-1];
	}
	w=(day+d2)%7;
	printf("%s",week[w]);
}

	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:d=(y+1)%7;break;
		case 2:d=(32+y)%7;break;
		case 3:d=(60+y)%7;break;
		case 4:d=(91+y)%7;break;
		case 5:d=(121+y)%7;break;

		case 7:d=(182+y)%7;break;
		case 8:d=(213+y)%7;break;
		case 9:d=(244+y)%7;break;
		case 10:d=(174+y)%7;break;
		case 11:d=(305+y)%7;break;
		case 12:d=(335+y)%7;break;
	}
	switch(d)
	{
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;

20190318176:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
}

20190302008:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double m,z,x1,x2;
	while(~scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)){
		z=b*b-4*a*c;
		if ( z<0 ) {
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
		else {
			m=pow(z,0.5);
			x1=0.5*(-b+m);
			x2=0.5*(-b-m);
			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x1,x2);
	}
}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
    double disc,x1,x2,p,q;
    disc=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(disc<0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    else
    {
        p=-b/(2.0*a);
        q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
        x1=p+q;
        x2=p-q;
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    }
    
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c,d,x;
scanf("%d",&a);
do
{
b=a/100;
c=(a-100*b)/10;
d=a%10;
x=a%100;
if(x==0)
{
switch((int)(a/100))
{
case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
}
}
else if(x!=0)
{
	switch((int)b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("三百");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch((int)c)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break; 
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch((int)d)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
		case 9:printf("玖");break;
	}
}
	printf("元整\n"); 
}

20190318180:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,f;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	f=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(f<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
	else if(f>=0)
	{
    	x1=(-b+sqrt(f))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(f))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
}
    return 0;
}

main()
{

	while (a>0) {
		b=a%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
		}
		a=a/10;
		if (c==3){
			printf("佰");
			c --;
		}
		else if (c==2){
			printf("拾");
			c --;
		}
    }
    printf("元整");

20190318059:Problem1158:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=x/10-a*10;
		c=x-a*100-b*10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");	break;
		    case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");	break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");	break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");	break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");	break;
		}
		
		if(b==0&&c==0)
		printf("元整\n");
		else
	{
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");	break;
		    case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");	break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");	break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");	break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");	break;
			case 0:printf("零");	break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
		    case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
			case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
		}
	}
		
				
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c,d;
scanf("%d",&a);
if(a>99&&a<1000)
{
do
{
b=a/100;
c=(a-100*b)/10;
d=a%10;
if(a%100==0)
{
switch((int)(a/100))
{
case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
}
}
else if(a%100!=0)
{
	switch((int)b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("三百");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch((int)c)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break; 
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch((int)d)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
		case 9:printf("玖");break;
	}
}
	printf("元整\n"); 
}

20190302008:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double m,z,x1,x2;
	while(~scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)){
		z=b*b-4*a*c;
		if ( z<0 ) {
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
		else {
			m=pow(z,0.5);
			x1=0.5*(-b+m)/a;
			x2=0.5*(-b-m)/a;
			printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
}
}

20190302012:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a;
	int b;
	int c=3;
	int digit;
	int ret=0;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	while (a>0){
		digit=a%10;
		ret=ret*10+digit;
		a=a/10;
	}
	while (ret>0) {
		b=ret%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: break;
		}
		ret=ret/10;
		if (b>0&&c==3){
			printf("佰");
			c --;
		}
		else if (b>0&&c==2){
			printf("拾");
			c --;
		}
    }
    printf("元整");
}

#include<stdio.h>

main()
{      
    char x[10][10]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
    int a,b,c,d;
    while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
    b=a/100%10;
    c=a/10%10;
    d=a%10;
    //printf("%d%d%d",b,c,d);
    if(b*c*d!=0)
      printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整",x[b],x[c],x[d]);
    if(c!=0&&d==0)
      printf("%s佰%s拾元整",x[b],x[c]);
    if(c==0&&d!=0)
      printf("%s佰零%s元整",x[b],x[d]);
    if(c==0&&d==0)
      printf("%s佰元整",x[b]);
    }
    
}

    while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
    b=a/100%10;
    c=a/10%10;
    d=a%10;
    //printf("%d%d%d",b,c,d);
    if(b*c*d!=0)
      printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",x[b],x[c],x[d]);
    if(c!=0&&d==0)
      printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",x[b],x[c]);
    if(c==0&&d!=0)
      printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",x[b],x[d]);

20190318005:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
    double disc,x1,x2,p,q;
    disc=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(disc<0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    else
    {
        p=-b/(2.0*a);
        q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
        x1=p+q;
        x2=p-q;
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    }
}
    
}

20190302033:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>


int main()
{
int year,leap_year;
scanf("%d",&year);
if(year%400==0)
{
leap_year=1;
printf("L");
}
else if(year%100==0)
{
leap_year=0;
printf("N");
}
else if(year%4==0)
{
leap_year=1;
printf("L");
} 
else
{
leap_year=0;
printf("N");
}

}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c,d;
scanf("%d",&a);
if(a>99&&a<1000)
{
do
{
b=a/100;
c=(a-100*b)/10;
d=a%10;
	switch((int)b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("三百");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
if((c==0&&d!=0)||(c!=0&&d!=0)||(c!=0&&d==0))
{
	switch((int)c)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break; 
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch((int)d)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
		case 9:printf("玖");break;
	}
}
else if(c==0&&d==0)
{
	printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n"); 
}
while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF);
}
}

20190318121:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()

{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		if(a>c){
			if(b>c){
				printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
			}
		}else{
			printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
		}
	}else{
		if(b>c){
			if(a>c){
				printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a,b);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c\n",a,c,b);
			}
		}else{
			printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
			
		}
	}
	
}

20190318080:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
		else if(t==0)
		{
			x1=-b/(2*a);
			x2=x1;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
		else 
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
	}
}

20190302033:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
 char a,b,c,t;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  t=a;
  a=b;
  b=t;
 }
 if(a>c)
 {
  t=a;
  a=c;
  c=t;
     }
    if(b>c)
     {
  t=c;
  c=b;
  b=t;
     }
     printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
     return 0;
}

main()
{

while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{

d=a%10;
	switch((int)b)
	{
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("三百");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;

		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}

{
	printf("");
}	
else

	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;

		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;

		case 3:m=31+28+y;break;
		case 4:m=31+28+31+y;break;
		case 5:m=31+28+31+30+y;break;

		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;

#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ( "%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) {
y--; 
m += 12;
}
c=y/ 100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w<0)w+=7;
w%=7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190318042:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>          //2019年1月1日是星期二，2019年x月y日是星期几。
main()
{
	int x,y,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x){
	case 1:
	n=(y+1)%7;       // printf("%d",n); //n=0即为星期天 
	break;
	case 2:
	n=(31+y+1)%7;     //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 3:
	n=(31+28+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 4:
	n=(31+28+31+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 5:
	n=((31+28+31+30)+y+1)%7; //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 6:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 7:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 8:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30+31)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 9:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 10:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 11:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
	case 12:
	n=((31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30)+y+1)%7;  //printf("%d",n);
	break;
   	} 
	switch(n){
		case 1:
		    printf("Monday\n");
		    break;
		case 2:
		    printf("Tuesday\n");
			break;	
		case 3:
		    printf("Wednesday\n");
			break;		
		case 4:
		    printf("Thursday\n");
		    break;
		case 5:
		    printf("Friday\n");
		    break;
		case 6:
		    printf("Saturday\n");
		    break;
		case 0:
		    printf("Sunday\n");		
	        break;
			}
}

#include   <stdio.h>

main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b) 
	{
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
		
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;
		
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190302035:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
	{
		a=n/100;b=(n-a*100)/10;c=n%10;
		switch (a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch (b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if (b==0&&c!=0) printf("零");
		if (b==0&&c==0) printf("");
		if (b!=0&&c==0)
		{printf("");}
		else
		{
		switch (c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹");break;
			case 2:printf("贰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁");break;
			case 4:printf("肆");break;
			case 5:printf("伍");break;
			case 6:printf("陆");break;
			case 7:printf("柒");break;
			case 8:printf("捌");break;
			case 9:printf("玖");break;	 
	    }
        }
        printf("元整\n");
	}
 }

20190318153:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) !=EOF){
	double x1,x2;
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;	
	if(delta>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}else
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a-x*100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
}
if(y!=0)
{
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}
	else
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("零壹元整\n");break;
	case(2):printf("零贰元整\n");break;
	case(3):printf("零叁元整\n");break;
	case(4):printf("零肆元整\n");break;
	case(5):printf("零伍元整\n");break;
	case(6):printf("零陆元整\n");break;
	case(7):printf("零柒元整\n");break;
	case(8):printf("零捌元整\n");break;
	case(9):printf("零玖元整\n");break;
	case(0):printf("元整\n");

	}}

20190318176:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3f~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            }}
}

	if(d>=0){
	
	double x,y;

#include   <stdio.h>
#include   <math.h>
void main()
{
	int a,b,c,x,y,z,t1,t2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&x,&y,&z);
	t1=b*b-4*a*c,t2=y*y-4*x*z;
	if(t1<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		x1=(-b-sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t2<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x3=(-y+sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		x4=(-y-sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

20190318158:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int r,w,x,disc;
scanf("%d %d %d",&r, &w, &x);
double x1,x2;
disc=w*w-4*r*x;
x1=(-w+sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
x2=(-w-sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
if(disc<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
else if(disc>=0)
{
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
}    return 0;
}

20190318001:Problem1147:答案错误
#include   <stdio.h>
#include   <math.h>
void main()
{
	int a,b,c,x,y,z,t1,t2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&x,&y,&z);
	t1=b*b-4*a*c,t2=y*y-4*x*z;
	if(t1<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		x1=(-b-sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t2<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x3=(-y+sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		x4=(-y-sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

#include   <stdio.h>
#include   <math.h>
 main()
{
	int a,b,c,x,y,z,t1,t2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&x,&y,&z);
	t1=b*b-4*a*c,t2=y*y-4*x*z;
	if(t1<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		x1=(-b-sqrt(t1) )/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t2<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else
	{
		x3=(-y+sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		x4=(-y-sqrt(t2) )/(2*x);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()

{
	int a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2,e;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	e=sqrt (d);
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(d=0){
	
	x1=(-b)/(2*a);
	printf("%f~~~%f",x1,x1);
	}if(d>0){
		x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
		
	printf("%f~~~%f",x1,x2);
    }
}

20190318176:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

	{
	
	
	t1=b*b-4*a*c,t2=y*y-4*x*z;

		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

20190318162:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d>=0){
			x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
		return 0;
	
}

20190301012:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
#include<string.h>
main()
{
	int s,m,n,q;
	char*p[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while(scanf("%d",&s)!=EOF){
		m=s/100;
		n=(s-m*100)/10;
		q=s%10;
		if(n==0&&q==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",p[m-1]);
		else if(n!=0&&q==0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",p[m-1],p[n-1]);
		else if(n==0&&q!=0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",p[m-1],p[q-1]);
		else if(n!=0&&q!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",p[m-1],p[n-1],p[q-1]);
	}

}

20190318040:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main ()
{
	int found;
	double x1,x2,n,a,b,c,m;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		m=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(m>=0)
		{
			found=1;
			n=sqrt((double)m);
			x1=(-b+n)/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-n)/(2*a);
		}
		else
			found=0;

		if(found==0)
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		if(found==1)
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}	
}

20190318133:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char ha,hb,hc,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&ha,&hb,&hc);
	if (ha>hb) {t=ha;ha=hb;hb=t;};
	if (ha>hc) {t=ha;ha=hc;hc=t;};
	if (hb>hc) {t=hc;hc=hb;hb=t;};
	printf("%c%c%c\n",ha,hb,hc);
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
mian()
{
	int a,b,x,y,z;
	z=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31;
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default:
        	return 28;
	}
	for(x=1;x<13;x++){
		z=x+z;
	} 
	a=z+y;
	b=a%7;
	switch (b)
    {
        case 5:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 0:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
 }

main()
{

    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a>b&&b>c){
    	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);	
	}
	if(a>c&&c>b){
		printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	}
	if(b>a&&a>c){
		printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	}
	if(b>c&&c>a){
		printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	}
	if(c>a&&a>b){
		printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	}
	if(c>b&&b>a){
		printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int a,b,c,s;
    scanf("%d",&s);
    a=s/100;
    b=(s-a*100)/10;
    c=s%10;
    if(a==1) printf("壹佰");
    if(a==2) printf("贰佰");
    if(a==3) printf("叁佰");
    if(a==4) printf("肆佰");
    if(a==5) printf("伍佰");
    if(a==6) printf("陆佰");
    if(a==7) printf("柒佰");
    if(a==8) printf("捌佰");
    if(a==9) printf("玖佰");
    
    if(b==1) printf("壹拾");
    if(b==2) printf("贰拾");
    if(b==3) printf("叁拾");
    if(b==4) printf("肆拾");
    if(b==5) printf("伍拾");
    if(b==6) printf("陆拾");
    if(b==7) printf("柒拾");
    if(b==8) printf("捌拾");
    if(b==9) printf("玖拾");
    if(b==0&&c==0) printf("");
    if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零");
    
    if(c==1) printf("壹");
    if(c==2) printf("贰");
    if(c==3) printf("叁");
    if(c==4) printf("肆");
    if(c==5) printf("伍");
    if(c==6) printf("陆");
    if(c==7) printf("柒");
    if(c==8) printf("捌");
    if(c==9) printf("玖");
    if(c==0) printf("");
    
    printf("元整");
    
    return 0;
}

20190302010:Problem1069:正确
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,i;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) {i=a;a=b;b=i;}
	if (a>c) {i=a;a=c;c=i;}
	if (b>c) {i=c;c=b;b=i;}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2;
	double x1,x2,de1,de2;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a2,&b2,&c2);
	de1=sqrt(b1*b1-4*a1*c1);
	if(de1>=0)
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-b1+de1)/(2*a1),(-b1-de1)/(2*a1));
	else
	 printf("NO SOLUTION");
	de2=sqrt(b2*b2-4*a2*c2);
	if(de2>=0)
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(-b2+de2)/(2*a2),(-b2-de2)/(2*a2));
	else
	 printf("NO SOLUTION");

main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2;
	double x1,x2,de1,de2;
	scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a2,&b2,&c2);
	de1=sqrt(b1*b1-4*a1*c1);
	if(de1>=0)
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(de1-b1)/(2*a1),(-de1-b1)/(2*a1));
	else
	 printf("NO SOLUTION");
	de2=sqrt(b2*b2-4*a2*c2);
	if(de2>=0)
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",(de2-b2)/(2*a2),(de2-b2)/(2*a2));
	else
	 printf("NO SOLUTION");
}

	switch(c)
	{

20190318006:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,a,b,c;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	a=year%4;
	b=year%100;
	c=year%400;
	if (a==0&&b!=0)
	{
		printf("L\n");
	}
	else if (c==0)
	{
		printf("L\n");
	}
	else
	{
		printf("N\n");
	}
}

main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c)
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	if(a>c&&c>b)
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	if(c>b&&b>a)
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	if(c>a&&a>b)
	printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	if(b>c&&c>a)
    printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
    if(b>a&&a>c)
    printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
}

#include<stdio.h>
void main()
{
    int a,b,c,temp;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(b<a) 
    { 
        temp=a;a=b;b=temp;
    }
    if(c<b)
    {
        temp=b;b=c;c=temp;
    }
    if(b<a) 
    {
        temp=a;a=b;b=temp;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,dt;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	double x1,x2;
	dt=(b*b-4*a*c);
	if(dt<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else    {
		x1=(-b+sqrt(dt))/2*a;
		x2=(-b-sqrt(dt))/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
  }
}

int main()
{
	int x,y,c,d,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=0;break;
		case 2:t=31;break;
		case 3:t=59;break;
		case 4:t=90;break;
		case 5:t=120;break;
		case 6:t=151;break;
		case 7:t=181;break;
		case 8:t=212;break;
		case 9:t=243;break;
		case 10:t=273;break;
		case 11:t=304;break;
		case 12:t=334;break;
	}
	d=t+y+1;
	c=d%7;
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;

20190318009:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ( "%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) {
y--; 
m += 12;
}
c=y/ 100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w<0)w+=7;
w%=7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190318189:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	
	if(x>y){
		if(y>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
		}else{
			if(x>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",y,z,x);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",y,x,z);
			}
		}
	}else{
		if(x>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
		}else{
			if(y>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",x,z,y);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
			}
		}
	}
}

20190302023:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
	if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	b=a/100;
	c=(a-b*100)/10;
	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	switch(b)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:break;
    }
	switch(c)
     {
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:break;
    }
	switch(d)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:break;
    }
    printf("元整\n"); 
    }
    }
}

20190318040:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main ()
{
	char a,b,c;
	int d,e,f,temp;
	a=getchar();
	b=getchar();
	c=getchar();
	d=(int)a;
	e=(int)b;
	f=(int)c;
	if(e<d) 
    { 
        temp=d;d=e;e=temp;
    }
    if(f<e)
    {
        temp=e;e=f;f=temp;
    }
    if(e<d) 
    {
        temp=d;d=e;e=temp;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c",d,e,f);
}

20190318006:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delt1,d,e,f,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	delt1=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	x1=(-b+delt1)/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-delt1)/(2*a);
	delt2=sqrt(e*e-4*d*f);
	x3=(-e+delt2)/(2*d);
	x4=(-e-delt2)/(2*d);
	if (delt1<0&&delt2<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}
	if (delt1>=0&&delt2<0)
	{
		printf("%.3ld~~~%.3ld\n",x1,x2);
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}
	if (delt1<0&&delt2>=0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		printf("%.3ld~~~%.3ld\n",x3,x4);
	}
	if (delt1>=0&&delt2>=0)
	{
		printf("%.3ld~~~%.3ld\n",x1,x2);
		printf("%.3ld~~~%.3ld\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delt1,d,e,f,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	delt1=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	x1=(-b+delt1)/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-delt1)/(2*a);
	delt2=sqrt(e*e-4*d*f);
	x3=(-e+delt2)/(2*d);
	x4=(-e-delt2)/(2*d);
	if (delt1<0&&delt2<0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}
	if (delt1>=0&&delt2<0)
	{
		printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}
	if (delt1<0&&delt2>=0)
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x3,x4);
	}
	if (delt1>=0&&delt2>=0)
	{
		printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

20190318001:Problem1158:答案错误
#include   <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x;
	while (scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=x%100;
		c=b/10;
		d=b%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(d)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("零壹");break;
			case 2:printf("零贰");break;
			case 3:printf("零叁");break;
			case 4:printf("零肆");break;
			case 5:printf("零伍");break;
			case 6:printf("零陆");break;
			case 7:printf("零柒");break;
			case 8:printf("零捌");break;
			case 9:printf("零玖");break;

		printf("元整");

20190302029:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include "math.h"  
main()  
{  
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,d;  
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){

d=b*b-4*a*c;  

if(d < 0)  
{


printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
}
if (d>=0)  {

  
x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);  
x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);  
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delt;
	double x1,x2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delt=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
	x1=(-b+delt)/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-delt)/(2*a);
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if (delt>=0)
		  printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		else
	      printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}

20190318001:Problem1158:正确
#include   <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,x;
	while (scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=x%100;
		c=b/10;
		d=b%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(c==0)
		{
			switch(d)
			{
			    case 0:printf("");break;
			    case 1:printf("零壹");break;
		     	case 2:printf("零贰");break;
			    case 3:printf("零叁");break;
		    	case 4:printf("零肆");break;
			    case 5:printf("零伍");break;
			    case 6:printf("零陆");break;
			    case 7:printf("零柒");break;
			    case 8:printf("零捌");break;
			    case 9:printf("零玖");break;
			}
		}
		else
		{
			switch(d)
			{
				case 0:printf("");break;
			    case 1:printf("壹");break;
		     	case 2:printf("贰");break;
			    case 3:printf("叁");break;
		    	case 4:printf("肆");break;
			    case 5:printf("伍");break;
			    case 6:printf("陆");break;
			    case 7:printf("柒");break;
			    case 8:printf("捌");break;
			    case 9:printf("玖");break;
			}
		}
		printf("元整\n");
	}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0)
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);		
	printf("%4.3f~~~%4.3f\n",x1,x2);
     }
   }
}

{
	de=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);	
	x1=(-b+de)/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-de)/(2*a);
	if(de>=0)
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else
	 printf("NO SOLUTION");
}

20190301004:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
#include<math.h>
main() 
{ 
	int a,b,c;
	double disc,x1,x2,p,q;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	x1=p+q;
	x2=p-q; 
	if(disc>=0)
	   printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	} 
}
}

20190318169:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d", &year);
    if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0){
        printf("L");
    }
    else{
        printf("N");
    }
}

20190318153:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int get_days ( int x)
{
    switch (x)
    {
        case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31;
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default:

                return 28;
    }
}

void print_week(int weekday)
{
    switch (weekday)
    {
        case 3:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 0:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
}

int main()
{
    int x,y, i;

    scanf  ("%d,%d", &x, &y);

    int sum = 0;

    print_week (sum % 7);

    return 0;
}

	t=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=((-b)+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
	x2=((-b)-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
	{
		if(t>=0)
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		if(t<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

20190318006:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,sum,a;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
	}
	a=(sum+y+1)%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		default:printf("Sunday\n");break;
	}
}

	if(d<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(d>=0)
	{
		x1 = ((-b)+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
		x2 = ((-b)-sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);

	 printf("NO SOLUTION ");

	{x1=-(b/2*a);
	 printf("%.3f",x1);
	}
	if(delta>0)
	{x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
     x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	 printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);

20190318143:Problem1147:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,delta;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delta=b^2-4*a*c;
	x1=(-b+delta)/2*a;x2=(-b-delta)/2*a;
	if(delta>=0)
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

main()
{

	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{

		printf("NO SOLUTION ");

		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);

20190301006:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main(void)
{
    char n[10], p;
    gets(n);
    for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++)
    {
        for (int j = i + 1; j < 3; j++)
        {
            if (n[j] < n[i])
            {
                p = n[i];
                n[i] = n[j];
                n[j] = p;
            }
        }
    }
    puts(n);
    return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	  { if(a>=100&&a<=999) {
	  	b=a/100;
	  	c=(a%100)/10;
	      d=a-b-c;
	      if(c==0&&d==0){
	      	switch(b){
	      	case 1:printf("壹佰元整");break;
	      	case 2:printf("贰佰元整");break;
	      	case 3:printf("叁佰元整");break;
	      	case 4:printf("肆佰元整");break;
	      	case 5:printf("伍佰元整");break;
	      	case 6:printf("陆佰元整");break;

	      	case 8:printf("捌佰元整");break;
	      	case 9:printf("玖佰元整");break;   
	      	default :printf("");} }

	      	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
    while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{  
	a=n/100;
	b=(n-a*100)/10;
	c=n%10;
	switch(a)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(b)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("零");
}
	switch(c)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
    while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{  
	a=n/100;
	b=(n-a*100)/10;
	c=n%10;
	switch(a)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(b)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(c)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}

20190318097:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
    while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{  
	a=n/100;
	b=(n-a*100)/10;
	c=n%10;
	switch(a)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
} 
	switch(b)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:
	if(c==0&&b==0)
	printf("");
	else printf("零"); 
}
	switch(c)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}
 }

20190301006:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int max(int, int);
int max(int a, int b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c, x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
    else
    {
        x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
        x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f", (double)max(x1, x2), (double)(x1 + x2 - max(x1, x2)));
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318022:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ( "%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) {
y--; 
m += 12;
}
c=y/ 100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w<0)w+=7;
w%=7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190301006:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int max(int, int);
int max(int a, int b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c, x1, x2;
        scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION");
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f", (double)max(x1, x2), (double)(x1 + x2 - max(x1, x2)));
        }
    } while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------

            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), (double)(x1 + x2 - max(x1, x2)));
        }
    } while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(){
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
    {   if(b*b-4*a*c>=0) {
	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
         printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf",x1,x2);}
         if(b*b-4*a*c<0) printf("NO SOLUTION ");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190301006:Problem1147:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int max(int, int);
int max(int a, int b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int min(int, int);
int min(int a, int b)
{
    return a < b?a:b
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        getchar();
        if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), min(x1, x2));
        }
    }while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------

#include <math.h>
int max(int, int);
int max(int a, int b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int min(int, int);
int min(int a, int b)
{
    return a < b?a:b
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        getchar();
        if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), min(x1, x2));
        }
    }while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;

{
    return a >= b?a:b;

    return a < b?a:b
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        getchar();
        if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), min(x1, x2));
        }
    }while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;
}

20190302029:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	c=b-1;
	if(a==1) d=(a-1)*31+c;
	
	if(a==2) d=(a-1)*31+c;
	
	if(a==3) d=31+28+c;
	
	if(a==4) d=31*2+28+c;
	
	if(a==5) d=31*2+30+28+c;
	
	if(a==6) d=31*3+30+28+c;
	
	if(a==7) d=31*3+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==8) d=31*4+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==9) d=31*5+30*2+28+c;
	if(a==10) d=31*5+30*3+28+c;
	if(a==11) d=31*6+30*3+28+c;
	if(a==12) d=31*7+30*3+28+c;
    for(d=d+2;d>7;d=d-7) 
	d=d;
	
	
    if(d==1) printf("Monday");
    if(d==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(d==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(d==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(d==5) printf("Friday");
    if(d==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(d==7) printf("Sunday");
    
}

	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
         printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);}

20190318032:Problem1069:正确
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>=b&&b>=c)printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	else if(a>=c&&c>=b)printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	else if(b>=a&&a>=c)printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	else if(b>=c&&c>=a)printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	else if(c>=a&&a>=b)printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	else printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

	for(i=1;i<=x;i++)
	j=j+a[i];

	z=k%7;

	case 3:printf("Thursday");break;

20190301006:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int max(int, int);
int max(int a, int b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        getchar();
        if ((double)(b*b - 4*a*c) < 0)
        {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
        else
        {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), (double)(x1 + x2 - max(x1, x2)));
        }
    }while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;
}

	switch(a)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;

     if(b==0&&c!=0)

     printf("零");

	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;

20190318118:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	if(d>=0)
	{
		x1 = ((-b)+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2 = ((-b)-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}	
	}
}

	if(p>=0){
	x1=((-b)+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	x2=((-b)-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}

20190318153:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int get_days ( int x)
{
    switch (x)
    {
        case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31;
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default:

                return 28;
    }
}

void print_week(int i)
{
    switch (i)
    {
        case 5:
            printf ("Sunday");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Monday");
            break;
        case 0:
            printf ("Tuesday");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Wednesday");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Thursday");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Friday");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Saturday");
            break;
    }
}

int main()
{
    int x,y, i;

    scanf  ("%d,%d", &x, &y);

    int sum = 0;
for (i = 1; i < x; i++)
    {
        sum +=i;
    }

    sum += y + 1;

    print_week (sum % 7);

    return 0;
}

int main()
{

		printf("L\n");
	}
	else{
		printf("N\n");
	}
	return 0;

    {
        case 5:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 0:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
}

int main()
{
    int x,y, i;

    scanf  ("%d,%d", &x, &y);

    int sum = 0;
for (i = 1; i < x; i++)
    {
        sum +=i;
    }

    sum += y + 1;

    print_week (sum % 7);

    return 0;
}

20190318153:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int get_days ( int x)
{
    switch (x)
    {
        case 1:
        case 3:
        case 5:
        case 7:
        case 8:
        case 10:
        case 12:
            return 31;
        case 4:
        case 6:
        case 9:
        case 11:
            return 30;
        default:

                return 28;
    }
}

void print_week(int i)
{
    switch (i)
    {
        case 5:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 0:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
}

int main()
{
    int x,y, i;
    (0<x)&&(x<13);
    (0<y)&&(x<32);
    scanf  ("%d,%d", &x, &y);

    int sum = 0;
for (i = 1; i < x; i++)
    {
        sum +=i;
    }

    sum += y + 1;

    print_week (sum % 7);

    return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	//printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
	if(b>a){
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
	if(c>a){
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
	}
	if(c>b){
		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c
	,b,a);
	return 0;
}

main()
{
	int a,b,d,e;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	b=a%4;
	d=a%100;
	e=a%400;
	if((b==0&&d!=0)||(e==0)){
		printf("L");
	}
	else{printf("N");
	}
}

20190318089:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
    if(b*b-4.0*a*c<0||a==0)
    {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    else
    {
    	double x1,x2;
    	x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
    	x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4.0*a*c))/(2.0*a);
    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
    
    return 0;
}

20190318017:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		d=a;a=b;b=d;
	}
	if(a>c){
		d=c;c=a;a=d;
	} 
	if(b>c){
    	d=b;b=c;c=d;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int m,d,y,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	y=2019;
	if(m==1||m==2) {
        m+=12;
        y--;
    }
    w=(d+2*m+3*(m+1)/5+y+y/4-y/100+y/400)%7;
    switch(w)
    { case 0: printf("Monday\n"); break;
    case 1: printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
    case 2: printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
    case 3: printf("Thursday\n"); break;
    case 4: printf("Friday\n"); break;
    case 5: printf("Saturday\n"); break;
    case 6: printf("Sunday\n"); break;
	}
}

    {
	double x1,x2;
    double m1;
    m1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;

    if(m1>0){
		x1=((-b1)+sqrt(m1))/2*a1;
		x2=((-b1)-sqrt(m1))/2*a1;
		printf("%.3d~~~%.3d",x1,x2);
		}
			else{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}

main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,d;
	double x1,x2;
    while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1)!=EOF) //读多组数据
    {d=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;

    if(d>=0){
		x1=((-b1)+sqrt(d))/(2*a1);
		x2=((-b1)-sqrt(d))/(2*a1);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
			else{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	
}
}

20190301024:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main(){
	double a,b,c,date,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c) != EOF){
		date= pow(b,2) - 4*a*c;
		if(date >= 0){
			x1= (-b + date)/2*a;
			x2= (-b - date)/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main(){
	double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c) != EOF){
		d= b*b - 4*a*c;
		if(d >= 0){
			x1= (-b - pow(d,0.5))/2*a;
			x2= (-b + pow(d,0.5))/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main(){
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF){
		if(a==0){
			break;
		}
		d= b*b - 4*a*c;
		if(d >= 0){
			x1= (-b + sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			x2= (-b - sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}

int main()
{
	int x,y,k1,k2,k3,k4,k5,k6,k7,k8,k9,k10,k11,k12;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1){
		k1=(y-1)%7;
	switch(k1){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%4==0)
	{
		if(year%100!=0)
		{
			printf("L\n");
		}
		else if(year%400==0)
		{
			printf("L\n");
		}
		else{
			printf("N\n");
		}
	}
	else{
		printf("N\n");
	}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int year,a,b,c;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	a=year%4;
	b=year%100;
	c=year%400;
	if(a==0&&b!=0||c==0)
	printf("L");
	else
	printf("N");
	return 0;
	 
}

    {
	n=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(n<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    if(n>=0){
    x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);

20190318057:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
  char a,b,c,t;
  scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
  if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
  if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
  if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
  printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

20190301006:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
double max(double, double);
double max(double a, double b)
{
    return a >= b?a:b;
}
int main(void)
{
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c);
    do
    {
        getchar();
        if ((double)(b*b - 4*a*c) < 0)
        {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
        else
        {
            x1 = (double)(-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x2 = (double)(-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", (double)max(x1, x2), (double)(x1 + x2 - max(x1, x2)));
        }
    }while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c) != EOF);
    return 0;
}

20190318048:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&m)!=EOF)
	{
		a=m/100;
		b=(m%100)/10;
		c=m%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 0:printf("零");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹");break;
			case 2:printf("贰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁");break;
			case 4:printf("肆");break;
			case 5:printf("伍");break;
			case 6:printf("陆");break;
			case 7:printf("柒");break;
			case 8:printf("捌");break;
			case 9:printf("玖");break;

		printf("元整\n");

20190318010:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,delt1,delt2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c,&d,&e,&f)!=EOF)
	{
		delt1=b*b-4*a*c;
		delt2=e*e-4*d*f;
		if(delt1<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delt1))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		if(delt2<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x3=(-e+sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			x4=(-e-sqrt(delt2))/(2*d);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
		}
		
	}
	
	return 0;
		
		
		
	
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		if(delta>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
			x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	
	} 
}

20190301006:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main(void)
{
    int n[]={31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31}, x, y, m = 0;
    scanf("%d,%d", &x, &y);
    for (int i = 0; i < x - 1; i++)
    {
        m += n[i];
    }
    m += y - 1;
    switch (m % 7)
    {
    case 0:
        printf("Tursday");
        break;
    case 1:
        printf("Wednesday");
        break;
    case 2:
        printf("Thursday");
        break;
    case 3:
        printf("Friday");
        break;
    case 4:
        printf("Saturday");
        break;
    case 5:
        printf("Sunday");
        break;
    case 6:
        printf("Monday");
        break;
    default:
        break;
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&m)!=EOF)
	{
		a=m/100;
		b=(m%100)/10;
		c=m%10;
		if((m%100)!=0)
	{
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 0:printf("零");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹");break;
			case 2:printf("贰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁");break;
			case 4:printf("肆");break;
			case 5:printf("伍");break;
			case 6:printf("陆");break;
			case 7:printf("柒");break;
			case 8:printf("捌");break;
			case 9:printf("玖");break;
		}}
		if((m%100)==0)
		{
			switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹");break;
			case 2:printf("贰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁");break;
			case 4:printf("肆");break;
			case 5:printf("伍");break;
			case 6:printf("陆");break;
			case 7:printf("柒");break;
			case 8:printf("捌");break;
			case 9:printf("玖");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,disc1;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    
	}

20190318039:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	int min=a,med=b,max=c,t;

    if(min>max){
    	t=min;
    	min=max;
    	max=t;
	}
	if(max<med){
		t=med;
		med=max;
		max=t;
	}
	if(min>med){
		t=min;
		min=med;
		med=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",min,med,max);
	return 0;
	 
}
