#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	//printf("%d,%d\n",x,y);
	if(x==1){
	    a=0; 
	}else if(x==2){
	    a=31;
	}else if(x==3){
	    a=31+28;
	}else if(x==4){
	    a=31+28+31;
	}else if(x==5){
	    a=31+28+31+30;
	}else if(x==6){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31;
	}else if(x==7){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30;
	}else if(x==8){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30+31;
	}else if(x==9){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31;
	}else if(x==10){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30;
	}else if(x==11){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31;
	}else if(x==12){
	    a=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30;
	}
	b=a+y;
	c=b%7-1;
	//printf("%d,%d",b,c);
	switch(c){
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday ");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
	}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,x,q;
	
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	
	a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	double x1,x2;
	q=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(q))/(2*a);
	
	if(q<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}else{
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
	}
}

	int m,d,s,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	s=int(xz[m]);
	s=s+(d-1);
	z=s%7;
	if(z==0)
	{
		printf("Tuesday"); 
	}
	if(z==1)
	{
		printf("Wednesday");
	}
	if(z==2)
	{
		printf("Thursday");
	}

	{
		printf("Friday");

	if(z==4)
	{
		printf("Saturday");

		printf("Sunday");

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char ch;
ch=getchar();
if(ch>='a'&&ch<='z'||ch>='A'&&ch<='Z')
printf("NO\n");
if(ch>='0'&&ch<='9')
printf("YES\n");
return 0;
}

main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(c>b&&b>a)
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	if(b>c&&c>a)
	printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	if(c>a&&a>b)
	printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	if(a>c&&c>b)
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	if(b>a&&a>c)
	printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	if(a>b&&b>c)
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
}

	if(a>b&&a>c)
	{
		f=a;
		if(b>c)
		s=b,t=c;
		else
		s=c,t=b;
	}
	else if(b>a&&b>c)
	{
		f=b;

		s=a,t=c;
		else
		s=c,t=a;
	}

		s=a,t=b;

main()
{
	int a,x1,x2,x3;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
		x1=a/100;
		x2=a/10-10*x1;
		x3=a%10;
		
	
	switch(x1){
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;

		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
		case 9:printf("玖");break;
		case 0:printf("零");break;
	}
	printf("佰");
	if(x2==0&&x3==0){
		printf("");
	}else{
		switch(x2){
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;

		case 0:printf("零");break;

		case 1:printf("壹");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
 }

20190318091:Problem1069:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,f,s,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&a>c)
	{
		f=a;
		if(b>c)
		s=b,t=c;
		else
		s=c,t=b;
	}
	else if(b>a&&b>c)
	{
		f=b;
		if(a>c)
		s=a,t=c;
		else
		s=c,t=a;
	}
	else if(c>a&&c>b)
	{
		f=c;
		if(a>b)
		s=a,t=b;
		else
		s=b,t=a;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",t,s,f);
}

20190318057:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
 }

main()

		x3=a%10;
	    switch(x1){
		    case 1:printf("壹");break;

	    	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖");break;
	    	case 0:printf("零");break;
	    	default:printf("");
	    }
	    printf("佰");

		    printf("");

		    case 2:printf("贰");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,delta;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	
		if(delta>0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
			x2=(b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
		
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
		else if (delta==0)
		{
			x1=(-b)/(2*a);
			x2=x1;
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	
	
}

20190318043:Problem1158:正确
//输入一个三位数的整数（100至999）输出这个数的人民币大写。	
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int t,i=100,j,k=100;
	while(scanf("%d",&t)!=EOF)
	{
	while(i>=1)
	{
		j=t/i;
		switch(j)
		{
		case 1:printf("壹");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    case 9:printf("玖");break;
	    default :break;
		}
		if(i==100)
		{
			if(t%100==0)
			{
				printf("佰元整\n");
				i=k;
				break;
			}
			else
			{
			printf("佰"); 
			}
		}
		else if(i==10)
		{
			if(j==0)
			{
				printf("零");
			}
			else
			{
			printf("拾");
			}
		}
		else
		{
			printf("元整\n");
			i=k;
			break;
		}
		t=t-i*j;
		i=i/10;
		
	}
	}
}

20190318181:Problem1147:答案错误
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double m,n,p,q,t;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		q=-b/(2*a);
		p=sqrt(t)/(2*a);
		if(t>=0){
			m=p+q;
			n=q-p;
			printf("%d~~~%d\n",m,n);}
			else
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
}

20190318057:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int month,day,n,x;
	while(scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day)!=EOF)
	{
		switch(month)
		{
			case 1:n=0;break;
			case 2:n=31;break;
			case 3:n=59;break;
			case 4:n=90;break;
			case 5:n=120;break;
			case 6:n=151;break;
			case 7:n=181;break;
			case 8:n=212;break;
			case 9:n=243;break;
			case 10:n=273;break;
			case 11:n=304;break;
			case 12:n=334;break;
		}
		n=n+day;
		x=(n-1)%7;
		if(x==0)
		printf("Tuesday");
		if(x==1)
		printf("Wednesday");
		if(x==2)
		printf("Thursday");
		if(x==3)
		printf("Friday");
		if(x==4)
		printf("Saturday");
		if(x==5)
		printf("Sunday");
		if(x==6)
		printf("Monday");
	}
 }

20190318131:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#define LEAP_YEAR(y) (y)%400==0||((y)%4==0&&(y)%100!=0)
main()
{int a;
scanf("%d",&a);
if (LEAP_YEAR(a)==1)
printf("L",a);
else
printf("N",a);
}

20190318131:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
 char a,b,c,t;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  t=a;
  a=b;
  b=t;
 }
 if(a>c)
 {
  t=a;
  a=c;
  c=t;
     }
    if(b>c)
     {
  t=c;
  c=b;
  b=t;
     }
     printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
     return 0;
}

20190318057:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
void program(int a)
{
  if(a==0) printf("");
  else if(a==1) printf("壹");
  else if(a==2) printf("贰");
  else if(a==3) printf("叁");
  else if(a==4) printf("肆");
  else if(a==5) printf("伍");
  else if(a==6) printf("陆");
  else if(a==7) printf("柒");
  else if(a==8) printf("捌");
  else if(a==9) printf("玖");
} 
main()
{
  double i;
  int k,m,n;
  while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
  k=(int)i/100;
  m=(int)i%100/10;
  n=(int)i%100%10;
  if(i<1000&&i>=100)
{	
  program(k);
  printf("佰");
  program(m);
  if(m!=0){
  printf("拾");}
  else if(n!=0&&m==0){
  printf("零");} 
  program(n);
  printf("元整\n");

}
}
}

main()

    {
    case 1:c=2;break;

    case 8:c=4;break;
	case 9:c=7;break;
	case 10:c=2;break;
	case 11:c=5;break;
	case 12:c=7;break;														
	}
    a=((da%7)+(c-1))%7;
    if(a==0)
    printf("Sunday\n");

    printf("Monday\n");
    if(a==2)
    printf("Tuesday\n");
    if(a==3)

main()
{
	int mo,da,a,c;

    switch(mo)
    {
    case 1:c=2;break;
    case 2:c=5;break;
    case 3:c=5;break;
    case 4:c=1;break;
    case 5:c=3;break;

    case 8:c=4;break;
	case 9:c=7;break;
	case 10:c=2;break;
	case 11:c=5;break;
	case 12:c=7;break;														
	}
    a=((da%7)+(c-1))%7;
    if(a==0)
    printf("Sunday\n");

    printf("Monday\n");

    printf("Tuesday\n");

    printf("Wednesday\n");

		m=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(m<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else if(m==0){
			x1=x2=b/(-2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else if(m>0){
			x1=(b+sqrt(m))/(-2*a);
			x2=(b-sqrt(m))/(-2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int r,w,x,disc;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&r,&w,&x)!=EOF);
{
disc=w*w-4*r*x;
if(disc<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
else if(disc>=0)
{
x1=(-w+sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
x2=(-w-sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
}    
}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,de;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF,a,b,c)
    {   
        de=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        x1=(-b+de)/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-de)/(2*a);
        if(de>=0)
         printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        else
         printf("NO SOLUTION");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318068:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year,q;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        q=1;
    else{
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            q=1;
        else
            q=0;
    }
    if(q==1)
    {
        printf("L\n",year);
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N\n",year);
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318195:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);}
	if(a>b&&a>c&&b<c){printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);}
	if(b>a&&a>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);}
	if(b>a&&b>c&&c>a){printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);}
	if(c>a&&a>b){printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);}
	if(c>a&&c>b&&b>a){printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);}
	return 0;
}

20190302012:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a;
	int b;
	int digit;
	int ret=0;
	while (scanf("%d",&a) != EOF){
	int c=1;
		
	while (a>0){
		digit=a%10;
		ret=ret*10+digit;
		a=a/10;
	}
	
	while (ret>0) {
		b=ret%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		ret=ret/10;
		
		if (b>0&&c==1){
			printf("佰");
			c ++;
    	}
    	else if (b>0&&c==2){
    		printf("拾");
			c ++; 
		}
		else if (b==0&&c==2){
			printf("");
			c ++;
		}
	}
	printf("元整\n");
}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	int a1,b1,c1;
	double d,d1,x1,x2,y1,y2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1);		    
	d=b*b-4*a*c;  
	d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	y1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	y2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	if(d1<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",y1,y2);
}

20190302026:Problem1069:正确
//输入三个字母，按字母表顺序输出这三个字母
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char word1,word2,word3,a,b,c;
	word1=getchar();
	word2=getchar();
	word3=getchar();
	if(word1>word2&&word1>word3)
	    a=word1;
	else if(word2>word1&&word2>word3)
	    a=word2;
	else
	    a=word3;
	if(word1<word2&&word1<word3)
	    b=word1;
	else if(word2<word1&&word2<word3)
	    b=word2;
	else
	    b=word3;
	c=word1+word2+word3-a-b;
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
}

20190302052:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{	
    char x,y,z,mini,min,max;	
    scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);	
    if(y<x&&y<z)
      { mini=y;
       if(z>x)
          max=z,min=x;
        else
          max=x,min=z;}
    else if(z<x&&z<y)
       {mini=z;
       if(y>x)
          max=y,min=x;
        else
          max=x,min=y;}
    else if(x<y&&x<z)
       {mini=x;
       if(z>y)
          max=z,min=y;
        else
          max=y,min=z;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",mini,min,max);
    }

#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	int w;
	if(x<3){
		w=(y+2*x+24+3*x/5+39/5+2018+2018/4-2018/100+2018/400)%7;
	}
	else{
		w=(y+w*x+3*x/5+3/5+2019+2019/4-2019/100+2019/400)%7;
	}
	switch(w){
		case 0:printf("Tuesday",w);break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday",w);break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday",w);break;
		case 3:printf("Friday",w);break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday",w);break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday",w);break;
		case 6:printf("Monday",w);break;
	}
	return 0;
}

//求一元二次方程的解
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x1=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.31f~~~%.31f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTTON\n");
		}
	}
	
}

#include<stdio.h> 
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,m,n; 
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    m=b*b-4*a*c;
        n=sqrt(m);
		if (m>=0){
		x1=((-b)+n)/(2*a);
	    x2=((-b)-n)/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
		if (m<0) 
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

//2019年x月y日是星期几
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char* week[7]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thurday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	b=x-1;
	if(b==0)
	{
		a=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[a]);
	}
	else if(b==1)
	{
		a=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);

	}
	else if(b==2)
	{
		a=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b>=3&&b<=7)
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*30+(b-c-1)*31+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*31+(b-c-1)*30+y;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
		
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1: c=y-1+2;break;
		case 2: c=30+y+2;break;
		case 3: c=30+28+y+2;break;
		case 4: c=30+28+31+y+2;break;
		case 5: c=30+28+31+30+y+2;break;
		case 6: c=30+28+31+30+31+y+2;break;
		case 7: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+y+2;break;
		case 8: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+y+2;break;
		case 9: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y+2;break;
		case 10: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y+2;break;
		case 11: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y+2;break;
		case 12: c=30+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y+2;break;
	}
	c=c%7; 
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
		case 2: printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
        case 3: printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
        case 4: printf("Thursday\n"); break;
        case 5: printf("Friday\n"); break;
        case 6: printf("Saturday\n"); break;
        case 7: printf("Sunday\n"); break;
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318091:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a, &b,&c) != EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*a*c;  
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else if(d>=0){
	x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
		}

}

20190318074:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta,s,d,e,f,deltb,i;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
		s=sqrt(delta);
		x1=(-b+s)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-s)/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	deltb=e*e-4*d*f;
	if(deltb<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
		i=sqrt(deltb);
		x3=(-e+i)/(2*d);
		x4=(-e-i)/(2*d);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x3,x4);
	}
}

    {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c,l=sqrt(delta);
        if(delta<0)
           printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
           {x1=(-b+l)/(2*a),
            x2=(-b-l)/(2*a);
            printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);}    
    }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double d,e;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	if(b*b-4*a*c<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
		d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b/(2*a);
		e=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)+b/(-2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",d,e);
	}
	return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;
}

main()
{
char a,b,c,d;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {d=a;a=b;b=d;}
if (a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}
if (b>c) {d=c;c=b;b=d;}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char alpha[3];
    char temp;
    int i,j;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&alpha[0],&alpha[1],&alpha[2]);
    for(i=0;i<3;i++)
    {
        for(j=i+1;j<3;j++)
        {
            if(alpha[i]<alpha[j])
            {
                temp = alpha[i];
                alpha = alpha[j];
                alpha = temp;
            }
        }
    }
    for(i=0;i<3;i++)
    {
        printf("%c,alpha[i]");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318196:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

include<stdio.h>
main()
{
 float a, b, c
 double s, x1, x2;
 while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
 {
 s = b * b - 4 * a*c;
 if(s >= 0)
 {
  x1 = (-b + sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  x2 = (-b - sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2)
 }
 else if(s < 0)
 {
 printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
 }
 }
}

20190302039:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=y-1;
	if(x==1||x==2) b=(x-1)*31+a;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
    if(b==1) printf("Monday");
    if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(b==5) printf("Friday");
    if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    int a;
    int i;
    scanf ("%d",&a);
    if(a%400==0)
       i=1;
    else{
    	if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0)
    	  i=1;
    	else
    	  i=0;
	}
    if(i==1)
      {printf("L");} 
    if(i==0)
      {printf("N");} 
}

20190301008:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
	char number[]="壹贰叁肆伍陆柒捌玖拾";
	while (scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
	{
		a=n/100;
		n-=100*a;
		b=n/10;
		n-=10*b;
		c=n; 
		if (b==0 && c!=0)
		printf("%c%c佰零%c%c元整\n",number[2*a-2],number[2*a-1],number[2*c-2],number[2*c-1]);
		else if (c==0 & b!=0)
		printf("%c%c佰%c%c拾元整\n",number[2*a-2],number[2*a-1],number[2*b-2],number[2*b-1]);
		else if (b==0 && c==0)
		printf("%c%c佰元整\n",number[2*a-2],number[2*a-1]);
		else printf("%c%c佰%c%c拾%c%c元整\n",number[2*a-2],number[2*a-1],number[2*b-2],number[2*b-1],number[2*c-2],number[2*c-1]);
	}
}

20190318127:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,delta,x1,x2;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>0)
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2;
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2;
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else if(delta==0)
	{
	x1=( -b+sqrt(delta) )/2;
	x2=x1;
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    }
	else
	printf("NO SOLUTION ");
}

20190301053:Problem1069:正确
#include<ctype.h>
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    int t;
    scanf ("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b)
       {
       	t=a;
       	a=b;
       	b=t;
	   }
    if(a>c) 
      { 
      t=a; 
      a=c; 
      c=t; 
      } 
    if(b>c) 
      { 
      t=b; 
      b=c; 
      c=t; 
      }
    printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

    	printf("NO SOLUTION");

20190301010:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
}
if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
else x1=g,x2=f;
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
else
{
m=-b/(2*a);
n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
printf("NO SOLUTION",m,n,m,n);
}
return 0;
}

    q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{	
    	f=p+q;
        g=p-q;
    }
    if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
    else x1=g,x2=f;
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);

	if(x==1) if(y>=8) d=(y-1)%7+2;else if(y<8) d=1+y;}
    if(x==2) d=(30+y)%7+2;
    if(x>2&&x%2==0) d=(58+31*(x/2-1)+30*(x/2-2)+y)%7+2;
    if(x%2!=0) if(x>2&&x<9) d=(61*((x-1)/2-1)+58+y)%7+2;
    else if(x>=9) d=(61*((x-1)/2-1)+58+y)%7+3;

#include<stdio.h>
main(){
    int x,y,d,m;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    {
	if(x==1) if(y>=8) d=(y-1)%7+2;else if(y<8) d=1+y;}
    if(x==2) d=(30+y)%7+2;
    if(x>2&&x%2==0) d=(58+31*(x/2-1)+30*(x/2-2)+y)%7+2;
    if(x%2!=0) if(x>2&&x<9) d=(61*((x-1)/2-1)+58+y)%7+2;
    if(x>=9) d=(61*((x-1)/2-1)+58+y)%7+3;
    if(d>7) m=d%7;
    if(d>=0&&d<=7) m=d;
    if(m==1) printf("Monday");
     if(m==2) printf("Tuesday");
      if(m==3) printf("Wednesday");
       if(m==4) printf("Thursday");
        if(m==5) printf("Friday");
         if(m==6) printf("Saturday");
          if(m==7) printf("Sunday");}

{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,disc1;
	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else {
		x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
	}
	
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{  char  a,b,c,d;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(a>b)
   {d=a;
    a=b;
    b=d;}
    if(a>c)
   {d=a;
    a=c;
    c=d;}
    if(b>c)
   {d=c;
    c=b;
    b=d;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d,e,f;
    scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
    c=a-1;d=b-1;
    if(a==1){e=d;
    }
    if(a==2){e=31+d;
    }
    if(a==3){e=31+28+d;
    }
    if(a==4){e=31+28+31+d;
    }
    if(a==5){e=31+28+61+d;
    }
    if(a==6){e=59+61+31+d;
    }
    if(a==7){e=59+61+61+d;
    }
    if(a==8){e=59+61+61+31+d; 
    }
    if(a==9){e=59+61+61+62+d;
    }
    if(a==10){e=120+123+30+d;
    }
    if(a==11){e=120+123+61+d;
    }
    if(a==12){e=120+123+91+d;
    }
    f=e%7;
    if(f==6)
    {printf("Monday\n");}
    if(f==5)
    {printf("Sunday\n");}
    if(f==4)
    {printf("Saturday\n");}
    if(f==3)
    {printf("Friday\n");}
    if(f==2)
    {printf("Thursday\n");}
    if(f==1)
    {printf("Wednesday\n");}
    if(f==0)
    {printf("Tuesday\n");}
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	a=getchar();
	b=getchar();
	c=getchar();
	if(a>b&&a>c)
	{if(b>c) printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	 else
     printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	}
	else if (b>a&&b>c)
	{if(a>c) printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	 else printf("%c %c %c",a,c,b);
	}
	else
	{if(a>b) printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
     else printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);	
}
}

	{

	{
	b=a/100;
	c=(a-b*100)/10;
	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	switch(b)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;

	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;

	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
	if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	b=a/100;
	c=(a-b*100)/10;
	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	if(c==0&&d==0)
	{
		switch(b)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:break;
    }
    printf("元整\n"); 
	}
	else
	{
	switch(b)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:break;
    }
	switch(c)
    {
    case(0):printf("零");break;
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:break;

	switch(d)
    {
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;

main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            }}
    return 0;
}

20190318163:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190318163:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>

void printf1(int,double);

void printf2(int);

void printf3(int);

int main(void)

{

int n=11;

double k;

scanf("%lf",&k);

printf("k0=%lf\n",k);

printf1(n,k);

}

void printf1(int n,double k)

{

int t,f=0,flag=0;

double m=1e11;

for(;n>=0;n--)

{

t=(int)(k/m)%10;

// k=k-t*m;

// printf("n=%d,k=%f,t=%d\n",n,k,t);

m=m/10;

if(t!=0)

{

f=n;

}

else if(n>=f)

continue;

switch(t)

{

case 0:flag=1;break;

case 1:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("壹");break;

case 2:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("贰");break;

case 3:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("叁");break;

case 4:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("肆");break;

case 5:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("伍");break;

case 6:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("陆");break;

case 7:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("柒");break;

case 8:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("捌");break;

case 9:if(flag&&(n+1)%4)printf("零");flag=0;printf("玖");break;

default:break;

}

if(flag==0||n%4==0)

printf2(n);

}

printf("\n");

}

void printf2(int n)

{

switch(n%4)

{

case 0:printf3(n);break;

case 1:printf("什");break;

case 2:printf("佰");break;

case 3:printf("仟");break;

default:break;

}

}

void printf3(int n)

{

switch(n/4)

{

case 1:printf("萬");break;

case 2:printf("亿");break;

default:break;

}

}

20190318163:Problem1158:输出超限
#include<stdio.h> 
void xs(int a) 
{   
    if(a==0) printf("零"); 
 else if(a==1) printf("壹"); 
 else if(a==2) printf("贰"); 
 else if(a==3) printf("叁"); 
 else if(a==4) printf("肆"); 
 else if(a==5) printf("伍"); 
 else if(a==6) printf("陆"); 
 else if(a==7) printf("柒"); 
 else if(a==8) printf("捌"); 
 else if(a==9) printf("玖"); 
 
} 
 
void main() 
{ 
 int y=1; 
 while(y) 
 { 
 double i; 
 int j,j1; 
 int k,k1; 
 int m,m1; 
 int n,n1; 
 int g,g1; 
 int h,h1; 
printf("请输入人民币小写数额:"); 
printf("\n"); 
scanf("%lf",&i); 
//万以上部分 
j1=(int)i/10000000; 
k1=(int)i%10000000/1000000; 
m1=(int)i%10000000%1000000/100000; 
n1=(int)i%10000000%1000000%100000/10000; 
//万以下部分 
  j=(int)i%10000000%1000000%100000%10000/1000; 
  k=(int)i%1000/100; 
  m=(int)i%1000%100/10; 
  n=(int)i%1000%100%10; 
  //小数部分 
  g=(int)(i*10)%10000%1000%100%10; 
  h=(int)(i*100)%100000%10000%1000%100%10; 
if(i>=10000&&i<100000000) 
{ 
 printf("转化为大写金额应为：\n"); 
xs(j1); 
printf("仟"); 
xs(k1); 
printf("佰"); 
xs(m1); 
printf("拾"); 
xs(n1); 
printf("万"); 
xs(j); 
printf("仟"); 
xs(k); 
printf("佰"); 
xs(m); 
printf("拾"); 
xs(n); 
printf("元"); 
xs(g); 
printf("角"); 
xs(h); 
printf("分"); 
printf("\n"); 
} 
else if(i<10000&&i>=0) 
{ 
 printf("转化为大写金额应为：\n"); 
 xs(j); 
printf("仟"); 
xs(k); 
printf("佰"); 
xs(m); 
printf("拾"); 
xs(n); 
printf("元"); 
xs(g); 
printf("角"); 
xs(h); 
printf("分"); 
printf("\n"); 
 
} 
else  
printf("您所输入的数值超出范围！！\n"); 
 printf("输入1重新开始\n"); 
 printf("输入0结束程序\n"); 
    scanf("%d",&y); 
 printf("\n"); 
 printf("\n"); 
 } 
 
     
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t1,t2,t3;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a<b,a<c,b<c)
	t1=a,t2=b,t3=c;
	if(a<b,a<c,c<b)
	t1=a,t2=c,t3=b;
	if(b<a,b<c,a<c)
	t1=b,t2=a,t3=c;
	if(b<a,b<c,c<a)
	t1=b,t2=c,t3=a;
	if(c<a,c<b,a<b)
	t1=c,t2=a,t3=b;
	if(c<a,c<b,b<a)
	t1=c,t2=b,t3=a;
	printf("%c%c%c",t1,t2,t3);
	
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190301010:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
    p=-b/(2.0*a);
    q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{	
    	f=p+q;
        g=p-q;
    }
        if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
        else x1=g,x2=f;
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
        else
        {
    	    m=-b/(2*a);
    	    n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
            printf("NO SOLUTION",m,n);
        }
        return 0;
}

	t1=a,t2=c,t3=b;

20190301024:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int n,x,y,time = 0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for( n= 1; n < x; n = n + 1 )
	{
		if(n==1 || n==3 || n==5 || n==7 || n==8 || n==11 || n==12){
			time = time + 31;
		}
		if(n==4 || n==6 || n==9 || n==11){
			time = time + 30;
		}
		if(n==2){
			time = time + 28;
		}
	}
	time= time+ y - 1;
	//printf("%d\n",time);
	time= time % 7;
	if(time==1){
		printf("Wednesday\n");
	}
	if(time==2){
		printf("Thursday\n");
	}
	if(time==3){
		printf("Friday\n");
	}
	if(time==4){
		printf("Saturday\n");
	}
	if(time==5){
		printf("Sunday\n");
	}
	if(time==6){
		printf("Monday\n");
	}
	if(time==0){
		printf("Tuesday\n");
	}
	return 0;	
 }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int n,x,y,time = 0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if((x>0 && x<13) && (y>0 && y<32)){
	for( n= 1; n < x; n = n + 1 )
	{
		if(n==1 || n==3 || n==5 || n==7 || n==8 || n==11 || n==12){
			time = time + 31;
		}
		if(n==4 || n==6 || n==9 || n==11){
			time = time + 30;
		}
		if(n==2){
			time = time + 28;
		}
	}
	time= time+ y - 1;
	//printf("%d\n",time);
	time= time % 7;
	if(time==1){
		printf("Wednesday\n");
	}
	if(time==2){
		printf("Thursday\n");
	}
	if(time==3){
		printf("Friday\n");
	}
	if(time==4){
		printf("Saturday\n");
	}
	if(time==5){
		printf("Sunday\n");
	}
	if(time==6){
		printf("Monday\n");
	}
	if(time==0){
		printf("Tuesday\n");
	}
	
	}
	return 0;	
 }

20190318180:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int month[12] = {31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
    int m,d,i,t = 0;
    scanf("%d,%d", &m, &d);
    for(i = 0; i < m - 1; i++)
    {
        t += month[i];
    }
    t += d - 1;
    t = (t + 2) % 7;
    switch(t)
    {
        case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
        case 1:printf("Monday");break;
        case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
        case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
        case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
        case 5:printf("Friday");break;
        case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
    }  
}

		a=c;
		c=d;
	}
	if(a>b)
	{
		d=a;
		a=b;
		b=d;
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		d=b;
		b=c;
		c=d;
	 } 
	 printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);

main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>c)
	{
		d=a;
		a=c;
		c=d;
	}
	if(a>b)
	{
		d=a;
		a=b;
		b=d;
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		d=b;
		b=c;
		c=d;
	 } 
	 printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190318165:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
	int h,i,j,k,l;
    char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
    scanf ( "%d,%d", &i, &j);
    h=2019;
    if (i==1||i==2)
    {
	    h--; 
        i+=12;
    } 
    k=h/ 100;
    h=h-k*100;
    l=(k/4)-2*k+(h+h/4)+(13*(i+1)/5)+j-1;
    while (l<0)l+=7;
    l%=7;
    if (l==0) printf ("Sunday");
    else puts(a[l-1]);;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
        while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        	int d;
            double x1,x2;
	        d=b*b-4*a*c;
         	if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");} 
	        else{x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a), x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);}
	    	printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
	
}

20190318146:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int z,w,h,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&z,&w,&h)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=w*w-4*z*h;
		if (delta>=0)
		{
			x1=((-w)+sqrt(delta))/2.0*z;
			x2=((-w)-sqrt(delta))/2.0*z;
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		 
	}
}

20190301024:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int n,x,y,time = 0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if((x>0 && x<13) && (y>0 && y<32)){
	for( n= 1; n < x; n = n + 1 )
	{
		if(n==1 || n==3 || n==5 || n==7 || n==8 || n==11 || n==12){
			time = time + 31;
		}
		if(n==4 || n==6 || n==9 || n==11){
			time = time + 30;
		}
		if(n==2){
			time = time + 28;
		}
	}
	time= time+ y - 1;
	//printf("%d\n",time);
	time= time % 7;
	if(time==1){
		printf("Wednesday\n");
	}
	if(time==2){
		printf("Thursday\n");
	}
	if(time==3){
		printf("Friday\n");
	}
	if(time==4){
		printf("Saturday\n");
	}
	if(time==5){
		printf("Sunday\n");
	}
	if(time==6){
		printf("Monday\n");
	}
	if(time==0){
		printf("Tuesday\n");
	}
	
	}
	return 0;	
 } 
------------------------------------------------------
20190318118:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
 	int  month, day;
	scanf("%d,%d", &month, &day); 	
  	int week = 19+ 19 / 4 + 20 / 4 - 20 * 2 + 26 * (month + 1) / 10 + day - 1;
  	week %= 7;
  	switch (week)
  {
  		case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
  		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  		case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
  		case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
  		case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
  		case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
    }
 return 0;
}

int main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(((year%4==0)&&(year%100!=0))||(year%400==0))
	printf("L\n");
	else
	printf("N\n");
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year;
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if (year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
		printf("L");
	else if(year%400==0)
	printf("L");
	else printf("N");
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,p;
	scanf("%f %f %f",&a,&b,&c);
	p=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(p>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
		x2+(-b-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else if(p<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}

{

	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) t=a,a=b,b=t;

20190301005:Problem1069:编译错误
main()
{
    char x,y,z,m;
    scanf("%c%c%c"&x,%y,%z);
    if(x>y)
    {
        m=x;
        x=y;
        y=m;
    }
    if(x>z)
    {
        m=x;
        x=z;
        z=m;
    }
    if(y>z)
    {
        m=z;
        z=y;
        y=m;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c\n",x,y,z);
    return 0;
}

20190318051:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int y,x,sum,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&y,&x);
	x>0&&x<13;
	y>0&&y<32;
	switch(y)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
		
	}
	sum=sum+x;
	n=(sum+6)%7;
	if(n==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(n==1)
    printf("Wednesday");
    if(n==2)
    printf("Thursday");
    if(n==3)
    printf("Friday");
	if(n==4)
	printf("Satueday");
	if(n==5)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(n==6)
	printf("Monday");
	
	return 0;
}

   t=a;
   a=c;
   a=t;
     }
    if(b>c)
     {
    t=c;
    c=b;
    b=t;
      }
      printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
      return 0;
}

20190318051:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int month,day,sum,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	day>0&&day<32;
	month>0&&month<13;
	switch(month)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
		
	}
	sum=sum+day;
	n=(sum+6)%7;
	if(n==6)
	printf("Monday");
	if(n==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(n==1)
    printf("Wednesday");
    if(n==2)
    printf("Thursday");
    if(n==3)
    printf("Friday");
	if(n==4)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(n==5)
	printf("Sunday");

	return 0;
}

20190318146:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int z,w,h,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d%d%d",&z,&w,&h)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=w*w-4*z*h;
		if (delta>=0)
		{
			x1=((-w)+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*z);
			x2=((-w)-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*z);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else if (delta<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		 
	}
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{

        {
            double x1,x2;
	        d=b*b-4*a*c;
         	if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");} 
	        else{x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a), x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);}
	    	printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0) {
		x1=(sqrt(delta)-b)/(2*a);
		x2=(sqrt(delta)+b)/(-2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
    else
    printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
}

20190301004:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
#include<math.h>
main() 
{ 
    int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		int disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	    int p=-b/(2.0*a);
	    int q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	    x1=p+q;
	    x2=p-q;
	    if(disc>=0)
	       printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
 	    else
	    {
		    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=y-1;
	if(x==1||x==2) b=(x-1)*31+a;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
    if(b==1) printf("Monday");
    if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(b==5) printf("Friday");
    if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
}

int main()
{

	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;

		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;

#include <math.h>
#include "stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,n;
    double x,y;
    while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    n=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(n<0){
    	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    }
	if(n>=0){
		x=((-1)*b+sqrt(n))/(2.0*a);
		y=((-1)*b-sqrt(n))/(2.0*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x,y);
	    }
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318104:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a, b, c;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
if (b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else	
{
x1 = ((-b)+ sqrt(b*b -4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
x2 = ((-b) -sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int x,y,z,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1;i<=x;i++)
	y=a[i]+y;
	z=y%7;
	switch(z){
		case 1:printf("Saturday ",z) ;break;
		case 2:printf("Sunday",z) ;break;
		case 3:printf("Monday",z) ;break;
		case 4:printf("Tuesday",z) ;break;
		case 5:printf("Wednesday",z) ;break;
		case 6:printf("Thursday",z) ;break;
		case 0:printf("Friday",z) ;break;
	}
	return 0;
}

int main()
{
	int year;          //year==真年份 
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 ==0) {
		printf("L");
	}else{
		printf("N");
	}

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	s=2019
	if(x==1||x==2){
		s--;
		x+=12;
	}
	c=s/100;
	s=s-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1
	while (w<0)
	w+=7;
	w%=7;
	switch (w){
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
    	case 1:printf("Monday");break;
    	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
    	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
    	case 4:printf("Thurday");break;
    	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
    	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	}
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,t;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{	
		t = b*b-4*a*c;
	if (t >= 0)
	{
		x1 = (-b+sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
		x2 = (-b-sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
	}
	else printf("NO SOLUTION");}
}

20190318093:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,t;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{	
		t = b*b-4*a*c;
	if (t >= 0)
	{
		x1 = (-b+sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
		x2 = (-b-sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
}

	s=s-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1;

	w+=7;
	w=(w+1)%7;
	switch (w){
		case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
    	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
    	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
    	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
    	case 4:printf("Thurday\n");break;

	c=a/10-b*10;
	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	switch(b){
		case 1:printf("Ò¼°Û");break;
		case 2:printf("·¡°Û");break;
		case 3:printf("Èþ°Û");break;
		case 4:printf("ËÁ°Û");break;

		case 9:printf("¾Á°Û");break;

		case 2:printf("·¡Ê°");break;
		case 3:printf("ÈþÊ°");break;

		case 9:printf("¾ÁÊ°");break;

20190302044:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
//求一元二次方程的解

int main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,d1;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1)!=EOF){
	
		d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
		
		if(d1<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else{
			
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
			
		}
		return 0;
	}
}

20190301010:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2.0*a);
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
		f=p+q;
		g=p-q;
	}
	if(f>g)
	{
	    x1=f,x2=g;
    }
	else
	{
        x1=g,x2=f;
    }
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
    else
    {
    	m=-b/(2*a);
    	n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
    	printf("NO SOLUTION",m,n,m,n);
    }
	return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190302044:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
//求一元二次方程的解

main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,d1;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1)!=EOF){
	d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	if(d1<0){
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
	x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	}
}

20190301010:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	p=-b/(2.0*a);
	q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2.0*a);
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
		f=p+q;
		g=p-q;
	}
	if(f>g)
	{
	    x1=f,x2=g;
    }
	else
	{
        x1=g,x2=f;
    }
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
    else
    {
    	m=-b/(2.0*a);
    	n=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(a*2.0);
    	printf("NO SOLUTION",m,n,m,n);
    }
	return 0;
}

20190318141:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()

{

    int year;

    scanf("%d", &year);

    if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0)

        printf("L");

    else

        printf("N");
    return 0;

}

main()
{
	int year,mon,day,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&mon,&day);
	if(mon==1||mon==2)
	mon+=12;
	else
	w=(day+2*mon+3*(mon+1)/5+year+year/4-year/100+year/400+1)%7;
	switch(w){
	case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
	case 0:printf("Monday");break;
	case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 4:printf("Friday");break;

	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	p=-b/(2*a);
	q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
		f=p+q;
		g=p-q;
	}
	if(f>g)
	{
	    x1=f,x2=g;
    }
	else
	{
        x1=g,x2=f;
    }
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
    else
    {
    	m=-b/(2*a);
    	n=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(a*2);
    	printf("NO SOLUTION",m,n,m,n);
    }
	return 0;

20190318187:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    switch(x)
    {
    	case 1 : a=1+y;break;
    	case 2 : a=31+y;break;
    	case 3 : a=31+28+y;break;
    	case 4 : a=31*2+y+28;break;
    	case 5 : a=31*2+y+28+30;break;
    	case 6 : a=31*3+y+28+30;break;
    	case 7 : a=31*3+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 8 : a=31*4+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 9 : a=31*5+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 10 : a=31*5+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 11 : a=31*6+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 12 : a=31*6+y+28+30*4;break;
	}
	int b=(a+1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0 : printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 1 : printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2 : printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3 : printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 4 : printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 5 : printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 6 : printf("Saturday\n");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318120:Problem1147:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
main()
{
	
	double a,b,c,e;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!EOF);
	double x1,x2;
	e=b*b-4*a*c;
	printf("%f",e);
	if(e<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	else{
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(e))/(2*a);
	    x1=(-b-sqrt(e))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1/1,0,x2/1.0);
	}
}

		printf("NO SOLUTION");

	x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,disc;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
     disc=b*b-4*a*c;
     if(disc<0)
     printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
     else
     {
     	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc))/(2.0*a);
     	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc))/(2.0*a);
     	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	 }
	}
 }

#include <math.h> 
int main()
{
	int m,d,a,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	a=19+19/4+20/4-2*20+(26*(m+1)/10)+d-1;
	c=a%7;
	switch(c){
		case(1):printf("Monday");break;
		case(2):printf("Tuesday");break;
		case(3):printf("Wednesday");break;
		case(4):printf("Thursday");break;
		case(5):printf("Friday");break;
		case(6):printf("Saturday");break;
		case(7):printf("Sunday");break;
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()

{
	char a,b,c,i;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	{
		if(a>b)
		{i=a;a=b;b=i;}
		if(a>c)
		{
			i=a;a=c;c=i;
		}
		if(b>c)
		{
			i=b;b=c;c=i;
	    }
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

20190318131:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year,month,day,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	if(month==1||month==2)
	year=2018;
	else
	year=2019;
	w=(day+2*month+3*(month+1)/5+year+year/4-year/100+year/400)%7;
	switch(w)
	{
		case 0:printf("Monday");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

20190318197:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int day[]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
	char *week[8]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	int x,y,sum=0,temp,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1;i<x;i++)
{
	sum+=day[i-1];
}
    temp=(sum+y)%7;
    printf("%s",week[temp]);
    return 0;
}

20190302033:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	float a, b, c;
 	double k, x1, x2;
 	while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
 {
     k = b * b - 4 * a*c;
     if(k >= 0)
 {
    x1 = (-b + sqrt(k)) / (2 * a);
    x2 = (-b - sqrt(k)) / (2 * a);
    printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
 }
 	else if(k < 0)
 {
 	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
 }
 }
}

20190302033:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int m,n,a,b;
scanf("%d,%d",&m,&n);
a=n-1;
if(m==1||m==2) b=(m-1)*31+a;
if(m==3) b=31+28+a;
if(m==4) b=31*2+28+a;
if(m==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
if(m==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
if(m==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
if(m==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
if(m==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
if(m==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
if(m==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
if(m==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
b=b;
if(b==1) printf("Monday");
if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
if(b==5) printf("Friday");
if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
return 0;
}

20190302032:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	while  (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){//题目要求输入整数所以这里用int  EOF读多组数据  解为double意思我浮点数 
    
	float delta;  //float和double都可以 
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if (delta<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	} else{
		double x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		double x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);//这里double后面的X1和X2都不用在前面建立变量，float delta也是一样的 
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
}
	return 0;
}

 int main()
{
    int mouth[12] = {31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
    int m,d,i,t = 0;
    scanf("%d,%d", &m, &d);
    for(i = 0; i < m - 1; i++)
    {
        t += mouth[i];
    }
    t += d - 1;
    t = (t + 2) % 7;
    switch(t)
    {
        case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
        case 1:printf("Monday");break;
        case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
        case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
        case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
        case 5:printf("Friday");break;
        case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
    } 
    return 0; 
}

20190301010:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
	{
	    x1=((-b)+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	    x2=((-b)-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }
	else
	{
	    printf("NO SOLUTION ");
	}
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{   
   int x,y,a,b,c;
   scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
   switch(x)
   {case 1:a=0;break;
    case 2:a=31;break;
    case 3:a=59;break;
    case 4:a=90;break;
    case 5:a=120;break;
    case 6:a=151;break;
    case 7:a=181;break;
    case 8:a=212;break;
    case 9:a=243;break;
    case 10:a=273;break;
    case 11:a=304;break;
    case 12:a=334;break;
   }
   c=a+y+1;
   b=c%7;
   	if(b==1) printf("Monday\n");
	if(b==2) printf("Tuesday\n");	
	if(b==3) printf("Wednesday\n");
	if(b==4) printf("Thursday\n");	
	if(b==5) printf("Friday\n");
	if(b==6) printf("Saturday\n");
	if(b==0) printf("Sunday\n");
}

20190318195:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,p;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    p=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(p<0){
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        else if(p>=0){
	    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
	char x;//字符用char 整数用int
	scanf("%c",&x);//上边用char 下边输入用%c
	if (x>='0'&&x<='9'){// 字符判断中用‘’来表示数字
		printf("YES\n"); 
	}else{
		printf("NO\n");
	}

20190301021:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!= EOF)
	{   delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (delta>=0)
		{
			x1=((-b)+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
			x2=((-b)-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else if (delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	
	
}

20190318195:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,w,a;
	x>0&&x<13;
	y>0&&y<32;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	w=19+(19/4)+(20/4)-2*20+(26*(x+1))/10+y-1;
	a=(abs(w)%7+7)%7;
	switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
	    case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
	    case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
    	case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
    	case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
    	case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;
    	case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		break;
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf ("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	getchar();
	if(a>b) {d=a;a=b;b=d;}
	if(a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}
	if(b>c) {d=c;c=b;b=d;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);

}

20190318054:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
 	int  month, day;
	scanf("%d,%d", &month, &day); 	
  	int week = 19+ 19 / 4 + 20 / 4 - 20 * 2 + 26 * (month + 1) / 10 + day - 1;
  	week %= 7;
  	switch (week)
  {
  		case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
  		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  		case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
  		case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
  		case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
  		case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
    }
 return 0;
}

{

	while(scanf("%d\n",&a)){
	b=a/100;
	c=a/10%10;
	d=a%100;
	switch(b){
		case 1:
		printf("壹佰");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("贰佰");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("叁佰");
		break;

		break;
		case 5:
		printf("伍佰");
		break;
		case 6:
		printf("陆佰");
		break;
		case 7:
		printf("柒佰");
		break;
		case 8:
		printf("捌佰");
		break;
		case 9:
		printf("玖佰");
		break;
	}
	if(c!=0){
	switch(c){
		case 1:
		printf("壹拾");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("贰拾");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("叁拾");

		case 8:

		break;
		case 9:
		printf("玖拾");
		break;
		case 0:
		printf("零");
		break;}
	}
	else if(c=0){
		printf("");	}
	switch(d){
		case 1:
		printf("壹元整");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("贰元整");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("叁元整");

20190301029:Problem1114:正确
#include "stdio.h" 
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	switch(a)
	{
		case 1:
			c=b-1;
			break;
		case 2:
			c=b-1+31;
			break;
		case 3:
			c=b-1+31+28;
			break;
		case 4:
			c=b-1+31+28+31;
			break;
		case 5:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30;
			break;
		case 6:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 7:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30;
			break;
		case 8:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 9:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31;
			break;
		case 10:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30;
			break;
		case 11:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 12:
			c=b-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+31;
			break;
	}
	d=c%7;
	switch(d)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Saturday");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Sunday");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Monday");
			break;
		case 0:
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;
	}
}

20190318035:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION");}
    else{
         x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
         x2=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);}
    
    };
    return 0;
}

20190318128:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,A,B,C;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	A=a;
	if(a>b)
	B=b;
	else
	{
		A=b;
		B=a;
	}
	if(c<B)
	C=c;
	else
	{
		if(c>A)
		{
		    C=B;
	    	B=A;
	    	A=c;	
		}
		else
		{
			C=B;
	    	B=c;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",C,B,A);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    else{
         x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
         x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%100!=0 && year%4==0) {
        printf("L\n");
    } else if (year%100!=0 && year%400==0) {
        printf("L\n");
    } else if (year%100!=0 && year%4==0 && year%400==0) {
        printf("L\n");
    } else {
        printf("N\n");
    }
}

20190318035:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
  char a,b,c,d;
  scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
  if(a>b){d=a,a=b,b=d;}
  if(a>c){d=a,a=c,c=d;}
  if(b>c){d=b,b=c,c=d;}
  printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190301021:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>       
main()
{
	int x,y,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1 || x==2)
	{
		x=x+12;
		w=18+4+5-40+((26*(x+1))/10)+y-1;
	}
	else
	w=19+4+5-40+((26*(x+1))/10)+y-1;
	if(w<0)
	w=(w%7+7)%7;
	else 
    w=w%7;
    if(w==1)
	printf("Monday\n",w);
	if(w==2)
	printf("Tuesday\n",w);
	if(w==3)
	printf("Wednesday\n",w);
	if(w==4)
	printf("Thursday\n",w);
	if(w==5)
	printf("Friday\n",w);
	if(w==6)
	printf("Saturday \n",w);	
	if(w==0)
	printf("Sunday\n",w);
}

main()
{
	int n,a,b,c;
	char *number[10]={"Ò¼","·¡","Èþ","ËÁ","Îé","Â½","Æâ","°Æ","¾Á","Ê°"};
	while (scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
	{
		a=n/100;
		n-=100*a;
		b=n/10;
		n-=10*b;
		c=n; 
		if (b==0 && c!=0)
		printf("%s°ÛÁã%sÔªÕû\n",number[a-1],number[c-1]);
		else if (c==0 & b!=0)
		printf("%s°Û%sÊ°ÔªÕû\n",number[a-1],number[b-1]);
		else if (b==0 && c==0)
		printf("%s°ÛÔªÕû\n",number[a-1]);
		else printf("%s°Û%sÊ°%sÔªÕû\n",number[a-1],number[b-1],number[c-1]);
	}

main()

	{

		b=n/10;
		n-=10*b;
		c=n;

		printf("%s°ÛÁã%sÔªÕû\n",number[a-1],number[c-1]);
		else if (c==0 & b!=0)
		printf("%s°Û%sÊ°ÔªÕû\n",number[a-1],number[b-1]);

		printf("%s°ÛÔªÕû\n",number[a-1]);

20190318093:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c=1,d;
	int r=0;
	scanf("%d",&a);
		
	while (a>0){
		d=a%10;
		r=r*10+d;
		a=a/10;
	}
	
	while (r>0) {
		b=r%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		r=r/10;
		
		if (b>0&&c==1){
			printf("佰");
			c ++;
    	}
    	else if (b>0&&c==2){
    		printf("拾");
			c ++; 
		}
		else if (b>0&&c==3){
			printf("");
			c ++;
		}
	}
    printf("元整\n");
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&d) != EOF){
	a=(int)d/100;
	b=(int)(d%100)/10; 
	c=(int)d%100%10;
	if(a!=0&&b==0&&c==0)
	switch(a){ 
	case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	} 
	else {
	switch(a){
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
			}
	switch(b){
	case 0:printf("零");break; 
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch(c){
	case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
	case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
	case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
	case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
	case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;

	case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
	case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}

{
	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&d) != EOF){
	a=(int)d/100;
	b=(int)(d%100)/10; 
	c=(int)d%100%10;
	if(a!=0&&b==0&&c==0)
	switch(a){ 
	case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
	} 
	else {
	switch(a){
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
			}
	switch(b){
	case 0:printf("零");break; 
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	}
	switch(c){
	case 0:printf("元整\n");break;	
	case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
	case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
	case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
	case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
	case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
	case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
	case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
	case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
	case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
	}
}
}
}

		b=g;
	}

	{
		g=a;
		a=c;
		c=g;
	
	}
	if(b>c)

		g=b;
		b=c;
		c=g;

{

    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
   {
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
    else
    {
    x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);       
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
     }
   }
}

{

		double x1,x2;
        while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
       	{
			delt = b*b-4*a*c;
            if(delt>=0)
            {
			   x1 = (-b+sqrt(delt))/(2*a);
        	   x2 = (-b-sqrt(delt))/(2*a);
			   printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		    }
		    else
		   {
			   printf("NO SOLUTION\n"); 
		    }  
	    }

#include <stdio.h>
int main(int argc, char **argv) {
    int x, y, sum = 0;
    int days[12] = {31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
    char *weeks[] = {"Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday",
                     "Saturday", "Sunday", "Monday"
                    };
    scanf("%d,%d", &x, &y);
    for (int i = 1; i < x; i++) {
        sum += days[i];
    }
    sum += y;
    printf("%s", weeks[(sum - 1) % 7]);
    return 0;
}

20190318111:Problem1114:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
int NOLEAP_MON[13] = { 0, 31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
int LEAP_MON[13] = { 0, 31, 29, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
bool isLeap(int year) {
return (year%400==0) || (year%4==0 &&year%100!=0);
}
int countDays(int year, int mon, int day)
{
int i, total = 0, j;
if (year< 1980) {
total = 0;
for(i=1979; i>year; i--) {
total += 365;
if(isLeap(i)) total ++;
}
if(isLeap(year)) {
for(i=12; i>mon; i--) total += LEAP_MON[i];
total += LEAP_MON[mon] - day +1;
} else {
for(i=12; i>mon; i--) total += NOLEAP_MON[i];
total += NOLEAP_MON[mon] - day +1;
}
total = - total;
} else {
total = 0;
for(i=2019; i<year; i++) {
total += 365;
if(isLeap(i)) total ++;
}
if(isLeap(year)) {
for(i=1; i<mon; i++) total += LEAP_MON[i];
} else {
for(i=1; i<mon; i++) total += NOLEAP_MON[i];
}
total += day -1;
}
return total;
}
void countWeek(int year, int mon, int day)
{
char WEEK_DAY[7][10] = {"Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday", "Sunday"}; 
int diff, week;
diff = countDays(year, mon, day);
week = 2 + diff % 7;
if(week> 7) week -= 7; 
else if (week <=0) week += 7;
printf("%s\n",WEEK_DAY[week-1]);
}
int main()
{
int n, y=2019, m, d, days, week;
char str[1001], *p;
scanf("%d,%d", &m, &d); 
countWeek(y, m, d);
system("pause");
return 0;
}

20190318055:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,x,D,m;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
		D=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(D>=0){
			m=sqrt(D);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-b+m)/(2*a),(-b-m)/(2*a));
		}
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

20190318158:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int r,w,x,disc;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&r, &w, &x)!=EOF)
{
disc=w*w-4*r*x;
if(disc>=0)
{
x1=((-w)+sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
x2=((-w)-sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n");
}
else if(disc<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
}
return 0;
}

20190318111:Problem1114:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
int x,y,i;
int a[20]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31},aa[20]={0};
for(i=1;i<13;i++)aa[i]=aa[i-1]+a[i-1];
while(scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y))
{
int ss=(aa[x]+y-1)%7;
switch(ss)
{
case 0:{printf("Tuesday\n");break;}
case 1:{printf("Wednesday\n");break;}
case 2:{printf("Thursday\n");break;}
case 3:{printf("Friday\n");break;}
case 4:{printf("Saturday\n");break;}
case 5:{printf("Sunday\n");break;}
case 6:{printf("Monday\n");break;}
}
}
return 0;
}

20190318055:Problem1114:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:b=y-1;break;
		case 1:b=y-1+31;break;
		case 2:b=y-1+59;break;
		case 3:b=y-1+90;break;
		case 4:b=y-1+120;break;
		case 5:b=y-1+151;break;
		case 6:b=y-1+181;break;
		case 7:b=y-1+212;break;
		case 8:b=y-1+243;break;
		case 9:b=y-1+273;break;
		case 10:b=y-1+304;break;
		case 11:b=y-1+334;break;
	}
	c=b%7;//b为日期差
	if(b>=7)
	d=2+c;
	else
	d=2+b;
	if(d>7)
	d=d-7;
	else
	d=d;
	switch(d)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 7:printf("Sunday");break; 
	}
}

20190318055:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:b=y-1;break;
		case 1:b=y-1+31;break;
		case 2:b=y-1+59;break;
		case 3:b=y-1+90;break;
		case 4:b=y-1+120;break;
		case 5:b=y-1+151;break;
		case 6:b=y-1+181;break;
		case 7:b=y-1+212;break;
		case 8:b=y-1+243;break;
		case 9:b=y-1+273;break;
		case 10:b=y-1+304;break;
		case 11:b=y-1+334;break;
	}
	c=b%7;//b为日期差
	if(b>=7)
	d=2+c;
	else
	d=2+b;
	if(d>7)
	d=d-7;
	else
	d=d;
	switch(d)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;

20190318111:Problem1114:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
int x,y,i;
int a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31},aa[13]={0};
for(i=1;i<13;i++)aa[i]=aa[i-1]+a[i-1];
while(scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y))
{
int ss=(aa[x]+y-1)%7;
switch(ss)
{
case 0:{printf("Tuesday\n");break;}
case 1:{printf("Wednesday\n");break;}
case 2:{printf("Thursday\n");break;}
case 3:{printf("Friday\n");break;}
case 4:{printf("Saturday\n");break;}
case 5:{printf("Sunday\n");break;}
case 6:{printf("Monday\n");break;}
}
}
return 0;
}

      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);

20190318035:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a;
	int b;
	int c=1;
	int digit;
	int ret=0;
	scanf("%d",&a);
		if(a==0){printf("零元整");}
else{
	while (a>0){
		digit=a%10;
		ret=ret*10+digit;
		a=a/10;
	}
	
	while (ret>0) {
		b=ret%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		ret=ret/10;
		
		if (b>0&&c==1){
			printf("佰");
			c ++;
    	}
    	else if (b>0&&c==2){
    		printf("拾");
			c ++; 
		}
		else if (b>0&&c==3){
			printf("");
			c ++;
		}
	}
    printf("元整\n");}
}

#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta,s;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(delta<0){
		   printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
	    else{
		s=sqrt(delta);
		x1=(-b+s)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-s)/(2*a);
		   printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
    }
}

20190318029:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double e,f;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		e=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/(2*a);
		f=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)+b)/(-2*a);
		if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else if(d>0){
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e,f);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318074:Problem1158:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,money;
	while(scanf("%d",&money)!=EOF)
	{
	
	a=money/100;
	b=money%100/10;
	c=money%10;
	switch(a){
		case 0:printf("");break; 
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break; 
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break; 
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break; 
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break; 
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break; 
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;  
	}
	if(c!=0){
	
	switch(b){ 
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break; 
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break; 
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break; 
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break; 
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break; 
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break; 
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		} 
	} 
	else{
		switch(b){ 
		case 0:printf("");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break; 
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break; 
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break; 
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break; 
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break; 
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break; 
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		} 	
	} 
	switch(c){
		case 0:printf("");break; 
		case 1:printf("壹");break; 
		case 2:printf("贰");break; 
		case 3:printf("叁");break; 
		case 4:printf("肆");break; 
		case 5:printf("伍");break; 
		case 6:printf("陆");break; 
		case 7:printf("柒");break; 
		case 8:printf("捌");break; 
		case 9:printf("玖");break; 
	}
    
	printf("元整\n");
    }
}

20190301013:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{ 
	int year; 
	scanf("%d",&year);
	if(year%400==0)
	printf("L\n");
	else if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
	printf("L\n");
	else printf("N\n");
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c){
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	}
	if(a>c&&c>b){
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	}
	if(b>c&&c>a){
	printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	}
	if(b>a&&a>c){
	printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	}
	if(c>a&&a>b){
	printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	}
	if(c>b&&b>a){
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	}

main()
{

		a1=(y-1)%7;
	    switch(a1){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}

20190318111:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int x,y,d,p;
while(scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y)!=EOF)
{
switch(x)
{
	case1:d=0;break;
	case2:d=31;break;
	case3:d=59;break;
	case4:d=90;break;
	case5:d=120;break;
	case6:d=151;break;
	case7:d=181;break;
	case8:d=212;break;
	case9:d=243;break;
	case10:d=273;break;
	case11:d=304;break;
	case12:d=334;break;
}
d=d+y;
p=(d-1)%7;
if(p=0)
{
	printf("Wensday\n");break;
}
if(p=1)
{
printf("Thursday\n");break;
}
if(p=2)
{
	printf("Friday\n");break;
}
if(p=3)
{
	printf("Saturday\n");break;
}
if(p=4)
{
	printf("Sunday\n");break;
}
if(p=5)
{
	printf("Monday\n");break;
}
if(p=6)
{
	printf("Tuesday\n");break;
}

}

}

int main()
{
    int a,b,c,s;
    while(scanf("%d",&s)!=EOF);
    {   a=s/100;
        b=(s-a*100)/10;
        c=s%10;}
        if(a==1) printf("壹佰");
        if(a==2) printf("贰佰");
        if(a==3) printf("叁佰");
        if(a==4) printf("肆佰");
        if(a==5) printf("伍佰");
        if(a==6) printf("陆佰");
        if(a==7) printf("柒佰");
        if(a==8) printf("捌佰");
        if(a==9) printf("玖佰");

        if(b==1) printf("壹拾");
        if(b==2) printf("贰拾");
        if(b==3) printf("叁拾");
        if(b==4) printf("肆拾");
        if(b==5) printf("伍拾");
        if(b==6) printf("陆拾");
        if(b==7) printf("柒拾");
        if(b==8) printf("捌拾");
        if(b==9) printf("玖拾");
        if(b==0&&c==0) printf("");
        if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零");

        if(c==1) printf("壹");
        if(c==2) printf("贰");
        if(c==3) printf("叁");
        if(c==4) printf("肆");
        if(c==5) printf("伍");
        if(c==6) printf("陆");
        if(c==7) printf("柒");
        if(c==8) printf("捌");
        if(c==9) printf("玖");
        if(c==0) printf("");

        printf("元整\n");
    

    return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d",&year);

    printf("L");
    else
    printf("N");
}

20190301002:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
    int y;
    scanf("%d",&y);
    if(y%4==0)
    {
        if( y%100==0)
        {
            if ( y%400==0)
                printf("L",y);
            else
                printf("N",y);
        }
        else
            printf("L",y);
    }
    else
        printf("N",y);
}

20190318094:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
int main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	a=getchar();
	b=getchar();
	c=getchar();
	if(a<b&&a<c)
	{
		if(b<c)
		printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
		else
		printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	}
	
	if(b<a&&b<c)
	{
		if(a<c)
		printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
		else
		printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	}
	
		if(c<a&&c<b)
	{
		if(a<b)
		printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
		else
		printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	}
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,x,d,z;
     while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
    
   {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    x=(-2*a)/b;
    z=sqrt(d);
    x1=(-b+z)/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-z)/(2*a);
    
    if(d==0) {printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,x);}
    else if(d>0) {printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
   else if(d<0) {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    
    
}

#include <iostream>

using namespace std;


int main(){
	
	int day[13]={0};
	day[1] =day[3]=day[5]=day[7]=day[8]=day[10]=day[12]=31;
	day[2]=28;
	day[4]=day[6]=day[9]=day[11]=30;
	char name[7][4]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"} ; 
	int x,y;
	scanf("%d %d",&x,&y);

		int i;
		int sum=0;
		for(i=1;i<=x-1;i++){
			sum+=day[i];
		}
		sum+=y;
		printf("%s",name[sum%7]);
	return 0;
}

#include <iostream>

using namespace std;


int main(){
	
	int day[13]={0};
	day[1] =day[3]=day[5]=day[7]=day[8]=day[10]=day[12]=31;
	day[2]=28;
	day[4]=day[6]=day[9]=day[11]=30;
	char name[7][4]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"} ; 
	int x,y;
	scanf("%d %d",&x,&y);
	if(!((x>=1&&x<=12)&&(y>=1&&y<=day[x])) ){
		printf("输入不正确！"); 
		}
	else{
		int i;
		int sum=0;
		for(i=1;i<=x-1;i++){
			sum+=day[i];
		}
		sum+=y;
		printf("%s",name[sum%7]);
	}
	return 0;
}

if (a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}

20190301052:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta;
	double x1,x2;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0)
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else if(delta<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION ");
	}
	return 0;
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double e,f;
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
		e=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)-b)/(2*a);
		f=(sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)+b)/(-2*a);
			if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else if(d>0){
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e,f);
		}
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		
		if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else if(d>=0){
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e,f);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301002:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,t;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {t=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(t>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(t))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318035:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<time.h>
#include<string.h> 
main()
{
int a,b;
scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
char*arr[]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
struct tm info;

info.tm_year=119;
info.tm_mon=a-1;
info.tm_mday=b;
mktime(&info);
printf("%s",arr[info.tm_wday]);
}

20190318035:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h> 
main()
{
	int A,B,C,x;
	char *a[]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while (scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	A=x/100;
	C=x%10;
	B=x%100/10;
	if(B==0){if(C==0)printf("%s佰元整\n",a[A]);else printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",a[A],a[C]);}
	else if(C==0)printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",a[A],a[B]);
	else printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",a[A],a[B],a[C]);
}}

	scanf("%d", &a);
	x=a%4;
	y=a%400;
	z=a%100;
	if (z==0)
	   if (y==0)
	    printf("L");
	   else printf("N");
	else 
	   if (x==0)
	      printf("L");

20190318086:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    char a, b, c, s;
    scanf("%c%c%c", &a, &b, &c);
    if (a>b)
    {
        s=a;
        a=b;
        b=s;
    }
    if (a>c)
    {
        s=a;
        a=c;
        c=s;
    }
    if (b>c)
    {
        s=b;
        b=c;
        c=s;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c", a, b, c);
}

#include<math.h>
