	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0)
	{
	x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else if(delta<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	}
	}

20190318086:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int a, b, c, s;
	double x1, x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
	{	 
        s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
	      if (s<0) 
	         printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	      else
	      {
	       x1=(-b + sqrt(s))/(2*a);
	       x2=(-b - sqrt(s))/(2*a);
        	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n", x1, x2);
          }
    }
}

20190318086:Problem1114:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x, y, c, s, w;
	scanf("%d, %d", &x, &y);
	s=2019;
	if (x==1 || x==2){
		s--;
		x+=12;
	}
	c=s/100;
	s=s-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1;
	while (w<0)
	w+=7;
	w%=7;
    switch (w){
    	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	   	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	   	case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	   	case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	   	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	   	case 0:printf("Sunday\n\n");break;
	}
}

main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){ 
	x=a/100;
	y=a/10%10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
}
	switch(y)
{
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
}
	switch(z)
{
	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	case 9:printf("玖");break;
}
	printf("元整\n");} 
}

20190301052:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	{
	    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(delta>=0)
     	{
    	x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
    	x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    	}
    	else if(delta<0)
      	{
	    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
	    }
	}
	return 0;
	
}

	{

     	{
    	    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);

         	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);

20190301051:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int m,d,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:a=0;break;
		case 2:a=31;break;
		case 3:a=59;break;
		case 4:a=90;break;
		case 5:a=120;break;
		case 6:a=151;break;
		case 7:a=181;break;
		case 8:a=212;break;
		case 9:a=243;break;
		case 10:a=273;break;
		case 11:a=304;break;
		case 12:a=335;break;
	}
	b=(a+d-1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{   case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318060:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	d=a,a=b,b=d;
	if(b>c)
	d=b,b=c,c=d;
	if(a>c)
	d=a,a=c,c=d;
	if(a>b)
	d=a,a=b,b=d;
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			x1=((-b)+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
			x2=((-b)-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	}return 0;
 }

20190318103:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(b>c){t=c;c=b;b=t;}
	if(a>c){t=a;a=c;c=t;}
	if(a>b){t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

int main()
{

	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:a=0;break;
		case 2:a=31;break;
		case 3:a=59;break;
		case 4:a=90;break;
		case 5:a=120;break;
		case 6:a=151;break;
		case 7:a=181;break;
		case 8:a=212;break;
		case 9:a=243;break;
		case 10:a=273;break;
		case 11:a=304;break;
		case 12:a=335;break;
	}
	b=(a+d-1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{   case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
	return 0;

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f;
	double x1,x2,disc1;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    
	}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,k1,k2,k3,k4,k5,k6,k7,k8,k9,k10,k11,k12;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1){
		k1=(y-1)%7;
	switch(k1){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==2){
		k2=(31+y-1)%7;
	switch(k2){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}

#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int year,a,b,c;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=0;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=c;
        else
            a=b;
    }
    if(a==c)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318060:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=(x/10)%10;
		c=x%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(b==0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
		if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零"); 
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		}
		if(b!=0&&c==0) printf("元整\n"); 
	}
 }

20190318177:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
    else
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    if(a==1)
        printf("L");
    else
        printf("N");
    return 0;
}

20190318062:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,e;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	e=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(e<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else 
		{
			x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(e))/(2.0*a);
			x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(e))/(2.0*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
    }
}

{

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta>=0)
		{ 
		x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	else if(delta<0)
	    {
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	    }
	} 
}

		{

20190318177:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int fun(double *x1, double *x2, double a, double b, double c)
{
double dt,absdt;
if(fabs(a)<1e-14)
return 0;
dt=b*b-4*a*c;
absdt=fabs(dt);
if(absdt<1e-14){
*x1=*x2=-b/(2*a);
return 1;
} else if(dt>0){
*x1=(-b+sqrt(dt))/(2*a);
*x2=(-b-sqrt(dt))/(2*a);
return 1;
} else return 0;
}
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2;
printf("输入a b c:\n");
scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
if(fun(&x1,&x2,a,b,c)==1){
printf("x1=%lf\n",x1);
printf("x2=%lf\n",x2);
}else 
printf("无解");
return 0;
} 
------------------------------------------------------
20190318177:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int fun(double *x1, double *x2, double a, double b, double c)
{
double dt,absdt;
if(fabs(a)<1e-14)
return 0;
dt=b*b-4*a*c;
absdt=fabs(dt);
if(absdt<1e-14){
*x1=*x2=-b/(2*a);
return 1;
} else if(dt>0){
*x1=(-b+sqrt(dt))/(2*a);
*x2=(-b-sqrt(dt))/(2*a);
return 1;
} else return 0;
}
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2;
scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
if(fun(&x1,&x2,a,b,c)==1){
printf("x1=%lf\n",x1);
printf("x2=%lf\n",x2);
}else 
printf("无解");
return 0;
}

    while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("无解");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("x1=%lf\n",x1);
                printf("x2=%lf\n",x2);
            }}
    return 0;
}

20190301013:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>

int main ()

{

int y, m, d, c, w;

printf ("");

scanf ("%d，%d", &m, &d);

if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 

y--;

m += 12;

}

c = y / 100;

y = y - c * 100;

w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;

while (w < 0) w += 7;

w %= 7;

if (w == 0) printf ("星期日");

else printf ("星期%d", w);

return 0;

}

20190318177:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double m,n,delta;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else{
			delta=b*b-4*a*c;
			m=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
			n=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",m,n);
		}
	}
	
	
	return 0;
}

main()
{
	char n1,n2,n3,t1,t2;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&n1,&n2,&n3);
	if(n1>n2)
	{
	t1=n1;
	n1=n2;
	n2=t1;
	}
	if(n2>n3)
	{
	t2=n2;
	n2=n3;
	n3=t2;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",n1,n2,n3);
}

20190318108:Problem1069:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	char n1,n2,n3,t1,t2;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&n1,&n2,&n3);
	while(n1>n2)
	{
	t1=n1;
	n1=n2;
	n2=t1;
	}
	while(n2>n3)
	{
	t2=n2;
	n2=n3;
	n3=t2;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",n1,n2,n3);
}

{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if(c<b<a)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
    if(c<a<b)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a,b);
    if(b<a<c)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
    if(b<c<a)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
    if(a<b<c)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    if(a<c<b)
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,c,b);
}

20190301005:Problem1069:正确
main()
{
	char x,y,z,max,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	max=x;
	min=z;
	if(max<y)
	max=y;
	if(max<z)
	max=z;
	if(min>x)
	min=x;
	if(min>y)
	min=y;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",min,x+y+z-max-min,max);
}

20190318108:Problem1147:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,s;
	double x1,x2;
	while(1)
	{
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	s=b*b-4*a*c;
	x1=(sqrt(s)-b)/(2*a);
	x2=(-sqrt(s)-b)/(2*a);
	if(s<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,x;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		c=x%10;
		b=(x-c)%100;
		b=b/10;
		a=x-b-c;
		a=a/100;
		if(a==1)
		printf("壹佰");
		if(a==2)
		printf("贰佰");
		if(a==3)
		printf("叁佰");
		if(a==4)
		printf("肆佰");
		if(a==5)
		printf("伍佰");
		if(a==6)
		printf("陆佰");
		if(a==7)
		printf("柒佰");
		if(a==8)
		printf("捌佰");
		if(a==9)
		printf("玖佰");
		if(b==0&&c!=0)
		printf("零");
		if(b==0&&c==0)
		printf("");
		if(b==1)
		printf("壹拾");
		if(b==2)
		printf("贰拾");
		if(b==3)
		printf("叁拾");
		if(b==4)
		printf("肆拾");

		printf("柒拾");

		printf("捌拾");
		if(b==9)
		printf("玖拾");
		if(c==0)
		printf("元整\n");
		if(c==1)
		printf("壹元整\n");
		if(c==2)
		printf("贰元整\n");

20190318133:Problem1147:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,de;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF,a,b,c)
    {   
        de=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        x1=(-b+de)/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-de)/(2*a);
        if(de>=0)
         printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        else
         printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
    return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,de;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
    {   
        
        de=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
        if(de>=0)
        {
        	x1=(-b+de)/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-de)/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
        else
        {
        	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190301006:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
void print(int x, char n[]);
int main()
{
	char x[3], y;
	while (scanf("%s", x) != EOF)
	{
		getchar();
		for (int i; i < 3; i++)
		{
			if (i==2&&x[2]=='0')
				break;
			print(i, x);
			switch (i)
			{
			case 0:
				printf("佰");
				break;
			case 1:
				if (x[1] != '0')
					printf("拾");
				break;
			default:
				break;
			}
			if (x[1]=='0'&&x[2]=='0')
				break;
		}
		printf("元整\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
void print(int x, char n[])
{
    switch (n[x] - 48)
    {
        case 0:
            printf("零");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf("壹");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf("贰");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf("叁");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf("肆");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf("伍");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf("陆");
            break;
        case 7:
            printf("柒");
            break;
        case 8:
            printf("捌");
            break;
        case 9:
            printf("玖");
            break;
        default:
            break;
    }
}

{
	char x[3], y;
	while (scanf("%s", x) != EOF)
	{
		getchar();
		for (int i; i < 3; i++)
		{
			if (i==2&&x[2]=='0')
				break;
			print(i, x);
			switch (i)
			{
			case 0:
				printf("佰");
				break;

					printf("拾");
				break;

void print(int x, char n[]);
int main()
{
	char x[3], y;
	while (scanf("%s", x) != EOF)
	{
		getchar();
		for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)
		{
			if (i==2&&x[2]=='0')
				break;
			print(i, x);
			switch (i)
			{
			case 0:
				printf("佰");
				break;
			case 1:
				if (x[1] != '0')
					printf("拾");
				break;
			default:
				break;
			}
			if (x[1]=='0'&&x[2]=='0')
				break;
		}
		printf("元整\n");
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318168:Problem1147:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0);
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
}
if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
else x1=g,x2=f;
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0);
printf("x1=%lf, x2=%lf",x1,x2);
else
{
m=-b/(2*a);
n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
printf("x1=%lf+%lf i, x2=%lf-%lf i",m,n,m,n);
}
return 0;
}

	{
		t=181+y-1;
	}
	if(x==8)
	{
		t=212+y-1;
	}
	if(x==9)
	{
		t=243+y-1;
	}
	if(x==10)
	{
		t=273+y-1;
	}
	if(x==11)
	{
		t=304+y-1;
	}
	if(x==12)
	{
		t=334+y-1;
	}
	t=t%7+2;
	if(t==1)
	printf("Monday");
	if(t==2)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(t==3)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(t==4)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(t==5)
	printf("Friday");
	if(t==6)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(t==7)
	printf("Sunday");

int main()
{

    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
    if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
    if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
    printf("%c%c %c",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}

20190318137:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()

{
	int a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2,e;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	e=sqrt (d);
	if(d<0){
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }    
	if(d==0){	
	x1=(-b)/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x1);
	}
	if(d>0){
		x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
		
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    }
}
}

20190302054:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{  
    int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(delta>=0)
        {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
         x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
         printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        } 
        else
        {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
    char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
    int x,y,sum=0;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
    {
        sum+=a[i];
    }
    sum+=y;
    sum%=7;
    for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
    {
        if(sum+1==i)
        printf("%s",b[i]);
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302054:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
    int n;
    while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
    {
        int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
        t=n;
        while(t!=0)
        {
            b[k++]=t%10;
            t/=10;
        }
        for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位
        {
            if(b[2]==i)
            printf("%s佰",a[i]);
        }
        for(int i=0;i<10;i++)
        {
            if(b[1]==i)
            {
                if(b[1]!=0)
                printf("%s拾",a[i]);
                else
                printf("零");
            }
        }
        for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位
        {
            if(b[0]==i)
            {
                if(b[0]!=0)
                printf("%s元整",a[i]);
                else
                printf("元整");
            }
        }
        printf("");
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int a;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
	int b,c,d;
	b=a/100;
	c=a/10-b*10;
	d=a-b*100-c*10;
	switch(b){
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(c){
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
		case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
		case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
		case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		default:printf("");
		
	}
	switch(d){
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
		case 2:printf("贰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁");break;
		case 4:printf("肆");break;
		case 5:printf("伍");break;
		case 6:printf("陆");break;
		case 7:printf("柒");break;
		case 8:printf("捌");break;
		case 9:printf("玖");break;
		default:printf("");
	}
	printf("元整\n",a);}
	return 0;
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(delta>=0){
	    	x1=(-1*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-1*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}else printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	return 0;

20190318162:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a-x*100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
}
if(y!=0)
{
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}
	else
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("零壹元整\n");break;
	case(2):printf("零贰元整\n");break;
	case(3):printf("零叁元整\n");break;
	case(4):printf("零肆元整\n");break;
	case(5):printf("零伍元整\n");break;
	case(6):printf("零陆元整\n");break;
	case(7):printf("零柒元整\n");break;
	case(8):printf("零捌元整\n");break;
	case(9):printf("零玖元整\n");break;
	case(0):printf("元整\n");

	}} 
	
}

	{

	if(e<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else 
		{
			x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(e))/(2.0*a);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta>=0)
	{
	  x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	  x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
	  printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
	}
	else
	    printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
	}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
		else if(t==0)
		{
			x1=-b/(2*a);
			x2=x1;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
		else 
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
}

20190318138:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double d,x1,x2,e;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	e=sqrt (d);
	if(d<0){
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }    
	if(d==0){	
	x1=(-b)/(2*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x1);
	}
	if(d>0){
		x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
		
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
    }
}
}

main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x<3)
	{
		t=31*(x-1)+y-1;
	}
	if(x==3)
	{
		t=59+y-1;
	}
	if(x==4)
	{
		t=90+y-1;
	}
	if(x==5)
	{
		t=120+y-1;
	}
	if(x==6)
	{
		t=151+y-1;
	}
	if(x==7)
	{
		t=181+y-1;
	}
	if(x==8)
	{
		t=212+y-1;
	}
	if(x==9)
	{
		t=243+y-1;
	}
	if(x==10)
	{
		t=273+y-1;
	}
	if(x==11)
	{
		t=304+y-1;
	}
	if(x==12)
	{
		t=334+y-1;
	}
	t=t%7+2;
	if(t==1)
	printf("Monday");
	if(t==2)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(t==3)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(t==4)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(t==5)
	printf("Friday");

	printf("Saturday");

	printf("Sunday");

	for(i=0;i<=x;i++)
	y=a[i]+y;
	z=y%7;
	switch(z){
		case 1:printf("Saturday ") ;break;
		case 2:printf("Sunday") ;break;
		case 3:printf("Monday") ;break;
		case 4:printf("Tuesday") ;break;
		case 5:printf("Wednesday") ;break;

#include<math.h>
int main(){
	int a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int x,y,z,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=0;i<x;i++)
	y=a[i]+y;
	z=y%7;
	switch(z){
		case 1:printf("Tuesday") ;break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday") ;break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday") ;break;
		case 4:printf("Friday") ;break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday") ;break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday") ;break;
		case 0:printf("Monday") ;break;
	}
	return 0;

20190318194:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	
	if(x>y){
		if(y>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
		}else{
			if(x>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",y,z,x);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",y,x,z);
			}
		}
	}else{
		if(x>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
		}else{
			if(y>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",x,z,y);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
			}
		}
	}
}

20190318194:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
void main ()
{
double x1;
double x2;
double x3;
double x4;
double melt1; 
double melt;
int a;
int b;
int c;
int d;
int e;
int f;
scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a, &b ,&c);
scanf("%d %d %d",&d, &e ,&f);
melt = b*b - 4*a*c;
melt1 = e*e - 4*d*f;
if (melt>=0)
{ x1=(-b + sqrt(melt))/(2*a);
x2=(-b - sqrt(melt))/(2*a);
printf ("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
if (melt1>=0)
{ x3=(-e + sqrt(melt1))/(2*d);
x4=(-e - sqrt(melt1))/(2*d);
printf ("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
}
else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

}

20190302013:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c;
	double a1,b1,c1;
	double x1,x2,p,q;
	double x3,x4,p1,q1;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	p=b*b-4*a*c;
	q=-b/(2*a);
	x1=q+p; 
	x2=q-p;
	if(p<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}else{
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x1,x2);
	}
	p1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	q1=-b1/(2*a1);
	x3=q1+p1; 
	x4=q1-p1;
	if(p1<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}else{
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x3,x4);
	}
}

20190301013:Problem1114:答案错误

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int x,y;
	int i,r,su,m;
	int s[12]={31,29,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	r=0;
	for(i=0;i<(x-1);i++){
		r=r+s[i];
	}
	su=r+y;
	m=(su+1+7)%7;
	if(m==0)
	printf("Sunday\n");
	if(m==1)
	printf("Monday\n");
	if(m==2)
	printf("Tuesday\n");
	if(m==3)
	printf("Wednesday\n");

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c;
	double a1,b1,c1;
	double x1,x2,p,q;
	double x3,x4,p1,q1;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	p=b*b-4*a*c;
	q=-b/(2*a);
	x1=q+p; 
	x2=q-p;
	if(p<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else{
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	p1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	q1=-b1/(2*a1);
	x3=q1+p1; 
	x4=q1-p1;
	if(p1<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}else{
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x3,x4);
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
void sum(int a)
{    
    switch(a)
	{
		case 0: printf("零");break;
		case 1: printf("壹");break;
		case 2: printf("贰"); break;
		case 3: printf("叁"); break;
		case 4: printf("肆"); break;
		case 5: printf("伍"); break;
		case 6: printf("陆"); break;
		case 7: printf("柒"); break;
		case 8: printf("捌"); break;
		case 9: printf("玖"); break;
	}
}
int main() 
{
	int number;
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&number)!=EOF){
	    c=number%10;
     	b=number/10%10;
    	a=number/100%10;
		if(b!=0&&c!=0) {
		    sum(a);printf("百");
			sum (b);printf("十");
			sum (c);
			printf("元整");	
	   }else if(b==0&&c!=0){
	   	   	sum (a);printf("百");
	   	   	sum (b);
	   	   	sum (c);
			printf("元整");	  	
	   }else if(b==0&&c==0){
	   	    sum (a);printf("百");
			printf("元整");   	
	   }else if(b!=0&&c==0){
	   	    sum (a);printf("百");
	   	   	sum (b);printf("十");
	   	   	printf("元整");
	   }
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d "),&a,&b,&c)!=EOF{
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d>=0)
        {
            x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf`~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
        else
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
}

main()
{

	double a1,b1,c1;
	double x1,x2,p,q;
	double x3,x4,p1,q1;
	double disc,disc1;
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a1,&b1,&c1);
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	p=sqrt(disc)/(2*a);
	q=-b/(2*a);
	x1=q+p; 
	x2=q-p;
	if(disc<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else{
		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}
	disc1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
	p1=sqrt(disc1)/(2*a1);
	q1=-b1/(2*a1);
	x3=q1+p1; 
	x4=q1-p1;
	if(disc1<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION");

		printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f",x3,x4);
	}

#include<stdio.h>
void sum(int a)
{    
    switch(a)
	{
		case 0: printf("零");break;
		case 1: printf("壹");break;
		case 2: printf("贰"); break;
		case 3: printf("叁"); break;
		case 4: printf("肆"); break;
		case 5: printf("伍"); break;
		case 6: printf("陆"); break;
		case 7: printf("柒"); break;
		case 8: printf("捌"); break;
		case 9: printf("玖"); break;
	}
}
int main() 
{
	int number;
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d\n",&number)!=EOF){
	    c=number%10;
     	b=number/10%10;
    	a=number/100%10;
		if(b!=0&&c!=0) {
		    sum(a);printf("佰");
			sum (b);printf("拾");
			sum (c);
			printf("元整\n");	
	   }else if(b==0&&c!=0){
	   	   	sum (a);printf("佰");
	   	   	sum (b);
	   	   	sum (c);
			printf("元整\n");	  	
	   }else if(b==0&&c==0){
	   	    sum (a);printf("佰");
			printf("元整\n");   	
	   }else if(b!=0&&c==0){
	   	    sum (a);printf("佰");
	   	   	sum (b);printf("拾");
	   	   	printf("元整\n");
	   }
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c %c %c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b){
		if(b>c){
			printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
		}else{
			if(a>c){
				if(a>c){
					printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
				}
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
			}
		}
	}else if(b>a){
		if(a>c){
			printf("%c%c%c",c,a,a);
		}else{
			if(b>c){
				printf("%c%C%c",a,c,b);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
			}
		}
			
		}
		}

20190318006:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;//百位 
		c=a/10;
		d=c%10;//十位
		e=a%10;//个位 
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			default:printf("玖佰");break; 
		}
		switch(d)
		{
			case 0:printf("零");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		}
		switch(e)
		{
			case 0:printf("元整");break;
			case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整");break; 
		}
	
	}
}

20190318178:Problem1059:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year,n;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        n=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            n=1;
        else
            n=0;
    }
    if(n==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318178:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0) 
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
            {
                x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
                printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            }}
    return 0;
}

20190318178:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	int y,x,sum,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:sum-0;break;
		case 2:sum-31;break;
		case 3:sum-59;break;
		case 4:sum-90;break;
		case 5:sum-120;break;
		case 6:sum-151;break;
		case 7:sum-181;break;
		case 8:sum-212;break;
		case 9:sum-243;break;
		case 10:sum-273;break;
		case 11:sum-304;break;
		case 12:sum-334;break;
	}
	sum-sum+y;
	w=(sum+1)%7;
	if(w==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(w==1)
	printf("Wesdnesday");
	if(w==2)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(w==3)
	printf("Friday");
	if(w==4)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(w==5)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(w==6)
	printf("Monday");

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{if(a>=100&&a<=999&&a%100!=0)
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	
	switch(x)
{   case(0):printf("零");break; 
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");break;
}
	switch(y)
{   case(0):printf("零");break;
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");break;
}   
	switch(z)
{   
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");break;}
	printf("元整\n");}
else if(a%100==0)
    {x=a/100;
    switch(x)
{   
    case(1):printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰元整\n");break;}}
}

20190302013:Problem1147:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double disc;
	double x1,x2,n;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF,n=2){
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		x1=(-1*b-sqrt(disc)/(2*a));
		x2=(-1*b+sqrt(disc)/(2*a));
		n=n-1;
		if(disc<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}if(n==0)break;
		}
}

20190318186:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,s;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	{
		s=(b)*(b)-4*a*c;
		if(s<0){
		
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		
		}
		else
		{
		x1=(-b + sqrt(s))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b - sqrt(s))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}

		}		
		
	}

20190301051:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,i,r=0,sum,a;
	int s[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=0;i<(x-1);i++){
		r=r+s[i]; 
	}
	sum=r+y;
	a=(sum+8)%7;
    switch (a)
    {
        case 0:
            printf ("Sunday\n");
            break;
        case 1:
            printf ("Monday\n");
            break;
        case 2:
            printf ("Tuesday\n");
            break;
        case 3:
            printf ("Wednesday\n");
            break;
        case 4:
            printf ("Thursday\n");
            break;
        case 5:
            printf ("Friday\n");
            break;
        case 6:
            printf ("Saturday\n");
            break;
    }
}

20190318125:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main ()
{
double x1;
double x2;
double melt;
int a;
int b;
int c;
 while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
melt = b*b - 4*a*c;
if (melt>=0)
{ x1=(-b + sqrt(melt))/(2*a);
x2=(-b - sqrt(melt))/(2*a);
printf ("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    return 0;
}

main()
{
    int x,y,a;

    switch(x)
    {
    	case 1 : a=1+y;break;
    	case 2 : a=31+y;break;
    	case 3 : a=31+28+y;break;
    	case 4 : a=31*2+y+28;break;
    	case 5 : a=31*2+y+28+30;break;
    	case 6 : a=31*3+y+28+30;break;
    	case 7 : a=31*3+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 8 : a=31*4+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 9 : a=31*5+y+28+30*2;break;
    	case 10 : a=31*5+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 11 : a=31*6+y+28+30*3;break;
    	case 12 : a=31*6+y+28+30*4;break;
	}
	int b=(a+1)%7;
	switch(b)
	{
		case 0 : printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 1 : printf("Monday\n");break;
		case 2 : printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 3 : printf("Wednesday\n");break;

20190318193:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;
		case 7:t=180+y;break;
		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
	}
}

20190302013:Problem1147:输出超限
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double disc;
	double x1,x2,n;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF,n=2){
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		x1=(-1*b-sqrt(disc)/(2*a));
		x2=(-1*b+sqrt(disc)/(2*a));
		n=n-1;
		if(disc<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}if(n==0)break;
		}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;//百位 
		c=a/10;
		d=c%10;//十位
		e=a%10;//个位 
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			default:printf("玖佰");break; 
		}
		switch(d)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		}
		if (d==0&&e==0) printf("元整");
		if (d==0&&e!=0) printf("零");
		switch(e)
		{
			case 0:printf("元整");break;
			case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整");break;

	{delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
		x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
        x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);

main()
{

	{
		b=a/100;//百位

		e=a%10;//个位

		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;

			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;

20190318047:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m,d,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	if(m==1||m==2)
	{
		if(m==1)
		m=13;
		if(m==2)
		m=14;
		n=(d+1+2*m+3*(m+1)/5+2018+2018/4-2018/100+2018/400)%7;
	}

	else
	n=(d+1+2*m+3*(m+1)/5+2019+2019/4-2019/100+2019/400)%7;
	switch(n)
	{
		case 0:printf("Sunday");
		break;
		case 1:printf("Monday");
		break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");
		break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");
		break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");
		break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");
		break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");
		break;
	}
}

20190318006:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;//百位 
		c=a/10;
		d=c%10;//十位
		e=a%10;//个位 
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			default:printf("玖佰");break; 
		}
		switch(d)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
		}
		if (d==0&&e==0) printf("元整\n");
		if (d==0&&e!=0) printf("零");
		switch(e)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break; 
		}
	    if (d!=0&&e==0) printf("元整\n");
	}
}

20190318179:Problem1147:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scnaf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(delta<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else{
		x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
        x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	}
	return 0;
}

    switch(m)
    {
        case 1:x=0;break;
        case 2:x=31;break;
        case 3:x=59;break;
        case 4:x=90;break;
        case 5:x=120;break;
        case 6:x=151;break;
        case 7:x=181;break;
        case 8:x=212;break;
        case 9:x=243;break;
        case 10:x=273;break;
        case 11:x=304;break;
        case 12:x=334;break;
    }
    x=x+d;
    y=(x-1)%7;
    if(y==0)
    printf("Wednesday");
    if(y==1)
    printf("Thursday");
    if(y==2)
    printf("Friday");
    if(y==3)
    printf("Saturday");
    if(y==4)
    printf("Sunday");

	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		delta = b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
		else{
		x1=(-b + sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b - sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);}
		}
    }

20190318158:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int r,w,x,disc;
double x1,x2;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&r, &w, &x)!=EOF)
{
disc=w*w-4*r*x;
if(disc>=0)
{
x1=((-w)+sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
x2=((-w)-sqrt(disc))/(2*r);
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
else if(disc<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
}
return 0;
}

	{
		a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
		D=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(D>=0)
		{E=sqrt(D);

	int m,d,sum=0,i;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	for(i=0;i<m;i++)
	{
	  sum+=c[i];
	}
	sum=(sum+d+2-1)%7;
	if(sum==0)printf("Sunday");
	if(sum==1)printf("Monday");
	if(sum==2)printf("Tuesday");
	if(sum==3)printf("Wednesday");
	if(sum==4)printf("Thursday");

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main() {
   double a, b, c, x1, x2, t;
   scanf("%lf %lf %lf", &a, &b, &c); 
   t = b*b - 4*a*c; 
   if (t<0) {
      printf("NO SOLUTION.\n"); 
      return 0; 
   }
   t = sqrt(t);
   x1 = (-b + t)/(2*a); 
   x2 = (-b - t)/(2*a); 
   printf("%lf～～～%lf\n", x1, x2); 
   return 0; 
}

20190318125:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,g;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	
	switch (a)
	{case 1:a=0;break;
	case 2:a=31;break;
	case 3:a=31+28;break;
	case 4:a=31+28+31;break;
	case 5:a=120;break;
	case 6:a=151;break;
	case 7:a=181;break;
	case 8:a=212;break;
	case 9:a=243;break;
	case 10:a=273;break;
	case 11:a=304;break;
	case 12:a=334;break;
	default:printf("Error!\n");	
}
	c=a+b-1;
	d=c%7;
	{
	switch (d)
	{
	case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 1: printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 2: printf("Thursday");break;
	case 3: printf("Friday");break;
	case 4: printf("Saturday");break;
	case 5: printf("Sunday ");break;
	case 6: printf("Monday");break;
	default:printf("Error!\n");	}}



}

20190318080:Problem1114:时间超限
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int month,day,week,i,all;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	i=0,all=0;
	while(i<month-1)
	{
	i++;
	if(i=1,3,5,7,8,10,12)
	{all+=31;}
	if(i=4,6,9,11)
	{all+=30;}
	if(i=2)
	{all+=28;}
	}
	all+=day;
	week=(all-1)%7;
	switch(week)
	{
	case 1:printf("Mondy\n");break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
	case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
	}
}

{

        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;

20190318129:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) w += 7;
w %= 7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190301019:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
int n;
while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
else
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}
printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

20190301019:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;//上面两个数组的a[0],b[0]都是无关量；这是为了让月数和周数与下标对应； 
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i];//求这几个月的整月天数； 
}
sum+=y;//再加上零头； 
sum%=7;//总天数对7求余，余数就当天的星期数； 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)//因为1月1号是星期二，往后推一天； 
printf("%s",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}
------------------------------------------------------
20190301019:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main() {
    int a, b, c;
    double x1, x2, delta;
    while ((scanf("%d%d%d", &a, &b, &c)) != EOF) {
        delta = b * b - 4 * a * c;
        if (delta < 0) {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
            continue;
        }
        x1 = (-b + sqrt(delta)) / (2 * a);
        x2 = (-b - sqrt(delta)) / (2 * a);
             printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1, x2);
    }
    return 0;
}

{
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
else
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}
printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){ 
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d>=0)
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	 }
	if(d<0)
	{ 
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}
}

20190318013:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ( "%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) {
y--; 
m += 12;
}
c=y/ 100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w<0)w+=7;
w%=7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
    char a, b, c, s;
    scanf("%c%c%c", &a, &b, &c);
    if (a>b)
    {
        s=a;
        a=b;
        b=s;
    }
    if (a>c)
    {
        s=a;
        a=c;
        c=s;
    }
    if (b>c)
    {
        s=b;
        b=c;
        c=s;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c", a, b, c);
}

int main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c)
	printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);
	if(a>c&&c>b)
	printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
    if(b>a&&a>c)
	printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	if(b>c&&c>a)
	printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	if(c>a&&a>b)
	printf("%d%d%d",b,a,c);
	if(c>b&&b>a)
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

main()
{
	int x, y, c, s, w;
	scanf("%d, %d", &x, &y);
	s=2019;
	if (x==1 || x==2){
		s--;
		x+=12;
	}
	c=s/100;
	s=s-c*100;
	w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1;
	while (w<0)
	w+=7;
	w%=7;
    switch (w){
    	case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
	   	case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;

20190301031:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
int getDate(int month,int day);
main()
{	int month,day,x,d;	
printf("请输入日期");	
scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);	
x=getDate(month,day);	
switch(x)	
{		
case 0:printf("Monday");break;		
case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;		
case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;		
case 3:printf("Thursday");break;		
case 4:printf("Friday");break;		
case 5:printf("Saturday");break;		
case 6:printf("Sunday");break;	 	
}	
}
 int getDate(int month,int day)
{	
int i,sum=0,y;	
int a[100]={31,29,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	for(i=0;i<month-1;i++)
	{		
	sum+=a[i];	
	}	
	sum+=day;	
	y=sum%7;	
	return y;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

int main() {
   double a, b, c, x1, x2, t;
   scanf("%lf %lf %lf", &a, &b, &c); 
   t = b*b - 4*a*c; 
   if (t<0) {
      printf("NO SOLUTION.\n"); 
      return 0; 
   }
   t = sqrt(t);
   x1 = (-b + t)/(2*a); 
   x2 = (-b - t)/(2*a); 
   printf("%lf~~~%lf\n", x1, x2); 
   return 0;

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
int n;
while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{ 
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
else
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}

}
return 0;

      return 0;

   t = sqrt(t);
   x1 = (-b + t)/(2*a); 
   x2 = (-b - t)/(2*a);

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	switch(a){
		case 1:c=b%7;break;
		case 2:c=(b+31)%7;break;
		case 3:c=(b+59)%7;break;
		case 4:c=(b+90)%7;break;
		case 5:c=(b+120)%7;break;
		case 6:c=(b+151)%7;break;
		case 7:c=(b+181)%7;break;
		case 8:c=(b+212)%7;break;
		case 9:c=(b+243)%7;break;
		case 10:c=(b+273)%7;break;
		case 11:c=(b+304)%7;break;
		case 12:c=(b+334)%7;break;
	}
	switch(c){
		case 0:printf("Monday");break;
		case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 4:printf("Friday");break;
		case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 6:printf("Sunday");break;

20190301031:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);//输入三个字母; 
	if (a>b)
	{
		t=a;
		a=b;
		b=t;
	}
	if (a>c)
	{
		t=a;
		a=c;
		c=t;
	}
	if (b>c)
	{
		t=b;
		b=c;
		c=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c); 
    return 0;
}

20190318093:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){ 
	x=a/100;
	y=a/10%10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
}
if(y==0&&z==0||y!=0&&z!=0){
	switch(y)
{
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
}
	switch(z)
{
	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	case 9:printf("玖");break;
}}
if(y==0&&z!=0){
	switch(y)
{
	case 0:printf("零");break;
}
	switch(z)
{
	case 1:printf("壹");break;
	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁");break;
	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	case 9:printf("玖");break;
}}
if(y!=0&&z==0){
	switch(y)
{
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
}}
	printf("元整\n");} 
}

20190318192:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	
	if(x>y){
		if(y>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
		}else{
			if(x>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",y,z,x);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",y,x,z);
			}
		}
	}else{
		if(x>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
		}else{
			if(y>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",x,z,y);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
			}
		}
	}
}

20190318192:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}return 0;
}

20190301031:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{ 
	double a,b,c,x1,x2,delta;
	while (scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    delta=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if (delta>=0){
		   x1=((-b)+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
	       x2=((-b)-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
	       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2); }
	    else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
 }

20190301004:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
#include<math.h>
main() 
{ 
    int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    int disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	    int p=-b/(2.0*a);
	    int q=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
	    x1=p+q;
	    x2=p-q;
	    if(disc>=0)
		{
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	    else
	    {
		    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    }
    }
}

20190318170:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b&&b>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a);}
	if(a>b&&a>c&&b<c){printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);}
	if(b>a&&a>c){printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);}
	if(b>a&&b>c&&c>a){printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);}
	if(c>a&&a>b){printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);}
	if(c>a&&c>b&&b>a){printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);}
	return 0;
}

	if(a>b&&a>c)
	 d=a;
	else if(b>a&&b>c)
	 d=b;
	else
	 d=c;
	if(a<b&&a<c)
	 e=a;
	else if(b<a&&b<c)
	 e=b;
	else
	 e=c;
	f=c;

20190318170:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,p;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    p=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(p<0){
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        else if(p>=0){
	    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
	return 0;
}

20190318170:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,w,a;
	x>0&&x<13;
	y>0&&y<32;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	w=19+(19/4)+(20/4)-2*20+(26*(x+1))/10+y-1;
	a=(abs(w)%7+7)%7;
	switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
	    case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
	    case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
    	case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
    	case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
    	case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;
    	case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		break;
	}
}

#include"math.h" 
main()
{
	double t,x1,x2;
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    t=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(t>=0)
	    {
	    	x1=(-b-sqrt(t))/2*a;
	        x2=(-b+sqrt(t))/2*a;
	        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
		}
		else
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;
		case 7:t=180+y;break;
		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
	}
}

20190318094:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>

main()
{
	double a,b,c,x,D,m;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) 
	{
	a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	D=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(D>=0)
	{
	m=sqrt(D);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-b+m)/(2*a),(-b-m)/(2*a));
	}
	else 
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	};
	
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d,&x")!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=(x/10)&10;
		c=x&10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		if(b==0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
		if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零");
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		}
		if(b!=0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
	}
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

20190301031:Problem1114:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
	int month,day,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);//输入日期； 
	switch(month)
	{
		case 1:a=0;break;
		case 2:a=31;break;
		case 3:a=59;break;
		case 4:a=90;break;
		case 5:a=120;break;
		case 6:a=151;break;
		case 7:a=181;break;
		case 8:a=212;break;
		case 9:a=243;break;
		case 10:a=273;break;
		case 11:a=304;break;
		case 12:a=334;break;
	}
	a=a+day;
    b=(a-1)%7;
    if (b==0){
	printf("Tuesday");}
    if (b==1){
    printf("Wednesday");}
    if (b==2){	
    printf("Thursday");}
    if (b==3){
    printf("Friday");}
    if (b==4){
    printf("Saturday");}
    if (b==5){
    printf("Sunday");}
    if (b==6){
    printf("Monday"); }
}

    {d=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;

    if(d>=0){
		x1=((-b1)+sqrt(d))/(2*a1);
		x2=((-b1)-sqrt(d))/(2*a1);

{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=(x/10)&10;
		c=x&10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break; 
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(b==0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
		if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零");
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		}
		if(b!=0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
	}
}

20190318015:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main ()
{
int y,m,d,c,w;
char a[7][10]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
scanf ( "%d,%d", &m, &d);
y=2019;
if (m==1||m==2) {
y--; 
m += 12;
}
c=y/ 100;
y=y-c*100;
w=(c/4)-2*c+(y+y/4)+(13*(m+1)/5)+d-1;
while (w<0)w+=7;
w%=7;
if (w == 0) printf ("Sunday");
else puts(a[w-1]);;
}

20190318064:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h" 
main()
{
	double t,x1,x2;
	int a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	    t=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(t<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
	    if(t>=0){
	    	x1=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
	        x2=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
	        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);}
    }	   
}

        d=a;a=b;b=d;
    } else if (a>c) {
        d=a;a=c;c=d;
    } else if (b>c) {
        d=c;c=b;b=d;
    }
    printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;

		case 1:x=0;break;
		case 2:x=31;break;
		case 3:x=59;break;
		case 4:x=90;break;
		case 5:x=120;break;
		case 6:x=151;break;
		case 7:x=181;break;
		case 8:x=212;break;
		case 9:x=243;break;
		case 10:x=273;break;
		case 11:x=304;break;
		case 12:x=334;break;
	}
	y=(x+b-2)%7;
	if(y==0)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(y==1)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Friday");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(y==5)
	printf("Sunday");

int main()
{
    char a,b,c,t;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
    if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
    if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;

main()
{

	int a;
	int c;
	int d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(a=1;a<=x;a=a+1)
	{
		c=n[a]+y;//天数 
		d=c%7;
	}
	switch(d)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");
		break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");
		break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");
        break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");
		break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");
		break;

		break;

20190318058:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main(void)
{
	int a,b,c;
	double dela;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		dela = b*b - 4*a*c;
		if(dela >= 0)
		{
			x1 = (-1*b + sqrt(dela)) / (2*a);
			x2 = (-1*b - sqrt(dela)) / (2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
		}else printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;
 }

20190302034:Problem1147:编译错误
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	double x1,x2;
	e=scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	do
	{
		if(b*b+4*a*c<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	break;	
	}while(e!=EOF);
 }

20190302006:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=y-1;
	if(x==1||x==2) b=(x-1)*31+a;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
    if(b==1) printf("Monday");
    if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(b==5) printf("Friday");
    if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
}

20190318190:Problem1069:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int A,B,C;
	int max,mid,min;
	scanf("%c %c %c",&A,&B,&C);
	if (A>B && A>C){
		if (B>C){
			max=A,mid=B,min=C;
		}
		else {
			max=A,mid=C,min=B;
		}
	}
	if (B>C && B>A){
		if (A>C){
			max=B,mid=A,min=C;
		}
		else {
			max=B,mid=C,min=A;
		}
	}
	if (C>A && C>B){
		if (B>A){
			max=C,mid=B,min=A;
		}
		else {
			max=C,mid=A,min=B;
		}
	}
	printf("%c %c %c",min,mid,max);
}

#include"stdio.h"
main(){
	int x,y,d,i,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	d=(x-1)*30+y-1;
	if(x==1){d=y-1;}
	if(x>1&&x<=7)
	{
		for(i=1;i<x;i=i+2){d=d+1;}
		}
	if(x>=8)
	{   d=d+4;
		for(t=8;t<x;t=t+2){d=d+1;}
		}
	if(x>2){d=d-2;}
	while(d>=7){d=d-7;}
	switch(d)
	{
		 case 0:printf("Tuesday");
	         break;
	     case 1:printf("Wednesday");
	         break;
	     case 2:printf("Thursday");
	         break;  
	     case 3:printf("Friday");
	         break;
	     case 4:printf("Saturday ");
	         break;
	     case 5:printf("Sunday");
	         break;
	     case 6:printf("Monday");
	         break;
		}
	}

		case 12:a=335;break;

	if (A>B && A>C){
		if (B>C){
			max=A,mid=B,min=C;
		}
		else {
			max=A,mid=C,min=B;
		}
	}
	if (B>C && B>A){
		if (A>C){
			max=B,mid=A,min=C;
		}
		else {
			max=B,mid=C,min=A;
		}
	}
	if (C>A && C>B){
		if (B>A){
			max=C,mid=B,min=A;
		}
		else {
			max=C,mid=A,min=B;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",min,mid,max);
}
------------------------------------------------------

	sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;

main()
{
    int year,a;
    printf("");
    
    scanf("%d",&year);
    
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L\n");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N\n");
    }
}

	if(a>b){t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	if(a>c){t=a;a=c;c=t;} 
	if(b>c){t=c;c=b;b=t;}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int x,y;
	int a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int i,j=0,h,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for (i=1;i<x;i++)
	j=j+a[i];
	//printf("%d\n",j);
	h=j+y;
	//printf("%d\n",h);
	n=h%7;
	switch (n){
		case 0: printf("Monday"); break;
		case 1: printf("Tuesday"); break;
		case 2: printf("Wednesday"); break;
		case 3: printf("Thursday"); break;
		case 4: printf("Friday"); break;
		case 5: printf("Saturday"); break;
		case 6: printf("Sunday"); break;
	}
}

20190302006:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
 float a, b, c;
 double s, x1, x2;
 while(scanf("%f %f %f",&a, &b, &c)!=EOF)
 {
 s = b * b - 4 * a*c;
 if(s >= 0)
 {
  x1 = (-b + sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  x2 = (-b - sqrt(s)) / (2 * a);
  printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
 }
 else if(s < 0)
 {
 printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
 }
 }
}

20190301014:Problem1069:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b && a>c && b>c) 
        printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
    else if (a>c && a>b && c>b) 
        rintfp("%c %c %c\n",a,c,b);
    else if (b>a && b>c && a>c) 
        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,a,c);
    else if (b>c && b>a && c>a) 
        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,c,a);
    else if (c>a && c>b && a>b) 
        printf("%c %c %c\n",c,a,b);
    else if (c>b && c>a && b>a) 
        printf("%c %c %c\n",c,b,a);
    return 0;
}

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:
			z=0;
			break;
		case 2:
			z=a;
			break;
		case 3:
			z=a+b;
			break;
		case 4:
			z=a+b+c;
			break;
		case 5:
			z=a+b+c+d;
			break;
		case 6:
			z=a+b+c+d+e;
			break;

			z=a+b+c+d+e+f;
			break;

			break;

			break;

			break;

			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h+i+j;
			break;
		case 12:
			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h+i+j+k;
			break;
	}
	int w=z%7;
	switch(w)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;

			printf("Saturday");
			break;

			printf("Sunday");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Monday");
			break;
		case 0:
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;

20190318094:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;//a为月差 
	switch (a){
	         case 0:b=y-1;break;
	         case 1:b=y-1+31;break;
	         case 2:b=y-1+59;break;
	         case 3:b=y-1+90;break;
	         case 4:b=y-1+120;break;
	         case 5:b=y-1+151;break;
	         case 6:b=y-1+181;break;
			 case 7:b=y-1+212;break;
			 case 8:b=y-1+243;break;
			 case 9:b=y-1+273;break;
			 case 10:b=y-1+304;break;
			 case 11:b=y-1+334;break;
			 };
	c=b%7;//c为余数 b为日期差 d为星期号 
    if(b>=7) d=2+c;
    else d=2+b;
    if(d>7) d=d-7;
    else d=d;
    switch (d){
	         case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	         case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	         case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	         case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	         case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	         case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	         case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
			 };
}

20190318143:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){

	g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	while(y<3){
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		y++;if(b!=0){
		switch(y){
			case 1: printf("佰");break;
			case 2: printf("拾");break;
			case 3: printf("元整");break; 
		}}
		if(s>0&&g!=0){
		b=s;s=-1;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");continue;}
		if(s==0&&g==0){
		printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		} 
		if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	}break;
	
    }
}
}

main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	if(b*b - 4*a*c < 0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	else{
	x1 = ((-b) + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	x2 = ((-b) - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c))/(2.0*a);
	printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);

			break;
		case 9:
			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h;
			break;
		case 10:
			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h+i;
			break;
		case 11:
			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h+i+j;
			break;
		case 12:
			z=a+b+c+d+e+f+g+h+i+j+k;
			break;
	}
	int w=z%7;
	switch(w)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Saturday");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Sunday");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Monday");
			break;
		case 0:
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;
	}
}

20190318164:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
	char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	int x,y,sum=0,i,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1;i<x;i++)
	{
		sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;
	c=sum%7;
	c=c+1;
	printf("%s\n",b[c]);
	return 0;
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	double x1,x2;
	e=scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	while(e!=EOF)
	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	break;	
	}
}

20190301005:Problem1147:编译错误
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,d,m;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            m=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(m>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(m<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

20190318143:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	while(y<3){
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		y++;if(b!=0){
		switch(y){
			case 1: printf("佰");break;
			case 2: printf("拾");break;
			case 3: printf("元整");break; 
		}
		}
		if(s>0&&g!=0){
		b=s;s=-1;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");continue;}
		if(s==0&&g==0){
		printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		} 
		if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	}break;
	
    }
}
return 0;
}

20190318024:Problem1069:正确
#include "stdio.h"
int main()
{
    char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);//注意输入没有空格的，直接就这3个字母
	if (a>b) 
	{
	t=a;a=b;b=t;
	}
	if (a>c) 
	{
	t=a;a=c;c=t;
	}if (b>c) 
	{
	t=c;
	c=b;
	b=t;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

{

	b=a%4;
	c=a%100;
	d=a%400;

	    printf("L");

	    printf("N");

    if (a>b) {d=a;a=b;b=d;}
    if (a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}
    if (b>c) {d=c;c=b;b=d;}
    printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318143:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	while(y<3){
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		y++;if(b!=0){
		switch(y){
			case 1: printf("佰");break;
			case 2: printf("拾");break;
			case 3: printf("元整");break; 
		}
		}
		if(s>0&&g!=0){
		b=s;s=-1;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");b=g;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g==0){
		printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		} 
		if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	}break;
	
    }
}
return 0;
}

#include  <math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	switch(a){
		case 1:x=0;break;
		case 2:x=31;break;
		case 3:x=59;break;
		case 4:x=90;break;
		case 5:x=120;break;
		case 6:x=151;break;
		case 7:x=181;break;
		case 8:x=212;break;
		case 9:x=243;break;
		case 10:x=273;break;
		case 11:x=304;break;
		case 12:x=334;break;
	}
	y=(x+b)%7;
	if(y==6)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(y==0)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(y==1)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(y==2)
	printf("Friday");
	if(y==3)
	printf("Saturday");
	if(y==4)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(y==5) 
	printf("Monday");

20190318094:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int n;
	while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF) 
	{
	int g=0,s=0,b=0;
	b=n/100;
	s=(n%100)/10;
	g=n%10;
	switch(b)
	{
	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	case 9:printf("玖佰");break; 
    }
    if(g!=0)
    {
	
    	switch(s)
	{
		case 0:printf("零");break;
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
    }
}
else
	switch(s)
	{
	case 0:break;
	case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	case 9:printf("玖拾");break; 
    }
    switch(g)
	{
	case 0:printf("元整");break;
	case 1:printf("壹元整");break;
	case 2:printf("贰元整");break;
	case 3:printf("叁元整");break;
	case 4:printf("肆元整");break;

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	while(y<3){
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		y++;if(b!=0){
		switch(y){
			case 1: printf("佰");break;
			case 2: printf("拾");break;
			case 3: printf("元整");break; 
		}
		}
		if(s>0&&g!=0){
		b=s;s=-1;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");b=g;continue;}
		if(s==0&&g==0){
		printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		} 
		if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	}
	
    }printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

int main()

20190302047:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main() 
{
    double a, b, c, disc, x1, x2, realpart, imagpart;
    scanf("%lf%lf%lf", &a, &b, &c);
    printf("The equation ");
    if (fabs(a) <= 1e-6)
        printf("is not a quadratic");
    else {
        disc = b * b - 4 * a * c;
        if (fabs(disc) <= 1e-6)
            printf("has two equal roots:%8.4f", -b / (2 * a));
        else if (disc > 1e-6) {
            x1 = (-b + sqrt(disc)) / (2 * a);
            x2 = (-b - sqrt(disc)) / (2 * a);
            printf("has two differ roots:%8.4f and %8.4f", x1, x2);
        } else {
            realpart = -b / (2 * a);
            imagpart = sqrt(-disc) / (2 * a);
            printf(" has complex roots:\n");
            printf("%8.4f+%8.4fi\n", realpart, imagpart);
            printf("%8.4f-%8.4fi\n", realpart, imagpart);
        }
    }
}

	printf("Wednesday");
