20190318100:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z;
    double x1,x2,h;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
        z=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(z>=0)
        {
            h=sqrt(z);
            x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
            else
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
}

20190301049:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
double a,b,c;
double p;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
p=b*b-4*a*c;
if (p<0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
p=sqrt(p)/2/a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-b/2/a+p,-b/2/a-p);
return 0;
}

#include   "math.h"
 void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >=0)
    { 
    x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
} 
    else if (d < 0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    else
    printf("%.3lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,t;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double d;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d=(b*b)-(4*a*c);
		if(d<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",((-b)+sqrt(d))/(2*a),((-b)-sqrt(d))/(2*a));
	}
	return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int x,y,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:z=y-1;break;
		case 2:z=31+y-1;break;
		case 3:z=31+28+y-1;break;
		case 4:z=31+28+31+y-1;break;
		case 5:z=31+28+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 6:z=31+28+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 7:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 8:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 9:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y-1;break;
		case 10:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 11:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 12:z=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y-1;break;
	}
	z=(z+2)%7;
	switch(z)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

20190318049:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
void main()
{
    char a,b,c,A,B,C;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a<b)
	    A=a,B=b;
	else
	    A=b,B=a;
	if(c<A)
	    C=B,B=A,A=c;
	else
	    {
	    	if(B<c)
	    	    C=c;
	    	else
	    	    C=B,B=c;
		}
	printf("%c%c%c",A,B,C);
}

#include <math.h>
main()
{
double a,b,c;
double p;
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
p=b*b-4*a*c;
if (p<0)
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else
p=sqrt(p)/2/a;
printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",-b/2/a+p,-b/2/a-p);
return 0;
}

20190318072:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,disc,x1,x2,m,n;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	disc=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(disc<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	else {
		m=-b/(2.0*a);
		n=sqrt(disc)/(2.0*a);
		x1=m+n;x2=m-n;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include   "math.h"
 void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2,e,f,g,h,x3,x4;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf\n",&a,&b,&c);
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&e,&f,&g);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    h=f*f-4*e*g;
    if (d >=0||h>=0)
    { 
    x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    //printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
} 
    else if (d < 0||h<0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    //else
    //printf("%.3lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
   // printf("%.3lf\n", -f / (2 * e));

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,t; 
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);//注意输入没有空格的，直接就这3个字母 
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;} 
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;} 
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;} 
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c); 
return 0; 
 }

20190302041:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int y=2019,i,c,m,d,w,sum;
	const int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31,30,31};

	{
		scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
		sum=d-1;
		for(i=0;i<m-1;i++)
		{
			sum+=days[i];
		}
		if(m>2){
			if((0==y%4&&0!=y%100)||0==y%400)
			{
				sum+=1;
			}
		}
		sum+=1;
			}
			switch((sum-(7-w)%7)%7)
			{
				case 0:printf("Monday");break;
				case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
				case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
				case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
				case 4:printf("Friday");break;
				case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
				case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
				
			}
	 
	 

	 
	 
	 
	 
	 
}

20190301007:Problem1158:正确
#include  <stdio.h>
int main()
{
 int a,b,c,x;
 while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
  a=x/100;
  b=(x%100)/10;
  c=x%10;
  if(a!=0&&b==0&&c==0){
   switch(a){
    case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
    case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
    case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
    case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
    case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
    case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
    case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
    case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
    case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
   }
  }
  else{
     switch(a){
       case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
       case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
       case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
       case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
       case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
       case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
       case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
       case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
       case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
     }
  switch(b){
   case 0:printf("零");break;
   case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
   case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
   case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
   case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
   case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
   case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
   case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
   case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
   case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
  }
  switch(c){
   case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
   case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break; 
   case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
   case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
   case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
   case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
   case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
   case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
   case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
   case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
  }
     }
   
 }
}

printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
else

20190301005:Problem1147:编译错误
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
	}
}

20190318143:Problem1158:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF{
	    g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	    while(y<3){
		    switch (b){
			    case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			    case 0: printf("零"); break;
	     	}
	    	y++;
	    	switch(y){
			    case 1: printf("佰");break;
		     	case 2: printf("拾");break;
			    case 3: printf("元整");break; 
	    	}
	    	if(s>0&&g!=0){
	    	b=s;s=-1;continue;}
	    	if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");b=g;continue;}
		    if(s==0&&g==0){
		    printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		    if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		    } 
		    if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	    }if(s==-1&&g==-1)break;
	        continue;
        }printf("\n");
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302017:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a,b,c,tmp;
    while(scanf("%c%c%c%*c",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) 
    {
        if(a>b) tmp=a,a=b,b=tmp;
        if(a>c) tmp=a,a=c,c=tmp;
        if(b>c) tmp=b,b=c,c=tmp;
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    }
    return 0;
}

{

	{
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);

            if(t<0)

#include <stdio.h>

int main ()

{

int y, m, d, c, w;

//printf ("输入年 月 日（空格间隔）：");

scanf ("%d %d", &m, &d);

if (m ==1 || m == 2) { //判断月份是否为1或2

//y--;

m += 12;

}

c = 2019 / 100;

y = 2019 - c * 100;

w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;

while (w < 0) w += 7;

w %= 7;

if (w == 0) 
printf ("Sunday ");
if(w==1)
printf ("Monday");
if (w == 2) 
printf ("Tuesday");
if (w == 3) 
printf ("Wednesday");
if (w == 4) 
printf ("Thursday");
if (w == 5) 
printf ("Friday");
if (w == 6)
 printf ("Saturday ");
}

int main ()

{

int y, m, d, c, w;

//printf ("输入年 月 日（空格间隔）：");

scanf ("%d,%d", &m, &d);

if (m ==1 || m == 2) { //判断月份是否为1或2

//y--;

m += 12;

}

c = 2019 / 100;

y = 2019 - c * 100;

w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;

while (w < 0) w += 7;

w %= 7;

if (w == 0) 
printf ("Sunday ");
if(w==1)
printf ("Monday");
if (w == 2) 
printf ("Tuesday");
if (w == 3) 
printf ("Wednesday");
if (w == 4) 
printf ("Thursday");
if (w == 5) 
printf ("Friday");
if (w == 6)
 printf ("Saturday ");

int main(void)
{
 char a,b,c,t;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  t=a;a=b;b=t;
 }
 if(a>c)
 {
  t=a;a=c;c=t;
 }
 if(b>c)
 {
  t=c;c=b;b=t;
 }
 printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
 char a,b,c,t;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 if(a>b)
 {
  t=a;
  a=b;
  b=t;
 }
 if(a>c)
 {
  t=a;
  a=c;
  c=t;
     }
    if(b>c)
     {
  t=c;
  c=b;
  b=t;
     }
     printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
     return 0;
}

20190318030:Problem1147:编译错误

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double delta; 
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
		else{
			x1 =(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			x2 =(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		return 0;
	}
}

20190318143:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	    g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	    while(y<3){
		    switch (b){
			    case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			    case 0: printf("零"); break;
	     	}
	    	y++;
	    	switch(y){
			    case 1: printf("佰");break;
		     	case 2: printf("拾");break;
			    case 3: printf("元整");break; 
	    	}
	    	if(s>0&&g!=0){
	    	b=s;s=-1;continue;}
	    	if(s==0&&g!=0){y=2;s=-1;printf("零");b=g;continue;}
		    if(s==0&&g==0){
		    printf("元整");y=4;break;} 
		    if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		    } 
		    if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	    }if(s==-1&&g==-1)break;
	        continue;
        }
    }
    return 0;
}

#include   "math.h"
 void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2,e,f,g,h,x3,x4;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf\n",&a,&b,&c);
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&e,&f,&g);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    h=f*f-4*e*g;
    if (d >=0||h>=0)
    { 
    x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    //printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);
} 
    else if (d < 0||h<0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    //else
    //printf("%.3lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
    //printf("%.3lf\n", -f / (2 * e));
    
}

int main()
{
	int x,y;
	scanf("%d",&x);
	if(x%400==0)
	y=1;
	else
	{
	    if(x%4==0&&x%100!=0)
	    y=1;
    else
	y=2; 
    }
	if(y=1)
	{
		
	    printf("L");
    }
	else
	{
	printf("N");
	} 
}

20190301053:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
   int a;
   while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
   	 int b;
     int c=1;
     int n;
     int m=0;
	 while (a>0){
		n=a%10;
		m=m*10+n;
		a=a/10;
	 }
	
	 while (m>0) {
		b=m%10;
		switch (b){
			case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			case 0: printf("零"); break;
		}
		m=m/10;
		
		if (b>0&&c==1){
			printf("佰");
			c++;
    	}
    	else if (b>0&&c==2){
    		    printf("拾");
			    c++;}
	    else if (b==0&&c==2){
				printf("");
			    c++;}
		else if (b>0&&c==3){
			printf("");
			c++;
		}
	 }
     printf("元整\n");
 }
}

20190318030:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	if(a==1&&b<=7)c=b;
	if(a==1&&b>7)c=b%7;
	if(a==2)c=(31+b)%7;
	if(a==3)c=(59+b)%7;
	if(a==4)c=(90+b)%7;
	if(a==5)c=(120+b)%7;
	if(a==6)c=(151+b)%7;
	if(a==7)c=(181+b)%7;
	if(a==8)c=(212+b)%7;
	if(a==9)c=(243+b)%7;
	if(a==10)c=(273+b)%7;
	if(a==11)c=(304+b)%7;
	if(a==12)c=(334+b)%7;
	if(c==0)printf("Monday");
	if(c==1)printf("Tuesday");
	if(c==2)printf("Wednesday");
	if(c==3)printf("Thursday");
	if(c==4)printf("Friday");
	if(c==5)printf("Saturday");
	if(c==6)printf("Sunday");
}

20190302055:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	while(scanf("%d",&e)!=EOF)
	{
		char *d[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","零"}; 
		a=e/100;
		b=e/10-10*a;
		c=e%10;
		if(b==0&&c==0)
		printf("%s佰元整\n",d[a-1]);
		if(b!=0&&c==0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",d[a-1],d[b-1]);
		if(b==0&&c!=0)
		printf("%s佰零%s元整\n",d[a-1],d[c-1]);
		if(b!=0&&c!=0)
		printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",d[a-1],d[b-1],d[c-1]);
	}
 }

20190301014:Problem1069:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
    if (a>b) {
        if (b>c) {
            printf("%c %c %c",a,b,c);
            
        } else if (c>b && a>c) {
            printf("%c %c %c",a,c,b);
    } else if (b>a) {
        if (a>c) {
            printf("%c %c %c",b,a,c);
            
        }else if (c>a && b>c) {
             printf("%c %c %c",b,c,a);
        }
    } else if (c>a) {
        if (a>b) {
             printf("%c %c %c",c,a,b);
        } else if (b>a && c>b) {
             printf("%c %c %c",c,b,a);
        }
    }
}

20190318049:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    float x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF)
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION");
        else
        {
        	x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	        x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
    return 0;
}

20190318024:Problem1147:答案错误
#include  "stdio.h"
#include   "math.h"
 void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2,e,f,g,h,x3,x4;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >=0)
    { 
    x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
} 
    else if (d < 0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    else
    printf("%.3lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
    while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)  //读多组数据
{
     d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >=0)
    { 
    x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
} 
    else if (d < 0)
    printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
    else
    printf("%.3lf\n", -b / (2 * a));

}
//while这一行已经把一组数据都读出来放到a,b,c了。你只需要在{ }中处理就可以了。

//PROBLEM D的提示

}

main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b && a>c && b>c) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if (a>c && a>b && c>b) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",a,c,b);
    } else if (b>a && b>c && a>c) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,a,c);
    } else if (b>c && b>a && c>a) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,c,a);
    } else if (c>a && c>b && a>b) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",c,a,b);
    } else if (c>b && c>a && b>a) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",c,b,a);
    }
}

20190318200:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main(void)
{
    int x, y;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    int MONTH[] = { 0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31 };
    int i=0;
    int days=0;
    for (i = 0; i < x; i++)
    {
        days = MONTH[i];
    }
    days = days + y-1;
    int a;
    a= days % 7;
    switch (a)
    {
    case 0:printf("Tuesday"); break;
    case 1:printf("Wednesday"); break;
    case 2:printf("Thursday"); break;
    case 3:printf("Friday"); break;
    case 4:printf("Saturday"); break;
    case 5:printf("Sunday"); break;
    case 6:printf("Monday"); break;
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318185:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char q,w,e;
	
	scanf("%c%c%c",&q,&w,&e);
	
	if(q>w){
		if(w>e){
			printf("%c%c%c",e,w,q);
		}else{
			if(q>e){
				printf("%c%c%c",w,e,q);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",w,q,e);
			}
		}
	}else{
		if(q>e){
			printf("%c%c%c",e,q,w);
		}else{
			if(w>e){
				printf("%c%c%c",q,e,w);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",q,w,e);
			}
		}
	}
}

        printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if (a>c>b) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",a,c,b);
    } else if (b>a>c) {
        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,a,c);

        printf("%c %c %c\n",b,c,a);

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;
		case 7:t=180+y;break;
		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char work1,work2,work3;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&work1,&work2,&work3);
	if(work1<work2)
	{if(work2<work3)
	  printf("%c%c%c",work1,work2,work3);
	else {if(work3>work1)
	    printf("%c%c%c",work1,work3,work2);
	    else{
		printf("%c%c%c",work3,work1,work2);}}
	}
	else
	{if(work2<work3)
	 {if(work1>work3)
	 printf("%c%c%c",work2,work3,work1);
	 else
	 printf("%c%c%c",work2,work1,work3);
	 }
	 else
	 printf("%c%c%c",work3,work2,work1);
	 
	}
	

	
}

20190318150:Problem1059:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
main()
//给年份year，判别该年份是否闰年。一个年份如果是4的倍数但不是100的倍数，或这个年份是400的倍数，则这个年份为闰年。
{
	int a;
	scanf("a");
	if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0)
	printf("L");
	else if (a%400==0)
	printf("L");
	else printf("N");
	
}

20190301049:Problem1059:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int year,y,z;
scanf("%d",&year);
y=year%4;
z=year%100;
if(y==0&&z!=0){
printf("%s\n","L");
}
else if(y==0&&z==0){
printf("%s\n","L");
}
else{
printf("%s\n","N");
}
return 0;
}

20190318169:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int m,d;
	int mth=1,day=1;
	int temp;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	if(m==1)
	{
		temp=(d-day)%7;

	}
	else if(m==2)
	{
		temp=(31+d-day)%7;
	}
		else if(m==3)
	{
		temp=(31+28+d-day)%7;
	}
			else if(m==4)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+d-day)%7;
	}
				else if(m==5)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+d-day)%7;
	}
					else if(m==6)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+d-day)%7;
	}
						else if(m==7)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+d-day)%7;
	}
							else if(m==8)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+31+d-day)%7;
	}
								else if(m==9)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+d-day)%7;
	}
								else if(m==10)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+d-day)%7;
	}
								else if(m==11)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+d-day)%7;
	}
								else if(m==12)
	{
		temp=(31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+d-day)%7;
	}




	switch (temp)
		{
		 case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		 case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		 case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		 case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		 case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		 case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		 case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
		 default:printf("No\n");
		 }

}

20190302001:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year,a;
    scanf("%d",&year);
    if(year%400==0)
        a=1;
    else
    {
        if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
            a=1;
        else
            a=0;
    }
    if(a==1)
    {
        printf("L");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("N");
    }

}

20190301038:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i) 
printf("%s",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

20190301036:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

20190318105:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,A,B,C;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	A=a;
	if(a>b)
	B=b;
	else
	{
		A=b;
		B=a;
	}
	if(c<B)
	C=c;
	else
	{
		if(c>A)
		{
		    C=B;
	    	B=A;
	    	A=c;	
		}
		else
		{
			C=B;
	    	B=c;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",C,B,A);
}

20190301038:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
int n;
while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
if(b[1]==0&&b[0]!=0)
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}
printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

20190302017:Problem1147:正确
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
int main() 
{
	double a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	    d=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(d==0||d>0)
	{
		if(d==0)
		{
			x1=x2=(-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);	
		}
	}
	else
	{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");		
    }
    }
	return 0;
}

20190318105:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x1,x2,k;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=b*b-a*c*4;
		if(delta<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else
		{
			k=sqrt(delta);
			x1=(-b+k)/(a*2);
			x2=(-b-k)/(a*2);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

20190318124:Problem1147:正确
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h" 
main()
{
	int a,b,c,p;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    p=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(p<0){
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        else if(p>=0){
	    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    char ch;
    ch=getchar();
    if(ch>='a'&&ch<='z'||ch>='A'&&ch<='Z')
    printf("NO\n");
    if(ch>='0'&&ch<='9')
    printf("YES\n");
}

#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    float x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c) != EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION");
        else
        {
            x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
	        x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
    return 0;
}

20190301036:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
int n;
while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
if(b[1]==0&&b[0]!=0)
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}
printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

20190318153:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,z;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
		switch(x)
	{
		case 1:
		z=y-1;
		break;
		case 2:
		z=30+y;
		break;
		case 3:
		z=58+y;
		break;
		case 4:
		z=89+y;
		break;
		case 5:
		z=119+y;
		break;
		case 6:
		z=150+y;
		break;
		case 7:
		z=180+y;
		break;
		case 8:
		z=211+y;
		break;
		case 9:
		z=242+y;
		break;
		case 10:
		z=272+y;
		break;
		case 11:
		z=303+y;
		break;
		case 12:
		z=333+y;
		break;
	}
	int a;
	a=z%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 6:
		printf("Monday\n");
		break;
		case 0:
		printf("Tuesday\n");
		break;
		case 1:
		printf("Wednesday\n");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("Thursday\n");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("Friday\n");
		break;
		case 4:
		printf("Saturday\n");
		break;
		case 5:
		printf("Sunday\n");
		break;
	}
}

#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,d,z;
     while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
    
    {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    
    z=sqrt(d);
    x1=(-b+z)/(2*a);
    x2=(-b-z)/(2*a);
    
    
    
    if(d>=0) printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
  else if(d<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    
    }

20190301016:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main(){
	char a,b,c;
	int q;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	a=toascii(a);b=toascii(b);c=toascii(c);
	if(a>b){
		q=a;a=b;b=q;
	}
	if(a>c){
		q=a;a=c;c=q;
	}
	if(b>c){
		q=b;b=c;c=q;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190318024:Problem1147:答案错误

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{

    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >= 0)
    {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }   
    else if (d < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
}    //else
        //printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

20190302015:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int o,p,q,r;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&o,&p,&q);
    
    if (o>p) {r=o;o=p;p=r;}
    if (o>q) {r=o;o=q;q=r;}
    if (p>q) {r=q;q=p;p=r;}
    printf("%c%c%c\n",o,p,q);
    
    return 0;
}

#include <ctype.h>
int main(void)
{
    scanf("");
    if(isalpha(getchar()))
        printf("NO\n");
    else
        printf("YES\n");
    return 0;

#include "stdio.h"
main()
//给年份year，判别该年份是否闰年。一个年份如果是4的倍数但不是100的倍数，或这个年份是400的倍数，则这个年份为闰年。
{
	int a;
	scanf("a");
	if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0||a%400==0)
	printf("L");
	
	else printf("N");
	
}

20190318024:Problem1147:答案错误

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    x1<x2;
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >= 0)
    {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }   
    else if (d < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
}    //else
        //printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

20190301037:Problem1069:编译错误
#include "stdio.h" 
main()
{
    int q;
    
    char m,n,p;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&m,&n,&p);
    if(m>=n)
    {
        
        q=n;
        n=m;
        m=q;
    }
 
    if(m>=p)
    {
        q=p;
        p=m;
        m=q;
    }
    if(n>=p)
    {
        q=p;
        p=n;
        n=q;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c\n",m,nq,p);
}m

20190318024:Problem1147:答案错误

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    x1>x2;
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >= 0)
    {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }   
    else if (d < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
}    //else
        //printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

	int a;
	scanf("a");

int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c %c %c\n",a,b,c);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

void main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    x1>x2;
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >= 0)
    {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }   
    else if (d < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION \n");
}    //else
        //printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

20190302011:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190301014:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double delta;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if (delta<0) {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        } else if (delta>=0) {
            x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
            x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
        }
    }
}

20190318049:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double e,d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0)
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
        	e=sqrt(d);
            x1=(-b+e)/(2*a);
	        x2=(-b-e)/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
    }
}

main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        d=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        if(d>=0){
            x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }
}

20190302053:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t1;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (t1<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		else 
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a; 
            x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/2*a;
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
		}
	}
}

20190318140:Problem1069:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,x,y,z;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=a;
	if(a>b)
	y=b;
	else
	{
		x=b;
		y=a;
	}
	if(c<y)
	z=c;
	else
	{
		if(c>x)
		{
		    z=y;
	    	y=x;
	    	x=c;	
		}
		else
		{
			z=y;
	    	y=c;
		}
	}
	printf("%c,%c,%c",z,y,x);
}

20190302034:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char*week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	if(a==0)
	{
		b=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[b]);
	}
	else if(a==1)
	{
		b=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a==2) 
	{
		b=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a>=3&&a<=7)
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*30+(a-c-1)*31+y;
		d=b%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else 
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*31+(a-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
 }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t1;
	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (t1<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		else 
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(t1))/(2*a); 
            x2=(-b-sqrt(t1))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
		}
	}
}

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	if(a==0)
	{
		b=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[b]);
	}
	else if(a==1)
	{
		b=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a==2) 
	{
		b=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a>=3&&a<=7)
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*30+(a-c-1)*31+y;
		d=b%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	t=a,a=b,b=t;
	if(b>c)
	t=b,b=c,c=t;
	if(a>c)
	t=a,a=c,c=t;
	if(a>b)
	t=a,a=b,b=t;
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 }

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,x,y,z;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=a;
	if(a>b)
	y=b;
	else
	{
		x=b;
		y=a;
	}
	if(c<y)
	z=c;
	else
	{
		if(c>x)
		{
		    z=y;
	    	y=x;
	    	x=c;	
		}
		else
		{
			z=y;
	    	y=c;
		}
	}
	printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
	return 0;
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double delta;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if (delta>=0) {
            x1=(-1*b+sqrt(delta))/2*a;
            x2=(-1*b-sqrt(delta))/2*a;
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
            //printf("NO SOLUTION\r\n");
        } else {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\r\n");
        }
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,d;
	double x1,x2;
    while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a1,&b1,&c1)!=EOF) //读多组数据
    {d=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;

    if(d>=0){
		x1=((-b1)+sqrt(d))/(2*a1);
		x2=((-b1)-sqrt(d))/(2*a1);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
			else{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	
}

		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;

		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;

20190318088:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z;
    double x1,x2,h;   
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)	
	{
	z=b*b-4*a*c; 
	if(z>=0)
	{
	  h=sqrt(z);
 	  x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	  x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
      printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
	else	
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n"); 	
    }
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) 
w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w)
{
case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c %c %c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a<b&&b<c)
		printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
	if(a<c&&c<b)
		printf("%c%c%c",a,c,b);
	if(b<a&&a<c)
		printf("%c%c%c",b,a,c);
	if(b<c&&c<a)
		printf("%c%c%c",b,c,a);
	if(c<a&&a<b)
		printf("%c%c%c",c,a,b);
	if(c<b&&b<a)
		printf("%c%c%c",c,b,a); 
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>

void main ()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
    x1>x2;
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d >= 0)
    {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
    }   
    else //if (d < 0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}    //else
        //printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) 
w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w)
{
case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;

20190302034:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char*week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	if(a==0)
	{
		b=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[b]);
	}
	else if(a==1)
	{
		b=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a==2) 
	{
		b=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a>=3&&a<=7)
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*30+(a-c-1)*31+y;
		d=b%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else 
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*31+(a-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
    }
 }

20190318116:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char x,y,z,h;
scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
if(x>y)
{
h=x,x=y,y=h;
}
if(x>z)
{
h=x,x=z,z=h;
}
if(y>z)
{
h=y,y=z,z=h;
}
printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{   int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	d=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(d>=0)
      {   
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int  a,b,c,d,e,f,m1,m2;
double x1,x2,x3,x4;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);

	
	
	
	
m1=b*b-4*a*c;
m2=e*e-4*d*f;

if(m1<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
else if(m1==0)
{
printf("x1=x2=%.3lf\n",(-b)/(2.0*a));
}
else
{
x1=(-b+sqrt(m1))/(2.0*a);
x2=(-b-sqrt(m1))/(2.0*a);
printf("x1=%.3lf\nx2=%.3lf\n",x1,x2);


if(m2<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
else if(m2==0)
{
printf("x3=x4=%.3lf\n",(-e)/(2.0*d));
}
else
{
x3=(-e+sqrt(m2))/(2.0*d);
x4=(-e-sqrt(m2))/(2.0*d);
printf("x1=%.3lf\nx2=%.3lf\n",x3,x4);}



}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
        	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
        	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
        	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
        	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
        	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
        	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
        	case(0):printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖");break;
        }

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c,d;
	double e,f;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		d=(b*b-4*a*c);
		if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else{
			d=sqrt(d);e=(-b+d)/2*a;f=(-b-d)/2*a;
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",e,f);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	if(a==0)
	{
		b=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[b]);
	}
	else if(a==1)
	{
		b=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a==2) 
	{
		b=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a>=3&&a<=7)
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*30+(a-c-1)*31+y;
		d=b%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);

20190318117:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
 	int b,c,d,s;
 	scanf("%d,%d",&b,&c);
 	switch(b)
 	{
 			case 1: d = c;
 			break;
 			case 2: d = c + 31 - 1;
 			break;
 			case 3: d = c + 60 - 1;
 			break;
 			case 4: d = c + 91 - 1;
 			break;
 			case 5: d = c + 121- 1;
 			break;
 			case 6: d = c + 152- 1;
 			break;
 			case 7: d = c + 182- 1;
 			break;
 			case 8: d = c + 213- 1;
 			break;
 			case 9: d = c + 244- 1;
 			break;
 			case 10:d = c + 274- 1;
 			break;
 			case 11:d = c + 305- 1;
 			break;
 			case 12:d = c + 335- 1;
 			break;
 		}
 	s = (2018+(2018/4)-2018/100 + 2018/400 + d)%7;
 	switch(s)
 	{
 		case 0: printf("Sunday\n");
         break;
 		case 1: printf("Monday\n");
 		break;
 		case 2: printf("Tuesday\n");
 		break;
 		case 3: printf("Wednesday\n");
 		break;
 		case 4: printf("Thursday\n");
 		break;
 		case 5: printf("Firday\n");
 		break;
 		case 6: printf("Saturday\n");
 		break;
 	}
 }

x1=(-b+sqrt(m1))/(2.0*a);
x2=(-b-sqrt(m1))/(2.0*a);
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}


if(m2<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION");
}
else if(m2==0)
{
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-e)/(2.0*d),(-e)/(2.0*d));
}
else
{
x3=(-e+sqrt(m2))/(2.0*d);
x4=(-e-sqrt(m2))/(2.0*d);
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x3,x4);}



}

          char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
          int x,y,sum=0;
          scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
          for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
          sum+=a[i];
}
          sum+=y; 
          sum%=7; 
          for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
          if(sum+1==i) 
          printf("%s",b[i]);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double delta;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if (delta>=0) {
            x1=(-1*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            x2=(-1*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
            //printf("NO SOLUTION\r\n");
        } else {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
    }
}

main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;

    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
        if(z!=0)
        {
	        switch(y)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	            case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
            	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
            	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
            	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;

            	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
            	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
            	case(0):printf("零");break; 
            }
        }
        else
        {
        	switch(y)
            {
	            case(1):printf("壹拾");break;

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a;
    char b;
    char c;
    char t;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {
        t=a;
        a=b;
        b=t;
    }
    if (a>c) {
        t=a;
        a=c;
        c=t;
    }
    if (b>c) {
        t=c;
        c=b;
        b=t;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}

main()
{

    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&m,&n,&p)!=EOF)
    {
		q=n*n-4*m*p;
	    x1=(-n+sqrt(q))/(2.0*m);
	    x2=(-n-sqrt(q))/(2.0*m);
		if(q<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		} 
		else
        {
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}

20190318150:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>

#include <math.h>

int main() {

    int a, b, c;

    double x1, x2, delta;
    while ((scanf("%d %d %d", &a, &b, &c)) != EOF) {

        delta = b * b - 4 * a * c;

        if (delta < 0) {

            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");

            continue;

        }

        x1 = (-b + sqrt(delta)) / (2 * a);

        x2 = (-b - sqrt(delta)) / (2 * a);

             printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n", x1, x2);}
	
	
}

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,p;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	    p=b*b-4*a*c;
	    if(p<0){
	    printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
        else if(p>=0){
	    x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(p))/(2*a);
	    printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    }

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,w,a;
	x>0&&x<13;
	y>0&&y<32;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	w=19+(19/4)+(20/4)-2*20+(26*(x+1))/10+y-1;
	a=(abs(w)%7+7)%7;
	switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
	    case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
	    case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
    	case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
    	case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
    	case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;
    	case 7:
		printf("Sunday");

20190301014:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a,b,c;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b>c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if ( a > c > b ) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,c,b);
    } else if ( b > a > c ) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
    } else if ( b > c > a ) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
    } else if ( c > a > b ) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a,b);
    } else if ( c > b > a ) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
    } else if (a==b==c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if (a==b>c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if (a>b==c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    } else if (a==b<c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a,b);
    } else if (a<b==c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
    } else if (b>a==c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
    } else if (b<a==c) {
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
    }   
    return 0;
}

void kx(int a)
{
if(a==0) printf("");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁");
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆");
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌");
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
main()
{
double i;
int k,m,n;
while(scanf("%lf",&i)!=EOF){
k=(int)i/100;
m=(int)i%100/10;
n=(int)i%100%10;
kx(K);
printf("佰");
kx(m);
if(m!=0){
printf("拾")；}
if（n!=0&&m==0){
printf("零")；}
kx(n);
printf("元整\n");
}

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	a>99&&a<1000;

	b=a/100;
	c=a/10%10;
	d=a%10;
	switch(b){
		case 1:	printf("壹佰");	break;
		case 2:	printf("贰佰");	break;
		case 3:	printf("叁佰");	break;

		case 7:	printf("柒佰");	break;
		case 8:	printf("捌佰");	break;

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f;
	double x1,x2,disc1;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=((-1)b+sqrt(disc1))/(2.0*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2.0*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    
	}
return 0
 }

20190318004:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	c=a-1;d=b-1;
	if(a==1)
	{e=d;}
	if(a==2)
	{e=31+d;}
	if(a==3)
	{e=31+28+d;}
	if(a==4)
	{e=31+28+31+d;}
	if(a==5)
	{e=31+28+61+d;}
	if(a==6)
	{59+61+31+d;}
	if(a==7)
	{e=59+61+61+d;}
	if(a==8)
	{e=59+61+61+31+d;}
	if(a==9)
	{e=59+61+61+62+d;}
	if(a==10)
	{e=120+123+30+d;}
	if(a==11)
	{e=120+123+61+d;}
	if(a==12)
	{e=120+123+91+d;}
	f=e%7;
	if(f==6)
	{printf("Monday\n");}
	if(f==5)
	{printf("Sunday\n");}
	if(f==4)
	{printf("Saturday\n");}
	if(f==3)
	{printf("Friday\n");}
	if(f==2)
	{printf("Thursday\n");}
	if(f==1)
	{printf("Wednesday\n");}
	if(f==0)
	{printf("Tuesday\n");}
	
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	char*week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	if(a==0)
	{
		b=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[b]);
	}
	else if(a==1)
	{
		b=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a==2) 
	{
		b=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(b+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(a>=3&&a<=7)
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*30+(a-c-1)*31+y;
		d=b%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else 
	{
		c=a/2;
		b=28+c*31+(a-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
    }

20190302042:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double p,q,f,g;
    double m,n,i;
    scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
    p=-b/(2.0*a);
    q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    {
        f=p+q;
        g=p-q;
    }
    if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
    else x1=g,x2=f;
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
    else
    {
        m=-b/(2*a);
        n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
    }
    return 0;
}

	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;

        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");break;

20190302042:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double p,q,f,g;
    double m,n,i;
    scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
    p=-b/(2.0*a);
    q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
    {
        f=p+q;
        g=p-q;
    }
    if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
    else x1=g,x2=f;
    if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x2,x1);
    else
    {
        m=-b/(2*a);
        n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
        printf("NO SOLUTION");
    }
    return 0;
}

		printf("%s",week[a]);
	}

	{
		a=(30+y)%7;

		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);

{
    char c;
    scanf("%c",&c);
    if(c>='0' && c<='9')
    printf("YES\n");
    else
    printf("NO\n");
}

main()

    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case (1):printf("壹佰");break;

	        case (3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case (4):printf("肆佰");break;

        {

20190318036:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b=(x/10)%10;
		c=x%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
		}
		if(b==0&&c==0) printf("元整\n");
		if(b==0&&c!=0) printf("零"); 
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
		}
		if(b!=0&&c==0) printf("元整\n"); 
	}
 }

#include <stdio.h>
main(){
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	if(a==1){
		c=(1+b)%7;
	}
	if(a==2){
		c=(1+b+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==3){
		c=(1+b+31+28)%7;
	}
	if(a==4){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==5){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30)%7;
	}
	if(a==6){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==7){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30)%7;
	}
	if(a==8){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==9){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==10){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30)%7;
	}
	if(a==11){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31)%7;
	}
	if(a==12){
		c=(1+b+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30)%7;
	}
	if(c==1){
		printf("Monday");
	}
	if(c==2){
		printf("Tuesday");
	}
	if(c==3){
		printf("Wednesday");
	}
	if(c==4){
		printf("Thursday");
	}
	if(c==5){
		printf("Friday");
	}
	if(c==6){
		printf("Saturday");
	}
	if(c==0){
		printf("Sunday");
	}
}

int main()
{

	a>99&&a<1000;

	b=a/100;
	c=a/10%10;
	d=a%10;
	switch(b){
		case 1:	printf("壹佰");	break;
		case 2:	printf("贰佰");	break;
		case 3:	printf("叁佰");	break;
		case 4:	printf("肆佰");	break;

		case 7:	printf("柒佰");	break;
		case 8:	printf("捌佰");	break;
		case 9:	printf("玖佰");	break;
	}
	if(c!=0){
	switch(c){
		case 1:	printf("壹拾");	break;
		case 2:	printf("贰拾");	break;
		case 3:	printf("叁拾");	break;
		case 4:	printf("肆拾");	break;
		case 5:	printf("伍拾");	break;
		case 6:	printf("陆拾");	break;
		case 7:	printf("柒拾");	break;
		case 8:	printf("捌拾");	break;
		case 9:	printf("玖拾");	break;}
	}
	else if(c==0&&d!=0){printf("零");}
	else if(c==0&&d==0){printf("");}
	switch(d){
		case 1:	printf("壹元整");break;
		case 2:	printf("贰元整");break;
		case 3:	printf("叁元整");break;
		case 4:	printf("肆元整");break;

20190318183:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char x,y,z;
	
	scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
	
	if(x>y){
		if(y>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,y,x);
		}else{
			if(x>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",y,z,x);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",y,x,z);
			}
		}
	}else{
		if(x>z){
			printf("%c%c%c",z,x,y);
		}else{
			if(y>z){
				printf("%c%c%c",x,z,y);
			}else{
				printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
			}
		}
	}
}

20190318183:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double x1,x2,q;
	
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			x2=(-sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;
		case 7:t=180+y;break;
		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
	}
}

20190302042:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    double a,b,c;
    double x1,x2;
    double p,q,f,g;
    double m,n,i;
    while(scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
    {
        p=-b/(2.0*a);
        q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
            f=p+q;
            g=p-q;
        }
        if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
        else x1=g,x2=f;
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
        else
        {
            m=-b/(2*a);
            n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
            printf("NO SOLUTION");
        }
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    int i,n,t=0;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(i=1;i<x;i++)
    {
        switch(i)
        {
            case 1:
            case 3:
            case 5:
            case 7:
            case 8:
            case 10:
            case 12:n=31;break;
            case 4:
            case 6:
            case 9:
            case 11:n=30;break;
            case 2:n=28;break;
            default:n=0;
        }
        t=t+n;
    }
    t=t+y;
    a=(t+1)%7;
    switch(a)
    {
        case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
        case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
        case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
        case 3:printf("Friday");break;
        case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
        case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
        case 6:printf("Monday");break;
    }
}

main()
{

	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:b=y-1;break;
		case 2:b=31+y-1;break;
		case 3:b=31+28+y-1;break;
		case 4:b=31+28+31+y-1;break;
		case 5:b=31+28+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 6:b=31+28+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 7:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 8:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 9:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y-1;break;
		case 10:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y-1;break;
		case 11:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y-1;break;
		case 12:b=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y-1;break; 
	}
	c=(b+a)%7;
	switch(c)
	{
		case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;

main()
{
	int x,y,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);//0<x<13,0<y<32
	int i,sum=0,j;
	int a[100]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	for(i=0;i<x-1;i++)
	{
	sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;
	j=sum%7;
	switch(w)
	{
	case 0:printf("Monday");break;
	case 1:printf("Tuseday");break; 
	case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 4:printf("Friday");break;

20190318116:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int a, b, c, d;
double x1, x2;
while (scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
{
d=b*b-4*a*c;
if(d<0)
{
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
else{
x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/2*a;
x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/2*a;
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
}
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
		{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
    if(z!=0)
	  {
	  case (0):printf("零");break;
	  case (1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case (2):printf("贰拾");break;
	  case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	  case(4):printf("肆拾");break;

	  case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	  case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	  case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	  default:printf("");}
    else(z==0);
	  {
	  case(0):printf("");break;
	  case(1):printf("壹拾");break;

	  default:printf("");}
}

	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;

	case(5):printf("伍");break;

main()
{

		{
	x=a/100;

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double x1,x2,p,q;
    while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
    {
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
            p=-b/(2.0*a);
            q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
            x1=p+q;
            x2=p-q;
            printf("%.3f~~~%.3f",x1,x2);
        }
        else
        {
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
    }
}

main()
{

{
		{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");

{
    if(z!=0)
	  {
	  case (0):printf("零");break;
	  case (1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case (2):printf("贰拾");break;

	  case(8):printf("捌拾");break;

	  default:printf("");}

	  {
	  case(0):printf("\n");break;
	  case(1):printf("壹拾");break;

main()
{

    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {
        t=a;
        a=b;
        b=t;
    } else if (a>c) {
        t=a;
        a=c;
        c=t;
    } else if (b>c) {
        t=b;
        b=c;
        c=t;
    }
    printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);

20190301001:Problem1069:编译错误
#incldue<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    char a,b,c,e;
    scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
    if (a>b) {e=a;a=b;b=e;}
    if (a>c) {e=a;a=c;c=e;}
    if (b>c) {e=c;c=b;b=e;}
    printf("%c %c %c",a,b,c);
    return 0;
}

20190302003:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
  char a,b,c;
  scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
  if(a>b){
     if(b>c){
        printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
     }else{
        if(a>c){
           printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
        }else{
           printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
        }
     }
  }else{
     if(c>b){
        printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
     }else{
        if(a>c){
           printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a,b);
        }else{
           printf("%c%c%c\n",a,c,b);
        }
     }
  }
  return 0;
}

20190302026:Problem1034:编译错误
//求一元二次方程的解
#inclued"stdio.h"
#inclued"math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d%d%d",a&,b&,c&)!=EOF)
    {
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
            x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x1=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.31f~~~%.31f\n",x1,x2);
        }
        else
        {
            printf("NO SOLUTTON\n");
        }
    }
}

main()
{

    {
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
            p=-b/(2.0*a);
            q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
            x1=p+q;
            x2=p-q;

20190302011:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,a;
    int i,n,t=0;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(i=1;i<x;i++)
    {
        switch(i)
        {
            case 1:
            case 3:
            case 5:
            case 7:
            case 8:
            case 10:
            case 12:n=31;break;
            case 4:
            case 6:
            case 9:
            case 11:n=30;break;
            case 2:n=28;break;
            default:n=0;
        }
        t+=n;
    }
    t=t+y;
    a=(t-1)%7;
    switch(a)
    {
        case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
        case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
        case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
        case 3:printf("Friday");break;
        case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
        case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
        case 6:printf("Monday");break;
    }
}

#include "stdio.h" 
main()
{
	int m,n,p,q;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&n);
	switch(m)
	{
	    
		case 1:
			p=n-1;
			break;
		case 2:
		
			p=n-1+31;
			break;
		case 3:
			p=n-1+31+28;
			break;
			
		case 4:
			p=n-1+31+28+31;
			break;
		case 5:
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30;
			break;
		case 6:
		
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 7:
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30;
			break;
		case 8:
		
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 9:
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31;
			break;
		case 10:
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30;
			break;
		case 11:
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31;
			break;
		case 12:
		
			p=n-1+31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+31;
			break;
	}
	q=p%7;
	switch(q)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Wednesday");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Thursday");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Friday");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Saturday");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Sunday");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Monday");
			break;
		case 0:
			printf("Tuesday");
			break;
	}
}

20190301052:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);//0<x<13,0<y<32
	int i,sum=0,j;
	int a[13]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	for(i=0;i<x-1;i++)
	{
	sum+=a[i];
	}
	j=sum+y;
	w=j%7;
	switch(w)
	{
	case 0:printf("Monday");break;
	case 1:printf("Tuseday");break; 
	case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 4:printf("Friday");break;
	case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
	case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
    }
}

#include<stdlib.h>
main()
{
int y=2019,i,c,m,d,w,sum;
const int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
sum=d-1;
for(i=0;i<m-1;i++)
{
sum+=days[i];
}
if(m>2)
{
if((0==y%4 && 0!=y%100) || 0==y%400)
{
sum+=1;
}
}
switch((sum-(7-w)%7)%7)
{
case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
case 1:printf("Monday");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
case 5:printf("Friday");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday");break;}
}

20190318119:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,s,d,f;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&s,&d);
	if(d<a)
	{
		f=a;a=s;s=f;
	}
	if(s<a)
	{
		f=a;a=d;d=f;
	}
	if(d<s)
	{
		f=d;d=s;s=f;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,s,d);
	
}

20190302027:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	double x1,x2; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		t=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(t>=0)
		{
			x1=(-1*b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			x2=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d > 0)
    {
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.2lf %.2lf\n",x1,x2);
    }
   else if (d < 0)
   printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
   else
   printf("x1 = x2 = %.2lf\n", -b / (2 * a));
}

if(m>2)

//求一元二次方程的解
#inclued"stdio.h"
#inclued"math.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d%d%d",a&,b&,c&)!=EOF)
    {
        if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
        {
            x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
            x1=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
            printf("%.31f~~~%.31f\n",x1,x2);
        }
        else
        {
            printf("NO SOLUTTON\n");
        }
    }
    
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int month,day,now;
	scanf("%d,%d",&month,&day);
	switch(month)
	{
		case 1:now=(day+1)%7;break;
		case 2:now=(day+4)%7;break;
		case 3:now=(day+4)%7;break;
		case 4:now=day%7;break;
		case 5:now=(day+2)%7;break;
		case 6:now=(day+5)%7;break;
		case 7:now=day%7;break;
		case 8:now=(day+3)%7;break;
		case 9:now=(day-1)%7;break;
		case 10:now=(day+1)%7;break;
		case 11:now=(day+4)%7;break;
		case 12:now=(day-1)%7;break;
		
	}

	switch(now){
	
	case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
}
	
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	e=scanf("%d",&a);
	while(e!=EOF)
	{
	b=a/100;
	c=(a%100)%10;
	d=a%10;
	switch (b)
	{case (1):printf("壹佰");
	 break;
	 case (2):printf("贰佰");
	 break;
	 case (3):printf("叁佰");
	 break; 
	 case (4):printf("肆佰");
	 break;
	 case (5):printf("伍佰");
	 break;
	 case (6):printf("陆佰");
	 break;
	 case (7):printf("柒佰");
	 break;
	 case (8):printf("捌佰");
	 break;
	 case (9):printf("玖佰");
	 break;
	}
	switch (c)
	{case (0):printf("零");
	break;
	case (1):printf("壹拾");
	break;
	case (2):printf("貳拾");
	break;
	case (3):printf("叁拾");
	break;
	case (4):printf("肆拾");
	break;
	case (5):printf("伍拾");
	break;
	case (6):printf("陆拾");
	break;
	case (7):printf("柒拾");
	break;
	case (8):printf("捌拾");
	break;
	case (9):printf("玖拾");
	break;
	} 
	switch (d)
	{case (0):printf("零");
	break;

	break;
	case (2):printf("贰");
	break;

20190318049:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1||x==10)
	    a=(y+1)%7;
    if(x==2||x==3||x==11)
	    a=(y+4)%7;
	if(x==4)
	    a=y%7;
	if(x==5)
        a=(2+y)%7;
	if(x==6)
        a=(5+y)%7;
    if(x==7)
        a=y%7;
    if(x==8)
        a=(3+y)%7;
    if(x==9||x==12)
        a=(6+y)%7;
    if(a==1)
        printf("Monday\n");
    if(a==2)
        printf("Tuesday\n");
    if(a==3)
        printf("Wednesday\n");
	if(a==4)  
	    printf("Thursday\n");
	if(a==5)
	    printf("Friday\n");
	if(a==6)
	    printf("Saturday\n");
	if(a==0)
	    printf("Sunday\n");                                   
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int y=2019,i,c,m,d,w,sum;
	const int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31,30,31};

	{
		scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
		sum=d-1;
		for(i=0;i<m-1;i++)
		{
			sum+=days[i];
		}
		if(m>2){
			if((0==y%4&&0!=y%100)||0==y%400)
			{
				sum+=1;
			}
		}
		sum+=1;
			}
			switch((sum-(7-w)%7)%7)
			{
				case 0:printf("Monday");break;
				case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
				case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
				case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
				case 4:printf("Friday");break;
				case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
				case 6:printf("Sunday");break;
				
			}

20190301001:Problem1114:正确

#include<stdio.h>

#include<math.h>

int main()

{

int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};

char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};

int x,y,sum=0; 

scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);

for(int i=1;i<x;i++)

{

sum+=a[i];

}

sum+=y; 

sum%=7; 

for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)

{

if(sum+1==i) 

printf("%s",b[i]);

}

return 0;

}

20190301055:Problem1147:答案错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    double x1,x2,a,b,c,delta ;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {   delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(delta<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else
        {
            delta=b*b-4*a*c;
            x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
         return 0;
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int year;
scanf("%d",&year);
if(year%400==0)
{
	printf("L\n");
}
else if(year%4==0&&year%100!=0)
{
	printf("L\n");
}
else 
{
	printf("N\n");
}
}

#include<math.h>

{

    sum+=y;

    sum%=7;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
		{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
    if(z!=0)
	  {
	  case (0):printf("零");break;
	  case (1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case (2):printf("贰拾");break;
	  case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	  case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	  case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	  case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	  case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	  case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	  case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	  default:printf("");}
    else (z==0)
	  {
	  case(0):printf("\n");break;
	  case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	  case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	  case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	  case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	  case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	  case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	  case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	  case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	  default:printf("");}
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
		{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	if(a%100==0)

	switch(a)	
	{ 
	    case(1):printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
	    case(2):printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
	    case(3):printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
	    case(4):printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
	    case(5):printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
	    case(6):printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case(7):printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case(8):printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
		case(9):printf("玖佰元整\n");break; }   
	else
	{
	switch(x)	
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");

	  {
	  case(0):printf("");break;
	  case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	  case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	  case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	  case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	  case(6):printf("陆拾");break;

	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;

	case(9):printf("玖");break;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{
		{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	if(a%100==0)

	{
	switch(x)	
	{ 
	    case(1):printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
	    case(2):printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
	    case(3):printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
	    case(4):printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
	    case(5):printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
	    case(6):printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case(7):printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case(8):printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
		case(9):printf("玖佰元整\n");break; }   }
	else
	{
	switch(x)	
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)

	  {
	  case(0):printf("零");break;
	  case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	  case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	  case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	  case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	  case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	  case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	  case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	  case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	  case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	  default:printf("");}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}

main()
{
    int x,y;
    int n=0;
    scanf("%d %d",x,y);
    if (x==0 && y<=7) {
        n=y;
    } else if (x==0 && y>7) {
        n=y%7;
    } else if (x>=1 && x<2) {
        n=(31+y)%7;
    } else if (x>=2 && x<3) {
        n=(31+28+y)%7;
    } else if (x>=3 && x<4) {
        n=(31+28+31+y)%7;
    } else if (x>=4 && x<5) {
        n=(31+28+31+30+y)%7;
    } else if(x>=5 && x<6) {
        n=(31+31+28+31+30+y)%7;

        n=(30+31+31+31+28+31+30+y)%7;

        n=(30+31+30+31+31+31+28+31+30+y)%7;

    sum1=0;sum2=d;sum=0;

	if(y%4==0&&y%100!=0||y%400==0)
	a[2]=29;
	else a[2]=28;
	for(i=1;i<=12;i++)

	a[i]=31;
	else if(i==4||i==6||i==9||i==11)
	a[i]=30;
    for(i=1;i<m-1;i++)

main()
{
	int x,y,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch (x) {
		case 1: x=0; break;
		case 2: x=31; break; 
		case 3: x=28+31; break;
		case 4: x=31+28+31; break;
		case 5: x=30+31+28+31; break;
		case 6: x=31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 7: x=30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 8: x=31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 9: x=31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 10: x=30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 11: x=31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 12: x=30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break; 
	}
	n=(x+y)%7;
	switch (n){
		case 0: printf("Monday\n"); break;
		case 1: printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
		case 2: printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
		case 3: printf("Thursday\n"); break;
		case 4: printf("Friday\n"); break;
		case 5: printf("Saturday\n"); break;

20190302037:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()   
{
	char m1,m2,m3,a,b,c;
	
	m1=getchar();
	m2=getchar();
	m3=getchar();
	if(m1>m2&&m1>m3)
	    a=m1;
	else  if(m2>m1&&m2>m3)
	    a=m2;
	else
	    a=m3;
	if(m1<m2&&m1<m3)
	    b=m1;
	else  if(m2<m1&&m2<m3)
	    b=m2;
	else
	    b=m3;
	c=m1+m2+m3-a-b;
	printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);    
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
	int y,x,sum,w;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;
	}
	sum=sum+y;
	w=(sum+1)%7;
	if(w==0)
	printf("Sunday");
	if(w==1)
	printf("Monday");
	if(w==2)
	printf("Tuesday");
	if(w==3)
	printf("Wednesday");
	if(w==4)
	printf("Thursday");
	if(w==5)
	printf("Friday");
	if(w==6)
	printf("Saturday");
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,w,a;
	x>0&&x<13;
	y>0&&y<32;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	w=19+(19/4)+(20/4)-2*20+(26*(x+1))/10+y-1;
	a=(abs(w)%7+7)%7;
	switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
	    case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
	    case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
    	case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
    	case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
    	case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;
    	case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		break;
	}
}

20190302036:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	int A=b*b-4*a*c;
	int B=e*e-4*d*f;
	double x,y;
	if(A<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(A==0){
		x=-b/2*a;
		y=-b/2*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y); 
	}else if(A>0){
		x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);
		y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);	
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);	
	}
	double p,q;
	if(B<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(B==0){
		x=-e/2*d;
		y=-e/2*d;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",p,q); 
	}else if(B>0){
		x=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		y=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",p,q);	
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
int main()
{
	int y=2019,i,c,m,d,w,sum;
	const int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31,30,31};
	{
		scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
		sum=d-1;
		for(i=0;i<m-1;i++)
		{
			sum+=days[i];
		}
		if(m>2){
			if((0==y%4&&0!=y%100)||0==y%400)
			{
				sum+=1;
			}
		}
		sum+=1;
			}
			switch((sum-(7-w)%7)%7)
			{
				case 0:printf("Monday");break;
				case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
				case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
				case 3:printf("Thursday");break;
				case 4:printf("Friday");break;
				case 5:printf("Saturday");break;
				case 6:printf("Sunday");break;}
                default:break;
			}
}
