int main()
{
	int y=2019,i,c,m,d,w,sum;
	const int days[]={31,28,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31,30,31};
	{
		scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
		sum=d-1;
		for(i=0;i<m-1;i++)
		{
			sum+=days[i];
		}
		if(m>2){
			if((0==y%4&&0!=y%100)||0==y%400)
			{
				sum+=1;
			}
		}
		sum+=1;
			}
			switch((sum-(7-w)%7)%7)
			{
				case 0:printf("Monday");break;
				case 1:printf("Tuesday");break;
				case 2:printf("Wednesday");break;
				case 3:printf("Thursday");break;

20190318078:Problem1114:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,MONTH;
	int z=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x%2==0&&x!=2&&x<8||x==9||x==10)//偶数
	{MONTH=30;} 
	else if(x%2==1&&x<8||x==10||x==12)//奇数月
	{MONTH=31;}
	if((x==1&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==2&&0<y&&y<29)||(x==3&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==4&&0<y&&y<31)||(x==5&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==6&&0<y&&y<31) 
	||(x==7&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==8&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==9&&0<y&&y<31)||(x==10&&0<y&&y<32)||(x==11&&0<y&&y<31)||(x==12&&0<y&&y<32))
{
	switch(x){
	case 3:z=-3;
	break;
	case 2:z=+3;
	break;
	case 5:z=-4;
	break;
	case 6:z=+1;
	break;
	case 7:z=-5;
	break;
	case 8:z=+2;
	break;
	case 9:z=-4;
	break;
	case 10:z=-4;
	break;
	case 11:z=+3;
	break;
	case 12:z=0;
	break; 
	}
		
	x=x-1;
	a=x*MONTH+y+z;
	a=a%7+1; 
	  switch(a){
		case 1:
		printf("Monday");
		break;
		case 2:
		printf("Tuesday");
		break;
		case 3:
		printf("Wednesday");
		break;
		case 4:
		printf("Thursday");
		break;
		case 5:
		printf("Friday");
		break;
		case 6:
		printf("Saturday");
		break;	
		case 7:
		printf("Sunday");
		break;
	 
}  
}
else
printf("error"); 
}

20190302036:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	int A=b*b-4*a*c;
	int B=e*e-4*d*f;
	double x,y;
	if(A<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(A==0){
		x=-b/2*a;
		y=-b/2*a;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y); 
	}else if(A>0){
		x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);
		y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);	
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);	
	}
	double p,q;
	if(B<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(B==0){
		p=-e/2*d;
		q=-e/2*d;
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",p,q); 
	}else if(B>0){
		p=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		q=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",p,q);	
	}
	
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
 int a,b,c,d;
 double s1,s2;
 while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
  {d=b*b-4*a*c;
  if(d<0)
   printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
  else
  {s1=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
   s2=((-1)*b-sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
   printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",s1,s2);}
}
return 0;
}

20190318078:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
	if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
	if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	return 0;
}

20190318128:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,a,b,c;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
    {
	    a=x/100;
	    b=(x%100)/10%10;
	    c=x%10;
	    switch(a)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");
			break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");
			break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");
			break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");
			break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");
			break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");
			break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");
			break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");
			break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");
			break;
        }
	    switch(b)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");
			break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");
			break;
        	case(3):printf("叁拾");
			break;
        	case(4):printf("肆拾");
			break;
        	case(5):printf("伍拾");
			break;
        	case(6):printf("陆拾");
			break;
        	case(7):printf("柒拾");
			break;
        	case(8):printf("捌拾");
			break;
        	case(9):printf("玖拾");
			break;
        	case(0):
			if(c!=0)
			printf("零");
			else
			break; 
        }
	    switch(c)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹");
			break;
        	case(2):printf("贰");
			break;
	        case(3):printf("叁");
			break;
	        case(4):printf("肆");
			break;
	        case(5):printf("伍");
			break;
        	case(6):printf("陆");
			break;
	        case(7):printf("柒");
			break;
	        case(8):printf("捌");
			break;
	        case(9):printf("玖");
			break;
        }
	    printf("元整\n");
    }
}

20190301049:Problem1158:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
int x,a,b,c;
char y[10][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
{
a=x/100;
b=(x%100)/10;
c=x%10;
if (b==0&&c==0)
printf("%s佰元整\n",y[a]);
else if (b==0&&c!=0)
printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",y[a],y[b],y[c]);
else if (b!=0&&c==0)
printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",y[a],y[b]);
else
printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",y[a],y[b],y[c]);
}
return 0;
}

20190301027:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
    double a,b,c,x1,x2,d,t;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    	if(a!=0)
        {
            t=(b*b-4*a*c);
            if(t>=0)
                {
                	d=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c);
                    x1=(-b+d)/(2*a);
                    x2=(-b-d)/(2*a);
                	if(x1<x2) 
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x2,x1); 
                    if(x1>=x2)
                        printf("%0.3f~~~%0.3f\n",x1,x2);
				}
            if(t<0)
                printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
}

20190301024:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	int m,d,i,date=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	for(i=1; i<m; i++){
		if(i==1 || i==3 || i==5 || i==7 ){
			date=date+31;
		}
		else if(i==8 || i==10 || i==12){
			date=date+31;
		}
		else if(i==2){
			date=date+28;
		}
		else{
			date=date+30;
		}
	}
	date = date + d;
	//printf("%d",date);
	switch(date%7){
		case 0: printf("Monday\n"); break;
		case 1: printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
		case 2: printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
		case 3: printf("Thursday\n"); break;
		case 4: printf("Friday\n"); break;
		case 5: printf("Saturday\n"); break;
		case 6: printf("Sunday\n"); break;
	}
	return 0;
 }

		q=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(q<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}else{
			x1=(sqrt(q)-b)/(2*a);

	{

20190302053:Problem1158:运行错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,a,b,c,b1;
	while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF)
	{
		a=x/100;
		b1=x-a*100;
		b=b1/b1*10;
		c=b1%10;
		switch(a)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		    case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		    case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		    case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		    case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		    case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	        case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
		}
		switch(b)
		{
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
		    case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
		    case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
		    case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
		    case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
		    case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	        case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
	    	case 10:printf("零");break;
		}
		switch(c)
		{
			case 1:printf("壹");break;
		    case 2:printf("贰");break;
		    case 3:printf("叁");break;
		    case 4:printf("肆");break;
		    case 5:printf("伍");break;
		    case 6:printf("陆");break;
	        case 7:printf("柒");break;
	    	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	    	case 9:printf("玖");break;
		}
		printf("元整\n",b);
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    char b[8[20]]={"aaa","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
    int a[13]= {0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
    int x,y;
    int c=0;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(int i=1; i<x; i=i+1){
        c+=a[i];
    }
    c+=y;
    c%=7;
    for(int i=1; i<=7; i=i+1){
        if(c+1==i)
            printf("%s",b[i]);
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	
	switch(x)
	{
		case 1:t=y-1;break;
		case 2:t=30+y;break;
		case 3:t=58+y;break;
		case 4:t=89+y;break;
		case 5:t=119+y;break;
		case 6:t=150+y;break;
		case 7:t=180+y;break;
		case 8:t=211+y;break;
		case 9:t=242+y;break;
		case 10:t=272+y;break;
		case 11:t=303+y;break;
		case 12:t=333+y;break;
	}
	int a;
	a=t%7;
	switch(a)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday\n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
	}
}

20190318078:Problem1114:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
    int a,b,c,d,e,f;
    scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
    c=a-1;d=b-1;
    if(a==1){e=d;
    }
    if(a==2){e=31+d;
    }
    if(a==3){e=31+28+d;
    }
    if(a==4){e=31+28+31+d;
    }
    if(a==5){e=31+28+61+d;
    }
    if(a==6){e=59+61+31+d;
    }
    if(a==7){e=59+61+61+d;
    }
    if(a==8){e=59+61+61+31+d; 
    }
    if(a==9){e=59+61+61+62+d;
    }
    if(a==10){e=120+123+30+d;
    }
    if(a==11){e=120+123+61+d;
    }
    if(a==12){e=120+123+91+d;
    }
    f=e%7;
    if(f==6)
    {printf("Monday\n");}
    if(f==5)
    {printf("Sunday\n");}
    if(f==4)
    {printf("Saturday\n");}
    if(f==3)
    {printf("Friday\n");}
    if(f==2)
    {printf("Thursday\n");}
    if(f==1)
    {printf("Wednesday\n");}
    if(f==0)
    {printf("Tuesday\n");}
}

20190318159:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h> 
main()
{
    int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
        delta=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(delta>=0)
        { 
        x1=(-b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
    else if(delta<0)
        {
        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
    } 
}

int main()   
{
	int a,b,c,d,x,y;
	char * week[7]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"};
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	b=x-1;
	if(b=-0)
	{
		a=(y+1)%7;
		printf("%s",week[a]);
	}
	else if(b==1)
	{
		a=(30+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	else if(b==2)
	{
		a=(58+y)%7;
		printf("%s",week[(a+2)%7]);
	}
	 else if(b>=3&&b<=7)
	{
		c=b/2;
		a=28+c*30+(b-c-1)*31+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}
	else{
		c=b/2
		a=28+c*31+(b-c-1)*30+y;
		d=a%7;
		printf("%s",week[(d+2)%7]);
	}        
}

20190302005:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    char b[8][20]={"aaa","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
    int a[13]= {0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
    int x,y;
    int c=0;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    for(int i=1; i<x; i=i+1){
        c+=a[i];
    }
    c+=y;
    c%=7;
    for(int i=1; i<=7; i=i+1){
        if(c+1==i)
            printf("%s",b[i]);
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302036:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	scanf("%d %d %d",&d,&e,&f);
	int A=b*b-4*a*c;
	int B=e*e-4*d*f;
	double x,y;
	if(A<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(A==0){
		x=-b/2*a;
		y=-b/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y); 
	}else if(A>0){
		x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);
		y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);	
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);	
	}
	double p,q;
	if(B<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(B==0){
		p=-e/2*d;
		q=-e/2*d;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",p,q); 
	}else if(B>0){
		p=(-e+sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		q=(-e-sqrt(e*e-4*d*f)/2*d);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",p,q);
	}
	
	return 0;
}

main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d",&year);

    printf("L");
    else

20190301014:Problem1158:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
        	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
        	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
        	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
        	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
        	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
        	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
        	case(0):printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖");break;
        }
    }
    if (y>=0 && z>0) {
        printf("%d%d%d元整\n",x,y,z);
    } else if (y>0 && z==0) {
        printf("%d%d元整\n",x,y);
    } else if (y==0 && z==0) {
        printf("%d元整\n",x);
    }
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main ()
{ int a,b,c;
  double X1,X2,M;
  while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
  M=b*b-4*a*c;
  X1=(-b+sqrt(M))/(2*a);
  X2=(-b-sqrt(M))/(2*a);
  if(M>=0){
  	printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf",X1,X2);
  }
  else{
  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
  }
  
}

20190318119:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
 	int  amonth, bday;
	scanf("%d,%d", &amonth, &bday); 	
  	int week = 19+ 19 / 4 + 20 / 4 - 20 * 2 + 26 * (amonth + 1) / 10 + bday - 1;
  	week %= 7;
  	switch (week)
  {
  		case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
  		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  		case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
  		case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
  		case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
  		case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
    }
}

main()
{
    int x,y,z,m[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31},i;
    scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
    z=y+1;
    for(i=0;i<x;i++){
    	z=(z+m[i]);
	}
    z=z%7;	
	switch(z)
	{ case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
	  case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;

	  case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    scanf("%d %d %d",&x,&y,&z);
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
        	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
        	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
        	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
        	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
        	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
        	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
        	case(0):printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖");break;
	        case(0):printf("零");break; 
        }
    }
    if (y>=0 && z>0) {
        printf("%d%d%d元整\n",x,y,z);
    } else if (y>0 && z==0) {
        printf("%d%d元整\n",x,y);
    } else if (y==0 && z==0) {
        printf("%d元整\n",x);
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	char d,e,f;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&d,&e,&f);
    //scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
    a=d;
    b=e;
    c=f;
	if(a<b)
	{
		t=b;
		b=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(a<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(b<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=b;
		b=t;
	} 
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
}

20190318087:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z;
    double x1,x2,h;   
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)	
	{
	z=b*b-4*a*c; 
	if(z>=0)
	{
	  h=sqrt(z);
 	  x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	  x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
      printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
	else	
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n"); 	
    }
}

20190318087:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) 
w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w)
{
case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
}
}

20190302036:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
	int A=b*b-4*a*c;
	double x,y;
	if(A<0){
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}else if(A==0){
		x=-b/2*a;
		y=-b/2*a;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y); 
	}else if(A>0){
		x=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);
		y=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/2*a);	
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x,y);	
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301055:Problem1147:编译错误
#include "stdio.h"
#include "math.h"
main()
{
    double x1,x2,a,b,c,delta ;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
    {   
        if(b*b-4*a*c<0)
        printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        else{
            delta=b*b-4*a*c;
            x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        }
        
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	switch(a){
		case 1:c=b%7;break;
		case 2:c=(b+31)%7;break;
		case 3:c=(b+59)%7;break;
		case 4:c=(b+90)%7;break;
		case 5:c=(b+120)%7;break;
		case 6:c=(b+151)%7;break;
		case 7:c=(b+181)%7;break;
		case 8:c=(b+212)%7;break;
	    case 9:c=(b+243)%7;break;
	    case 10:c=(b+273)%7;break;
	    case 11:c=(b+304)%7;break;
	    case 12:c=(b+334)%7;break;
	}
	if(c==0){
	printf("Monday");
	}
	if(c==1){
	printf("Tuesday");
	}
	if(c==2){
	printf("Wednesday");
	}
	if(c==3){
	printf("Thursday");
	}
	if(c==4){
	printf("Friday");
	}
	if(c==5){
	printf("Saturday");
	}
	if(c==6){
	printf("Sunday");
	}
}

#include"math.h"
#include"string.h"
main()
{
 	char *s[]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","拾","零"};
 	int a,b,c,d;
	while(scanf("%d",&d)!=EOF){
		a=d/100;
		b=(d-a*100)/10;
		c=d%10;
		if(c==0&&b==0)
			printf("%s佰元整\n",s[a-1]);
		if(c==0&&b!=0)
			printf("%s佰%s元整\n",s[a-1],s[b-1]);
		if(c!=0&&b!=0)
			printf("%S佰%S拾%S元整\n",s[a-1],s[b-1],s[c-1]);
	}		
}

    {

20190318119:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int q,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&q,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
	d=b*b-4*q*c;
		if(d>=0)
	{
		x1 = ((-b)+sqrt(d))/(2.0*q);
		x2 = ((-b)-sqrt(d))/(2.0*q);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x1,x2);
	}	
	if(d<0)
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

20190318073:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;

scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}

printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);

return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,t;
	char d,e,f;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&d,&e,&f);
    //scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
    a=d;
    b=e;
    c=f;
	if(a<b)
	{
		t=b;
		b=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(a<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=a;
		a=t;
	}
	if(b<c)
	{
		t=c;
		c=b;
		b=t;
	} 
	printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
}

20190318085:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include"math.h"
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,z;
    double x1,x2,h;   
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)	
	{
	z=b*b-4*a*c; 
	if(z>=0)
	{
	  h=sqrt(z);
 	  x1=(-b+h)/(2*a);
 	  x2=(-b-h)/(2*a);
      printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
	else	
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n"); 	
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main ()
{ int a,b,c;
  double X1,X2,M;
  while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
  M=b*b-4*a*c;
  X1=(-b+sqrt(M))/(2*a);
  X2=(-b-sqrt(M))/(2*a);
  if(M>=0){
  	printf("%4.3lf~~~%4.3lf\n",X1,X2);
  }
  else{
  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
  }
  
}

20190318085:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int y, m, d, c, w;
scanf ("%d,%d",&m,&d);
y=2019;
if (m ==1 || m == 2) { 
y--;
m += 12;
}
c = y / 100;
y = y - c * 100;
w = (c / 4) - 2 * c + (y + y / 4) + (13 * (m + 1) / 5) + d - 1;
while (w < 0) 
w += 7;
w %= 7;
switch(w)
{
case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
case 0:printf("Sunday\n");break;
}
}

void main()
{
int year,leap_year;
scanf("%d",&year);
if(year%400==0)
{
leap_year=1;
printf("%d is 闰年",year);
}
else if(year%100==0)
{
   leap_year=0;
printf("%d is not 闰年",year);
}
else if(year%4==0)
{
leap_year=1;
printf("%d is 闰年",year);
} 
else 
{
leap_year=0;
printf("%d is not 闰年",year);
}

}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x,y;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {
	    d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0) 
		{printf("NO SOLUTION\n");} 
	if (d>=0)
		{x=(-b+sqrt(d))/(a*2);
		y=(-b-sqrt(d))/(a*2);
		printf("%.3f~~~%.3f\n",x,y);} 
		//1.000~~~1.000
	
 }return 0; 
 }

20190318034:Problem1059:答案错误


#include <stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
    int year, rem_4, rem_100, rem_400;

    printf("Enter the year to be tested: ");
    scanf("%i", &year);

    rem_4 = year % 4;
    rem_100 = year % 100;
    rem_400 = year % 400;

    if((rem_4 == 0 && rem_100 != 0) || rem_400 == 0)
    {
        printf("It's a leap year.\n");
    }
    else
    {
        printf("Nope, it's not a leap year.\n");
    }

    return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int x,y,z,m;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&x,&y,&z)!=EOF)
    {m=y*y-4*x*z;
       if(m>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*y+sqrt(m))/(2.0*x);
       x2=((-1)*y-sqrt(m))/(2.0*x);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302014:Problem1069:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	a=(int)a;
	b=(int)b;
	c=(int)c;
	if (a>b&&b>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)c,(char)b,(char)a);
	}
	if (a>c&&c>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)b,(char)c,(char)a);
	}
	if (b>a&&a>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)c,(char)a,(char)b);
	}
	if (c>a&&a>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)b,(char)a,(char)c);
	}
	if (c>b&&b>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)a,(char)b,(char)c);
	}
	if (b>c&&c>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",(char)a,(char)c,(char)b);
	}	
 }

#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
int a[12]={31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[7][20]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x(0<x<13),y(0<y<32),sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)
printf("%s\n",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
int a[12]={31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[7][20]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)
printf("%s\n",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

20190318039:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,y=0;
	double x,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) 
	{
	    x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		printf("%d %d",x1,x2);
		if((y=a*x1*x1+b*x1+c)!=1&&(y=a*x2*x2+b*x2+c)!=1)
		{
			printf("%0.3lf ~~~ %0.3laf",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		return 1; 
	}
 }

20190302052:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
    int m,x,y,z;
    while(scanf("%d",&m)!=EOF)
    {
	z=m/100;
    y=m/10%10;
    x=m%100%10;
    if(y==0&&x==0)
    {
    	switch(z){ 
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
	  	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	  	case 3:printf("叁");break;	
	  	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	  	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	  	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	  	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	  	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	  	case 9:printf("玖");break;  
		}
	printf("佰"); 
	printf("元整\n");
	}
	else{ 
	
    switch(z){ 
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
	  	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	  	case 3:printf("叁");break;	
	  	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	  	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	  	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	  	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	  	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	  	case 9:printf("玖");break;  
	  	}printf("佰");  
    switch(y){ 
		case 0:printf("零");break;
		case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	  	case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
	  	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;	
	  	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
	  	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
	  	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
	  	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
	  	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
	  	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;  
	}
	switch(x){ 
		case 0:break;
		case 1:printf("壹");break;
	  	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	  	case 3:printf("叁");break;	
	  	case 4:printf("肆");break;
	  	case 5:printf("伍");break;
	  	case 6:printf("陆");break;
	  	case 7:printf("柒");break;
	  	case 8:printf("捌");break;
	  	case 9:printf("玖");break;  
	}
	printf("元整\n");
	} }
	return 0; 
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
int a[12]={31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[7][20]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)
printf("%s\n",b[i]);
}
return 0;

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int x,y,k1,k2,k3,k4,k5,k6,k7,k8,k9,k10,k11,k12;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1){
		k1=(y-1)%7;
	switch(k1){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==2){
		k2=(30+y)%7;
	switch(k2){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==3){
		k3=(58+y)%7;

		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;

int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,i,j,k,l,m,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
	if(a==1){
		c=(b-1)%7;
	switch(c){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(a==2){
		d=(31+b-1)%7;
	switch(d){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==3){
		e=(59+b-1)%7;
	switch(e){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==4){
		f=(90+b-1)%7;
	switch(f){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==5){
		g=(120+b-1)%7;
	switch(g){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}

	if(x==6){

		case 3:printf("Friday");break;

		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
    if(x==7){
    	i=(181+b-1)%7;
	switch(i){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==8){
		j=(212+b-1)%7;
	switch(j){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday");break;
		case 0:printf("Tuesday");break;
	}
	}
	if(x==9){

	switch(k){
		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday");break;

20190318142:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,t; 
	scanf("%c %c %c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a<b)
	{t=a,a=b,b=t;}
	if(a<c)
	{t=a,a=c,c=t;}
	if(b<c)
	{t=b,b=c,c=t;}
	printf("%c %c %C",c,b,a);
	return 0;
 }

20190302047:Problem1114:编译错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
int a[12]={31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[7][20]={"Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)
printf("%s\n",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)
printf("%s\n",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

20190318112:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,n;
	double x1,x2;
	double delta;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
    	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
    	if(delta>=0){
    		x1=(-1.0*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
    		x2=(-1.0*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
    		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}	else printf("NO SOLUTINO\n");
	
	}		
    return 0;
}

20190302037:Problem1158:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}

20190301019:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
char a[11][20]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
int n;
while(scanf("%d",&n)!=EOF)
{
int t=0,b[111]={0},k=0;
t=n;
while(t!=0)//个位上的书提取出来 
{
b[k++]=t%10;
t/=10;
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//百位 
{
if(b[2]==i)
printf("%s佰",a[i]);
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//十位 
{
if(b[1]==i)
{
if(b[1]!=0)
printf("%s拾",a[i]);
if(b[1]==0&&b[0]!=0)
printf("零");
}
}
for(int i=0;i<10;i++)//个位 
{
if(b[0]==i)
{
if(b[0]!=0)
printf("%s元整",a[i]);
else
printf("元整");
}
}
printf("\n");
}
return 0;
}

20190318034:Problem1059:正确
#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	if(a%400==0)
	printf("L\n");
	else if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0)
	printf("L\n");
	else printf("N\n");
}

  if(b>c){d=b,b=c,c=d;}

20190318034:Problem1114:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<time.h>
#include<string.h> 
main()
{
int a,b;
scanf("%d,%d",&a,&b);
char*arr[]={"Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"};
struct tm info;
//memset(&info,0,sizeof(info));
info.tm_year=119;
info.tm_mon=a-1;
info.tm_mday=b;
mktime(&info);
printf("%s",arr[info.tm_wday]);
}

int main()
{
    char c;
    
    
    c=getchar();
    if(c>=48&&c<=57)
    {printf("YES\n");}
    else
    {printf("NO\n");}
    return 0;
}

20190318034:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
    int a,b,c,d;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d<0){printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    else{
         x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
         x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(d))/(2.0*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);}
    
    }
    return 0;
}

20190302013:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double disc;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}	
		else{
			x1=((-1*b)+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			x2=((-1*b)-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,i,j,k,l,m,n;

20190318153:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF){
		x=a/100;
		y=a/10%10;
		z=a%10;
		switch(x){
			case 1:
				printf("壹佰");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰佰");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁佰");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆佰");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍佰");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆佰");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒佰");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌佰");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖佰");
				break;	
				
		}
		switch(y){
			case 1:
				printf("壹拾");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰拾");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁拾");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆拾");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍拾");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆拾");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒拾");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌拾");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖拾");
				break;
			case 0:
			if(z==0){
				printf("");
			}else
			printf("零");
				break;
				
		}

		switch(z){
			case 1:
				printf("壹");
				break;
			case 2:
				printf("贰");
				break;
			case 3:
				printf("叁");
				break;
			case 4:
				printf("肆");
				break;
			case 5:
				printf("伍");
				break;
			case 6:
				printf("陆");
				break;
			case 7:
				printf("柒");
				break;
			case 8:
				printf("捌");
				break;
			case 9:
				printf("玖");
				break;
			case 0:
				printf("");
				break;	
				
		}printf("元整\n");
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{

		c=(b-1)%7;

		case 1:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday");break;

20190302013:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c;
	double disc;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
		disc=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}	
		else{
			x1=((-1*b)+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			x2=((-1*b)-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	}
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int m,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	int w=2019+2019/4+20/4-2*20+26*(m+1)/10+d-1;
    while (w<0)
     w+=7;
    w%=7;
	switch (w)
	{
		case 1:
			printf("Monday\n");
			break;
		case 2:
			printf("Tuesday\n");
			break;
		case 3:
			printf("Wednesday\n");
			break;
		case 4:
			printf("Thursday\n");
			break;
		case 5:
			printf("Friday\n");
			break;
		case 6:
			printf("Saturday \n");
			break;
		case 7:
			printf("Sunday\n");
			break;
	}
 }

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	char * money[10]={"壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖","零"};
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;
		c=a%100;
		d=c/10;
		e=c%10;
		if(c==0) 
		   printf("%s佰元整\n",&money[b]);
		else   if(d==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",&money[b],&money[d],&money[e]);
		else   if(e==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",&money[b],&money[d]);
		else    
		   printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",&money[b],&money[d],&money[e]);      
	 } 
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;

	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;
		c=a%100;
		d=c/10;
		e=c%10;
		if(c==0) 
		   printf("%s佰元整\n",&money[b]);
		else   if(d==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",&money[b],&money[d],&money[e]);
		else   if(e==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",&money[b],&money[d]);
		else    
		   printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",&money[b],&money[d],&money[e]);      
	 }
	 return 0;

20190302030:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a;
	scanf("%d",&a);
	if(a%400==0){
		printf("L");
	}
	else{
		if(a%4==0&&a%100!=0){
		printf("L");
	}
	else{
		printf("N");
	}
}
	return 0;
}

20190318039:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,delta;
	double x,x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) 
	{
		delta=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(delta>=0){
		x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
		printf("%0.3lf~~~%0.3lf",x1,x2);
		}
	    
		else
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
		
		return 0; 
	}
 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,n;
	double x1,x2;
	double delta;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
    	delta=b*b-4*a*c;
    	if(delta>=0){
    		x1=(-1*b+sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
    		x2=(-1*b-sqrt(delta))/(2*a);
    		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}	else printf("NO SOLUTINO\n");
	
	}		
    return 0;
}

20190318073:Problem1147:答案错误

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main ()
{
    double a,b,c,d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
    d=pow(b,2)-4*a*c;
    if (d>=0)
    {
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a),
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        if (x1>=x2)
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        else
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
    }
    else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main ()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
    d=pow(b,2)-4*a*c;
    if (d>=0)
    {
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a),
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        if (x1>=x2)
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        else
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
    }
    else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
}

 		printf("True");

20190301043:Problem1034:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <ctype.h>
int main() 
{
 	char a;
 	a=getchar();
 	if(isdigit(a)){
 		printf("YES");
	}
	else{
		printf("NO");
	}
	getchar();
	return 0;		
}

20190318073:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main ()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double d,x1,x2;
    scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if (d>=0)
    {
        x1=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a),
        x2=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        if (x1>=x2)
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
        else
            printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x2,x1);
    }
    else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i]; 
}
sum+=y; 
sum%=7; 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i) 
printf("%s",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

        y=y;
    if (x==2)
        y=31+y;
    if (x==3)
        y=31+28+y;
    if (x==4) 
        y=31+28+31+y;

        y=31+28+31+30+y;

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e;
	char * money[10]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
	{
		b=a/100;
		c=a%100;
		d=c/10;
		e=c%10;
		if(c==0) 
		   printf("%s佰元整\n",money[b]);\
		else   if(d==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);
		else   if(e==0) 
		   printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[b],money[d]);
		else    
		   printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);      
	 }
	 return 0; 
}

int main()
{
 int  month, day;
 scanf("%d %d",&month, &day);
 {
  int week = 19 + 19 / 4 + 20 / 4 - 2 * 20 + 26 * (month + 1) / 10 + day - 1;
  while (week < 0)
   week += 7;
  week %= 7;
  switch (week)
  {
  case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
  case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  case 4:printf("Thursday\n");  break;
  case 5:printf("Friday\n");  break;

  case 0:printf("Sunday\n");  break;
  }
 }

20190302019:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char x,y,z,m;
scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
if (x>y) {m=x;x=y;y=m;}
if (x>z) {m=x;x=z;z=m;}
if (y>z) {m=z;z=y;y=m;}
printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

20190318075:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
{if(a>=100&&a<=999)
	{
	x=a/100;
	y=(a%100)/10;
	z=a%10;
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(y)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:{
	if(y==0&&z==0)
	{ printf("");
	}
	else{printf("零");
	}
	} 
}
	switch(z)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}
}

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int num;
	int a,b,c;
		while(getchar()!='n')
	{
	scanf("%d",&num);
	c=num%10;
	b=(num/10)%10;
	a=(num/100)%10;

	if(b==0&&c==0)
	{	switch(a) {
		case 0:printf("");break;
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
			default:printf("错误\n");
	}
	}
	else{
		switch(a) {
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
			switch(b) {
			case 0:printf("零");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
			switch(c) {
			case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;

			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
		}
	}

	return 0;

20190302001:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
int a,b,c;
double x1,x2,d;
scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
do 
{
    d=b*b-4*a*c;
    if(d>=0) 
    {
        x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
        printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2); 
    }
    else if(d<0)  
    {
    	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
    }
}
while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
}

20190302001:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=y-1;
	if(x==1||x==2) b=(x-1)*31+a;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+a;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+a;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+a;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+a;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+a;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+a;
	if(x==12) b=31*7+30*3+28+a;
    for(b=b+2;b>7;b=b-7) 
	b=b;
    if(b==1) printf("Monday");
    if(b==2) printf("Tuesday");
    if(b==3) printf("Wednesday");
    if(b==4) printf("Thursday");
    if(b==5) printf("Friday");
    if(b==6) printf("Saturday");
    if(b==7) printf("Sunday");
}

20190302047:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
	int a,b,c,x;
	scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c);
	a=x/100;
	b=x/10%10;
	c=x%10;
	switch(a){
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(b){
		case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
	}
	switch(c){
		case 1:printf("零壹");break;
		case 2:printf("零贰");break;
		case 3:printf("零叁");break;
		case 4:printf("零肆");break;
		case 5:printf("零伍");break;
		case 6:printf("零陆");break;
		case 7:printf("零柒");break;
		case 8:printf("零捌");break;
		case 9:printf("零玖");break;
	}
	printf("元整\n");
}

20190318126:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
int x,y,sum=0;//上面两个数组的a[0],b[0]都是无关量；这是为了让月数和周数与下标对应； 
scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
{
sum+=a[i];//求这几个月的整月天数； 
}
sum+=y;//再加上零头； 
sum%=7;//总天数对7求余，余数就当天的星期数； 
for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
{
if(sum+1==i)//因为1月1号是星期二，往后推一天； 
printf("%s",b[i]);
}
return 0;
}

20190301200:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int num;
	int a,b,c;
		while(scanf("%d",&num)!=EOF)
	{
	c=num%10;
	b=(num/10)%10;
	a=(num/100)%10;

	if(b==0&&c==0)
	{	switch(a) {
		case 0:printf("");break;
		case 1:printf("壹佰元整\n");break;
		case 2:printf("贰佰元整\n");break;
		case 3:printf("叁佰元整\n");break;
		case 4:printf("肆佰元整\n");break;
		case 5:printf("伍佰元整\n");break;
		case 6:printf("陆佰元整\n");break;
		case 7:printf("柒佰元整\n");break;
		case 8:printf("捌佰元整\n");break;
		case 9:printf("玖佰元整\n");break;
			default:printf("错误\n");
	}
	}
	else{
		switch(a) {
			case 0:printf("");break;
			case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
			case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
			case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
			case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
			case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
			case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
			case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
			case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
			case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
			switch(b) {
			case 0:printf("零");break;
			case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
			case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
			case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
			case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
			case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
			case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
			case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
			case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
			case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
			switch(c) {
			case 0:printf("元整\n");break;
			case 1:printf("壹元整\n");break;
			case 2:printf("贰元整\n");break;
			case 3:printf("叁元整\n");break;
			case 4:printf("肆元整\n");break;
			case 5:printf("伍元整\n");break;
			case 6:printf("陆元整\n");break;
			case 7:printf("柒元整\n");break;
			case 8:printf("捌元整\n");break;
			case 9:printf("玖元整\n");break;
				default:printf("错误\n");
		}
		}
	}

	return 0;
	
}

20190302004:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
}

20190302030:Problem1069:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",c,b,a);
	}
	if(a>c>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",b,c,a);
	}
	if(b>c>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",a,c,b);
	}
	if(b>a>c){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",c,a<b);
	}
	if(c>b>a){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	if(c>a>b){
		printf("%c%c%c\n",b,a,c);
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301040:Problem1034:正确
/*输入一个字符，判断是否阿拉伯数字。
若是则输出：YES
否则输出:NO*/
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char c;
	c=getchar();
	if(c>=48&&c<=57)
	printf("YES\n");
	else
	printf("NO\n");
}

20190301040:Problem1059:正确
/*给年份year，判别该年份是否闰年。一个年份如果是4的倍数但不是100的倍数，或这个年份是400的倍数，则这个年份为闰年。
输入一个年份,根据是否闰年输出，是输出"L",否输出"N"*/
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int year;
    scanf("%d", &year);
    if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0)
	printf("L");
    else
	printf("N");
}

20190301043:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main() 
{
 	char a,b,c,t;
 	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
 	if(a>b){
 		t=a;a=b;b=t;
	}
	if(a>c){
	    t=a;a=c;c=t;
	}
	if(b>c){
		t=c;c=b;b=t;
	}		
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190318073:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int m,d,sum,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&m,&d);
	switch(m)
	{
		case 1:sum=0;break;
		case 2:sum=31;break;
		case 3:sum=59;break;
		case 4:sum=90;break;
		case 5:sum=120;break;
		case 6:sum=151;break;
		case 7:sum=181;break;
		case 8:sum=212;break;
		case 9:sum=243;break;
		case 10:sum=273;break;
		case 11:sum=304;break;
		case 12:sum=334;break;	
	}
	sum=sum+d;
	y=(sum-1)%7;
	switch(y)
	{
		case 0:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
		case 1:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
		case 2:printf("Thursday\n");break;
		case 3:printf("Friday\n");break;
		case 4:printf("Saturday \n");break;
		case 5:printf("Sunday\n");break;
		case 6:printf("Monday\n");break;
		
	}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
 char x,y,z,n;
 scanf("%c %c %c",&x,&y,&z);
 if(x>y)
 {
  n=x;
  x=y;
  y=n;
 }
 if(x>z)
 {
  n=x;
  x=z;
  z=n;
     }
    if(y>z)
     {
  n=z;
  z=y;
  y=n;
     }
     printf("%c %c %c",x,y,z);
     return 0;
}

20190301002:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
 char x,y,z,n;
 scanf("%c%c%c",&x,&y,&z);
 if(x>y)
 {
  n=x;
  x=y;
  y=n;
 }
 if(x>z)
 {
  n=x;
  x=z;
  z=n;
     }
    if(y>z)
     {
  n=z;
  z=y;
  y=n;
     }
     printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
     return 0;
}

20190301040:Problem1069:正确
/*输入三个字母，按字母表顺序输出这三个字母。*/
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,x;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	{
		x=a;
		a=b;
		b=x;
	}
	if(a>c)
	{
		
		x=a;
		a=c;
		c=x;
	}
	if(b>c)
	{
		
		x=c;
		c=b;
		b=x;
	}
	printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
}

20190302030:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	char a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if (a>b) {d=a;a=b;b=d;}
	if (a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}
	if (b>c) {d=c;c=b;b=d;}
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
}

20190302013:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int m[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
	int x,y;
	int i,day=0,k,z,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(i=1;i<x;i++)
	{
		day=day+m[i];
	}
	k=y+day-1;
	z=k%7;
	n=z+2;
	switch(n){
		case 1:printf("Monday");break;
		case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
		case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
		case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
		case 5:printf("Friday");break;
		case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
		case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

#include<math.h>
main()
{

	double x1,x2;
	while (scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		delta=a*a-4*b*c;
		if(delta>=0)
		{
			x1=((-a)+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*b);
			x2=((-a)+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*b);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
	    else if (delta<0)
	  {
	  	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	  }
    }

20190318083:Problem1034:输出超限
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
  int a,b,c;
  double DATA;
  double X1,X2;
  while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
  {
  	DATA=b*b-4*a*c;
  	if (DATA<0)
  	{
  	  printf("NO SOLUTION\n");	
	}
	else
	{
		X1=((-1*b)+sqrt(DATA))/(2*a);
		X2=((-1*b)-sqrt(DATA))/(2*a);
		printf("%3.1lf~~~%3.1lf\n",X1,X2);
	}
  }
  
}

20190318143:Problem1158:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	    g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
	    while(y<3){
		    switch (b){
			    case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			    case 0: printf("零"); break;
	     	}
	    	y++;
	    	switch(y){
			    case 1: printf("佰");break;
		     	case 2: printf("拾");break;
			    case 3: printf("元整\n");break; 
	    	}
	    	if(s>0&&g>0){
	    	b=s;s=-1;continue;}
	    	if(s==0&&g!=0){
			y++;s=-1;b=g;printf("零");continue;}
		    if(s==0&&g==0){
		    printf("元整\n");y=3;break;} 
		    if(s>0&&g==0){
			b=s;s=0;continue;
		    } 
		    if(s==-1&&g>0){
			b=g;g=-1;continue;
	 	    }
			if(s==-1&&g==-1)break;
	       
        }
    }
    return 0;
}

 	scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c);
 	t=b*b-4*a*c;
 	if(t>=0){
 		x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);

 		printf("%lf~~~%lf",x1,x2);

    {

20190318112:Problem1069:正确
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
	char a,b,c,*x,*y,*z; 
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=&a,y=&b,z=&c;
	if(*x>*y){
		if(*y>*z)printf("%c%c%c\n",*z,*y,*x);
		else{
			if(*z>*x)printf("%c%c%c\n",*y,*x,*z);
			else printf("%c%c%c\n",*y,*z,*x); 
		}
	}
	else{
		if(*y<*z)printf("%c%c%c\n",*x,*y,*z);
		else{
			if(*z<*x)printf("%c%c%c\n",*z,*x,*y);
			else printf("%c%c%c\n",*x,*z,*y);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,s;
	double x1,x2,q; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);{
	s=b*b-4*a*c;
	q=sqrt(s);
	if (s>=0)
	{
		x1=(-b+q)/(2*a);
		x2=(-b-q)/(2*a);
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);		
	}
	else
		printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
	return 0;
	
}

       printf("%s佰元整\n",money[b]);

       printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);

       printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[b],money[d]);

20190318117:Problem1114:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
 	int  month, day;
	scanf("%d,%d", &month, &day); 	
  	int week = 19+ 19 / 4 + 20 / 4 - 20 * 2 + 26 * (month + 1) / 10 + day - 1;
  	week %= 7;
  	switch (week)
  {
  		case 1:printf("Monday\n"); break;
  		case 2:printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
  		case 3:printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
  		case 4:printf("Thursday\n"); break;
  		case 5:printf("Friday\n"); break;
  		case 6:printf("Saturday\n"); break;
  		case 0:printf("Sunday\n"); break;
    }
 return 0;
}

20190318044:Problem1069:答案错误
#include<stdio.h> 
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	int x,y,z,p;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=a;
	y=b;
	z=c;
	p=x+y+z; 
	x=(x>y?x:y)<z?(x>y?x:y):z;
	z=(x>y?x:y)>z?(x>y?x:y):z;
	y=p-x-z;
	printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
}

//求一元二次方程的解
#include"stdio.h"
#include"math.h"
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			x1=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
			printf("%.31f~~~%.31f\n",x1,x2);
		}
		else
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
	}
	
}

#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int g,s,b,x,y=0;
    while(scanf("%d",&x)!=EOF){
	    g=x%10;s=x%100/10;b=x/100;
		    switch (b){
			    case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			    case 0: printf("零"); break;
	     	}
	    	y++;
	    	printf("佰"); 
			if(g==0&&s==0)printf("元整\n");
			else{
	    	switch(s){
			    case 1: printf("壹拾"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰拾"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁拾"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆拾"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍拾"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆拾"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒拾"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌拾"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖拾"); break;
			    case 0: printf("零"); break;
	    	}
				switch(g){
			    case 1: printf("壹"); break;
			    case 2: printf("贰"); break;
			    case 3: printf("叁"); break;
			    case 4: printf("肆"); break;
			    case 5: printf("伍"); break;
			    case 6: printf("陆"); break;
			    case 7: printf("柒"); break;
			    case 8: printf("捌"); break;
			    case 9: printf("玖"); break;
			}
			printf("元整\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

#include"stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,n;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	switch (x) {
		case 1: x=0; break;
		case 2: x=31; break; 
		case 3: x=28+31; break;
		case 4: x=31+28+31; break;
		case 5: x=30+31+28+31; break;
		case 6: x=31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 7: x=30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 8: x=31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 9: x=31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 10: x=30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 11: x=31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break;
		case 12: x=30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+31+28+31; break; 
	}
	n=(x+y)%7;
	switch (n){
		case 0: printf("Monday\n"); break;
		case 1: printf("Tuesday\n"); break;
		case 2: printf("Wednesday\n"); break;
		case 3: printf("Thursday\n"); break;
		case 4: printf("Friday\n"); break;
		case 5: printf("Saturday\n"); break;
		case 6: printf("Sunday\n"); break;
	}
	
 }

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,t;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	if(a>b)
	t=a,a=b,b=t;
	if(b>c)
	t=b,b=c,c=t;
	if(a>c)
	t=a,a=c,c=t;
	if(a>b)
	t=a,a=b,b=t;
	printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
 }

int main()
{
	int a,b,x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=19+19/4+20/4-2*20+(26*(x+1)/10)+y-1;
	b=a%7;
	switch(b){
	
    case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	case 0:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
    return 0;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
        	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
        	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
        	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
        	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
        	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
        	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
        	case(0):
			if(z!=0)
				printf("零");break;break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case(1):printf("壹");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍");break;
        	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖");break;
        }
	    printf("元整\n");
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a[13]={0,31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
	char b[8][20]={"www","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday"};
	int x,y,sum=0;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	for(int i=1;i<x;i++)
	{
		sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;
	sum%=7;
	for(int i=1;i<=7;i++)
	{
		if(sum+1==i)
		printf("%s",b[i]);
	}
	return 0;
}

	{b=a/100;
     c=a%100;

     e=c%10;

       printf("%s佰元整\n",money[b]);
     else if(d==0)
       printf("%s佰%s%s元整\n",money[b],money[d],money[e]);
     else if(e==0)
       printf("%s佰%s拾元整\n",money[b],money[d]);

20190318112:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
void kx(int a)
{

if(a==0)
printf("");
else if(a==1) printf("壹");
else if(a==2) printf("贰");
else if(a==3) printf("叁"); 
else if(a==4) printf("肆");
else if(a==5) printf("伍");
else if(a==6) printf("陆"); 
else if(a==7) printf("柒");
else if(a==8) printf("捌"); 
else if(a==9) printf("玖");
}
main()
{

 double d;
int k,m,n;
while( scanf("%lf" ,&d)!=EOF){
k=(int)d/100;
m=(int)d%100/10;
n=(int)d%100%10;
kx(k);
printf("佰");
kx(m);
if(m!=0){
printf("拾");}
if(n!=0&&m==0){
printf("零");}
kx(n);
printf("元整\n");
}
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,e,d,f;
	double x1,x2,disc1;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		disc1=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(disc1<0) printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	    else
	    {
	    	x1=(-b+sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	x2=(-b-sqrt(disc1))/(2*a);
	    	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	    }
	    
	}

 }

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main() 
{
 	int a,b,c,t;
 	double x1,x2;
 	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
 	t=b*b-4*a*c;
 	if(t>0){
 		x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
 		x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
 		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t==0) {
		x1=-b/(2*a);
		x2=x1;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main() 
{
 	int a,b,c,t;
 	double x1,x2;
 	scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c);
 	t=b*b-4*a*c;
 	if(t>0){
 		x1=(-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a);
 		x2=(-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a);
 		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t==0) {
		x1=-b/(2*a);
		x2=x1;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
return 0;
}

20190318141:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
int main()
{
double a,b,c,x1,x2,p,q,f,g,m,n,i;
scanf("%lf%lf%lf",&a,&b,&c);
p=-b/(2.0*a);
q=sqrt(b*b-4*a*c)/(2*a);
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
{
f=p+q;
g=p-q;
}
if(f>g)x1=f,x2=g;
else x1=g,x2=f;
if(b*b-4*a*c>=0)
printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
else
{
m=-b/(2*a);
n=sqrt(4*a*c-b*b)/(a*2);
printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
}
return 0;
}

main()
{
  int a,b,c,z;
  while(scanf("%d",&z)!=EOF){
  a=z/100;
  b=(z%100)/10;
  c=z%10;
  switch(a){
  case 1:
     printf("壹佰");
     break;
  case 2:
     printf("贰佰");
     break;
  case 3:
     printf("叁佰");
     break;
  case 4:
     printf("肆佰");
     break;
  case 5:
     printf("伍佰");
     break;
  case 6:
     printf("陆佰");
     break;
  case 7:
     printf("柒佰");
     break;
  case 8:
     printf("捌佰");
     break;
  default:
     printf("玖佰");
     break;
  }
  switch(b){
  case 1:
     printf("壹拾");
     break;
  case 2:
     printf("贰拾");
     break;
  case 3:
     printf("叁拾");
     break;
  case 4:
     printf("肆拾");
     break;
  case 5:
     printf("伍拾");
     break;
  case 6:
     printf("陆拾");
     break;
  case 7:
     printf("柒拾");
     break;
  case 8:
     printf("捌拾");
     break;
  case 9:
     printf("玖拾");
     break;
  default:
     if(c!=0){
        printf("零"); 
        switch(c){
        case 1:
           printf("壹");
           break;
        case 2:
           printf("贰");
           break;
        case 3:
           printf("叁");
           break;
        case 4:
           printf("肆");
           break;
        case 5:
           printf("伍");
           break;
        case 6:
           printf("陆");
           break;
        case 7:
           printf("柒");
           break;
        case 8:
           printf("捌");
           break;
        case 9:
           printf("玖");
           break;
        }
  }
  printf("元整\n");
  }
}

20190301020:Problem1059:正确
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    int year;
    scanf("%d", &year);
    if (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0 || year % 400 == 0)
        printf("L");
    else
        printf("N");
    return 0;
}

#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,b,c,d,e,f;
	char*money[10]={"零","壹","贰","叁","肆","伍","陆","柒","捌","玖"};
	f=scanf("%d",&a);
	while(f!=EOF)
	{b=a/100;
     c=a%100;
     d=c/10;
     e=c%10;
     if(c==0)
       printf("%s佰元整",money[b]);
     else if(d==0)
       printf("%s佰%s%s元整",money[b],money[d],money[e]);
     else if(e==0)
       printf("%s佰%s拾元整",money[b],money[d]);
     else
       printf("%s佰%s拾%s元整",money[b],money[d],money[e]); 
	 break;      
	}
}

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(x==1) b=y;
	if(x==2) b=31+y;
	if(x==3) b=31+28+y;
	if(x==4) b=31*2+28+y;
	if(x==5) b=31*2+30+28+y;
	if(x==6) b=31*3+30+28+y;
	if(x==7) b=31*3+30*2+28+y;
	if(x==8) b=31*4+30*2+28+y;
	if(x==9) b=31*5+30*2+28+y;
	if(x==10) b=31*5+30*3+28+y;
	if(x==11) b=31*6+30*3+28+y;
	if(x==12) b=31*6+30*4+28+y;
    a=b%7;
    if(a==3) printf("Friday");
    if(a==4) printf("Saturday");
    if(a==5) printf("Sunday");
    if(a==6) printf("Monday");
    if(a==0) printf("Tuesday");
    if(a==1) printf("Wednesday");
    if(a==2) printf("Thursday");
    return 0;
}

20190301020:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,d;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {d=a;a=b;b=d;}
if (a>c) {d=a;a=c;c=d;}
if (b>c) {d=c;c=b;b=d;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

#include <stdi0.h>
int main()
{
    int x,y,c,s,w;
    scanf("%d%d",&x,&y);
    s=2019;
    if(x==1||x==2)
    {
        s--;
        x+=12;
    }
    c=s/100;
    s=s-c*100;
    w=(c/4)-2*c+(s+s/4)+(13*(x+1)/5)+y-1;
    while (w<0)
    w+=7;
    w%=7;
    switch (w)
    {
        case 1:printf("Monday\n");break;
        case 2:printf("Tuesday\n");break;
        case 3:printf("Wednesday\n");break;
        case 4:printf("Thursday\n");break;
        case 5:printf("Friday\n");break;
        case 6:printf("Saturday\n");break;
        case 7:printf("Sunday\n");break;
    }
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	double a,b,c,d;
	double x1,x2;
	while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
	{
		d=b*b-4*a*c;
		if(d<0){
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
		}
		else{
			x1=(-b+sqrt(d)/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
		}
}
		
		
}

	if((b*b-4*a*c)<0)
	{
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
	else 
	x1=(-b+sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);
	x2=(-b-sqrt(b*b-4*a*c))/(2*a);

20190301047:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	char a,b,c,x;
	while(scanf("%c%c%c\n",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);{
		if(a>b){
			x=a;
			a=b;
			b=x;		
		}
		if(a>c){
			x=a;
			a=c;
			c=x;		
		}		
		if(b>c){
			x=b;
			b=c;
			c=x;		
		}		

		printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
	}
	return 0;	
}

20190301047:Problem1147:答案错误
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,s;
	double x1,x2,q; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);
	{
		s=b*b-4*a*c;
		q=sqrt(s);
		if (s>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b+q)/(2*a);
			x2=(-b-q)/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);		
		}
		else
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;
	
}

#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b,c,s;
	double x1,x2,q; 
	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF);{
		s=b*b-4*a*c;
		if (s>=0){
			x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(s))/(2*a);
			x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(s))/(2*a);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);		
		}
		else
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	}
	return 0;

main()
{

	if (x==1)
        y=y;
    if (x==2)
        y=31+y;
    if (x==3)
        y=31+28+y;
    if (x==4) 
        y=31+28+31+y;
    if (x==5)
        y=31+28+31+30+y;
    if (x==6)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==7)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+y;

        y=31+28+31+30+31+31+31+y;
    if (x==9) 
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y;
    if (x==10)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y;
    if (x==11)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==12)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y;
    n==(y+6)%7;
    if (n==1)
    	printf("Wednesday");
    if (n==2) 
		printf("Thurday");
	if (n==3)
		printf("Friday");
	if (n==4)
		printf("Saturday");
	if (n==5)
	    printf("Sunday");
	if (n==6)
		printf("Monday");

		printf("Tuesday");

20190302003:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>

main()
{
  int a,b,c,z;
  while(scanf("%d",&z)!=EOF){
  a=z/100;
  b=(z%100)/10;
  c=z%10;
  switch(a){
  case 1:
     printf("壹佰");
     break;
  case 2:
     printf("贰佰");
     break;
  case 3:
     printf("叁佰");
     break;
  case 4:
     printf("肆佰");
     break;
  case 5:
     printf("伍佰");
     break;
  case 6:
     printf("陆佰");
     break;
  case 7:
     printf("柒佰");
     break;
  case 8:
     printf("捌佰");
     break;
  default:
     printf("玖佰");
     break;
  }
  switch(b){
  case 1:
     printf("壹拾");
     break;
  case 2:
     printf("贰拾");
     break;
  case 3:
     printf("叁拾");
     break;
  case 4:
     printf("肆拾");
     break;
  case 5:
     printf("伍拾");
     break;
  case 6:
     printf("陆拾");
     break;
  case 7:
     printf("柒拾");
     break;
  case 8:
     printf("捌拾");
     break;
  case 9:
     printf("玖拾");
     break;
  default:
     if(c!=0){
        printf("零");
     }
  } 
  switch(c){
  case 1:
     printf("壹");
     break;
  case 2:
     printf("贰");
     break;
  case 3:
     printf("叁");
     break;
  case 4:
     printf("肆");
     break;
  case 5:
     printf("伍");
     break;
  case 6:
     printf("陆");
     break;
  case 7:
     printf("柒");
     break;
  case 8:
     printf("捌");
     break;
  case 9:
     printf("玖");
     break;

	while(scanf("%d",&d)!=EOF){
	a=d/100;
	b=d/10%10;
	c=d%10;
	switch (a){
        case 1:
            printf ("壹佰");
            break;

            printf ("壹拾");

20190302024:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,t;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {t=a;a=b;b=t;}
if (a>c) {t=a;a=c;c=t;}
if (b>c) {t=c;c=b;b=t;}
printf("%c%c%c\n",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

#include<stdio.h> 
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	int x,y,z,p;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=a;
	y=b;
	z=c;
	p=x+y+z; 
	x=(x<y?x:y)<z?(x<y?x:y):z;
	z=(x>y?x:y)>z?(x>y?x:y):z;
	y=p-x-z;
	printf("%c%c%c",x,y,z);
}

/*求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。
输入:有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
输出:如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
模板 
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int a,b;
	while(scanf("%d %d",&a,&b)!=EOF)
	{
		printf("%d\n",a+b);
	}
	return 0;
}*/
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h> 
int main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2,d1,d2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n%d%d%d",&a1,&b1,&c1,&a2,&b2,&c2)!=EOF)
	{
		d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
		d2=b2*b2-4*a2*c2;
		if(d1<0&&d2<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\nNO SOLUTION");
		}
		if(d1<0&&d2>=0)
		{
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
		if(d1>=0&&d2<0)
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		if(d1>=0&&d2>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

/*求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。
输入:有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
输出:如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
模板*/
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h> 
int main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2,d1,d2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n%d%d%d",&a1,&b1,&c1,&a2,&b2,&c2)!=EOF)
	{
		d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
		d2=b2*b2-4*a2*c2;
		if(d1<0&&d2<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\nNO SOLUTION");
		}
		if(d1<0&&d2>=0)
		{
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
		if(d1>=0&&d2<0)
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		if(d1>=0&&d2>=0)
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190301040:Problem1147:答案错误
/*求一元二次方程ax2+bx+c=0的解。a,b,c为整数。解为double。
输入:有多组测试数据，每行三个整数代表a,b,c的值 ，用空格隔开。
输出:如果没有实根则输出：NO SOLUTION 
如果有解则输出2个解，小数点后面保留3位。2个根输出时加delta的平方根在前，减在后，2个解中间用3个~隔开。 
模板*/
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h> 
int main()
{
	int a1,b1,c1,a2,b2,c2,d1,d2;
	double x1,x2,x3,x4;
	while(scanf("%d%d%d\n%d%d%d",&a1,&b1,&c1,&a2,&b2,&c2)!=EOF)
	{
		d1=b1*b1-4*a1*c1;
		d2=b2*b2-4*a2*c2;
		if(d1<0&&d2<0)
		{
			printf("NO SOLUTION\nNO SOLUTION");
		}
		if(d1<0&&d2>=0)
		{
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
		if(d1>=0&&d2<0)
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("NO SOLUTION");
		}
		else
		{
			x1=(-b1+sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x2=(-b1-sqrt(d1))/(2*a1);
			x3=(-b2+sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			x4=(-b2-sqrt(d2))/(2*a2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
			printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x3,x4);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}

20190318044:Problem1069:正确
#include<stdio.h> 
main()
{
	char a,b,c;
	int x,y,z,p,max,min;
	scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
	x=a;
	y=b;
	z=c;
	p=x+y+z; 
	min=(x<y?x:y)<z?(x<y?x:y):z;
	max=(x>y?x:y)>z?(x>y?x:y):z;
	y=p-min-max;
	printf("%c%c%c",min,y,max);
}

20190301047:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
int main()
{   int a,b,c,delta;
    double x1,x2;
   while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF)
    {delta=b*b-4*a*c;
       if(delta>=0)
      {x1=((-1)*b+sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       x2=((-1)*b-sqrt(delta))/(2.0*a);
       printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
      } 
      else
      {printf("NO SOLUTION\n");}
    }
    return 0;
}

#include<math.h>
main() 
{
 	int x,y,sum=0;
 	int a[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
 	char *b[]= {"Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday","Monday"};
 	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
 	for(int i=1;i<x;i++){
 		sum+=a[i];
	}
	sum+=y;
	sum%=7;
	printf("%s",b[(sum-1)%7]);

  if(z>=0){
     x1=((-1*b)+sqrt(z))/(2*a);
     x2=((-1*b)-sqrt(z))/(2*a);
     printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf",x1,x2);

     printf("NO SOLUTION");

        	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;

	        case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	        case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	        case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	        case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	        case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	        case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	        case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	        case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
        	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
        	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
        	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
        	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
        	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
        	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
        	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
        	case 0:printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case 1:printf("壹");break;
        	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	        case 3:printf("叁");break;
	        case 4:printf("肆");break;

	        case 7:printf("柒");break;

	        case 9:printf("玖");break;
        }

20190302003:Problem1147:正确
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
  int a,b,c;
  double z,x1,x2;
  while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
  z=b*b-a*c*4;
  if(z>=0){
     x1=((-1*b)+sqrt(z))/(2*a);
     x2=((-1*b)-sqrt(z))/(2*a);
     printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
  }else{
     printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
  }
 } 
}

	for(b=1;b<=x;b++)
	c=c+a[b];

	e=d%7;

#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a%100)/10%10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case 1:printf("壹佰");break;
        	case 2:printf("贰佰");break;
	        case 3:printf("叁佰");break;
	        case 4:printf("肆佰");break;
	        case 5:printf("伍佰");break;
	        case 6:printf("陆佰");break;
	        case 7:printf("柒佰");break;
	        case 8:printf("捌佰");break;
	        case 9:printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case 1:printf("壹拾");break;
	        case 2:printf("贰拾");break;
        	case 3:printf("叁拾");break;
        	case 4:printf("肆拾");break;
        	case 5:printf("伍拾");break;
        	case 6:printf("陆拾");break;
        	case 7:printf("柒拾");break;
        	case 8:printf("捌拾");break;
        	case 9:printf("玖拾");break;
        	case 0:
        	if(z==0){
        	    printf("");
        	}else
        	printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case 1:printf("壹");break;
        	case 2:printf("贰");break;
	        case 3:printf("叁");break;
	        case 4:printf("肆");break;
	        case 5:printf("伍");break;

	d=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(d<0)
	printf("NO SOLUTION");
	else
	{
		x1=(-b+sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	    x2=(-b-sqrt(d))/(2*a);
	    printf("x1 = %.3f~~~x2 = %.3f",x1,x2);
	}

#include "stdio.h"
main(int argc,char *argv[])
{
	int x,y;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	char z[7][10]={"Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday","Sunday","Monday"};
	if (x==1)
        y=y;
    if (x==2)
        y=31+y;
    if (x==3)
        y=31+28+y;
    if (x==4) 
        y=31+28+31+y;
    if (x==5)
        y=31+28+31+30+y;
    if (x==6)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==7)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+y;
    if (x==8)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==9) 
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+y;
    if (x==10)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+y;
    if (x==11)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+y;
    if (x==12)
        y=31+28+31+30+31+30+31+31+30+31+30+y;
    printf("%s",z[(y+6)%7]);
}
