20190301043:Problem1147:答案错误
#include <stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main() 
{
 	int a,b,c,t;
 	double x1,x2;
 	while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
	 ;
 	t=b*b-4*a*c;
 	if(t>0){
 		x1=((-b+sqrt(t))/(2*a));
 		x2=((-b-sqrt(t))/(2*a));
 		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	if(t==0) {
		x1=-b/(2*a);
		x2=x1;
		printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",x1,x2);
	}
	else{
		printf("NO SOLUTION");
	}
	}
return 0;
}

#include "stdio.h"
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,w,t;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	if(0<x<13,0<y<32)
	{
		x=x-1;
		a=30*(x);
		b=a+y;
		w=b-1;
		t=w%7;
		if(x==1){w=w+1,t=w%7,printf("%d",t);}
		else if(x==3){w=w-1,t=w%7,printf("%d",t);}
		else if(x==8){w=w+2,t=w%7,printf("%d",t);}
		else if(x==10){w=w+3,t=w%7,printf("%d",t);}
		else if(x==12){w=w+4,t=w%7,printf("%d",t);}
		else if(t==6)
		{
			printf("Monday");
		}
		else if(t==0)
		{
			printf("Tuesday");
		}
		else if(t==1)
		{
			printf("Wednesday");
		}
		else if (t==2)
		{
			printf("Thursday");
		}
		else if (t==3)
		{
			printf("Friday");
		}
		else if(t==4)
		{
			printf("Saturday");
		}
		else if(t==5)
		{
			printf("Sunday");	
		}
	}
	return 0; 
}

20190301047:Problem1114:运行错误
#include "stdio.h"

int main()
{
	int i,d,m,n,x,a[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};	
	scanf("%d,%d",&d,m);
	while (i<m)
		n=n+a[i];
	n=n+d;
	x=n%7;
	if (x==1)
		printf("Monday");
	if (x==2)
		printf("Tuesday");
	if (x==3)
		printf("Wednesday");
    if (x==4)
		printf("Thursday");
	if (x==5)
		printf("Friday");
	if (x==6)
		printf("Saturday");
	if (x==0)
		printf("Sunday");
	return 0;
}

20190302032:Problem1069:编译错误
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char a,b,c,change;
scanf("%c%c%c",&a,&b,&c);
if (a>b) {change=a;a=b;b=change;}
if (a>c) {change=a;a=c;c=change;}
if (b>c) {chane=c;c=b;b=change;}
printf("%c%c%c",a,b,c);
return 0;
}

20190302026:Problem1147:答案错误
//求一元二次方程的解
#include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
main()
{
    int a,b,c;
    double disc;
    double x1,x2;
    while(scanf("%d %d %d",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF){
        disc=b*b-4*a*c;
        if(disc<0){
            printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
        }
        else{
        	x1=((-1*b)+sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
        	x2=((-1*b)-sqrt(disc))/(2*a);
        	printf("X.3lf~ ~%. 3lf\n" ,x1,x2);
		}

    }

}

	scanf("%d,%d",&d,m);
	while (i<m){
		n=n+a[i];
		i=i+1;	
	}
	x=(n+d+2)%7;
	if (x==1)
		printf("Monday");
	if (x==2)
		printf("Tuesday");

		printf("Wednesday");
    if (x==4)
		printf("Thursday");

		printf("Friday");

{

	B=getchar();
	C=getchar();
	if(A>B>C)
	{
		printf("%C%C%C",A,B,C);
    }
    else if(A>C>B)
	{
		printf("%C%C%C",A,C,B);
    }
	else if(B>A>C)
	{
		printf("%c%c%c",B,A,C);
	}
		else if(B>C>A)
	{
		printf("%c%c%c",B,C,A);
    }
	else if(C>A>B)
	{
	    printf("%c%c%c",C>A>B);
    }
	else
	{
	    printf("%c%c%c",C>B>A);	
	}

20190318044:Problem1114:正确
#include <stdio.h>
main()
{
	int x,y,a,b,c,d;
	scanf("%d,%d",&x,&y);
	a=x-1;
	switch (a)
	{
	case 0:b=y-1;break;
	case 1:b=y-1+31;break;
	case 2:b=y-1+59;break;
	case 3:b=y-1+90;break;
	case 4:b=y-1+120;break;
	case 5:b=y-1+151;break;
	case 6:b=y-1+181;break;
	case 7:b=y-1+212;break;
	case 8:b=y-1+243;break;
	case 9:b=y-1+273;break;
	case 10:b=y-1+304;break;
	case 11:b=y-1+334;break;
	}
	c=b%7;//b为日期差
    if(b>=7)
	d=2+c;
    else 
	d=2+b;
    if(d>7) 
	d=d-7;
    else 
	d=d;
    switch(d)
	{
	case 1:printf("Monday");break;
	case 2:printf("Tuesday");break;
	case 3:printf("Wednesday");break;
	case 4:printf("Thursday");break;
	case 5:printf("Friday");break;
	case 6:printf("Saturday");break;
	case 7:printf("Sunday");break;
	}
}

20190318158:Problem1158:正确
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int h,r,w,x;
	
	while(scanf("%d",&h)!=EOF)
{   
    if(h>=100&&h<=999)
{
	r=h/100;
	w=(h%100)/10;
	x=h%10;
	switch(r)
{
	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	switch(w)
{
	case(1):printf("壹拾");break;
	case(2):printf("贰拾");break;
	case(3):printf("叁拾");break;
	case(4):printf("肆拾");break;
	case(5):printf("伍拾");break;
	case(6):printf("陆拾");break;
	case(7):printf("柒拾");break;
	case(8):printf("捌拾");break;
	case(9):printf("玖拾");break;
	default:printf("");
}
    if((h%100)!=0&&(h%10)!=0&&w==0)
{
printf("零");
}
	switch(x)
{
	case(1):printf("壹");break;
	case(2):printf("贰");break;
	case(3):printf("叁");break;
	case(4):printf("肆");break;
	case(5):printf("伍");break;
	case(6):printf("陆");break;
	case(7):printf("柒");break;
	case(8):printf("捌");break;
	case(9):printf("玖");break;
	default:printf("");
}
	printf("元整\n");}}
}

20190318044:Problem1147:正确
#include <stdio.h>
#include <math.h>
main()
{
	double a,b,c,x,D,m;
    while(scanf("%lf %lf %lf",&a,&b,&c)!=EOF) 
	{
	a*x*x+b*x+c==0;
	D=b*b-4*a*c;
	if(D>=0)
	{
	m=sqrt(D);
	printf("%.3lf~~~%.3lf\n",(-b+m)/(2*a),(-b-m)/(2*a));
	}
	else 
	printf("NO SOLUTION\n");
	};
}

main()
{
	int a,x,y,z;
	while(scanf("%d",&a)!=EOF)
    {
	    x=a/100;
	    y=(a/100)%10;
	    z=a%10;
	    switch(x)
        {
        	case(1):printf("壹佰");break;
        	case(2):printf("贰佰");break;
	        case(3):printf("叁佰");break;
	        case(4):printf("肆佰");break;
	        case(5):printf("伍佰");break;
	        case(6):printf("陆佰");break;
	        case(7):printf("柒佰");break;
	        case(8):printf("捌佰");break;
	        case(9):printf("玖佰");break;
        }
	    switch(y)
        {
	        case (1):printf("壹拾");break;
	        case (2):printf("贰拾");break;
        	case (3):printf("叁拾");break;
        	case (4):printf("肆拾");break;
        	case (5):printf("伍拾");break;
        	case (6):printf("陆拾");break;
        	case (7):printf("柒拾");break;
        	case (8):printf("捌拾");break;
        	case (9):printf("玖拾");break;
        	case (0):printf("零");break; 
        }
	    switch(z)
        {
	        case (1):printf("壹");break;
        	case (2):printf("贰");break;
	        case (3):printf("叁");break;
	        case (4):printf("肆");break;
	        case (5):printf("伍");break;
        	case (6):printf("陆");break;
	        case (7):printf("柒");break;
	        case (8):printf("捌");break;
	        case (9):printf("玖");break;
        }
	    printf("元整\n");
    }
